40001001	Naajri papera bidjapinrg jajaa naa Jesucristo. David jriwaira naa Jesús, oyatjri Abraam jriwaira naa David.
40001002	Abraam trrira naa Isaac, oyat Isaac trrira naa Jacob, oyat Jacob trrira naa Judá otpoi oyem nat Judá pedwat.
40001003	Judá trrira naa Fares, Zara poi oyem ja-u Tamar-shrt. Fares trrira naa Esron. Esron trrira naa Aram.
40001004	Áram trrira naa Aminadab. Aminadab trrira naa Naasón. Naasón trrira naa Salmón.
40001005	Salmón trrira naa Booz ja-u Raab-shrt. Booz trrira naa Obed ja-u Rut-shrt. Obed trrira Isaí.
40001006	Isaí trrira naa cajriwairüg David. Oyat David trrira naa Salamón jayrg wryu jaluugjee Uriajit ujin-shrt.
40001007	Salomón trrira naa Roboam. Roboam trrira Abías. Abras trrira Asa.
40001008	Asa trrira Josafat. Josafat trrira Joram. Joram trrira Uzías.
40001009	Uzías trrira Jotam. Jotam trrira Acaz. Acaz trrira Ezequías.
40001010	Ezequías trrira Manasés. Manasés trrira Amon. Amon trrira Josías.
40001011	Oyat Josías trrira Jeconías japedwat poi cabalolat carrnogbat Babilonia-teja.
40001012	Oyat cauprt quedyem Babilonia-teat, Jeconías trrira naa Salatiel. Salatiel trrira ZorobobeL
40001013	Zorobobel trrira Abiud. Abiud trrira Eliaquim. Eliaquim trrira Azor.
40001014	Oyat Azor trrira Sadoc. Sadoc trrira Aquim. Aquim trrira Eliud.
40001015	Eliud trrira Eleazar. Eleazar trrira Matán. Matan trrira Jacob.
40001016	Jacob trrira José, jabón naa María. Oyatjri oo-shrta jayrg wryu jaluugjee naa Jesúat, naa oodcamooli Cristo, Dioat icuiprn nani.
40001017	Catorce generación catoglig catrriot Abraam prnot jajuprtuju jaminyrglig naa David. Oyat catorce generación catoglig catrriot David prnot jajuprduju cabalolat carrnoglig Babilonia-teja nat Israelot. Oyat catorce generación catoglig catrriot shri cauprt quedyem Babilonia-teat jajuprduju jayuglig Cristo nani wryu-tee.
40001018	Ojerira jayrglig naa Jesucristo wryu jaluugjee. Bŕnju naa Joséat jainnbadi naa Jesús iin María, jatrririg Espíritu Santo-jet jajuprtuliju cacaouglig.
40001019	Ijeira jabigshayu naa José, ooshrmda jadshanjewi epinolat jainot juirig iebjet naa María. Ooshrmda jadnamnogshug jaanajet epinot-shrt.
40001020	Oyat Joséat jabigshagbat jadirgshirig jashrt, Biŕri ángele shog jamauye jayrca. Jamog jan, mam José David jriwai, macupoiom jarnaouglig ma-uja naa María. Espíritu Santola jalirr naa trriwai irig janamdee.
40001021	Jadshiwaoyawi naa jaWá, oyatjri jatam mauminrgya Jesús, ooshrmya cadjashijeicon jaepinot ebupaacacrt-shrtya jashrm naa ieb idminrg, canogjeeya paraiso-teja.
40001022	Biŕrira jalirrwi oje jabigye minog naa oodjamogli bŕn itrm jaipinjunndi.
40001023	Ojeri jamog, jatrri shirigya naa bon-jet ishanduquiju, jadshiwaoya naa jaWá, jatam cashiminrgya Imanuel. Ojaliyula jatam, Diolawi bijet.
40001024	Oyatjri José jeunocadu jayrgrririg quedyem. Oowi jajuimiragyrg jadrninrgjee oje Biŕri ángele mojani jan. Jad-ougjee ja-uja naa María,
40001025	ooshrt jashanjulut jajet naa ja-u jajuprduju jadwaolig naa jatrri-jurg. Oyat Joséat jatam minrg Jesús.
40002001	Jesús yigli wryu jaluugjee Belén Judea-tee cajriwairüca jaligbadi Heredes. Oyat mot bicacouot minnog Jerusalén-teja, nat Oriente atwinot.
40002002	Ojera camog, brrn jalii naa jujet-iminyrg Judioot jriwairüg. Bŕn jabirau jacrt Oriente-teat, ooshrmda biyug ijei bibrgjee jan.
40002003	Cainot jajuibat naa judioot jriwairüg Herodes, oowi jabigjashaglicat jijogjet, otpoi-oyem nat Jerusalén tepinot wrijn .
40002004	Oyatjri Herodeat caáglig jalica wrijin nat Unodigot sacerdoteot, natpoi oyem inaat. Cadcarm brrn-jaligu jashiminyig naa Dioat icuiprn jeicatei.
40002005	Oyatjri camog jan, jashiminyrgya wryu jaluugjee jatee naa moyan Belén Judea-tee ojewi idnaalauniri japapera-tee naa Dios yerog shipinidi bŕn.
40002006	Ojeri jamog, mam moyan Belén Judea-tee, uubiidprnjin shandita mam cashrt nat brrt moyanot Judea-tee, ooshrm jashiyrgya ma-tee itrm Iinodig caijajeujeeya aepinot Israelot.
40002007	Oyat Herodeat caág jalica jaanajet nat bicacouot Oriente atwinot, cadcarm brlau jaliguli ebushijayrg-jurg nat crt Oriente-tee.
40002008	Oyatjri cadjacuinoglig Belén-teja nat Oriente atwinot jamog calat, yaunimnog jajan jayajeujee naa trriwai. Oyatjri jayaluuguya naa trriwai, yauyugya nani ayapinrgjeeya am, anogjeeya poi jalica, ijei abrgjeeya jan amat poi.
40002009	Jayerog cajui quedyem Herodes, oowi canoglig calrg-uye Belénteja nat Oriente atwinot. Oyatjri naa ert idduugprn Oriente-teja janog cajuprta caminogjee jalica naa trriwai, oyatjri jajoolrg crt Jesús jushryé.
40002010	Jadduugbat naa crt cajii-jái nat Oriente atwinot.
40002011	Oowi caluuglig mooleja jadduug naa trriwai jaiin María-jet, oowi cashoglig cautjuiyag-jet jan, ijeí cabrgjee jan. Oyat jajuicayiglig caebu ot, oro cabrgjee jan, incenso poi, pomada ishicoi poi jatam mirra.
40002012	Oyatjri Dioat capinrg cayrgrri-tee cauprt-shrt shri Herode-lica, ooshrmda cauprt caniti-teja boi drg-uye.
40002013	Oyat cauprt quedyem nat bicacouot Oriente atwinot Biŕri ángele shog José cooye jayrgwi-tee. Jamog jan, majuicumig jamarenogjee naa trriwai jaiin-jet macuutjee Egipto-teja, maligjeeyaju jajan ata-on maágcaya shri, ooshrm Herodeat jashijeuya jadrrirgjee naa trriwai.
40002014	Oyatjri José juimig shaireiju jadrmogjee naa trriwai Jesús Egipto-teja jaiin-jet.
40002015	Oyatjri calig jajan prnpatjet ata-on jarria Herodes, jabigye minogli naa Biŕriat oodmogprndi jacooleat naa jaipin jurmdi. Ojeri jamog, jashiágya aWá Egipto-teat.
40002016	Oyatjri janrm naa Herodes jayerog cashanjui-shrm nat bicacouot Oriente atwinolat, cawug-shrm boi drg-uye jashrt. Oyat Herodeat sodawaot cui cadcarrirgjee wrijin taacrlot mot-trriot Belén-tee, jamaupinot poi, nat cau wüg iriinogot ishrmnooligot poi ojewi crt iinot jajuirauni jadduugli nat Oriente atwinolat.
40002017	Jadminrg ojewi jamojaniri bŕn naa profeta Jeremías,
40002018	Ojeri jamog, jaiquedrgla jaijuirig cawrr-áglig nat jii-shrmot Rama-tee, caguiglig jijogjet. Naa Raquel quiglig jatrriot-shrm, jadshanjeu jajajáirglig carri-shrm jashrt jatrriot.
40002019	Oyatjri jarri quedyem Herodes, oowi itrm ángele shoolig José cooye jayrca Egipto-tee.
40002020	Jamog jan, majuicumig marmogjee naa trriwai Israel-teja jaiin-jet. Bŕn carri nat jajewetdi jadrrirglig.
40002021	Oowi José juimiglig jadrmogjee naa trriwai Israel nitija jaiin-jet.
40002022	Oyat Joséat jainot juibat cajriwairüca jaliglig Aquelau Judea-tee jaiijin Herodes prnu, jaom janoglig on. Ooshrmda janog Galilea-teja ojewi Dios mojani jan jayrguwi-tee.
40002023	Oyatjri jaminucadu Galilea-teja, jalig Nazaret mojan-tee ojewi camojaniri nat Dios yerog shipinidi bŕn. Ojeri camog, Nazarenatwin cashimogya jajaa.
40003001	Oyat Juan Bautistaat cajuirrbog yee-uja Judea-tee.
40003002	Jamog nat epinolat, yabigshayu yaucambiarg, jii-shŕmjet jayeyawaag naa ieb iyarninrg, ooshrm janacawiat jabigye jayugjee naa Shrnoatwin iwairüg cajuijabergjeeya nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee.
40003003	Naa Juan oolawi naa-jaa Isaíaat iipinprndi bŕn japapera-tee. Ojeri jamog, ja-noot cashijuiya itrm iágbog yee-uja Birri jrirü jajeiconjee. Yabigshayu yaushalarg jabatyataijeeya, jamog.
40003004	Oyat naa Juan, carneyo jaashuta jayuiot, cameyo pigla jawrr. Crruota idjawougot, aabot pun-tepinot poi.
40003005	Cayug Juan-lica nat Jerusalén tepinot, wrijín Judea tepinot poi, rt Jordán coopinot poi.
40003006	Oyatjri jaicapin quedyem naa ieb idminrglig, Juanat bautisao carg rt Jordan-tee.
40003007	Oyatjri ibagjet Juanat caluug cayuglig jalica bautisao cadjargjee, nat fariseoot saduseoot poi. Jamog calat, yam shrrbot, brr yacuiyu yacuutjee jashrt naa payashicrtya jijogjet yanarr yam yaebyu-shrm.
40003008	Dumatjri ijei yauminrgya japishibiwaagjee yabigshayu yacambiarglig, japishibiwaagjee jii-shrmjet jayeyawaaglig naa ieb iyaminrg.
40003009	Yacupoimot bijeiata bidu Abraam jrdwata birig-shrm. Dumat yashipinrg, Dioat jacajeuu cadjacambiarglig nat jamolugot Abraam jrdwata cadjacug quedrg-om.
40003010	Dumatjri Dioat jajrr peglircat cayawaná nat pun tatchulot, oyatjri cajashieiya wrijin nat puulot cam shanjeinríot. Cadjashipanya cadjanamjee drrbica.
40003011	Amjri bautisao yarg rt-jet yayatadrgjee yabigshayu yacambiarglicat yaebyu-shrt. Ooshrtjri naa ishiyugya aprnat yalica, ooya bautisao yadshirm Espíritu Santo-jet drr-jetya poi. Oolawi inomjri wairüg ashrt. Ijei shandit am jacugshitjinu jasapatoot jashiim-shrt.
40003012	Jalap dig jet-cadjatouyawan cadjawawugjeeya jajrmcabigot-shrt nat cayagotjin, cajuijabergjeeya jaot-teja wrijin jajrmcabigot. Oyatjri cadjashitaiya nat cayagotjin drr ishantrmi-teja.
40003013	Oyat Jesús yug Galilea-teat Juan-lica rt Jordán cooja, bautisao jadrgjee.
40003014	Oyatjri yau Juanat jeuliprn bautisao jadrglig. Jamog Jesúat, anwi mashirm mam bautisao amargjee. Boirigshrmjam amarm am bautisao margjee.
40003015	Oyatjri Jesús mog jan, dumat jamauminrg oje amojani man. Biradwi jabishiminr oje Dioat jajeulauni. Oyat Juanat bautisao jarg.
40003016	Oyatjri Juanat bautisao jarg quedyem Jesús, jajuimig rt-teat. Oyat Paraíso juijiinog, oyat Jesúat Dios Espíritu luug jawondig jalica oje iitibrm wondauni.
40003017	Oyat boi moyerog cajui shrnoat, oola aWá naa, oola ijeuprn jii-jáijeta jaluu, jamog.
40004001	Oyatjri Espírituat jarrnog Jesús moyan-rría,oyatjri moweijinat jajeu jateejashaurglig jajan.
40004002	Oyatjri yau jayewairiprn Jesús cuarenta jatog wryu, shai poi oyem, jabuushig.
40004003	Oyat jayug Jesús-lica naa moteeshaur, jamog jan, Dios Wá jaligu mam jamaucambiarg nat jaamolugot ana.
40004004	Oyatjri Jesús mog jan, ojera jamo naa moyerog idnagprndi, an catrmjet shanditya cashijuu nat epinot, ooshrt cashirigya wrijin-jaa naa moyerog Dioat oodmog.
40004005	Oyatjri moweijinat jashri-rmog moyan Jerusalén-teja templo jupucá ishrn-jaa.
40004006	Jamog jan, maulrrjog náyat niti-uja, ooshrm ojera jamog naa idnagprn papera-tee, Dioat jaángeleot shicuiya maicajeujee, madwaorgjeeya calap-jet, mashim marrirg-shrt jáa-jaa.
40004007	Oyat Jesús mog naa moweijinat, bŕn canagli papera-tee, imacupoiminrtya oje bicashancowiprnjini jamaluugjee-cugjin marri Dios bigshayu.
40004008	Oyatjri moweijinat jashri-rrnog itrm wen ishrn-jaa, jadtadrg wrijin moyan shuwai-jet wryu-tee, wrijin mowoo ijeinogot poi.
40004009	Oyat moweijin mog jan, jashibrgya man wrijin naa jet-matadrg mashoobrgu an mautjuiyag-jet ijeí mabrgjeeya an.
40004010	Oyatjri Jesús mog jan, maunog ashrt mam moweijin, ooshrm ojera jamog naa idnagprndi, mamdawi ijei mashibr Marri Dioat, mamdawi imashibeebr jan itrmatwi brrt-shrt.
40004011	Oyat moweijin uprt Jesús-shrt, oyatjri ángeleot yug jalica cajrrja jadrgjee.
40004012	Oyat Jesúat Juan iinot juibat jadrrnoglig presoja moliiriprnteja, jauprt Galilea-teja.
40004013	Yau Jesús liiriprn Nazaret-tee, ooshrtjri janog jaligjee Capernaurn-teja, naa moyan rt ipeg-coo irig inagjetwi jashrt naa niti Zabulón Neftalí poi.
40004014	Jesúat iminrg oje idnaalauniri papera-tee jajaa naa Dios yerog shipini jatam Isaías
40004015	Ojeri jamog, naa niti Zabulón Neftalí poi, rt ipeg maupinot, rt Jordán yabata Galilea-tee, judioot niti shandid.
40004016	Nat epinot irigot ibrru-tee, boi caluug itrm Ebushiwiyu jijog. Oyat naa Ebushiwryu idyrg cajaa ijeijet nat iomotdi morriyu-shrt.
40004017	Oyat Jesúat juiwrgbat cadjajuirgwrglig, jamog calat, yabigshayu yaucambiarg. Jayeyawaag ishrmjet naa ieb iyaminrgprn ooshrm jabigye minocat naa Shmojawin iwairüg cajuijabergjeeya nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjeeya.
40004018	Oyatjri Jesús boolrgbat rt Galilea-coo, cadjaluug icauot mot, naa Simón Pedro, oopoi japeiwai Andrés. Cayou canam rt-teja ooshrm ishigbogota calig.
40004019	Oyat Jesús mo calat, yauyucat aprna, yajuirgjee cayashigbogjee epinot moweijin-shrt.
40004020	Oowi cayou canamnoglig canogjee Jesús prna.
40004021	Oyat Jesús shri-nog iyawaligjet, cashri cau-mot idjaluugot, nat Zebedeo trriot Jacobo, japewai Juan poi. Categ já-tee caii Zebedeo-jet, cajoula idjeicon. Oyatjri Jesúat caág jalica.
40004022	Oyat oowiat ca-já canamnoglig caii poi canogjee Jesús prna.
40004023	Oyat Jesús nog Galilea-teja cadjajuirgjee wrijin sinagoga-tee cayan tojani. Jaijapin calat naa moyerog ijei brjaliguya Dioat cajuiberg-shirig nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee. Oyat Jesúat cajeicon ibagot epinot, ishiyu janam cashrt wrijin.
40004024	Oyat Jesús iinot minog calica nat Siria tepinot wrijin, ooshrm cacarrnog jalica nat iebot, itabot poi, otpoi nat demoniolat ijiiprnot, iyurnprnotjin poi, otpoi taale rryugprnotjin. Oyatjri Jesúat cajeicon wrijin.
40004025	Oyat cayug Jesús prna ibagot Galilea atwinot, Decápolis atwinot poi, Jerusalén atwinot poi, Judea atwinot poi, otpoi oyem nat rt-Jordan yabatawinot.
40005001	Jesúat caluugbat nat ibagot epinot, oowi jajondig wen-jaa. Oyat jaligbatju jajan, cayug jalica nat idjajuirgprnot.
40005002	Oyat Jesúat juiwrg cadjajuirgjee.
40005003	Jii-jáiota nat cabigshanshaiot caalei bigshayu-jaatep, ooshrm jashiribrgya calat caliiriprn caijajeuliprn-tee naa Shmojawin iwairüg.
40005004	Jii-jáiota nat iquigot, ooshrm Dioya cajii jáirr.
40005005	Jii-jáiota nat pinshiirot, ooshrm jashiribrgya calat naa wryu Dioat oodmog birat.
40005006	Jii-jáiota nat Dios bigshayu jewet oje mojii jrrolauni, ooshrm Dioya cajuishituunr jabigshayu ijeijet.
40005007	Jii-jáiota nat brrt uubiidujut, ooshrm uubiidjetya Dioya cashiruu.
40005008	Jii-jáiota nat bigshayu jaapi-rriot, ooshrm Dios cashiruugya.
40005009	Jii-jáiota nat jalirt cayii caluugjee nat cabata carg, ooshrmya Dios trriot bishimog cajaa.
40005010	Jii-jáiota nat ebupaacrlot ijei iminrgu-shrm, ooshrm jashiribrgya calat caliiriprn caijajeuliprn-tee naa Shmojawin iwairüg.
40005011	Jii-jáiota yam cayaadu iebjet yajaa ashrm, ieb carninrgu poi ashrm, cateeshauu poi yajaa yajii-cujáiya yam.
40005012	Yayau jairgya, jayauluugyegya ijeijet yam ebupaacrlot ashrm, ooshrm jashiribrgya yan ijei ipegjet shrnoja. Ooshrm ojerira poi cabata cadcarglig nat yajuprtawinot ayerog juirtdi.
40005013	Yamdawi naa wryu shayu. Yau-jaligu shayuat jadquedrliprn jadshutrglig naa mowoug, brwrnjam jaiquedrgli jaijeiconjee naa mowoug. Ojatepdigu naa shayu, oowi jainamdig jadtadyegjee cashim-jet nat epinolat.
40005014	Yamdawi nat wryushiwtyuot. Yau jaiquedrliprn jaijaanu naa moyan irig wen-jaa.
40005015	Yau juitairiprn Iampara jaijaanjee caja nomat, ooshrt jairirg shrnoye jategot-jaye caijayrgjee ijeijet wrijin moleipinot.
40005016	Ojera poi yam, jayaulirg yaiwryuat iyrglig cajaa nat epinot jajet naa ijei iyarninrg, ijei cabrgjeeya Bii-Dioat naa shrnoja iricat.
40005017	Jayacupoishaat ayuglig janamjee yashrt Moisés yerog, cayerog poi nat Dios yerog shipinidi brn. Ashanyuut janamjee naa idnagprndi papera-uu, ooshrtjri ayug jaminrgjee oje camojaniri ajaa bŕnju.
40005018	Rjeta oodamo yan, caligbatju nat shrnoja iruugot, naa wryu poi, yauya itrm letra boishirmdrliprn jashrt naa jricanagprndi bŕn ajaa jajuprduju jaminrglig naa-jaa jricanagli papera-tee.
40005019	Ooshrmya naa jayerog-shanwaorri wrijin naa Dioat irirgprndi jayerog biwaorgjee, naa brrt shanjuirri Dios yerog cawaorgjee, shŕmjetya-yaiwi japishicashiwaa cajuiberliprn-tee naa Shmojawin iwairüg. Ooshrtjri naa ayerog-waorr wrijin, cadjuirg poi brrt ayerog cawaorgjee, japishicashiwaagya ijeiya-jaliglig cajuicaberliprn-tee naa Shmojawin iwairüg.
40005020	Yapinrg, yabigyashanshatu ijeijet cashrt nat ijuirt, fariseoot poi. yauya yashiruuliprn cajet nat juibergot jajet nat shrnojawin iwairüg.
40005021	Yandawi jayashijui brjaliyuli camog judioot doomotjin, epin macupoirrirt. Dioya jainot shipini ebupaajacrtjee naa epin-rrirr.
40005022	Ooshrt amog yan, Dioya jainot shipini ebupaajacrtjee naa iebjet jajrr-luju. Oyat naa moyerog iebprnjin iipini jajrrat, jainot shicashipinya nat iinodigolat inomjri wairüligot yashrt. Oyatjri naa, iigprnjinda mam, imog jajrrat, janwi jadshiruu jashrt brjashirii janogu infierno drr-teja.
40005023	Ooshrmya ofrenda marrnogbat Dioat, mabigmashagbat majrrjaa iebjet maluuju,
40005024	jamajeicon-jurg majet naa iebjet maluuju, oyatya jamashiquedr jamabrrlig ofrenda Dioat.
40005025	Itrmat marrnogu iwairüglica mainot shijapinjee jamaujeicon majet manogbatya jajan brjashirii iinodicat mabrgu polisiaolat madnamjee presoja liiriprn-teja.
40005026	Rjeta naa oodamog man, yauya madshishiuliprn jajuprduju jamii mabrglig wrijin jamii marriryu.
40005027	Yarndawi jajuiyut brjaligu camog bŕn, macupoiruut itrm denjet ma-u shrt. Macupoi-ruut itrm bon-jet mabon-shrt.
40005028	Ooshrt yashipinrg, iwoojeuprnjinda naa inai boi den-jet ja-u shrt, ooshrm ieb jaminocat jajet jabigshayu-jet.
40005029	Itrmbat mabicat jalirgu ieb maminrgli, jamau-oug mashrt jamanamjee. Jajeira jarmdrgu mashrt itrmbat mabig, madnam-shrt wrijin mataale-jet infierno-teja.
40005030	Jamajeuu ieb maminrglig itrmbat malap-jet, jamaupan jamanamjee mashrt. Jajeira jarmdrgu mashrt itrmbat malap madnamshrt wrijin mataale-jet infierno-teja.
40005031	Ojera poi camooli bŕn, naa ja-u namnog-shum jashrt, jandawi papera jashibrmo jan jet-ja-u ujaprtrca.
40005032	Ooshrt amjri yashipinrg, naajri ja-u namnoo jashrt jashanduutu boi bon-jet jashrt, jashirirgya ieb jaminrglig boyacajetep naa den. Oyat naajri jaoum ja-uja naa brrt boiat inamnogprnjin, iwoojeuprnjinda naa bon.
40005033	Yandawi jajuiyut brjaligu camog bŕn, mabigrricupoirit jashrt naa oodmarnog Dios-jaa. Imauminrg Dios-jaa oje naa mamojani.
40005034	Ooshrt amjri yashipinrg, yacupoimoot Dioat japishiwaag rjeta amo. Yacupoimoot poi Paraíso-jaa rjeta amo ooshrm Dios liiriprna jalii.
40005035	Yacupoimoot poi wryu-jaa rjeta amo ooshrm Dios shiim liiriprna jalig. Yacupoimoot poi Jerusalén-jaa ooshrm jayana jalig naa Bijriwairüg iwairüg.

40012030	Naajri ishandii ajet jabata adrg. Oyat naajri epinot juishanberbri an, cadjatepnipai ashrt.
40012031	Ooshrmda amog yan, Dioya jashinama cashrt wrijin capecado, wrijin poi iebjet camogu Dios-jaa nat wryu tepinot, ooshrt cayaadu iebjet Espíritu Santo-jaa yauya Dioat jashinamdiprn cashrt.

40012033	Ijei jaligu naa pun, ijeinogot poi jacaabot. Ooshrt ieb jaligu naa punjri, iebnogot poi jacaabot. Jacam-jaala japishibiwaa naa pun.
40012034	Yam shrrbot, bojejam jayaquedrg shirig yayaadig ijeijet, iebnogprnotjina yalig-shicom. Naajri ieb oodyamog yayee-jet jayrg yabigshayu ieb-shrt.

40015009	Oocatep-mog ijei cabrglig an, mot yerogla idjuirg Dios yerog-shrt.
40015010	Oyat Jesúat caág jalica nat epinot, jamog calat, jayaujui naa oodamog, yabigyaushag brjaliyu jaligu.
40015011	Epinot bigshayu jashanebrt naa mowoucat irnucat mocooleye, ooshrt naa moyerog iyrg mocooleat cabigshayu jaebrg nat epinot.
40015012	Oyat Jesúat ijuirgprnot yug jalica carnog jan, japishirnashanwaatejarn maeb caluuglig nat fariseoolat jashrm naa oodmamog.
40015013	Jesús mog calat, naajri Aii shrnoja cadjashiougya cadjanamjee wrijin nat brttep, nat idjashanjrmiprnot.
40015014	Yabigrriculig cayerog-shrt. Oodawi bigrriprnotjin ijuiot brrt bigrriprnotjin. Itnn bigrriprnjinat jarrnogu itrm bigrriprnjin cashilrgya itrmjani jajet wadyeg-teja.
40015015	Oyat Pedro mog Jesúat, bidmaupinrg brjaliyu jaligu naa comparación oodmamog.
40015016	Oyat Jesús mog jan, yam-tejam poi bicashancowit yam.
40015017	Japishiyashanwaat-tejam naa mowoug iniug monamdeja jaluugjurg mocoole-yei, oyat jayrg moshrt.
40015018	Ooshrt naa moyerog ieb iyrg mocooleat, jayrgtep mojii-teat, ooshrmda cadjaebrg nat epinot.
40015019	Mojii-teatwinda wrijin mobigshayu iebprnjin. Jadirg epin irrirglig, jadirg itrm den ijeujee mo-u shrt, jadirg mowoojeujee, moshegjee poi, moteeshaujee poi, moyaad ebjee brrt-jaa poi.
40015020	Oo-irigla cabigshayu ebrr nat epinot, ooshrtjri molap ishanshrrtu moyewai juprdu, mobigshayu jashanebrt.
40015021	Oyat Jesús uprt cashrt janogjee niti Tiro-teja, Sidón-teja poi.
40015022	Oyat itrm den yug Jesús prna. Canaatwin naa den. Jad-ág ishiigjet jamog, mam Aŕri, David jriwai, auubiid mauluug. Itrm demonio-lig alou jii-tee, jadirg ebupaajacrdi jijogjet.
40015023	Oyat yau Jesús jayerog waoliprn. Oyat idjajuirgprnolat janarg camog jan, jaumauprt cui bishrt ooshrm jaáashonog biprnot.
40015024	Oyat Jesús mog calat, oowi Dioat acuirig calica nat oveja biguwiprnotjini cajewaleot nat Israel jrdwat.
40015025	Oyat naa den Jesús janarg, jashoobrg jautjuiyag-jet jamog jan, Aŕri majrrja amaurg.
40015026	Oyat Jesús mog jan, jashanjei an iougu trrijulot-shrt, jainamjee iyoololat.
40015027	Oyat naa den mog jan, rcaji Aŕri, ooshrt nat yoolot jadwoug naa an ilrgprn carri raesa-noma.
40015028	Oyat Jesús mog jan, mam den, jijogjeta majii malirr ajaa, ooshrmda jaminrg man naa imajeu ashrt.
40015029	Oyat Jesús uprt caniti-shrt, oyat jabooluug rt-Galilea manye. Oyat jayrg wen-jaa, onda jalii.
40015030	Oyat canog jabea ibagot epinot, cadcarrnog jaiica nat peebot ebnogprnotjin, bigrriprnotjin poi, ishanyaalit poi, shanshoiot poi, brrt poi oyem nat wrrnoligot. Cadcalirg Jesús shiim cooye, oyat cadjajeicon wrijin.
40015031	Oyat caom Jesús rca jadduugbat cayaadicat nat ishanyaalidi, cajeiat poi nat peebot ebnogot, cabocat poi nat ishanboiodi, cabiglicat poi nat bigrriprnotjindi. Oyat nat epinot, ijei cabrg jan naa israelot jri-Dioat.
40015032	Oyat Jesúat caág jaiica nat idjajuiigprnot, jamog calat, cauubiid aluug nat epinot calicat ajet ipoi wryu, oyat dumat boiruud cawoug. Jashanjeu cauprdig caot-teja cawoug rrishicom brjashirii calrgu drg-uu cayeishanwai-shrm.
40015033	Oyat idjajuirgprnot mog jan, brrn-jam cawouca boibishiruu nat epinot ibagot nam boiruudutep epin.
40015034	Oyat Jesús mog calat, bojejam jatoo an yalica. Camog jan, siete jatog an irig birica, itrmnog yriot poi.
40015035	Oyat Jesúat categ cui niti-uu nat epinot.
40015036	Oyat jadwao nat siete itog an, yriot poi, ijei jabrg Dioat. Oyat jadmoopig naa an yriot poi, jadbrg idjajuirgprnolat jadbrrtegjee calat nat epinolat.
40015037	Oyat cayewai wrijin cateetogjee. Oyat cajuicatuunrg siete mapiriot cawoug peijin-jet.
40015038	Cuatro mil catog nat mot iyewaiot, oyat detpat trrijulot poi.
40015039	Oyat Jesúat cauprtrg jashrt nat epinot oyat jaluug já-teja janogjee niti Madala-teja.
40016001	Oyat nat fariseoot canimnog Jesús-lica cajet nat saduseoot, jadjeu Jesús teecashaurglig. Jadrm jadminrg-jee calat brrt ishanminrri.
40016002	Jesús mog calat, yamat duugbat yamog, boiruudyacom wau briem cacrdnog-shrm nat waojribrŕuot.
40016003	Oyat yamat yrgbat yamog, wau shicomdrg bijaa cacrdnog-shrm nat waojribrruot. Yam oiyatemog, japishiyawaagwi brjaliyu jaligu naa iyaluug wryu-uja. Ooshrt yau japishiyawaaliprn naa iyaluug dumat, iyajui poi.
40016004	Jadjeu jaminrglig brrt ishanminrri nat dumatwinot iebnogprnotjin iwoojeuprnotjin. Ooshrt jashanminrbrtya calat. Oowi ishiminrg oje Jonaat irninrlauni. Oyat Jesúat canarnnog janog cashrt.
40016005	Oyat caminogbat rt yabata nat Jesúat ijuirgprnot, boiruud an calat jaicashanwat-shrm an carrnoglig.
40016006	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayauluug yashrt calev adura nat fariseoot saduseoot poi.
40016007	Oyat camog caaleot, oje-tejam jamo birat an pishanrrnot-shrm.
40016008	Jesúat japishiwaagwi cabigshayu, ooshrm jarnog calat, yam mot yajii shandirriot ajaa rjet. Boirigshrmjam yajii-shŕm boiruud-shrm ya-an.
40016009	Japishiyashanwaat-tejamju brrjaligu arn jajet naa irninrg iyaluuca. Yau-tejam cayeiyawaaliprn nat sinco itog an naa-jet cateetoorrli sinco mil mot. Oyat bojelijam jatoo mapiriot cawoug peijin.
40016010	Yau-tejam cayeiyawaaliprn nat siete itog an cateetoorrli cuatro-mil mot. Oyat bojelijam jatoo mapiriot cawoug pejin.
40016011	Boirigshrmjam japishiyashanwaji ashanyaada an-jaa, yapinrgbat calevadura-jaa nat fariseoot saduseoot poi.
40016012	Oyat idjajuirgprnolat japishiwaacat Jesúat duug-cui cashrt naa idjuirg nat fariseoolat saduseoolat poi. Jesúlawi Dios Wá, Jáa-ijug poi
40016013	Oyat Jesús minogbat nitija Sesarea Filipo-tee, idjajuirgprnot jarm, bojejam carno ajaa nat epinot. Brr-majam am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee.
40016014	Oyat camog jan, itrmnogot mog Juan Bautistama mam, oyat itrmnogot mog Elíama mam, oyat itrmnogot mog, Jeremíama mam, o itrrn capei nat Dios yerog shipinjurdi.
40016015	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yam poi, bojejam yamo ajaa. Brr-jam am.
40016016	Oyat Simón Pedro mog Jesúat, Marndawi Cristo Dioat icuiprn nani. Marndawi jaWá naa Dios iwairüg.

40016018	Oyat dumat mapinrg, marndawi Pedro, ooshrtjri jashiwryrgya naa aiglesia jajaa naa Jáa ipeg. Oyat naa infierno jriWairüg, yauya jadshiquedrliprn jaijabeebdig.
40016019	Jashibrgya man naa jet-jajuiyiyu caluugjee cajuijaberliprn-teja naa Paraíso jriwairüca. Wrijin nat idmajiiprnot Dioat nam wryu-tee, cadjashijiipya poi jan shrnoja. Oyat wrijin nat idmanamnogprnotjin nam wryu-tee, cadjashinamnogya poi naa shrnoja iricat.
40016020	Oyat Jesúat capinrg jijogjet nat idjajuirgprnot jaicashanpinjee oo-jaliglig Dioat icuiprn nani.
40016021	Oyat oola wryulau Jesúat jalirg-jurlau japishicawaagjee nat idjajuirgprnolat janwi jashinoo Jerusalema. Jadshirirgya ebupaajacrtjee nat quepaolat, sacerdoteot jriwairügolat, inaat poi. Oyat jadshirrirgya, oyat jaipoiyu wryu-jayeya jabigleshiwrr-shri wadyegteat.
40016022	Oyat Pedro jarrnog Jesúat brrt-shrt, jamog jan ishiigjet, mam Aŕri mauubiid mauluug, jamacupoirirt idrninrbrgjee man oje mamojani.
40016023	Oyat Jesúat Pedro jeuwug, jamog jan, maunog ashrt mam moweijin, abigshayu matep-ebrg. Yau mayaadiprn Dios bigshayujet, ooshrt mayaad mot bigshayu-jet.
40016024	Oyat Jesús mog idjajuirgprnolat, naajri jajewe jayuglig aprna, yauya jadshiquedrliprn jabigjashaglig jaalei-jaatep, ooshrt jabigshayu jaawrg jarrijee wryu shitojani idminrgjee oje alijani.
40016025	Naajri jayiiruju naa wryu jashirmdrgya jashrt, Ooshrt naajri jajewe jarririg wryu-shrt ashrm, jadshitairirgya wryu ishanbeji.
40016026	Jaijabeebu wrijin wryu tepin mowoo, Boirigya jashimii jan naa bon irmdrg-yawan Dios-shrt. Boirig-jetwrnjam jadquedr jamii jabrglig wryu ishanbeji.
40016027	Ashiyugya-shri am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee, ishiyrgya ijeijet oje Aiini cajriat nat ánjeleot. Oyat carnii ashibrgya nat wryu tepinot catojani jarniija naa idminrg nam wryu-tee.

40017001	Oyat seis wryu prnot, Jesús nog epinot-shrt wen ishrn-jaa. Jadrrnog jajet Pedro, Jacobo poi, japewai Juan poi.
40017002	Oyat Jesús caluugbat, jataaleat jacambiarg ijeijet. Jaúuat iyrg ijeijet oje yamalat iyrrlauni. Oyat jayuiolat iyrg iwrgjet oje iwaalrlauni.
40017003	Oyat Moisés caluug, Elias poi, cayaad Jesús-jet.
40017004	Oyat Pedro mog Jesúat, Aŕri ijeira naa ibiruug. Cadmajeuu cabiminrglig ipoiot capillaot, jashitrrn man, itrm-poi Moiséat, itrm-poi Elíaat.
40017005	Oyat Pedro juyaadbat, itrm waujribrru yug caijawei. Oyat itrm yerog cajui waujribrru-teat. Ojera jamo, oola aWá ijeuprn, ijáijeta jaluu, jayerog yaujui.
40017006	Jadjuibat naa moyerog calrg niti-uja, caú cajaan nat idjajuirgprnolat, caom ipegjet.
40017007	Oyat Jesúat canarg, jalap jalirg cajaa, jamog, yajuicurniishog yacupoiom.

40017010	Oyat idjajuirgprnot mog jan, boirigshrmjam camog nat inaat jashiyugya Elias Dioat icuiprn juprta.

40017013	Oyat idjajuiprnolat japishiwaag Jesús yaadig jajaa naa Juan Bautista.

40017015	Jamog Jesúat, Aŕri, jauubiid mauluug naa a-wá. Jaeb oje iigprnjini, ebupaajacrt ipegjet. Jaibagla jalrcat drr-bica rt-teja poi.
40017016	Jacugrryug idmajuirgprnot-dica ooshrt yau jadquedrliprn jadjeicondig.
40017017	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yam epinot yajii shandirriot ajaa, yam bigshayu tiigot. Brrtog wryujam ashijulig yajet. Brrtog wryujam yajricaashicouju. Jayaurrgug nani jere trriwai.
40017018	Oyat Jesúat jayrg cui jijogjet naa demonio trriwai-shrt. Oyat demonioat yrg trriwai-shrt oowiat jajeirüglig.
40017019	Oyat idjajuirgprnolat janarg Jesús jadrmjee jaanajet epinotshrt, boirigshrmjam jabishan poi quedrriri demonio binamdig.
40017020	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayashanquedrdi demonio yanamdig, yajii yashandirt-shrm ajaa ijeijet. Rjeta amo yan, ayerog yawaorgu oje mostazo-bigni, jayashiquedrgya yamogu naa wenat, maunog boyeja, oyatya jashinogya. Yajii yalirgu rjet ajaa, boi-shiruudya naa iyashanquedrri jayaminrglig.
40017021	Jainamjee demonio iwairüg oje jalijaniri naa inarndi naa trriwai-shrt, molatwi Dios ipinr prnpatjet moyeishanju-waishicom.
40017022	Oyat cajuuligbat Galilea-tee, Jesús mog nat idjajuirgprnolat, adshibrgya mot lapuja, am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee.
40017023	Adshirrirgya, oyatjri japoi wryu-jaaya ajuishimii shri. Oyat cajii-shŕm ipegjet nat idjajuirgprnot jajuibat naa moyerog.
40017024	Oyat Jesús minogbat moyan Capernaum-teja cajriat nat idjajuirgprnot, cayug Pedro-lica nat palata-out temploat. Camog jan, Marriat jashanbrt-tejam naa palata idjeu templo-ŕriat.
40017025	Oyat Pedro mog calat, rcaji jadbrgwi calat. Oyat Pedro luug mooleja, oyat jajuprdu jayaadig Jesús mog jan, mam Simón, bojejam mabigshayu lii. Brr-shrtjam palata ca-oug nat wryu jriwairügolat, catrriot shrt-tejam jadoug o yawa-atwinot shrt.
40017026	Oyat Pedro mog jan, jadougjri yawa-atwinot shrt. Oyat Jesús mog jan, ooshrmda boirig shanditejam catrriolat mii-brg.
40017027	Ooshrt jabishanjeu cadbinrmrglig nat iwairügot. Dumat maumap-nog rt cooja, oyat naa imamap-jurg yrri, jacoole shimauyigya jarnashitairirgya palata jacoolee. Jamau-ougya jashrt jamaurryug iwairügolat, jarnii mabrgjee naa idrm mashrt, ashrt poi.
40018001	Oyat oo-wryulau Jesús canarg nat idjajuirgprnolat, camog jan, brr-yajam naa bipei bijuprtawin jajuibeeriprn-teja naa Paraíso jriwairüg.

40018003	Oyat Jesús mog calat, rjeta amo yan, yau-jaligu yabigshayu yacambiarliprn, yau-jaligu uubiidjet yabigyashaaliprn oje trrijulotni, yauya yashiruugliprn cajet nat Paraíso jriwairücat juibergprnot.
40018004	Oyatya naa cajuprtuwin shirig capei nat Paraíso Jriwairücat juibergprnot, oola naa jabigshamprn uubiidjet oje trriwaiat jabigshalauni.
40018005	Oyat naa jabataiya itrm capei ishrmnogot atam-jaa, jabatjatai poi arn.
40018006	Brr-jaligu jalirr ieb caminrgjee nat ishŕmnogolat ca-jürirlat ajaa, jajeiwi jaa ipeg jajiipu jayrr-jaye jadrrlugjee rt monye.
40018007	Iebya ishiyug calica nat wryu tepinot jashrm naa moteeshauyu naa wryu-tee jalirr ieb caminrgjee nat epinolat. Oiirigwi caliglig nat moteeshaurt, ooshrt jashiebya naa jalirrm brrlat ieb minrgjee.
40018008	Malapat jalirgu ieb maminrglig, mashiimat poi, jarnaupan jarnaunam mashrt. Janomjri jeira maluugu wryu ishanbeji-teja mashim-mu, madnam-shrt drr ishantrmi-teja malapot icauolat mashiimot poi.
40018009	Mabicat jalirgu ieb maminrglig jamau-oug jamaunam mashrt. Janomjri jeira maluugu wryu shanbeji-teja itrm mabigjet madnamshrt drr-teja icauot mabigot-jet.
40018010	Jayauluug yashrt jayashag-shrt mii-rriprnjina jaliglig itrm capei nat ishrmnogot trrijulot. Dumat yashipinrg, nat ángeleolot caijewet nat ishrmnog trriot, jadduug Aii-u oiirigwi shrnoja irig.
40018011	Ayug nani, am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee cadajeiconjee nat biguwiprnotjin ebupaacrt-shrtya jashrm naa ieb idminrg canogjeeya Paraíso-teja.
40018012	Bojejam yabigshayu-lig jajaa naa comparación. Itrm bon cien ovejaat itog, jabiguwiu itrm capei cadjanamnog nat noventa-nueve itogot ovejaot cawai-tee janogjee wen-jaa jadjeunogjee naa oveja biguwiprnjin.
40018013	Dumat yashipinrg, jadtairirgbat naa biguwiprnjin, jashijáiya jadduuglig cashrt nat noventa-nueve itogot bigshanuwiyit.
40018014	Ojera poi naa Yaii shrnoja irig, jadshanjeu boi rrndrglig jashrt itrmu Capei nat ishrmnog trriot. Idyajiiprnot Dioat naa wryu-tee, jajetwinota cashirigya shrnoja
40018015	Ieb jaminrgu man naa majrrat, maunog jalica jaimapinjee jan japecado-jaa ijaanjet epinot-shrt. Jadjuibrg man jamaquedrg jaumaprtrglig Dioat.
40018016	Ooshrt jadshanjuibrtu man, cadmaurrnogya jalica itrm o icauot iglesia atwinot jadjuijee brjaligu jamog naa ieb minrr man, japishicawaagjeeya jainot shicapinrgjeeya rjet.
40018017	Oyat jadshanjuibrtuyayan, jaimaupin nat iglesia atwinolat. Oyat jadshanjuibrtu calat, jayauluug oje cadyalulauni nat Dios yerog shanwaorriot.
40018018	Rjeta amo yan wrijin nat idyajiiprnot Dioat naa wryu-tee, cadjashijiipya poi janwi shrnoja. Oyat wrijin nat idyanamnogprnot yashrt naa wryu-tee, cadjashinamnogya poi jashrt naa shrnoja iricat.
40018019	Oyat yashripinrg, naa Aii shrnoja iricat idshiminrgya calat oje jadjeulauni nat icauolat yapet itrmjanibr bigshayu ligolat jajaa naa idrm Dios-shrt naa wryu-tee.
40018020	Ooshrm alig cajewalee brrn-jaligu cajuicaber atam-jaa nat icauolat o ipoiot poi.
40018021	Oyat Pedroat janarg Jesús jamog jan, mam Aŕri, bojeyajam jaishitoo jajeicondig ajet naa ieb-minrr an, siete jashitoijam jajeicondig ajet.
40018022	Jesús mog jan, jashandirt jamajeicondig majet siete iitogjet, iitogjet, ooshrt. jamashijeicon majet setenta jashitog siete naa iebminrr man.
40018023	Oyat naa Paraíso Jriwairüg cajuijashishugya jaepinota caligjee oje itrm iwairücat jaepinot cuenta duulauni.
40018024	Oyat cadjaág jalica. Oyat jadrryug jalica itrm jamii-rrirr cien mil pesos.
40018025	Oyat boiruud japalata jet-jamiijabrg naa jacuenta. Oyat jaŕriat jawenderg cul ja-u poi, jatrriot poi, wrijin jalapwoo poi jalewia mii-jabrgjee.
40018026	Oyat naa deewialig jashog jautjuiyag-jet jaŕriat, jadrm ishiigjet jamog, mam aŕri jajeimauteiju jarnii ashibrgya mashrt wrijin naa mamii arriryu.
40018027	Oyat jauubiid jaŕriat jaluuglig oyat jacuenta janam jashrt, jajrijamri jashrt wrijin naa jalewia.
40018028	Oyat naa jarnii rrirprn jayrg quedyem jaŕri ot-teat, oowi boi jatairirg jajrr jamii-rrirr ishŕmjetwi. Oyat jayrr tat-shijawaorg jamog jan, jarnii maubrg naa amii marrirryu.
40018029	Oyat naa jajrr dewiarm, jateg jautjuiyag-jet jan, jamog jan, jajeimauteiju jamii ashibrgya mashrt wrijin.
40018030	Ooshrt naa bon yau jadjeuliprn jajeijateirig jamii jabrgjee. Oowi jadrrnoglig jadnamjee presoja moliiriprn-teja ata-on jamii jabrca.
40018031	Oyat nat brrt ibeebet jaduugbat naa ieb idminrg cajrrat, cajiishŕm ipegjet, canog caŕririca jai-capinjee.
40018032	Oyat caŕriat jaág naa jajrr presormprn, jamog jan, mam ajetwin iebprnjin. Bŕn jajri-amriri mashrt wrijin naa amii marriryu amarmshrmdi ishiigjet.
40018033	Ooshrmda man poi, jauubiid mashiruu majrr oje poiwi naa mauubiid aluulauni amat.
40018034	Oyat janrm jaŕri jajet, oyat jadcui ebupaajacrtjee ata-on jamii jabrca jalewia wrijin.
40018035	Oyat Jesús mog calat, ojera poi idshirrbr yan naa Aiiat shrnoja iricat yau-jaligu yaperdonaliprn yajet nat yajrrot yajii-teat.
40019001	Oyat Jesús yaad quedyem brjaligu mojrr ijeicondig mojet, jauprt Galilea-teat, janog rt Jordán yabata Judea-teja.
40019002	Oyat ibagjet epinot nog japrna. Oyat cadjajeicon ibagot wrrnoligot on.
40019003	Oyat cayug Jesús-lica itrmnogot fariseoot, jadjeu jateecashaurglig, camog jan, jadquedrrijam bonat ja-u uprtrgu boirigshrm jaligutep.
40019004	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayashanlee-tejam naa idnagprndi bŕn papera-uu. Naa Caminrr wryu tepinot jadminrg-jurg itrm bon itrm den poi.

40019010	Oyat camog Jesúat nat idjajuirgprnot, cacaligu-om oje mamojani, jacugjeiwrnda casaa cashancalitu-om nat mot.

40019012	Natjri itrmnogot yau jadquedrliprn ca-u liglig cataale eb-shrm cayrglig caiin-shrt. Oyat yau itrmnogot u-uliiriprn idbeeb-shrm jan naa Paraíso Jriwairücat epinot juicashugjee jan. Brjaligu jaquedrr jadwaorglig naa moyerog janwi jadshiwaorg.

40019015	Oyat Jesúat cabendisiarg jalap-jet, oyat janog cashrt boyeja.

40019017	Jesús mog jan, boirigshrmjam ijerira mam mamog. Jatrmdawi Dios ijei. Jamajemi maluuglig wryu ishanbeji-teja jamauminrgya naa Dioat minrg-cui man.
40019018	Oyat naa bon-trt mog jan, boirigjam naa moyerog anwi ishiwaorg. Jesús mog jan, epin macupoirrirt, boi macupoijeu itrm denu ma-u shrt, macupoisheet, mateecupoishau brrt-jaa.

40019022	Oyat naa bon-trt jadjuibat naa Jesúat oodmog jan jajii-shŕm jauprtdig Jesús-shrt ooshrm jabagla naa iribrg jan.

40019026	Jesúat cayiijeu, jamo calat, nat mot yau jadquedrliprn cacajeicondig caalei bigshayujetep, ooshrt Dioat jaquedrg jadminrglig calat wrijin naa idjeu.
40019027	Oyat Pedro mog jan, Aŕri, bidujri jabinamnocat wrijin naa iribrgli birat binogjee maprna, oyat boirigyajam ishiribrg birat.

40019029	Oyat natjri caot namnot ashrm, capedwat poi, cajadwat poi, ca-ujut poi, catrriot poi, cajrmca poi, jashiribrgya calat cien itogjet jashrt naa idnamnogprn. Oyatya poi jashiribrg calat wryu ishanbeji.

40020001	Naa Paraíso Jriwairücat cajuiberg shirig nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee oje jalijani naa mojrmca ŕri janog pishicup cadjajeujee ibeebet cajuicashubrgjee jan nat jajrmcaat.
40020002	Jaijapin calat palata itrm wryu müjeitogye nat ibeeberat, oyat cadjacuinoo jajrmcajule-teja.

40020008	Oyat yamat duugbat naa tim-ŕri jamog naa ibeebet ijeweat, camau-ág nat ibeebet camü abrgjee. Camü maubrg-jurg nat ibeebetprnot cupwiat.

40020011	Oyat jadwaorg quedyem naa idbrgprn calat cayaad iebjet jajaa naa tim-ŕri.

40020019	Adshibrgya calat nat judioota ishandiot atamshicashiyoijee adshipaiya mowrr-jet, oyatya aicashibam cruza-jaa. Oyatya jaipoiyu wryu-jaiya ajuishirnii shri morriyu-shrt.
40020020	Oyat jayug Jesús-lica naa Zebedeo-u jatrriot jriat. Jateg jautjuiyag-jet Jesúat jadrm naa idjeu jashrt.
40020021	Oyat Jesús mog jan, boirig imajeu jaminrglig man. Oyat jamog Jesúat, natjri atrriot icauot cadmaulirgya categjee majet mategot-jaa iwairüca maligbatya, itrrnya mawireat ishiteg, itrm poi mashaat.
40020022	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yau japishiyawaaliprn brjaliyu jaligu naa iyarm ashrt. Jajrica-yashicowiyawrnjam naa jrica-ashicowiya amat. Jayaquedrriwrnjam bautisao yadrgu oje bautisao adshirlauniya arn. Oyat carnog Jesúat, rryawrn jajrica-bishicowiyawrn.
40020023	Oyat Jesús mog calat, rjeta jajrica-yashicowiya naa jricaashicowiya. Oyat bautisao yadshirgya oje bautisao adrlauni arn. Ooshrt yau jayaquedrliprn yaliglig ajet ategot-jaa, ooshrtjri cashirigya awireat ashaat poi nat Aiiat irirgprnot caligligya ajet on.

40020026	Ooshrt yam, jashandirt iyarninrgjee oje calijani, ooshrt naajri jajewe jajrrot jacuirig, jayaulirg yajetwina jaligjee.

40020028	Iyauminrg oje alijani am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee. Ashanyut cadacuijee idbeebrgjee an, ooshrtjri ayug ibeebjee calat. Ayug arrijee camii abrgjee nat ibagot cadashiujee naa iebprnjin-shrt.
40020029	Oyat cauprtbat moyan Jerico-teat, ibagot epinot nog Jesús prna.

40020031	Oyat nat epinot ishogot drg-uu, cadcamrn nat bigrriprnotjin. Onda yairii camog calat, ooshrt jijogjet canomjriág Jesús. Camog, mam Biŕri, mam David Wá, biuubiid mauluug.

40021001	Oyat jadnarcadu Jerusalén, caminog wen-jaa jatam Olivos inagjetwi moyan Betpage-shrt. Oyat Jesúat cacuinog icauot idjajuirgprnot moyan-teja.
40021002	Jamog calat, yaunog moyan ishŕm bijuprta irig. Omda boi yashitairirr itrm burra idjiip shaleiprn jatrri jriat. Jayaushiuya naa burra jatrri jriat, cadyaurryugya alica.
40021003	Bolat yarmuya boirig-shrm cadyashiu. Biŕrira cajewet yaumogya jan.oyatya cadjashicuiyubr an.

40021006	Oyat idjajuirgprnot nog jadminrg oje Jesús mojani calat.

40021016	Oyat nat sacerdoteot mog Jesúat, jamajuijam naa oodcamog majaa nat trrijulot. Oyat Jesús mog calat, rcaji jajuiwi. Jayashanlee-tejamju naa idnagprndi, ojera jamo, ijeira naa oodcamog majaa nat ishŕmnogot, otpoi nat idijushrgot.
40021017	Oyat Jesús nog cashrt janogjee moyan Betania-teja. shaí jawurgjee jajan.

40021019	Oyat jadduug itrm pun iguera jajuprta drg-uu. Oyat jadcugluuyug jayau jacam liiriprn, ootep jawan iduug. Oyat jamog naa punat, brlau shanshriritya macabot-shirii majaa. Oowiat jajuijawrglig jashiiglig naa pun iguera.
40021020	Oyat nat idjajuirgprnot caorn Jesús rca jadduugbat jadminrglig naa brrt ishanminrri jayerog-jet. Oyat camog jan, boirigshrmjam jashiig mogwaibmi naa pun iguera.
40021021	Oyat Jesús mog calat rjeta amo yan, yajii-yalirgu ajaa rjet. yabigshayu shancauu, jayaquedrgla jayaminrglig naa iminrg. Jayaquedrgla yamogu wenaí, maunog malrgjee rt ipeg-teja, oyatjri jashinogya jalrgjee rt ipeg-teja yabigshayu shancauu.
40021022	Wrijin naa iyarm Dios-shrt, jashiribrgya yan yajii yalirgu jajaa rjet.

40021024	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yashirmju itrm moyerog-jet. Ayerog yawaorgujri ishalalig-jet oyat yashipinr-om boirig bigshayu-jet jaligu jaminr naa iminrg.
40021025	Brrjam jabrm Juan Bautistaat naa moyerog idjuirg bautismojaa. Dios yerog-tejam o mot yerog-tejam. Oyat camoyeg caaleat. Dios yerogla naa Juanat oodmog bimogu, bidjashipinrgya, boirigshrmjam jayerog yashanwaorri.

40021028	Oyat Jesús mog calat, bojejam yabigshayu lii jajaa naa compa ración oodamog. Itrm bon trriot cau. Oyat jamog itrmat, mam a-wá, dumat maunog ajrmcaule-teja, cuimashuubrgjee an ajrmcaat cabot.
40021029	Oyat jamog jaiiat, jashanjeu, ooshrt jabigshayu jacambiarg naa bon-trlat. Oowi janoglig idbeebjee jaii jnncajule-tee.
40021030	Oyat jaiiat jaluug itrm ja-wá, jabeeb jacui poi oje jadcuilauni japewai. Oyat jamog jaiiat, ashinog ishibeebnog, ooshrt yau janooliprn.
40021031	Oyat Jesúat carm, brrjam capei nat icauot iminrt oje caiiat jajeulauni. Oyat camog Jesúat, naajri idcui-jurgprn. Oyat Jesús mog calat, rjeta amo yan, natjri impresto mii-out ebuteeshaurt, iwoojeuprnotjin poi, mogwaini shirigya yashrt cashiruug Dioat juishugprnot-jet shrnoja.
40021032	Bŕn Juan Bautista yugli yadjuirgjee ijei-yaminrgjee, oyat yau jayerog yawaorliprn. Ooshrt natjri impuesto mii-out iwoojeuot poi jayerog cajuqooshrtjri yam álujut naa-jaa Juanat oodmoglig, yau yabigshayu yacambiarliprn yajii yalirgjee ajaa.
40021033	Dumat boi yaujui comparación. Jatrmdi bon mojrmca ŕri. Jadjrm jabrtprn, oyat jaijawai. Oyat shushibot-piuot liiriprn jaminrg. Oyat jashooliprn jaminrg ishrn iduugjee jaiat. Oyat jadirg ibeeberat jajrmca iijeujee. Oyat janog boyeja.
40021034	Oyat jabigye-minocadu cajuicashuglig nat jajrmcaat cabot, cadjacui jajetwinot ibeebet-dica cadcabryugjee jan jajrmcaat.
40021035	Oyat nat ibeebet cadcawaorg calap-jet nat carriat icuiprnot, jatrm idpai, jatrm idrrirg, oyat jatrm idrrirg jaa-jet.
40021036	Oyat carriat brrt-shri cuinog jajetwinot. Oyat nat ibeebet idshriminrg calat oje brwi-shri idrbrlauni calat nat idjacui jurgprnolat.
40021037	Oyat oopegwi ja-wá jacui calica. Jamog jaaleat, cashiomyawrn jarea naa ja-wá.
40021038	Oyat jadduugbat ja-wá yuglig nat ibeebet, camoyeg caaleot, oolawi naa jashiwaorriyapeg naa jaii jrrncajule.

40021040	Oyat Jesúat carm nat sacerdoteot, jayugbatya naa caŕri, bojejam idshir calat nat ibeebet.
40021041	Camog Jesúat, cadjashirrirgya nat iebnogprnotjin. Yauya cauushibiidiprn jalica. Oyat brrt jalirg jatim iicajeujee, nat cajushut jajrmcaat cadcarryugjeeya jan jayaa minogbatya.
40021042	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayashanleetejam naa idnagprndi brn, naa Jáa idshanjewini nat templo minrlat, dumatdapeg templo dii jajaa naa Jáa idshanjewiri. Oolawi Biŕri iminr oje, ooshrmda ijeijet jabiruug naa idminrgprn.
40021043	Oyat yapinrg, Dioya jashioum yashrt naa jet-moluug caijajeuliprn-teja, jadbrgjeeya brrt epinolat, nat cabrlatya jan nat juicashuuprnot jan.
40021044	Naa ilrg jajaa naa Jáa jashiwoinogya, ooshrtjri brr-jaa jaligu Jáa Irr jashibinogya oje iitouprni.
40021045	Oyat nat sacerdoteot jriwairügot, fariseot poi, jadjuibat naa comparación Jesúat oodmog, japishicawaag caebyu ijapindig jajet naa comparación.
40021046	Oyat jadjeu Jesús cawaorglig presoja jadrgjee, ooshrt caom cashrt nat epinot ibagot, ooshrm Dios yerog shipini camog jajaa.
40022001	Oyat Jesús shri-yaad comparación-jet nat epinolat.
40022002	Ojera jamog, naa Paraíso Jriwairücat cajuiberg-shirig nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee oje jalijani naa iwairüg jaminrr cayewairiprn ja-wá uuligbat.
40022003	Cadjacuinog jajetwinot cadca-ágjee nat idjajeuprnot cayuglig. Oyat yau jadjeuliprn cayuglig.
40022004	Oyat brrt jashri-cuinog, jamog calat, camaupinrg cayugjee jaquercat jarninrglig wrijin biwoug. Bŕn carrirg acuiat nat ajiiwit jabitrdrgprnot, jajuiduulucat wrijin, ooshrmda yauyucat casamiento-teja.
40022005	Oyat nat idjaágprnot, yau idminrliprn oje jadjeulauni, itrm nog jatim-teja, itrm inog jawoo mii-jabrgjee.
40022006	Oyat nat brrt idjaágprnot cadcawaorg calap-jet nat cajriwairücat icuiprnot cadcarrirg.
40022007	Oyat jannn naa cajriwairüg, cadjacui calica ibagot sodawaat cadcarrirgjee nat jajetwinot rriotdi, cayan cataijee poi.
40022008	Oyat cajriwairüg mog jajetwinolat, jajuimlucat naa casamiento yawan, ooshrt nat idaágprnot cashanjei cayuglig.

41008001	Oyat boi wryulau cajuicashriberg Jesús-lica ibagot epinolat, boirig-shandit idwoug. Oyat Jesúat ca-ág jalica nat idjajuirgprnolat.

41008017	Jesúat cabigshayu pishiwaag, ooshrmda jamog calat, boirigshrmjam yabigyashag boiruud-shrm an. Apishiyajuwaatejam boirigjaligu am jajet naa iminrg iyaluuca.
41008018	Yabigligwi, iyashanduuttejam yabig-jet, iyashanjui-tejarn yabutog-jet. Jayeyashanwaatteja naa iyaluuglig ajet, iyajui poi ajet.

41010048	Oyat jadmrn nat epinolat, on jairigjee naa bigrriprnjin, ooshrt jadpatjri-ag Jesús jijogjet. Jamog, mam David jriwai, auubiid mauluug.

41010050	Oyat jaruana jateinog jashrt naa bigrriprnjinat, jajuimirayrg-shog, janog Jesús-lica.
41010051	Oyat Jesús mog jan, boirig imajeu jaminrbrglig man. Oyat Jesús yerog jawaorg, Arri jamaulirg iruugjee abigjet, jamog jan.
41010052	Oyat Jesús mog jan, maunog majrirü-teja, majii malircat ajaa ooshrmda majeiat. Oowiat idduuglig ijeijet naa bigrriprnjinotdi Bartimeo, oyat janog Jesús pina drg-uja.
41011001	Oyat jadnargbat Jerusalén, caminog wen Olivos batjogye, inagjetwi moyan Betpaje-shrt, Betania-shrt poi. Oyat Jesúat cacuinog icauot idjajuirgprnot moyan-teja.
41011002	Jamog calat, yaunog moyan-teja bijuprta-irig. Oyatjri yaluugbatya jajan, itrm burro yashitairirgya idjiip-shaleiprn, naa-jaa boi shanjutei. Jayaushiuya jayaurryugjeeya alica.
41011003	Briat yarmuya, boirigshrmjam jayashiu, Biŕrira jajewe, yaumogya jan. Oyatya jadshicuibr an.
41011004	Oyat canog moyan-teja nat idjajuirgprnot, jatairirg naa burro idjiip-shaleiprn moye-batjogu drg-uu, oyat jadshiu.
41011005	Oyat itrmnogot om-irigot camog calat, boirigshrmjam jayashiu jere burro.
41011006	Oyat camog calat oje Jesús mojaniri calat. Oyat jadirg jadrry ugjee naa burro Jesús-lica.
41011007	Oyat jadrryug Jesús-lica naa burro, oyat caruanaot calirg burrojaa, oyat Jesús teg jajaa.
41011008	Oyat cabag epinot caruanaat caniyeglei drg-uu Jesús juiwugjee cajaa jayugbat burro-jaa. Oyat itrmnogolat cajripaan wooyunot cadcayeglei drg-uu Jesús juprta jabatcataijee.
41011009	Oyat nat inogot Jesús juprta, japrnot inogot poi, ijei cabrgjan jijogjet, camog, Gloria Dioat, ijeira naa iyug birica bijri-Dios tamjaa.
41011010	Ijáijeta jabiruu naa iwairücat caijeuliprn ishiyugya, naa cajuijaberliprn jaepinot naa David jriwaiat. Idcantarg jan ijei shrnoja, camog.
41011011	Oyat Jesús lúug Jerusalén-teja, oyat janimnog templo-teja. Jadduug quedyem wrijin jajan, janog Betania-teja idjajuirgprnot jriat, ooshrm cajaicubat.
41011012	Oyat brlemdicat canogbat Betania-teat jabui-shig naa Jesús.
41011013	Oyat iyaujet boi jaluug pun iguera wan-bagpeg. Oyat Jesúat jaluunog jacam tamdigu, oyat boiruud jacam, oowi iitepduugjawan, ooshrm jayaa shanjumünoi.
41011014	Oyat Jesús mog naa punat, brr-shanditya macam shiwoum. Nat Jesúat ijuirgprnot jadjui jamoglig naa punat.
41011015	Oyat caminogbat Jerusalén-teja, Jesús luug templo-teja, oyat cadjayrrg templo-teat wrijin nat iwendert, nat-poi ebumiibrt jajan. Oyat mesaot jateo cashrt nat patata cambiart, categolot poi nat iitibrmot wendert.
41011016	Boirig-shandit idjeu jadrrnoglig templo-teja.
41011017	Oyat epinot jajuirg, jamog calat, idshannat-teerijam papera-uu bŕn, Dios ipinrliprn cashimogya aot-jaa nat epinot wrijin. Ooshrt yamjri jayalirg ishegprnotjin liiriprn jaliglig naa aot.
41011018	Oyat nat Moisés yerog juirit, sacerdoteot jriwairügot poi, jajuibat naa jesúat oodmog, jadjeu ieb catairirglig jajaa jadrrirgjee caom-shrm jarea, ijáijet jayerog cajui-shrm poi nat epinot ibagolat. Brrt ishanju-juirtdig ijeijet oje jalijani.
41011019	Oyat shaireiat Jesús nog cayan-teat.
41011020	Oyat pishicup canogbat drg-uye jaduug naa pun iguera, Bŕn jacom-rri jatatshulotjin poi wrijin.
41011021	Oyat Pedroat jayewaag bijaliguli Jesús mog naa punat, ooshrm jamog Jesúat, mam Biŕri, jamacaluug naa pun ood-ieb imapindi, bŕn jacomshiig.
41011022	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yajii yaulirg Dios-jaa.
41011023	Rjeta amo yan, naa imog wenat, mauyrgjégyat malrrlugjee rt Mar-teja, jadshiruugya naa idjeu jabigshayu shancauuya.
41011024	Oyat yashipinrg, brjaliguya jairmr Dios-shrt, yandawi japishiyashiwaa yajii-teat Dioat jabrgshirigya yan, oyatya jadshiribrgya yan naa iyarm.
41011025	Yayarmbat Dios-shrt jayeyawaagu naa ieb brrt iminrg yan, jayauperdonarg jashrt. Oyat naa Bíi shrnoja-irig, jadshipoi-namya yashrt naa ieb iyaminrg.
41011026	Jayashandirtu jawuglig yashrt naa ieb brrt iminrg yan, yauya poi Yaii shrnoja-iricat jashinamdiprn yashrt naa ieb iyaminrg.
41011027	Oyat cashriminog Jerusalén-teja Jesús idjajuirgprnot-jet. Oyat Jesús boolrgbat templo-tee cayug jalica nat sacerdoteot jriwairügot, otpoi nat Moisés yerog juirt, quepaat poi.
41011028	Oyat Jesús carm, brr bigshayu-jetjam jamaminr naa imaminrg, Brr-jam jabrm man naa mabigshayu imaminrgjee oje naa imarjani.
41011029	Jesús mog calat, amda poi yashirmr itrm moyerog-jet. Ayerog yawaorguya ishalalig-jet, yashipinrgya-jamo brr bigshayu-jet jaligu jaminr naa iminrg.
41011030	Ayaupinrg, brrlijam jabrm Juan Bautistaat naa moyerog idjuirgli bautismo-jaa. Dioat ibrgprnterijam jan, o mot yerog-teca.
41011031	Oyat camoyeg caaleiot, Dios licatwin bimogu Juan Bautista yerog-jaajri, bidjashipinrgya, boirigshrmjam jayerog yashanwaorri.
41011032	Mot yerog bimogu Juan yerog-jaa, biradwi bishiom epinot-rca ooshrt Dios bigshayu-jet jayaad naa Juan Bautista, carnog nat epinot wrijin.
41011033	Oyat nat iinodigot camog Jesúat, yau jabiquedrliprn japishibiwaaglig brriatwin jaligu jabigshayu naa Juan. Oyat Jesús mog calat, am-poi oyem jashanpoiquedrt yapinrgu brr-irig bigshayu-jet jaligu jaminr naa iminrg.
41012001	Oyat Jesúat capinrg-jurg itrm comparación-jet. Ojera jamo itrm bonat jajrm mriot ibagot jajrmcajule-tee, oyat caijawai. Oyat capog iuuliprn jaminrg, oyat jashooliprn jaminrg ishrn iduugjee jaiat. Oyat cadjalirg ibeeberat jajrmca ijeujee.
41012002	Oyat jabigye minocatu cajuicashuglig nat jajrmcaot, cadjacui jajetwinot ibeebet-dica cadcabryugjee jan jajrmcaot.
41012003	Oyat nat ibeebet jadwaorg calap-jet naa carriat icuiprn, jadpai oyat jaucaprtrg carri-lica jequewitep.
41012004	Oyat carriat boi-shri cuinog calica jajetwin, oyat jadjuiyeg jáamolugot-jet, jajaaprn caminrg jajuiyag.
41012005	Oyat carriat boi-shri cuinog calica, oyat jadrrirg. Oyat brrt jashri-cuinog ibagot jajetwinot, oyat cadcapou itrmnogot pun-jet, oyat cadcarrirg itrmnofot.
41012006	Omda boiju-lii caŕri-jet itrmwiat, naa ja-wá yii-jaluugprn. Oyat oopegwi jadcui calica, jamog jajii-teat, cashiomyawrn jarea naa a-wá.
41012007	Oyat nat ibeebet camoyeg caaleot, oo-yawm jashiwaorrya jau jnncajule. Shog biunog jabirrirgjee bipina jaligjeeya naa jajrmcajule.
41012008	Oyat jadwaorg jadrrirg naa carri wá, jataalejin canam jajrmcajule-teat.
41012009	Oyat boyajam carriat ishirr calat nat ibeebet. Oowi jayugshirigya calica cadjashirrirgya nat iebnog-prnotjin. Oyat jadshirirgya brrlat jaijeujee naa jajrmcajule.
41012010	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayashanlee-tejam naa idnagprndi papera-tee, naajri Jáa idshanjewi nat templo minrladi, oola templo iiriprnpecat dumat.
41012011	Oolawi Birri Dios jalirr oje, ijeijet jabiruug naa idminrgprn.
41012012	Oyat nat Jesús balot jadjeu jadwaorglig presoja jadrgjee japishicawaag-shrm cai-japindig jajet naa comparación oodjamog, ooshrt caom carca nat epinot jayerog juiyut, ooshrmda jadnamnog cauprt jashrt.
41012013	Oyat cadcacuinog Jesús-lica itrmnogot fariseoot, Herodes jetwinot poi, ieb catairirgjeema-cugjin jatee naa moyerog idjui.
41012014	Oyat caminogbat Jesús-nca, camog jan, mam Bijuirr, mapishibiwaagwi rjetwinda mam. Yau maomdiprn mot-rca, yau jamajeuliprn iinodigot majáirglig brrt-shrt, ooshrt imajuirg Dios jrirü-jaa rjet. Ooshrmda mabirm, jajeyijam impuesto mii bibrgu naa romanoot jriwairüg César-shrt o jarnii bishishanbrt.
41012015	Jesúat japishiwaagwi oocatep-moglig jan, ooshrm jamog calat, boirig shrmjam jayajeu ateeyashaurglig. Jayaurryubig an itrm palata jaluugjee.
41012016	Oyat itrm palata carryug Jesúat iruuca. Oyat jamog calat, brryaajam naa ijog palata-jaa, brr-jatam naa. Oyat camog Jesúat, ooligjawi bijriwairüg Cesaat yaa, César tam poi.
41012017	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayaurg yajriwairüg Césarat naa idjeu yashrt, oyat jayaubrg Dioat naa idjeu yashrt. Oyat nat Jesús balot caom jarea jayaad-shrm oje bicacouni.
41012018	Oyat canamyug Jesús-lica itrmnogot saduceoot, nat mojuishanmit morriyu-shrt imogot. Ooshrmda jadrm Jesús itrm moyerog-jet.
41012019	Camog jan, mam Bijuirr, bŕn Moiseat inagli papera-uu, jarriu itrm bon jatrri-rrishicomtep, japeiwaijinat jashi-oushogya japeiujin, jatrriot bigjashugrgjee japeiwaijin tam-jaa.
41012020	Omdi siete catogli itrm bon trriot, oyat capeiwaiat jaoug ja-uja, oyat jarri jatrri-mbatju.
41012021	Oyat japewai japrnatwinat jashri-oug naa den, oyat jashri-m jatrri rribatju. Oje shribr ooprnotwin.
41012022	Oyat ojeri poi wrijin nat siete itogot, carri wrijin catrritep rrishicom. Oyat caprnat japeg-rri naa den.
41012023	Oyat cajuirnigbatya morriyu-shrt, brrya capei uuja jashirig naa den, ooshrm nat siete itogodi jamotjin.
41012024	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yayaad boyaja Dios yerog-shrt japishiyashanwaat-shrm brjamoyu jaligu naa idnagprndi papera-uu. Yau-poi japishiyawaaliprn Dios bigshayu iwairüg-jaa.
41012025	Cajuimiibatya nat epinot irriprnotjin, yauya ca-u shishririiriprn, yauya poi cabon shiriiriprn. Ooshrt cashirigya oje calijani nat ángeleot shrnoja.
41012026	Oyatjri jayaquedrg japishiyawaagjee cajaa nat irriprnot cajuishimigya. Jayashanjulee-tejam Moisés papera-uu brjaliguli Dios yaadig jan pun shulot-teat. Ojeri jamo jan, amdawi Abraam jri-Dios, Isaac jri-Dios poi, Jacob jri-Dios poi.
41012027	Cajugwi nat irriprnotjindi, ooshrmda Moisés mog cajaa cajriDiosla naa Dios. Cashancajutu-om jadshancugjeu-om cajri-Dios. Ooshrt yam, iyajuirg boyajatep Dios yerog-shrt, yam cajuishanmit nat irriprnot imogot.
41012028	Oyat itrm capei nat Moisés yerog juirt, jadnarg Jesús, jadjuiat Jesús yaadig cajriat nat saduceoot, japishijawaag ijeiya jaliglig naa moyerog Jesúat iipin calat, ooshrm jadrm Jesús, boirigjam naa Dioat waorg cuijurg birat jijogjet brrt jayerogot-shrt.
41012029	Oyat Jesús mog jan, ojeriwi Dioat capinrg jurgli, jayaujuiyam israelolat, jatrmdawi Birria jaliglig naa Biŕri Dios.
41012030	Mandawi jayii mashiruu Maŕri Dios wrijin majii-teat, wrijin majuuyu-jet, wrijin mabigshayu-jet, wrijin mawairiyu-jet poi. Ojerawi Dioat jajeu iyarg jurg.
41012031	Oyat ojera poi naa orden japrnatwin. Cayii mauluug brrt epinot ojewi mayii maluulauni maaleat. Boiniuda itrm orden Dioat irirbrg birat ijeirig cashrt nat icauot oodamogot.
41012032	Oyat naa bon jamog Jesúat, jajeiwi mam Ijuirr, ijeta naa oodmamog, jatrmdawi naa Dios, boiruud itrm jashrt.
41012033	Ooshrmda jajeiwi jayii-biruugu wrijin bijii-jet bijuuyu-jet poi, bibigshayu-jet poi, wrijin biwairiyu-jet poi. Oyat jajeiwi cayii biruugu brrt epinot ojewi biyii biruulauni biireiat. Janomjri-jeirigla oiirgu jashrt naa idminrg nat mojiu rrirlat Dioat.
41012034	Jesúat jajuibat jayaadig oje bicacouni, jamog jan, mashanyaula jashrt naa Dioat cajuiberliprn jaepinota caligjee. Oyat yau itrmat Jesús rmdiprn caom-shrm jashrt.
41012035	Oyat Jesúat epinot juirgbat templo-tee, jamog calat, boirigshrmjam carnog nat inaat David jriwaira naa Dioat icuiprn Cristo.
41012036	Oolawi Davidat oodmogprndi Espíritu Santo-jet, Birri Dios mog Aŕriat, mauteg awireat ata-on cadalircaya mabalot mashiim norna.
41012037	Oolawi Davidat oodmogprndi bŕn Jaŕrira naa Dioat icuiprn Cristo, ooshrm boirigshrmjam yamog David jriwaira naa Cristo. Oyat nat epinot ibagot cajii-jái Jesús yerog cajuirig.
41012038	Oyat Jesúat cajujuirgbat, jamog nat epinolat, cadyauluug yashrt nat Moisés yerog juirt. Jayii caboolrglig canawaot ipaatnogot jriat. Jadjeu epinot omdig carca cadcayaadrbogbat waduu.
41012039	Iyii-jeta catee iinodig banco-jaa sinagoga-tee, jadpoijeu categot ijei cayewairiprn-tee.
41012040	Oyat catee cashaurg nat bonjin rriprnot capin caougjee cashrt. Oyat Dios capinrg prnpatjet jaicajaanjee cashrt naa ieb idminrg. Oodya ebupaashinomjri-crlrt jashrm naa idminrg.
41012041	Oyat boi wryulau Jesús lig templo-tee ofrenda ot manye. Jadduug brjaligu patata cabrglig Dioat nat epinolat. Cadjaluug nat wooligot jadnam ibag palata ofrenda ot-teja.
41012042	Oyat jayug itrm den bonjin-rriprn uubiidprnjin, jadirg icau centavo ofrenda ot-tee.
41012043	Oyat Jesúat ca-ág jalica nat idjajuirgprnot, jamog calat, rjeta amo yan, naajri bonjin-rriprn uubiidprnjin, jainomjri bajalig idbrg Dioat cashrt wrijin nat patata namat ofrenda ot-teja.
41012044	Wrijin nat brrt jadbrg japeitep-yai naa iribrg calat. Ooshrt naajri den uubiidprnjin jadircat Dioat wrijin naa jet-ebumii jabrgjin jan.
41013001	Jesús yrr quedyem templo-teat, itrm idjuirgprn mog jan, mam Bijuirr, cadmacaluug nat jáaot ijeinogot moot yawanot, nat-poi oyem moot jáaconot iyinogot.
41013002	Oyat Jesús mog jan, cayiiyijarn yalica cadyaluuglig nat moot jáaconot ipeinogot. Boi wryulauya cabalolat cashinam wrijin, yauya boi ishiruuliprn itrm jáau mooprnjinu.
41013003	Oyat canog wen Olivos-jaa, templo yabatye. Jesús teg jajan, jadrmyug jaanajet epinot-shrt nat Pedro, Jacobo poi, Juan poi.
41013004	Camog jan, bidmaupinrg brlauya jayaa shiminog naa oodmamog. boirigya imashirirgya jabiruuglig jet-japishibiwaacaya janacatuyawiat naa oodmamog.
41013005	Jesús mog calat, cayauluug yashrt, jayacupoirirt brrt yateeshaurglig.
41013006	Cashiyugya ibagot atam-jaa, omdawi naa Cristo jeiyateiri jayuglig, cashimogya. Cateecashishaurgya ibaglet epinot.
41013007	Jayashijuiya cayaadig moprtoyu-jaa, jayashipoi-juiya brjaliguya ebupaacacrt shirig moprtoyu-tee. Yacupoi-omya ooshrm ojeyawi idshirr nam wryu-tee, ooshrt mogwaini shanditya jashibee naa wry u.
41013008	Oyat nat epinot moprtoyu cashiminrgya brrt epinot ubata. Oyat itrm iwairücat moprtoyu shiminrgya itrm iwairüg ubata. Oyatya niti shiyai jijogjet wrijin wryu-teja ebupaa-cashipoicrtya bui-jet. Ojeyawi jajuicawrg-shirig ebupaacacrdig.

41013010	Yandawi jayashijuir naa moyerog jet-moijericon ieb-shrt wrijin wryu tepinolat jabeeg juprtuyaja naa wryu.
41013011	Yadrrnogbatya iwairügot-dica, yacupoiyiglrdya jajaa naa jetyadshirmya, ooshrt cadyaupinrgya jajet naa moyerog Dioat ishirigya yan oobat. Yam shanditya ishiyaalot ooshrt Espíritu Santoya ishiyaad yacooleat.
41013012	Oyat nat ayerog shanwaorriot capedwat cabrg cabalolat cadcarrirgjee. Oyat caiijirat cashibrgya catrriot carrirgjee. Oyat catrriot juishimigya caiijit ubata cadcarrirgjeeya.
41013013	Yaeb cashiruuya ashrm wrijin nat wiyu tepinolat ooshrt naa dai-imogjet irig ajet ata-on jarriya jadshi-ougya ieb-shrt jarrnogjeeya paraiso-teja.
41013014	Oyat jayaluugbatya naa iebprnjin yaebrr jateglig templo-tee, nam jadshanjeuu Dioat jalirglig, oje jamojaniri bŕn naa profeta Daniel, caladawi japishicashiwaa jajaa nat jayerog leejerat. Oyat nat Judea tepinot caladwi cashicuutya wen-jaa.
41013015	Oyatya naa iteg mo-jaat oo wryulau, jashanshiquedrtya jaluuglig mooleja japinit jarrnogjee.

41013017	Cauushibiidya nat detpat pubdigot oo wryulauya, otya poi nat trriotju shrgot.
41013018	Jayaurm Dios yashan-cuutjeeya rtyrgnom.
41013019	Ebupaacashicrtya ipegjet, ebupaacashancrdiju oje Dioat wryu juiwrg quedyem dumat-patjri. Oyatya ebupaa-cashanshricrtya oje.
41013020	Dioat jashandirtuya jawuglig mowaini brr-shandiya ishijug-om. Ooshrt Dioat jashirirgya jawuglig cashrt mogwaini naa ieb cashrm nat idja-ougprnot.
41013021	Omya boi moguya yan, oola naa Cristo, o Cristola jere, jayerog yacupoiwaortya.
41013022	Cashiyugya ibagjet teeshauot, Cristola am irnogot, otyapoi nat mawaira am Dios bigshayu-jet imogot. Jadshiminrgya ibagjet ibishanju-duji, brrt ishanminrri poi cateecashaurgjeeya nat epinot. Cateecashishaurg shugya poi Dioat iougprnot.
41013023	Ooshrmda cadyauluugya yashrt, yapinrcat dumat jajuprtuju cayuglig nat iebnogprnotjin.
41013024	Oyatya ebupaacacrt quedyem, mogwainiya jashibrru yamat, yauya-shri jrbrlat ishiwrrliprn.
41013025	Oyat eashilrgya shrnoat natcrlot, jashiyarya wrijin naa ibiruug wryu-uja shrnoja.
41013026	Oyatya adshiruu am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee, ashiyugya shrnoat waujribmi-teat, ashiyugya jijogjet ishiyrgya brtbrtirig-jet.
41013027	Oyat ángeleot ashicuiya cajuicashuunogjeeya wryu-shrt wrijin nat idaougprnot yamat yrcat, yamat duucatwinot poi.
41013028	Dumat yayaujuirg jajet naa comparación pun iguera-jaa. Jayaluugbat jawan-trddig japishiyashiwaagya janaglicat wiig.
41013029	Ojeyala poi yam, jayaluugbatya naa ieb oodamog japishiyashiwaagya janaglicatwiat jayuglig naa jeiyatei. Japishiyashiwacatya ashoglig wryu mauye am Ishiyugya.
41013030	Rjeta amo yan, yauya cashiwuuliprn nat dumatwinot jajuprtuju jayaa minoglig wrijin naa oodamog.
41013031	Cashibeegya wrijin nat idbiruugot wryu-uja shrnoja, wrijin naa wryu poi, ooshrt naa ayerog yauya jashi wuuliprn.
41013032	Brr-shandit japishiwaja brlau jaliguya ashiyuu am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee, yau-poi japishicawaaliprn nat ángeleolat shrnoja irigot, yau-poi Dios Wáat japishiwaaliprn. Oowi Aii japishiwaa.
41013033	Ooshrmda yabigshayu yaujeunorg, jayaupinrg Dios, ajeiyautei ayuglig am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee, ooshrm japishiyashanwaji ayaa ayugjee.
41013034	Ishiminrgya oje jalijani naa bon inog yawaja. Janog juprduju cabeeb jabrg jaeprnot catojani. Oyat jadcui naa moye ijewe jaríajeujee jashan-ou.
