42002039	Oyat jadminrg quedyem wrijin naa Biŕriat minrg cui-jurgli jayerog bŕnwinjin-tee, cauprt Galilea-teja cayan Nazaret-teja naa María, José poi.
42002040	Oyat naa trriwai jamin ijeijet.Oyatjabigshayu poi min bicacoujet. Dioat jaibenisiarg jajuituunjee ijeijet.
42002041	Oyat wiig shitojani jaquepaat nog Jerusalén-teja jadduugjee judioot juibeeriprn jatam Pascua.
42002042	Oyat naa trriwai Jesús jalibrcadu jan doce wiig oobat, cashiinogli Jerusalén-teja ojewi idrjani wiig shitojani Pascua-shrm.
42002043	Oyat Pascua prnat cauprlat, naa trriwai Jesús jaliipag cashrt Jerusalén-tee. Yau pishicawaaliprn jaliipag cashrt nat jaquepaalat.
42002044	Jaicashag jayuglicat cajet nat ibagot uuprlot cajuibeeriprn-shrt, ooshrmda canog drg-uye itrm wryu-jet jajuprtuju jadjeulig cajrrot jewalee, pishicawaagot jewalee poi.
42002045	Oyat yau jatairirliprn naa trriwai Jesús, ooshrmda caushriprt Jerusaléna jadjeujee jajan.
42002046	Oyat ipoi wryu prnat jatairirg Jesús templo-tee, jalig cajewalee nat jajuirt Dios yerog bŕnwinjin. Jadjui brjaligu camog jajaa naa moyerog idnaglig bŕn Biblia-tee, oyat cadjarm poi jajaa.
42002047	Oyat wrijin nat jayerog-shat Jesús, jijogjeta jadyiijeu ebupishijawaag-shrm ijeijet jajaa naa Biblia, japishijawaag-shrm poi naa jetjadrm Biblia-jaa.
42002048	Oyat jadduucatu jaquepaat naa Jesús, yau japishicawaaliprn brjaligu cashimog jan caom-shrm jadduuglig. Oyat jaiin mog jan, atrri, boirigshrmjam imaminrg birat oje. Bijii-shŕm mabijeu-boglig maii-jet, am poi.
42002049	Oyat Jesús mo calat boirigshrmjam ayajeu. Yau-tejam japishiyawaaliprn anwi jashiminr naa Aiiat irirbrg an jaminrglig.
42002050	Ooshrt yau pishicawaaliprn brjamoyu jaligu naa moyerog Jesúat oodmog calat.
42002051	Oyat Jesús nog cajet Nazaret-teja, cayerog jawaorg ijeijet, ooshrt jaiinat jayeiwaag jajii-teat wrijin naa idduugprn idjuiprn poi.
42002052	Oyat Jesús taale min ijeijet, jabigshayu min ijeijet poi. Ijeijet Dioat jalugg, nat poi epinolat wrijin.
42003001	Oyat jalibrcat jan quince wiig cajriwairüca jaliglig naa Tiberio César, gobernadorota jaligbatdi Poncio Filato Judea-tee. Oyat naa Herodes cajriwairüca jalig Galilea-tee ooliwi japeewai Felipe cajriwairüca iriishog Iturea-tee, Troconita-tee poi, ooliwi naa cajriwairüg Lisanias cayan Abilinia-tee.
42003002	Ooliwi sacerdoteot jriwairügot Anás, Caifás poi. Oyat Dioat boirirg itrm moyerog jajii-tee naa Zacarías wáJuan jaligbadi brg-uu.
42003003	Oyat Juan bog wrijin rt Jordan-coo, epinot jajuirg bautismo-jaa cajii-shŕmjee capecado iyei cawaaglig, Dioat janamjeeya cashrt.
42003004	Idminrg oje idnaalauni japapera-tee naa profeta Isaíaat. Ojeri jamog, jadshijuiya boi wrri-aglig brg-uu jayaujeicon Biŕri jrirüg. Yabigshayu yaushalarg jabatyatai-jee.
42003005	Cajuijashituunrgya wrijin uubiidot oje jajuituunrlauni yaglog. Oyatya cadjashiwonr wrijin nat caishaat cajeirig brrt-shrt, oje itrmjani jairlauni ishrnja inag-jet.
42003006	Oyat cabigshayu jashalarg oje jaishalarlauni itrm drg. Oyat jadjeicon wrijin cajrirü cashiim shicatou-shrt. Oyat wrijin nat wryu tepinot jadshiruugya naa jet-Dioat cashijeicon jashrtya naa paacashicrtya capecado-shrm.
42003007	Oyat cayug Juan-dica bautisao cadjargjee nat epinot ibagot. Oyat jamog calat, yam shrpot, brrjam yacuiyu yacuutjee jashrt naa ebupaacrdiprn jijogjet yaat-narcat.
42003008	Dumat ijei yauminrg japishibiwaagjee yabigshayu yacambiarlicat, yajii-shrmat yapecado iyeyawaaglicat. Jayacupoipin bijeirig bidu Abraam jrdwata birig-shrm. Yapinrg yam, Dioat jaquedrg cadjacarnbiarglig nat jaaot Abraam jrdwata caligjee.
42003009	Dumat Dioat jajrr shiriirgya catatshut-jaa, oyat cadjashipanya wrijin nat puulot cam-rriprnotjin, cadjashipantogya cadjanamjee drr-teja.
42003010	Oyat jadrm Juan nat epinot ibagolat, bojejam biradwi ibishirr, camog jan.
42003011	Oyat Juan mog calat naa oodjalibrg icau camisa janwi jadshibrr itrm naat ood-boiruulat. Oyat naa ood-jaliibrg jawoug, janwi boi jashibrr naat ood-boiruulat jawoug.
42003012	Oyat capoiyug Juan-dica itrmnogolat impuesto mii-out gobiernoat. Camog jan, mam bijuirr, brrjam ibishirr.
42003013	Oyat Juan mog calat, palata yacupoi-out epinot-shrt jashrt naa yajriwairücat irm cashrt.
42003014	Oyat itrmnogot sodawaolat jarm bojaligu idshirg. Camog jan, bojeyajam ibishirr bidu sodawaolat. Oyat jamog calat, epinot pin yacupoi-outya cashrt, yau ishrmjet. Epinot yacupoiomrbot jaquewitep, caiyacupoi epin jequewitep. Oyat yajii-cujái jajet naa palata gobiernoat yamii-brg.
42003015	Oyat nat epinot jajeiteiyetprnodi naa Dioat oodmogprndi, cabigcashag Juan-jaa oojaligligma-cugjin Dioat icuiprn jeicateiri.
42003016	Oyat Juanat capinrg wrijin nat epinot, amjri bautisao yarg rtjetep, ooshrt jashiyugya itrm inomjri-wairüg ashrt. Ashanjeira am jasapatoot iishiwija-cugjin jashrt. Ooyala bautisao yashirm Espíritu Santo-jet, drr-jetya poi.
42003017	Jalap-Uula jadwao jet-cadjawawugyawan, cadjawawugjeeya trigo-bigot cayagot-shrt, cajuicabergjee jaot-tee wrijin jatrigo-bigot. Oyat cadjashitaiya cayagotjin drr ishantnni-teja.
42003018	Ojeri Juanat ijuirglig, oyat ibag moyerog iwairüg-jet cadjapatjrijuirg nat epinot jajet naa moyerog ijei.
42003019	Oyat Juanat jaipin jaebyu cajriwairüg Herodeat, japeiwai Felipe u jaoubrg-shrm ja-uja. Ibagjet jaebyu jaminrgshrm poi naa Herodeat.
42003020	Oyat yau Herodeat jajuiriprn Juanat, oyat ieb japatjri minrg, jadnaam Juan presoja caliiriprn-teja.
42003021	Juanat bautisao cadjargbadi nat epinot ibagot, bautisao jadrg poi Jesús. Oyat Dios japinrgbat, paraiso juiyinog.
42003022	Oyat naa Espíritu Santo jawondi shrnoat Jesús-jaa oje iitibrm wondauni, oyat itrrn moyerog yug shrnoat. Marndawi aWá yiialuugprn, jamog, ajii-jái maluuglig.
42003023	Jalibrcaduli jan trenta wiig Jesúat jajuiwrgli epinot jajuirglig. Jaicashagli José wája jaliglig, Eli jriwai.
42003024	Matat wá jalig naa Eli, Leví wá jalig Matat, Maqui wá jalig Leví, Jana wá jalig Leví, José wa jalig Jana.
42003025	Matatías wá jalig José, Amos wá jalig Matatías, Nahum wá Amos, Esli wá jalig Nahum, Nagai wá jalig Esli.
42003026	Maat wá jalig Nagai, Matatías wá jalig Maat, Semei wá jalig Matatías, José wá jalig Semei, Juda wá jalig José.
42003027	Joana wá jalig Juda, Resa wá Joana, Zorobabel wá jalig Resa, Salatiel wá Zorobabel, Neri wá Salatiel.
42003028	Melqui wá jalig Neri, Adi wá jalig Melqui, Cosam wá jalig Adi, Elmodam wá jalig Cosam, Er wa jalig Elmodam.
42003029	Josué wá jalig Er. Eliezar wá jalig Josué. Jorirn wá jalig Eliezer. Matat wá jalig Jorim.
42003030	Leví wá jalig Matat. Simeón wá jalig Leví. Juda wa jalig Simeón. José wá jalig Juda. Jonan wá jalig José. Eliaquirn wa jalig Jonan.
42003031	Melea wá jalig Eliaquim. Mainan wá jalig Melea. Matata wá jalig Mainan. Natán wá jalig Matata.
42003032	David wá jalig Natán, Isai wá jalig David. Obed wa jalig Isai, Booz wá jalig Isai. Salmón wá jalig Booz. Naasón wá jalig Salmón.
42003033	Aminadad wá jalig Naasón. Ararn wá jalig Arninadad. Esrom wá jalig Ararn. Fares wá jalig Esrom. Juda wá jalig Fares.
42003034	Jacob wá jalig Juda. Isaac wá jalig Jacob. Abraam wá jalig Isaac. Taré wá jalig Abraam. Nacor wá jalig Taré.
42003035	Serug wá jalig Nacor. Ragau wá jalig Serug. Peleg wá jalig Ragau. Heber wá jalig Peleg. Sala wá jalig Heber.
42003036	Cainan wá jalig Sala. Arfaxad wá jalig Cainán. Sem wá jalig Arfaxad. Noé wá jalig Sern. Lamec wá jalig Noé.
42003037	Matusalén wá jalig Lamec. Enoc wá jalig Matusalén, Jared wá jalig Enoc. Maalaleel wá jalig Jared. Cainan wá jalig Maalaleel.
42003038	Enós wá jalig Cainán. Set wá jalig Enos. Adán wa jalig Set. Dios wá jalig Adán.
42004001	Oyat jajuituun Jesús Espíritu Santo-jet, jauprt Jordan-shrt. Oyat Espírituat jarrnog brg-uja.
42004002	Cuarenta wryuli jalig on brg-uja, moweijinat jajeu jateejashaurglig. Yauli Jesús yeiwairiprn jaligbatdi on, oyat jabuishiig.
42004003	Oyat moweijin mog jan, Dios Wá jaligu mam, cadmauminrg ana nat jaaot.
42004004	Oyat Jesús mog jan, ojeri idnagli papera-tee bŕn cashishan-jutya an catrm-jet nat epinot. Ooshrt cashijugya wrijin Dios yerog-jet
42004005	Oyat moweijinat jarrnog wen ishrn-jaa, mogwaini jatadrg wrijin moyanot-jet wryu tepinot.
42004006	Oyat moweijin mog jan, mashirirgya cajriwairüca maligjee wrijin. Jashirirbrgya man wrijin apin ijei. Bŕn jadbrglig an, ooshrm jaquedrg jabrglig boirig jaligu ijeu jabrglig.
42004007	Mashogu mautjuiyag-jet an ijei mabrgjee an, jashibrgya man wrijin naa jet-matadrg jarnaluuglig.
42004008	Oyat Jesús mog jan, maunog ashrt mam moweijin. Ojeri idnagli papera-tee bŕn, manwi ijei mashibr majri-Dioat. Manwi imashibeebr jan wrijin-shrt.
42004009	Oyat moweijinat jarrnog Jerusalén-teja, jashog templo jupugu. Oyat jamog jan, Dios Wá jaligu mam, maulrjog naiat niti-uja.
42004010	Ojeri idnagli papera-uu bŕn, Dioat cashicuiya jaanjeleot maicajeujeeya.
42004011	Madshiwaorgya calap-jet mashiim shimatou-shrtya jáajaá.
42004012	Oyat Jesús mog moweijinat, ooli camo bŕn, imacupoiminrt oje bicashancowiprnjini jamaluugjee-cugjin Maŕri Dios bigshayu.
42004013	Oyat moweijinat jaipin quedyem wrijin jateejashaur-sbuuyu Jesús, jauprt jashrt ata-on boi wryulauya-shri.
42004014	Oyat Jesús uprt Galilea-teja, jawairüg Espíritu Santo-jet. Oyat cayaad ijeijet Jesús-jaa nat epinot wrijin moyanot Galilea-tee.
42004015	Oyat Jesúat eajuirg sinagoga-tee moyanot tojani. Oyat jainot shicapin ijeijet wrijin.
42004016	Oyat Jesús nog Nazaret-teja jabigshugprnali. Oyat boi wryulau jijacaliiriprn-tee jaluug sinagoga-tee jajan ojewi idminrlauni moyan tojani. Oyat Jesús shog jadleegjee idnagprndi papera-tee.
42004017	Oyat jadyig jadleegjee naa profeta Isaíaat inaagprndi. Oyat Jesúat jayiig quedyem naa papera, cadjatairirg nat versiculoot Isaíaat inagprnodi.
42004018	Ojeri jamo naa iieeglig, Biŕri Espíritu lig ajaa, adeui jai-apinjee naa moyerog ijei uubiidolat. Adeui cabigshayu ajeiconjee nat jiishŕmot, jai-apinjee naa moyerog jet-cadashiuwa moweijinat ijiiprnotjin, jalirg idduugjee nat bigmolat, cadashiujee jashrt naa jalirr ebupaacacrdig,
42004019	adeui jalirgjee japishicawaaglig jaminyulicat Biŕri bigye.
42004020	Oyat Jesúat jashripau naa papera jaujashriprtrbrg jan naa sinagoga shijeweat, oyat jateg banco-jaa. Oyat jijogjet jadju-yiijeu Jesús nat sinagoga tepinolat wrijin.
42004021	Oyat Jesús mog calat, dumatjaminocatjayaa naa idnagprndi bŕn jayaluugjee.
42004022	Oyat cayaad ijeijet Jesús-jaa wrijin, caom jarca jashrm naa moyerog ijei iyrg jacooleat. Oyat cayaad caaleat, José wá shandit tewrnjam naa Jesús.
42004023	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jai-ashag yamog shirigya an, mam mowrnr, mamawrndig maaleat. Wrijin naa ibijuiprn jamaminrglig Capernaum-tee jamauminrgya poi nam mayan-tee.
42004024	Oyat Jesús shri-rnog calat, rjeta yapinrg, natjri profetaot, yau cayan couolat carg-brrliprn cayan-tee.
42004025	Yashipinrg yam rjet, cabagli nat motjin-rriprnot Israel-tee jaligbadi jajan naa Elias. Yauli wau lrrliprn ipoi wiig-jet seis jrbot poi. Buipaacacrdi jijogjet wrijin nat Israel tepinolat.
42004026	Oyat Dioat jashancui calica Elias. Oowi idcuiyugli jalica naa bon-rriprnjin irigprndi Sarepta-tee inagjetwi moyan Sidón-shrt.
42004027	Oyat cabagli jaacaiprnotjin Israel-tee jaligbadi on naa profeta Eliséo, ooshrt boi jashanjeicondi itrrnu capeiu. Jatrmdiwi idjeicon naa Siriaatwin jatam Naamán.
42004028	Oyat cannn Jesús caluuglig wrijin nat sinagoga tepinot jadjuibat naa moyerog oodjamog calat.
42004029	Oyat cajuimig nat epinot, jadnarnjee Jesús cayan-teat, jadrrnog jaddrrgjee wen-jaat cayan dig-shrm wen-jaa. Jadjeu Jesús canarndig wen juicruye jalrg monoja.
42004030	Oyat Jesús nog cashrt cajewaleyc.
42004031	Oyat Jesús nog Capemaum-teja, naa moyan Galilea-tee. Omdi cadjajuir epinot naa wryu jijacaliiriprn-tee.
42004032	Oyat cajii-jái jadjuirig naa moyerog jet-cadjajuirg, jayaad-shrm ishalalig-jet oje bicacouni naa Jesús.
42004033	Omdi boiri itrm bon ood-demonio lig jajii-tee, oyat jawrr-ág jijogjet.
42004034	Jamog, maucuprt bishrt mam Jesús Nasaret-atwin. Boirig irnajeu bijet. Mayuijam bidmanamjee. Mapishiawaagwi boirig-jaligu mam, oolawi mam naa ijei iyugprn Dios-licat.
42004035	Oyat Jesúat on-jadrg naa mojii iebprnjin. Jamog jan, macupoiyaat, mauyrg jashrt naa bon. Oyat naa mojii iebprnjin jadirg jalrgjee naa bon niti-uja cajewalee wrijin. Oyat jayrg jashrt, ieb jashanshri-minrg jan.
42004036	Jadduugbat jajeiricat naa bon, caom Jesús rca wrijin, cayaad caaleat, boirig moyerog-wrnjam naa. Jijogjet cadjacuinog nat mojii iebnogprnotjin, oyat cayrg epinot-shrt.
42004037	Oyat cayaad Jesús-jaa wrijin epinot moyan-tojani Galilea-tee.
42004038	Oyat Jesús nog sinagoga-teat, jaluug Simón ot-tee. Naa Simón Pedro hitan jataap ishiyu-jet jijogjet. Oyat Jesús carm jadjeiconjee.
42004039	Oyat Jesúat jayiijeu jacuinog jashrt naa shiyu. Oyat ishiyuat janarnnog. Oowi jajuimiglig ijeijet, cawoug jarrnogjee.
42004040	Oyat yamat duucadu, cadcarrnog Jesü-lica nat itaabot ishiyujet wrijin. Oyat jalap jalirg cajaa catojani, cadjajeicon ishiyu-shrt.
42004041	Cayrgli poi ibagot demonioot epinot-shrt. Cawrr-ág camog, mamdawi Dios Wá. Oyat Jesúat on-carg, cadjashandirt cayaadig japishicawaag-shrm Dioat icuiprna jaliglig.
42004042	Oyat jaiwryucadu Jesús, janog itrmjetwi cayan-shrt epinrripayeca. Oyat nat epinot nog jadjeujee, oyat caminog jalica. Jaiwincashog jashan-notjee cashrt.
42004043	Oyat Jesús mog calat, anwi jaiashipin naa moyerog ijei Dioat mojuibeeriprn-jaa brrt moyan-tepinot poi. Adcui nan jayerog iapinjee.
42004044	Oyat Jesús bog wrijin Galilea-tee, epinot jajuirgjee wrijin sinagoga-tee.
42005001	Oyat boi wryulau Jesús shogbadi rt Genesaret coo, ibagjet epinot yug jalica. Jadnarg jaicapiirei jayerog cajuijee.
42005002	Oyat Jesúat caluu icauot jáot wrg-coo rri-rriot cacomyrcat já-teat nat yrri-rriot cayou cashrrgjee.
42005003	Oyat Jesús luug itrm já ipeg-teja Simón pin, oyat jadjeu jajrri-catounoglig jugtat-shrt. Oyat Jesús teg ja ipeg-tee cadjajuirgjee jayat nat ibagot epinot.
42005004	Oyat Jesúat epinot juirg quedyem jamog Simónat, jamaurrnog ma-já jrn-shirig yayou yaunam rt-teja yrriot yaougjee.
42005005	Oyat Simón mog jan, mam Bijuirr, bicugmaap shai-jet, yaula boi biouliprn biyou-tee. Dumat bidmacui-shrm jashishri-nam ayou oje mamojani.
42005006	Oyat idminrgbat oje Jesús mojani calat, ibagjeta yrriot caoug, oyat jajuituun naa cayou jadpondei-shug.
42005007	Oyat cadcaág cajrrot calap-jet jrriwag-trmot cajrrja cadcarryugjee. Oyat cayug juicatuunrgjee icau já yrriot-jet, cajmrnonshug cabag-shrm yrriot.
42005008	Oyat Simón Pedroat jaluugbat naa Jesúat irninrg jashoobrg jautjuiyag-jet jan. Jamog jan, mam Aŕri, jajeirawi manogu ashrt, iebprnjinda am.
42005009	Ojeri jamog jaorn-shrm Jesús rca jijogjet, wrijin jajetwinot poi cadcaluugbat nat ibagot yrriot idcaougot.
42005010	Nat Zebedeo trriot Jacobo, Juan poi, capoi-om Jesús rca calig-shrm Simón-jet cayou jawrryrgbat. Oyat Jesús mog Sirnónat, macupoiom, durnatya mot mashimaabr an.
42005011	Cyat cadcawrryrg quedyern nat icauot jáot jug-jaa, eadeanamnog wrijin canogjee Jesús prna.
42005012	Oyat Jesús ligbat boi moyan-tee, jayug jalica boi jacaiprnjin wrijin jajayeicani. Jashog jautjuiyag-jet Jesúat, jadrrn ishiigjet, mam Aŕri, jamajeuu amalirglig jaapi-rrijot jamog.
42005013	Oyat Jesúat jalapdirg jajaa jamog, jajeu majaapi-rririg. Jadyaadbatju Jesús oowi jajaaprnot iyoobdig jashrt naa jaacaiprnjin.
42005014	Oyat Jesúat japinrg jaijapin-shrt brrlat jajaa naa idminrg. Jamog jan, maunocat cadmatadrgjee sacerdoteot maduugjee, oyat ofrenda maubrg Dioat oje Moisés mojaniri madjeicon-shrm mapishicawaagjee majeiricat nat epinolat.
42005015	Oyat janomjri-bajalig jai-capindig Jesús moyan tojani. Oyat ibagjet epinolat cajuiberg Jesús-lica jayerog cajuijee, ishiyu janamjee poi cashrt.
42005016	Oyat Jesús uprt cashrt epin-rripayeca, omdi Dios japinrg.
42005017	Boi wryulau Jesúat epinot juirgbadi itrmnogot fariseot teg banco-jaa, oodipoi Moisés yerog juirt, nat iyugprnot wrijin moyanteat Galilea-teat, Judea-teat poi, Jerusalén-teat poi. Oyat jijogjet Dios bigshayu lig jajii-tee cadjajeiconjee nat wrrnoligot.
42005018	Oyat caminyucat on itrmnogot mot, jadrryug itrm ishanboiprnjin caan-uu. Jadjeu jaduugrglig mooleja Jesúat jaluugjee.
42005019	Oyat caacashan-quedrt caluuglig mooleja cabag-shrm epinot. Oyat cajon mojopocat jajuicayigjee mojopog, oira jadwonr ishanboiprnjin mooleja epinot jewaleja Jesúat jaluugjee.
42005020	Jesúat caluugbat brjaligu cajii calirglig jajaa, jamog jan naa ishanboiprnjin, mam bon, janam mashrt naa ieb imaminrglig.
42005021	Oyat nat inaat, fariseoot poi, cabigcashag cajii-teat, boirigwrnjam naa bon, ieb jaminrg Dioat jajet naa moyerog oodjamog. Boirig-shamdit jaquedrr jadnamdig bishrt naa ieb ibiminrg. Jatrmwi Dios jaquedrr.
42005022	Jesúat japishiwaag cabigshayu ooshrm jamog calat, boirigshrmjam yabigyashag iebjet yajii-teat.
42005023	Japajijam arnogu mapecado ashinam, o amogu majuicumig maubog.
42005024	Ooshrmda yatadrg jayaluugjee jadquedrg pecado janarndig wryu-tee naa Iminyrcadi wryu jaluugjee. Oyat Jesús mog jan naa ishanboiprnjinat, mapinrg majuicumig, mapuuyu mauwao manogjee maot-teja.
42005025	Oowi jajuimiglig jadduugjee wrijin, japuuyu jawao janog jaotteja. Janogbat ijei jabrg Dioat.
42005026	Oyat jijogjet jadduug wrijin nat epinot, ijei icapin Dioat. Caom ipegjet Jesús rca, carnog, shiruu wryula jabiruuwi naa brrt ishanminrri.
42005027	Jadminrg quedyern Jesúat oiirig, janog cashrt. Oyat jad-duug itrm bon palaata oobrr qobiemoat jatam Mateo Leví, jateg impuesto ot-tee naa bon. Oyat Jesús mog jan, mauyug aprna.
42005028	Oyat jajuimig naa Leví, jadnamnog wrijin naa jalapwoo, jajrrot poi, janogjee Jesús prna.
42005029	Oyat naa bon jadminrg eajuicaberliprn iyiig Jesús-shrm. Omda cateeri mesa-coo ibagot nat impuesto mii outprnot, brrt epinot poi.
42005030	Oyat nat fariseoot, inaat poi, cayaad Jesúat ijuirgprnolat. Carnog calat, boirigshrmjam yayewai cajet nat impuesto mii outprnot, iebnogprnotjin-jet poi.
42005031	Oyat Jesús mog calat, natjri wrrno-rriot mowrrnr cashanjeu. Ooshrt nat wrrnoligot jadjeu mowrrnr.
42005032	Ashanyut nan cadaáyugjee ijeinogot. Ooshrt ayug cadaáyugjee nat iebnogprnotjin cajii shŕmjee capecado iyecawaaglig.
42005033	Oyat carnog Jesúat, boirigshrmjam cayeishanwayi ibagjet nat Juanat ijuirgprnot Dios capinrgjee, ootpoi nat fariseoolat ijuirgprnot. Ooshrt nat idmajuirgprnot cayewai wryu shitojani, puncampog cawóg poi.
42005034	Oyat Jesús mog calat, cadyalirrijam cayeshanwaijee nat iyugprnot casamiento-shrm moyeiwairiprn-tee jaligbatju cajet naa caájaprn.
42005035	Ooshrt boi wryulauya jadshioug cashrt naa caájaprn, oyemyala cayeshishanpoiwai.
42005036	Oyat itrm comparación ijapin calat Jesúat. Jamog calat, brrshandit jaijooyaa jayuiot brn-winjin jajuju-jet brjashirii jad-ebrgu jayuiot juju.
42005037	Jadshandirt pun-campog juju jaot bŕnwinjin-tee idminrgprn oveja pig-jet brjashirii jabamnogu jaot bŕnwinjin. Oyat jashinog jaot-shrt naa pun-campog, oyat jashiebya poi jaotjin.
42005038	Ooshrt jadirg puncampog juju jaot juju-tee jajeijeeya naa puncampog jaot poi.
42005039	Naajri jawócoo vino bŕnwinjin jadshanjeu jadwóglig vino juju ooshrm, janomjri-jeirigla naa vino bŕnwinjin jamog.
42006001	Oyat boi wryu jijacaliiriprn-tee Jesúat jabatshiwug cajrmca. Oyat idjajuirgprnolat trigoot woi cawouca, cabigot caoug cayag-shrt calap-jet.
42006002	Oyat itrrnnogot fariseoot mog Jesúat, boirigshrrnjam iyabeeb jatee naa wryu iwincashoglig.
42006003	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayashanlee-tejam brjaliguli Davirat irgli bŕn jabui-shigbadi jajetwinot-jet.
42006004	David nog Dios ot-teja, an jawao jadwougjee naa an idbrgprn Dioat. Oyat jadpoibrg calat nat jajetwinolat naa an sacerdoteot pin caaleot pin.
42006005	Oyat Jesús shri-mog calat, oowi jijacaliiriprn jriwairüg poi naa Iminyrgli wryu jaluugjee.
42006006	Oyat wryu jijacaliiriprn-tee, Jesús Iuug sinagoga-tee epinot jajuirgjee. Ornda boiri itrrn bon jaiap jataa-rrí jawireat.
42006007	Oyat nat inaat, fariseoot poi, Jesús cayiijeu boyawrn jadjeicon-shirig wryu jijacaliiriprn-tee jadjeu-shrm jai-caepindig idrninrgu oje.
42006008	Jesúat japishiwaag cabigshayu, oyat jamog jan naa lap jataarriprnjin, majuicumig mashogjee nam bijewalee. Oyat jajuimig jashogjee cajewalee.
42006009	Oyat Jesús mog nat irigolat on, dumat yashirrn itrm moyerog-jet. Boirigjam iiquedrg jaiminrglig wryu jijamoliiriprn-tee, ijei ishiminrrijam o ieb ishirninrrijam. Jaiquedrrijam caijeicondig epinot o cairirg jarrijee.
42006010	Oyat Jesúat cayiijeu wrijin nat irigot on, oyat jamog naa bonat, malap mauwrryrg. Oyat naa bon idminrg oje Jesús mojani jan, oyat jaiap ijeia.
42006011	Oyat canon jijogjet nat fariseoot, cayaad ieb-jet Jesús-jaa ieb caminrgjee jan.
42006012	Oyat Jesús nog wen-jaa Jaii-Dios japinrgjee. Itrm shaibrrla jalig on Dios japinrgjee.
42006013	Oyat jaiwryucatulig Jesús cadjaág jabea idjajuirgprnot capishiwaag idjacuiprnota caliglig idjajuirgprnot, oyat cadjaoug capet doce itogot. Oyat epinolat capishiwaag idjacuiprnota caliglig.
42006014	Jesúat jaoug naa Simón tam jaminrgprndi Pedro, japewai Andrés poi, oyat Jacobo, Juan poi, Felipe poi, Bartolomé poi.
42006015	Oyat Mateo jaág, Tomás poi, Alfeo poi. Jacobo poi, Simón jatam poi Zelote.
42006016	Oyat jadoug naa Jacobo wá Judas, oyat Judas Iscariote poi, naa Jesús brrnprn jabalolat ijaanjet.
42006017	Oyat Jesús uprt wen-jaat idjajuirgprnot jet. Oyat jalig cajet yee-uu cajriat poi nat ibagot epinot iyugot wrijin Judea-teat, Jerusalén-teat poi, nat-poi rt-coo irigot moyan Tiro-tee, Sidon-tee poi. Cayug jadjuijee Jesús yerog cadjajeiconjee ishiyu-shrt poi.
42006018	Oyat Jesiíat cajeicon poi nat ebupaacrlot mojii iebprnjin-jet.
42006019	Oyat wrijin nat epinot ibagot jadjeu calap calirglig Jesús-jaa jabigshayu ijei caougjee. Oyat jawairüyu jayrg jashrt cadjajeiconjee ishiyu-shrt wrijin.
42006020	Oyat Jesúat jajuiyag wrryrg cadjaluugjee idjajuirgprnot, jamog calat, jii-jáiota yam uubiidot yapina jashirig-shrm naa Dioat cajuiberliprn jaepinota yaligjee.
42006021	Jii-jáiota yam bui-shigot Dios bigshayu-shrm, ooshrm yajuishituunya ijeijet. Jii-jáiota yam iquigot naa wryu-tee, ooshrm Dioat yajii-shijairgya.
42006022	Yajii-shijáiya yaeb caluugbatya, yadnambatya cashrt poi. Yajii-shijáiya yadmrnbatya miirriprnotjin camogbatya poi yajaa ashrm arn Iyrgli wryu aluugjee.
42006023	Yayaujáiyeg jijogjet, yabigrriculig ijeijet oolau wryu ieb carninrgya yan ashrm, ooshrm ibagjet ijei shiriibrgya yan shrnoja. Ooshrm ojeri poi cajoornolat ieb-minrgli calat nat Dios yerog shipinidi brn.
42006024	Oyat yajii shishrmya yam wooligot jaliibrg-shrm yan wrijin jet-yayajáirg yaaleat naa wryu-tee.
42006025	Yajii shishrmya yam teetogot jajet naa iyajeu, ooshrm boi wryulauya yabui shishii. Yajii shishrmya yam iyoiot dumat, ooshrm boi wryulauya yashiquigya yajii shŕm-shrmya.
42006026	Yajii shishrmya yam cayaadbatya yajaa ijeijet nat wryu tepinolat, ooshrm ojeri poi ijeijet cayaadig yaloomot cajaa nat mawaiodi moweijin bigshayu-jet.
42006027	Dumat yashipinrg yam jajuiyut ayerog, janwi cayii yashiruu yabalot. Ijei yaurninrg nat yaeb dujulat.
42006028	Jayaujeu ijei yuglig calica nat jajewet ieb yuglig yalica. Dios yaurm cajaa nat yajii shrrnrt yaliglig.
42006029	Naa macou paiat, jarnaulirg jadpaijee itrm-balat. Oyat naa jajewe jadouglig mashrt maruana jarnaulirg poi jan macamisa.
42006030	Jamaulirbrg calat naa idjeu nat jarrmrlat mashrt, oyat naajri japrestaurm mashrt mapin jamacupoi-rm jaujaprtrgjee man.
42006031	Yaurninrg brrlat oje jamajeulauni idminrglig man.
42006032	Oodjatepdig yii-yaiuugot nat yayii-rujutep, ijei yaminrrijam brrt-shrt. Nat iebnogprnotjin cayii caluug poi nat cayii-rujut.
42006033	Ijei yateminrgu nat ijei minrrlat yan, ijei yaminrrijam brrt-shrt. Ojera poi idminrglig nat iebnogprnotjinolat.
42006034	Jayaliirgu jadrrnogligju yapin nat jaushiprtrlat yan, ijei yarninrrijarn brrt-shrtjamo. Nat iebnogprnotjin jadirg poi cajrrolat capin caprestaurglig jajeicatei-shrm jaucaprtrg-shirig calat regalo-jet poi.
42006035	Ooshrt yam, cayii yauluug yabalolat, ijei yauminrbrg calat. Jayaulirg jadrrnogjee yalapwoo jajeiyacupoitei jaucaprtrgjee yan regalo-jet. Oyat jashiribrgya yan ijei ibagjet, oyatya jatrriota yashirii naa Dios ipeg wrijin shrt, ooshrm ijei jaminrg calat nat ijeinogot iebnogprnotjin poi.
42006036	Brrt yauluug uubiidjet oje yauubiid jaluulauni naa Yaii shrnoja iricat.
42006037	Caimacupoi-epin brrt iebjet brjashirii Dioat yai-epinu poi. Macupoimot brrt-jaa jajeirawi carmdrglig Dios-shrt brjashirii yaurmdrg ashrt Dios mogu yan. Cadyaujeicon yajet brrt epinot, oyatya Dioat yashipoijeicon jajet.
42006038	Jayaubrg brrlat naa boiruud calica, oyatya Dioat jashibrrya yan inomjri-bajalig jashrt naa iyabrg calat oje jajuiituunrlauni itrm saco tai-imogjet. Oje iyaminrbrlauni brrlat, ojeya poiwi idminrgshirig yan brrlat.
42006039	Oyat itrm comparación iijapin Jesúat jet-japishicawaaca. Ojeri jamog, jadquedrrijam bigrriprnjinat jarrnogu itrm bigrriprnjin drguye. Cashishandr-tewrnjam nat icauot bigrriprnotjin wadyeg-teja.
42006040	Naajri idjuirgprn yau jajeiriprn jashrt naa jajuirrprn, ooshrt jadquedrg quedyem jajajuirglig jajet naa jajuirr ebupishijashiwaagya ojebr jalijani.
42006041	Boirigshrmjam jamaluug majrr bigterüg ishŕm jamashanquedrtshicom jamaluulig mabigterüg ipeg.
42006042	Boirigshrmjam mamog majrrat, ajrr jamaulirg jaougjee mashrt mabigterüg ishrmwi, jalig-shicom mabigterüg ipeg. Mam oiteprnog prnjin, jamauoug-jurg mabigterüg ipeg mabig-shrt imaluugjee ijeijet jamaougjeeya majrr bigterüg ishrmwi.
42006043	Boiruud itrm pun ijei cabot ebnog. Boi poiruud itrm pun ieb cabot jeinog.
42006044	Cacabot-jaala capishiiwaa nat puulot. Caishanquedrt cadiougu mowouca uulot caobt iebnogot. Caishanquedrt poi cadiougu mri cabot pun ieb-shrt.
42006045	Naa bon ijei, moyerog ijei jayrrg jacooleat jabigshayu juituunshrm ijeijet. Oyat naa bon iebprnjin jayaad moyerog iebprnjin-jet jabigshayu juituun-shrm iebjet. Jayrg jacooleye naa jet-jajuituun jabigshayu.
42006046	Boirigshrmjam, Aŕri Aŕri, yamog an jayashanminrt-shicom oje amojani yan.
42006047	Yashipinrgya jayajuijee brjaliyu jaliguya naa iyug jadjuijee ayerog. Oyatya idshirninr oje amojani.
42006048	Oje jalijani naa jaot-minrr jáa-jaá jajrijashagjee tai-imogjet. Oyat jawaabatu naa rt ipeg, jiim poi yug jijogjet jajrijayairg naa mo, ooshrt yau jajrirairiprn jashog-shrm tai-imogjet jáa-jaá.
42006049	Oyat naajri ayerog cug-juiyu ojewitep, naa ishanminrri oje amojani, ojera jatepdi naa jaot-minrrni ebushiwapdiprnu. Oyat rrlat jayairg naa mo jijogjet, oyat jalrg mogwaini, jaeb wrijin.
42007001	Jayaad quedyemdi Jesús nat jajuiyutprnot janog Capernaurnteja.
42007002	Ornda boi riiri sodawaot jriwairüg jetwin yii-jaluugprn, yowanjinwiat ishiyu-jet jarri-shucat.
42007003	Oyat naa capitán jadjuibat Jesús iinot, cadjacuinog jalica itrmnogot quepaat judioot jadrrn jayugjee Jesús jadjeiconbrgjee jan jajetwin.
42007004	Oyat caminocadu Jesús-lica jadnn ishiigjet, ijeira naa bon, camog Jesúat. Ijei mauminrbrg jan naa idjeu majet,
42007005	ooshrm cayii jaluug biepinot. Oolawi jaminrg cuiyu birat bijuibeeriprn sinagoga.
42007006	Oyat Jesús nog cajet, jadnacadu capitán ot cadjacuinog jaepinot Jesús-lica camogjee jan, Aŕri macupoiyut alica ooshrm ijei shandita arn maluugjee-cugjin aot-teja.
42007007	Ashanyut malica ooshrm bon ijei shandita am. Ooshrt itrm moyerog imaupin jajeijeiya naa ajetwin.
42007008	Calig ajriwairügot acuiyut am, oyat calig poiasodawaot idacuiot. Jacuibat itrm oowi janoglig, oyat amogbat itrrnat mauyug alica oowi jayuglig alica. Oyat amogbat ajetwinat jamauminrgbrg an naa, oowi jadrninrglig an.
42007009	Jesúat jajuibat jayerog jayejawaag ijeijet naa capitán. Oyat cadjaluug nat epinot iyugot japrna, jamog calat, rjeta amo yan, boi ashantairirt capeiu nat israelot jajii-rirr ajaa ijeijet oje jalijani naa capitán y a waatwin.
42007010	Oyat nat capitanat icuiprnot cauprladu mooleja jadtairirg jacornjeiyat naa capitán jetwin.
42007011	Oyat boi wryulau Jesús nog moyan-teja jatam Nain. Oodwi jajet nat idjajuirgprnot, ibagot epinot poi.
42007012	Jaminocaduli inagjet moyan-shrí, Jesúat jaluug jadrryuglig itrm irriprnjin jadnamjee. Jatrmdiwi jatrri nan bonjin-rriprnjin, oyat canog ibagot jaiinjin-jet jayan couot.
42007013	Oyat Biŕriat uubiidjet jadduug naa den, jamog jan, macupoiquit.
42007014	Oyat Jesúat janaarg naa irriprnjin idrryug, jalap jalirg jaotjaa, oyat yri cashoolrglig nat jarryut naa irriprnjin. Oyat Jesús mo jan naa irriprnjinat, mam trriwaiju, ashimog man majuicumig.
42007015	Oyat naa irriprnjin oowi jajuimiglig, jajuijawig jayaadig. Oyat Jesúat jalirbrcat jaiinat.
42007016	Oyat caom jijogjet wrijin nat epinot, ijei cabrg Dioat, camog, itrm profeta iwairüg imin bijewalee. Dios cadjaluuyugjee nat jaepinot.
42007017	Oyat jadjui Jesús iinot wrijin Judea-teja jajuijamirglig naa irriprnjin.
42007018	Oyat nat Juanat ijuirgprnot jaicapin jan naa-jaa Jesúat iminrg. Oyat Juanat caág jalica icauot idjajuirgprnot.
42007019	Cadjacuinog Jesús-lica jadrmnogjee brr-jaligu. Camog Jesúat, mam-tejarn Dioat icuiprn jeibitei mayuglig, o jajeibishiteijamju boi yugjee-shri mashrt.
42007020	Oyat caminocadu Jesús-lica nat mot, camog jan, Juan Bautistaat bicui malica mabinnjee boirig jaligu mam. Mam-tejarn jeibitei mayuglig o jajeibishiteijamju jayuglig boi-shri.
42007021	Oyat oo wryu-tee Jesúat cajeicon ibagjet epinot. Jadnam cashrt ishiyu, motapyu poi, mojiiot iebnogprnotjin poi, oyat cadjalirg cabigligjee bigrriprnotjin ibagot.
42007022	Oyat Jesús mo calat, yaucuprt Juan-dica, jayapinrgjee jajaa naa iyaluug, iyajuiprn poi. Cabiglicat nat bigrriprnotjindi, caboocat nat ishanboiprnotjindi, cajaaprn-rriat nat jaacaiprnotjindi, idjuiatpeg nat butogprroladi, cajuucat nat irriprnotjindi. Oyat nat uubiidprnotjin jadquedreat jadjuirig naa moyerog jet-moijeicon ieb-shrt.
42007023	Oyat jajii shijáiya naa bigshayu shanshaali ashrt.
42007024	Oyat cauprt quedyem nat Juanat icuiprnot, Jesús yaad Juanjaa nat epinolat. Jamog calat, boirigjam iyaluunog brg-uja. Jayaluunoijam jiimat jajuudig shunta.
42007025	Boirigjam iyaluunog jajan. Oo-tejam iyaluunog itrm bon ood-jalibrg jawoo miibag, nat cajáirt caaleot-tep.
42007026	Oyat boirigjam iyuluunog. Jayaluunoijam itrm profeta. Rcaji yapinrg, profeta rjetwinda jaliglig naa Juan Dios bigshayu-jet. Janomjri-jeirig wrijin profetaot-shrt naa Juan.
42007027	Oolawi naa Juan-jaa canagli capapera-uu bŕn. Ojeri camog, omda boi ashicuiya mainot shipinija majuprta, majrirü jajeiconjeeya man.
42007028	Yapinrg yam, boiruuda itrmu profeta inomjri-jei Juan Bautistashrt capei nat iminyrgot wryu-tee. Ooshrt janomjri-jeirig Juan-shrt naa caprnatwin capei nat Dioat mojuiberliprn tepinot.
42007029	Jadjuibat Jesús yerog nat epinot, camog wrijin, ijeira naa Dios. Ojeri poi camog nat impuesto mii-outprnot.
42007030	Oyat nat fariseoot, nat Moisés yerog juirtdi poi, nat bautisao idjashanrriodi Juanat, jarnii carrirgtep naa Dioat ijeu jaminrglig calat.
42007031	Oyat Birri mog calat, boirignijam calig nat epinot dumatwinot, boirignijam calii,
42007032	Ojera trrijulotni calii itegot wad-uu cajrrot ájat, camog, ibishiprrbrg yan oyat yashanwaat, ibishicantarg yan mojii shŕmrr oyat yashanquit.
42007033	Bŕn Juan Bautista yugli yalica, yau an jawouliprn, yau poi pun-campog jawógliprn. Oyat camog jajaa, demonio lig jajii-tee jayeishanwai-shrm.
42007034	Oyat ayug am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee, ayewai, pun-campog awóg poi. Oyat camog ajaa, jayacaluug naa iyewaiprnjin, puncampog nat wócooprnjin poi. Oyat cajrrja cadjarg impuesto miiout, iebnogprnotjin poi.
42007035	Oje jaddirg jabiruugjee cabigshayu catojani jajet naa idminrg.
42007036	Oyat itrm fariseoat Jesús ág jayewaijee jajet. Oyat Jesús nog fariseo ot-teja jateg mesa coo.
42007037	Oyat itrm den iebprnjin moyan-tee japishijawaag Jesús liglig fariseo ot-tee mesa-coo. Oyat jadrryug aceite ishicoi jaot-tee idrninrgprn alabastrocon.
42007038	Oyat jateerütog Jesús shiim-coo jaquiiteg. Jesús shiim jatrrurg jabigpog-jet, oyat jadmri jajuu-jet. Oyat jashiim jabesarg, oyat ishicoi jawui jashiim-jaa.
42007039	Oyat naa fariseo Jesús ájaprndi jaot-teja, jadduugbat brjaligu idrg naa denat jamog jajii-teat, profeta jaligu naa bon Jesús japishijashiwaagya boirigprnjin jaligu naa den jashiim waorrli ooshrm iebprnjinajalig naa den.
42007040	Oyat Jesús mog fariseoat, mam Simón, jajeu jaiapindig man itrm moyerog. Oyat jamog naa fariseo, amaupinrg ijuijet mam Bijuirr.
42007041	Oyat Jesús mog jan, cacau mot jarnii-rrirt itrm jabrm palata. Itrmat jamii-rrirg quiniento pesos, itrmat jamii-rrirg sincuenta pesos.
42007042	Oyat boiruud jet-jamií cabrg, oyat naa palata brmprn calat cacuenta janam cashrt nat icauot. Dumat amaupinrg, brrjaligu capei yii janomjri-ruug ibaajet naa cacuenta namaat;.
42007043	Oyat Simón mog Jesúat, oola yii janomjri-ruug naa cuenta janam jashrt ibagjet. Oyat Jesús mog jan, rjeta naa oodmamog.
42007044	Oyat Jesúat jajewug naa den, jamog Simónat, jamacaluug naa den. Aluugbat maot-teja yau rt mabrrliprn an ashiim ashrgjee, ooshrt naa den ashiim jashrg jabigpog-jet, oyat jadmri ashrt jajuujet.
42007045	Yau amabesarliprn am, ooshrt naa den yau jajaapdiprn ashiim jabesargli aluugbatdi maot-teja.
42007046	Yau aceite malirliprn ajuiyag-jaa, ooshrt naa den aceite ishicoi jawui ashum-jaa.
42007047	Ooshrmda mapinrg, janam jashrt japecado ibag naa den, ooshrm ayii jaluug ipegjet. Ooshrt naa pecado anam jashrt iyaiwi. jashŕm poi ayii jaluuglig.
42007048	Oyat Jesús mog naa denat, janam mashrt naa ieb imaminrgli.
42007049	Oyat nat irigot Jesu-jet mesa coo, cayaad caaleat, boirigwrnjam naa jadquedrr epinot pecado janamdig cashrt.
42007050	Oyat Jesús mog naa denat, majii málircat ajaa, ooshrmda majeicon ebupaamacrt-shrtya mapecado-shrm. Maunog mabigrriricatjee.
42008001	Oyat Jesús bog moyanot ibagot ipeinogot ishrmnogot-teja poi epinot jajuirgjee. Cadjapinrg boje-jaligu Dioat cajuiberg nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee. Nat idjajuirgprnot doce itogot canogjajet.
42008002	Capoinog Jesús jet itrmnogot detpat, nat shrt-mojii iebnogprnotjin janamprnot, ishiyu poi. Itrm capei oowi María, jatam poi Magdalena, naa-shrt cayrgli siete demonioot.
42008003	Janog poi cajet naa Juana, ja-u naa Herodes jetwin jatam Chusa, oyat Susana poi, cabagli poi brrt. Jajrrja jadrg Jesús cawoug-jet caminrg canogbat drg-uu.
42008004	Oyat cayug Jesú-lica ibagot epinot wrijin moyan-teat, oyat jai-japinrg calat itrm comparasión jet-japishicawaaca.
42008005	Jesús mog calat, itrm ijrmr nog idjrmjee. Oyat idjrmadu calrg jashrt mojrmcabigot drg-uu. Oyat epinolat catagyeg, oyat wiibot yug cadcawougjee.
42008006	Oyat itrmnogot mojrmca bigot lrg jaamoluculee. Oyat carninyrcat quedyem, oowi carririg jayai-shrm niti-jamo.
42008007	Oyat itrmnogot lrg ebushimag-uu oyat yoot min cajaa caijamai.
42008008	Oyat itrmnogot lrg niti ijeitee. Oyat camin ijeijet, oyat cacamdig. Itrmnogot mojrmca sien jacam-tog. Jayaad-quedyem Jesús jarnog jijogjet, naajri butoglig jet-idjui, janwi ayerog jashijui.
42008009	Oyat nat Jesúat ijuirgprnot jadrm bojaliyu jaligu naa comparasión jet-cadjajuirg.
42008010	Oyat Jesús mog calat, Dioat jaliirg pishiyawaagjee naa moyerog ebushijajeuliprn-jaa ijajaandi cashrt bŕn. Ooshrt nat brrt epinot cadajuirg comparasion-jet, iduugjee cabig-jet ooshrt yau pishicawaaliprn boirig jaligu idduug. Idjui cabutog-jet ooshrt yau japishicawaaliprn brjaliyu jaligu naa idjui.
42008011	Ojaliyula naa comparasión jet-cadajuirg. Dios yerogla naa mojrmca bigot.
42008012	Naajri ilrg drg-uu ooda nat ayerog cug-juiyut ojewitep. Oyat jayug naa moweijin jad-ougjee cajii-teat naa moyerog jadshanwaortjee, cadajeicon-shrt ieb-shrt.
42008013	Nat mojrmca bigot ilrgot jaarnoluculee, ojera caliitep nat moyerog juiyut ijáijet-cug. Ojera calii oje mojrmca tat-shut rriprnjini jadshandirt jamindig cajii-tee naa moyerog, oyat ieb yugbat calica oowi jadnamnoglig.
42008014	Oyat naa mojrmca bigot ilrgot uutjulee, ojera catepdii nat ayerog jujuiyut. Oyat wryu tepin mowooat cabigshayu jiip oje uulolat jaimairauni tim, cajii calirg-shrm cawoo-jaa, jet-cataale cajáirca poi. Oje pun cam-rriprnjini boirig-shandit idminrg Dioat iruugjet.
42008015	Oyat nat mojrmca bigot ilrgot ijei niti-tee, ojera calii nat ayerog juiyut. Oyat jadjeiwao cajii jeiyu-tee, oyat calig tai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog idjuiprn, ooshrm ijei caminrg Dioat iruuca ojewi jacamdirauni mojrmca ijei.
42008016	Jai-shanquedrt lampara ibrrt jaijaanu caja nomat, rripoi jateeriprn nomat. Ooshrt jaiteerei shrnoye jategot-jaa caijawrrgjee nat iruugot mooleja.
42008017	Boirig-shandit iiquedrg jaijaanu oiiricatwiat, ooshrt jadshirugya wrijin ibiminrgprn bibigshayu poi. Boiruud iiquedrg jaiminrgu ijaanjet naa-jaa japishicashishanwajiya wrijin. Dioya jashirirrm naa idminrgprn jadduugjeeya wrijin.
42008018	Ooshrmda jayaujui ijeijet naa oodamog, naajri oodjalibrg ijei, Dioya jashibrm jan patjei. Oyat naa ood-boiruud, Dioya jashiom jashrt naa iyejawaag iribrg jan.
42008019	Oyat cayug Jesu-lica naa jaiin, jajrdwat poi, ooshrt jadshanquedrt jadnarglig cabag-shrm epinot.
42008020	Oyat boi mog jan, maiin minyug mapedwat poi, nat ishogot mooyeja jadjeu madduuglig.
42008021	Oyat Jesús mog calat, ooda aiinit apedwat poi, nat Dios yerog juiyut oyat idminrg oje jamoiani.
42008022	Oyat boi wryulau Jesús won já-teja idjajuirgprnot jriat. Oyat jamog calat, shog biunog rt yabata. Oyat cajricatounog canogjee.
42008023	Oyat canocadu jacooshog Jesús jaoujee já-tee. Oyat jiim drg cajaa jijogjet rt ipeg-uu, oyat jaiolat jajuituunrg ca-já cajrimonshug.
42008024	Oyat idjajuirgprnot yug jalica jadjeunrrg, camog jan, Biŕri, Biŕri, bijrishicomon. Oyat Jesús juimig, jijogjet jayaadbrg jiimat yri-jaligjee jaiolat poi. Oyat caquet jaiot wrijin, jiim poi, yrijalicat rt.
42008025	Oyat Jesús mog calat, boirigshrmjam yajii yashandirri ajaa. Oyat caorn ipegjet jashrt nat idjajuirgprnot, yau pishicawaaliprn brjaligu cabigshayu lig jajaa. Oyat cayaad caaleot, boirigjam naa yri-mairig imog jiimat jaiolat poi, oyat idminrg oje jamojani.
42008026	Oyat Jesús minog Gadarana couot niti-teja, rt Galilea yabata.
42008027	Oyat Jesús yrgbat já-teat, itrm bon yug janbata moyan-teat, demonioot lig jajii-tee bŕndi dumat poi. Yau jayuiot diiriprn jajaa, yau poi jaliiriprn moolee, ooshrt jaliigli irriprnotjin ot-tee caacanamdiprn-tee.
42008028	Jesús jaluugbat naa bonat jashog jautjuiyag-jet jan, jawrr-ág jamog, boirig imajeu ajet mam Jesúat. Mamda jaWá naa Dios ipeg wrijin-shrt. Marm ishigjet, amacupoirirt ebupaa-acrtjee.
42008029	Ojeri jamog Jesúat demonio jayrg jacui-shrm bon-shrt, ooshrm cabaglig demonioot jawaoat naa bon. Bŕn jalap shicajiipdi cadenaot-jet jashiimdí poi, ooshrt cadjapanteinog jashrt nat jetjadjiibot. Oyat moweijin jalirg jacuutjee cashrt on boiruuda epinot.
42008030	Oyat Jesúat jarm demonio, boirig matam. Oola atarn Ibagot jamog, ooshrm ibogjet demonioot duuglig naa bon jii-tee.
42008031	Oyat nat demonioot Jesús carm cadjacuinog-shrt wadyeg imon infierno-teja.
42008032	Omda ibagot deebrmotdi cawougjewet ishrn-jaa. Oyat Jesús carm nat demonioolat caluugjee deebrmot jii-tee. Oyat Jesúat caliirg canogjee deebrmot jii-teja.
42008033	Oyat nat demonioot cayrg bon shrt, caluug deebrmot jii-teja. Oyat wrijin nat deebrmot ibagot camaan jijogjet cawoulugjee imonpayeca, carmdrg rt-teja wrijin.
42008034	Oyat nat deebrmot ijewet, jadduugbat carmdrglig, cacuut cashrt caom-shrm. Camaan cainotshicapinjee wrijin moyan-teja, wrijin yee-uja poi.
42008035	Oyat nat epinot jaduunog naa Jesúat iminrg. Caminogbat Jesús-lica jadduug naa bon demonioolat inamnogprn, jateg Jesús shiim cooye, jayuiot peglicat, jabigcapecouat ijeijet. Oyat nat jaluujut caom ipegjet Jesús rca.
42008036	Oyat nat jaluujutprnot cadcapinrg bojaligu Jesúat jajeicondig naa bon ood-demonioot digli.
42008037	Oyat wrijin nat epinot Gararenocouot, Jesús capinrg ishiigjet jauprtjee caniti-shrt caom-shrm jarea ipegjet. Oyat Jesús luug já-teja janogjee cashrt.
42008038	Oyat naa bon demonioolat inamnogprnjin, Jesús jarm janogjee jajet, ooshrt Jesúat jacuinog jayan-teja.
42008039	Jamog jan, maucuprt maot-teja, majrrot maupinrgya jajet naa Dioat iminrg man. Oyat naa bon janog wrijin jayan-teja, jaijapin jajaa naa ijei Jesúat iminrg jan.
42008040	Oyat Jesús shriyucatulig caniti-teja ijáijeta jabaat-catai nat Gadareno tepinolat wrijin ooshrm jajeicapegteiri.
42008041	Oyat boi yug bon Jesú lica jatam Jairo, oolii sinagoga ijewe. Oyat jashog Jesúat jautjuiyag-jet, jadrm ishiigjet jayugjee jaot-teja.
42008042	Jalou itrm rrishucat-shrm, naa oodjalibrcadi doce wiig. Oyat Jesús nogbatdi Jairo-jet, capoinog jajet nat epinot ibagot inagot jashrt.
42008043	Omda jaboo epinot jewailee itrm den doce wiigla jamaa nog jashrt. Boiruud jaquedrr jadjeicondig.
42008044	Oyat jayug Jesús prna inagjetwi naa den, jalap jalirg Jesús ruana-jaa. Oowi jaqueedig jashrt jamaa noglig.
42008045	Oyat Jesús mog, brr jalap dirr ajaa. Oyat camog nat epinot wrijin, bidu shandid. Oyat Pedro mog jan jajetwinot poi, mam Bijuirr, nat ibagot ooda ijogot majaa wrijin, boirigshrmjam, brr amaapaya mamog.
42008046	Oyat Jesús mog, itrmat amaapai, japishiawaagwi abigshayu iyrglig jajeiconjee itrm yapei.
42008047	Oyat naa den japishijawaagwi jajashanquedrt jajajaandig Jesús-shrt. Oyat jayug japiip jashog jautjuiyag-jet Jesúat, cadjapinrg jadjuijee wrijin boirigshrm jaligu jadmaapai jaruana Jesús. Oyat jaeirucat iminrg-shrm oje.
42008048	Oyat Jesús mog jan, mam alou, majii malircat ajaa ooshrmda majeiyat mam. Dumat maunog mabigrriricatjee maebyu-shrt. Cristoat jabiglewrrg Jaira lou morriyu-shrt
42008049	Jayaadbatju Jesús, jayug caubata itrm bon jaot-teat naa sinagoga ijewe. Jamog Jairoat, bŕn jarrira malou. Jamacupoirrnot maot-teja naa mojuirr.
42008050	Jesúat jainot juibat jamog Jairoat,, macupoiom. Oowi majii maulircat ajaa omya jashijuu malou.
42008051	Jesús minogbat mooleja, boi jashandirt jaluugjee jajet, otwi iruugot jajet Pedro, Juan poi, Jacobo poi, naa poi irriprnjin ii, jaiin poi.
42008052	Omdi wrijin nat epinot caquigíi jajaa naa trriwaira irriri cashrt. Oyat Jesús mog calat, yacupoiquit. Jashanrrira naa, jatep ou.
42008053	Oyat jatamshicayoi Jesús japishicawaacat-shrm jarririg.
42008054	Oyat Jesiíat jalap waorg naa irriprnjin. Jamog jan jijogjet, mam trriwaira majuicumig.
42008055	Oyat jajii uprt jataaleja jajugjee-shri, oowi jajuimiglig. Oyat Jesúat cacui jawoug cabrgjee.
42008056	Oyat caom jadduugbat jajuglicat-shri nat jaii jaiin poi, cajii-jái. Oyat Jesúat cacui jaicapin-shrt jajaa naa idminrg.
42009001	Oyat Jesúat caág jalica nat doce itogot idjajuirgprnot, jabigshayu jalirg calat jawairiiyu poi cadcanamjee demonioot epinot-shrt, ishiyu poi.
42009002	Cadjapoi-cui idjuirrnogjee brjaligu Dioat cajuibergshirig jaepinota caligjee nat wryu tepinot. Cadjapoi-cui cadcajeiconjee nat ishiyuot iwaorgot.
42009003	Oyat Jesús mog calat, boyacupoirrnot yaviaje yawana boirig jaligu, boyacupoirrnot punu jet-yabooca, rripoi yawaagot, rripoi an, rripoi palaata, rripoi icauot camisa.
42009004	Oyat brr mooleja jaliguya yashiruu, onya yaulii ata-on yauprtdaya cayan-shrt.
42009005	Brrn jaliguya yabatcashantayi, jayaushrgya niti yashiim-shrt yauprtbatya cayan-shrt, jet-cadyatadrcaya boirig-shanditya ishiriibrg calat Dios-jet.
42009006	Oyat nat Jesúat icuiprnot canimnogjee wrijin moyanot-teja, jaicapin naa moyerog jet-moijeicon. Oyat cadcajeicon nat ishiyuat lebrgprnot wrijin moyanot tojani.
42009007	Oyat naa cajriwairüg Herodes, Jesús iinot jajui wrijin-jaa naa idminrg. Oyat jaom naa Herodes jadpinrg-shrm Juan Bautista jaliglig-cugjin naa Jesús juimig morriyu-shrt.
42009008	Oyat itrmnogot mog, ooiawi naa Dios yerog ipini Elias. Oyat itrmnogolat jaipin, oolawi itrm capei nat profetaot juimig morriyu-shrt.
42009009	Oyat Herodes mog, amdirawi cacuiyu Juan juiyag capaanjee jashrt. Oyat brr-jam naa iinot ajui iminrr wrijin naa oodcamog jajaa. Oyat Herodeat jajeu jaduugh Jesús ipegjet.
42009010	Oyat cauprlatu Jesús-lica nat idjacuiprnot jaicapin jan wrijinjaa naa idminrg. Oyat cadjarrnog jajet epinot-shrt boiyeja inagjetwiat moyan Betsaida-shrt.
42009011	Oyat nat epinot jainot cajuibat Jesús noglig, canog japrna. Oyat cabatjatai, cadjapinrg boirig jaligu Dioat cajuiberg-shirig nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee. Oyat cadjajeicon nat oodishiyuligot.
42009012	Oyat cup shairei jadnarg Jesús nat doce itogot idjajuirgprnolat. Camog jan, cadmaulirg cauprtjee mashrt nat epinot moyanot inagot-teja, cawouca boi cajeujee. Caouliprna poi, ooshrm epinot-rri nam birigu.
42009013	Oyat Jesús mo calat, yamdawi cawoug-cubrt. Oyat camog jan, oowi, birat sinco jatog an, cacau yrriot bishan-notu boi miibibrgjee cawouca nat epinolat.
42009014	Ojeri camo ooshrm sinco-mil catog nat mot. Oyat Jesús mog calat nat idjajuirgprnolat, cadyaulirg categjee sincuenta itoonog-jet.
42009015	Oyat idminrg oje Jesús mojani calat, cadcalirg categjee wrijin.
42009016	Oyat Jesúat jawao naa sinco itog an, nat-poi icauot yrriot. Oyat janirn shrnoja, ijei jabrg an-jaa yrri-jaa poi, oyat jadmopig, oyat jadbrg idjajuirgprnolat jadbrgjee epinolat catojani.
42009017	Oyat cayeiwai teetogjet wrijin. Oyat cajuicatuunrg doce itogot mapiriot idnamjogprnjin-jet cayeiwai quedyem.
42009018	Oyat boi wryulau Jesús nog eprnot-shrt Dios japinrgjee. Canog poi jajet nat idjajuirgprnot. Oyat cadjarrn, boijam camo ajaa nat epinot. Brr-jaligu arn.
42009019	Oyat camog jan, camog majaa Juan Bautistala mam. Oyat itrmnogot mog. Elíama mam, oyat itrmnogot mogjri, mama-cugjin itrm Capei nat profetaot juimig-shri majugjee.
42009020	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yam poi, boijam yarnoo ajaa. Oyat Pedro mog jan, mamdawi Cristo, Dioat icuiprn shrnoat.
42009021	Oyat Jesúat capinrg jijogjet jainot shicapin-shrt.
42009022	Oyat Jesús mog calat, ebupaa-ashicrtya jijogjet am Iminyigli wryu aluugjee. Aashirirgya adnamjee nat quepa-lat, saserdoteot jriwairügolat poi, inaat poi. Aaleiya ashirirr adrriigjee, oyat jaipoiyu wryu jayeya ajuishimig ajugjeeya-shri.
42009023	Oyat Jesús mog calat wrijin, jadjeuu itrm noglig ajetjri, jabigjashishanshaat jaaler-jaatep, ooshrt jacrusala idshirrnog wryu shitojani janogjee ajet.
42009024	Naa wryu-yiiruju, jashirmdrgya jashrt. Ooshrt naa jajewe jarririg ashrm naa wryu-shŕt, jashiribrgya jan wryu ishanbeji.
42009025	Jaijabeebu wrijin wryu-tepin mo-woo, boirigya jashimii jan naa bonat irmdigyawan Dios-shrt.
42009026	Oyat jauuyiguya itrm bon ashrm, ayerog-shrm poi, auushiyigya poi jabat-atairig amat, am Iminyrgli wryu aluugjee ayugbatya shrnoat ishiyrgya oje Aiiat iyrrlauni cajrriat nat anjeleot ijeinogot.
42009027	Rjeta amo yan, itrmnogot yajetwinot cashishan-rriya jajuprduyaju jadduuglig Dioat cajuiberliprn jaepinota caligjee.
42009028	Oyat ocho jatog quedyem wryu jaijapin quedyem naa moyerog, Jesús juimig janogjee wen-jaa Jaii Dios japinrgjee. Jadrrnog jajet Pedro, Jacobo poi, Juan poi.
42009029	Jesúat Dios pinrgbat jaúat iyrg ijeijet, oyat janawaat iyrg ibrgjet brt-brt-brt irigjeí.
42009030	Oyat cadcaluug icauot mot iyaalot Jesús-jet, Moiséra itrm, naa itrm poi Elías.
42009031	Ijeijeta idyrg wrijin nat icaluugot. Oyat cayaad jajaa naa Jesús nooyu shrnoja, cayaad poi jajaa bojaliguya ebupaajaert-shirig Jerusalén-tee.
42009032	Oyat naa Pedro jajetwinot poi, caou-shug, ooshrt yau caouliprn. Jesús caluugbat idyrglig ijeijet, oodpoi nat icauot jajetwinot.
42009033	Oyat canocat quedyem Jesús-shrt nat icauot, Pedro mog jan, mam Bijuirr, ijeira naa ibiruug nam. Biradwi cadbishiminrg ipoiot capillaot. Jashitrm mapin, jashitrm Moisés pin, jashitrm Elias pin poi. Ooshrt yau Pedroat japishiwaaliprn brjaliyu jaligu naa oodjam og.
42009034	Jajuiyaadbatju Pedro, jayug itrm waojribrru calica, cajuijapujuyeg. Oowi caomdig ipegjet jalrgbat cajaa naa waojribrru.
42009035	Oyat jadjui itrm moyerog waajribrru-teat, jamog, oolawi aWá yii-aluugprn, jayerog yaujui.
42009036	Oyat jayaad quedyem naa moyerog waojribrru-teat, jadduug Jesús shoglig itrmjetwi. Oyat onda caliiwi jajaa naa idduug, iaicashanpin brrt.
42009037	Oyat brlemdicat cayugbat wen-jaat, cayug Jesús uubata nat epinot ibagot.
42009038	Oyat itrm bon capei Jesús japinrg ishügjet, mam Bijuirr, maág ajii-teat, jamauluuyug awá, ooshrm jatrmwi atrri.
42009039	Itrm demonioat atrri jiip, oyat jadirg jawrr-ágjee, oyat jadirg jalrgjee niti-uja. Oyat jataale oop, jacoopog nogjee. Ieb jaminrg demonioat jan. Yau jadjeuliprn jadnamnoglig.
42009040	Cadacugrmda idmajuirgprnot demonioat canamjee atrri-shrt, ooshrt yau jadquedrliprn jadnamdig.
42009041	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yam epinot yajii shandirriot, yam iebnogprnotjin. Boyajarn jashijutoo wryu ashirig yajet. Boyajam jashijutoo yajricaashicou. Jamaurryug matrri nani.
42009042	Oyat jayucadu inagjet Jesús-shrt naa trriwai, demonioat jalirg jairgjee niti-uja jadpiiprg. Oyat Jesilat jacuinog trriwai-shrt naa mojii iebprnjin, oyat jajeiat naa tnriwai, oyat Jesúat jabrg jaiiat.
42009043	Oyat caom Jesús rca wrijin nat epinot jadduugbat Dios bigshayu iwairüg. Oyat cajuombat Jesús caluug, jayaad idjajuirgprnolat.
42009044	Jamog calat, jayaulirg jaluugjee yabutogye naa moyerog oodamog ajaa am Iminyrgli wryu aluugjee. Adshibrgya calap-uu nat mot idminrgjee an oje jadjeulauni.
42009045	Oyat nat idjajuirgprnot, yau japishicawaaliprn jajaa naa oodjamog calat, jadshanjulirt-shrm japishicawaagjee bojaliyu jaligu naa oodjamog. Oyat caom jadrmdig bojaliyu jaligu.
42009046	Oyat camog caaleiot brr-yawrnjam idshirirg-om bipei inomjrijeirig brrt-shrt.
42009047	Jesúat japishiwaag brjaligu cabigcashaglig, ooshrm jadirg itrm trriwai shogjee jamauye.
42009048	Oyat Jesús mog calat, brr-jaliguya jabatshitaiya naa trriwai atam-jaa abatjashitaiya poi am. Oyat naa abataiya am, jabatjashitaiya naa acuiyuadi am nani. Oyat naa itrm yapei jabigsham uubiidprnjini, oola ijei brrt-shrt.
42009049	Oyat Juan mog jan, mam Bijuirr, jabiruugwi itrm bon demonioot nama matam-jaa, oyat jaiwinbishog idminrglig oje bijetwina jashandit-shrm.
42009050	Oyat Jesús mog jan, jaiwin-macupoishoot iminrglig oje. Naa bibatabishanrri bijetwindawi oo.
42009051	Oyat janacatuwiat jabigye Jesús nogjee shrnoja, jijogjeta jajii jalirli janogjee Jerusaléna.
42009052	Oyat Jesúat cacuinog itrmnogot jajuprta jainot shicapinjee. Oyat canog caluugjee itrm moyan-teja samaria-tee caouliprn cajeujee.
42009053	Oyat nat Samaría tepinot jadshanjeu Jesús batcatairíg jadduugbat jijogjet jajii jalirg janogjee Jerusalena.
42009054	Oyat nat idjajuirgprnot Jacobo, Juan poi, cadcaluugbat jadshanjeuh jabatcatairig, camog Jesúat, mam Bijriwairüg, jamajewijam drr biáglig jalrgjee shrnoat cabeegjee nat epinot oje idrjaniri naa profeta Eliaat.
42009055	Oyat Jesús jewuu cadjaluuca con cadjarg, jamog calat, yau japishiyawaaliprn brr bigshayu-jet jaligu yatepyaad.
42009056	Am Iminyrgli wryu aluugjee, ashanyut epinot alirgjee carradrgjee-cugjin Dios-shrt, ooshrt ayug cadajeiconjee ieb-shrt cadarrnogjee paraiso-teja. Oyat Jesús nog boi moyan-teja idjajuirgprnot jrriat.
42009057	Oyat canogbat drg-uu, itrrn bon mog Jesúat, Aŕri jajeula anoglig majet brrn-jaligu manoo.
42009058	Jesús mog jan, nat derot jaligwi caot niti-tee, natpoi wiibot jaligwi cajepeot puulot-jaa. Ooshrt boiruud jijajaliiriprn naa Iminyrgli wryu jaluugjee.
42009059	Oyat Jesús mog itrmat, mauyug aprna. Oyat jamog Jesúat, Aŕri, amaujulirg aii jeiateijee ata-on jabrgcaya.
42009060	Oyat Jesús mog jan, jamaulirg jadbrgjee irriprnotjinolat nat ishirriotya Dios-shrt. Oyat mamjri, maunog, epinot mapinrgjee brjaliguya Dioat cajuibergshirig nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee.
42009061	Oyat boi-shri mog Jesúat, Aŕri ashinog maprna ooshrt arnaulirgju cadashipinrrnog aot tepinot.
42009062	Oyat jesús mo jan, naajri ibeepe an jajewugu jaduugjee-shri naa wryu pin, boishanjeiat cajuijashugjee epinot Dioat.
42010001	Oyat itrmnog wryu prnat, Biŕriat caág setenta itogot mot. .IU Cadjacui canogjee jajuprta icauteenogjet wrijin moyanot-teja on jashinocaya.
42010002	Oyat jamog calat, rjet cabagla nat Dioat ijeuot cajuibishuglig jan, ooshrtjri cayaiwi nat ibeebrt jan. Ooshrmda jayaurm jashrt naa mojrmca Rri brrt jacuijee ibeebeta jan cajuicashugjee nat japinit.
42010003	Yaunog yacuinogjee oje oveja noolauni cajewaleye nat yoodanot innnot.
42010004	Jayacupoirrnotyajet yapaíaata ot, rripoi palaata, rripoi sapatoot. Yacupoi-shoot yayaadjee cajet nat iwuushogot drg-uye.
42010005	Yaluugbatya boi moolee Dios yaupinrgya yaumog jurgya. Cadmaulirg cabigrririgjee nat moolee-pinot.
42010006	Om-jaliguya boirii jajewe jajajeicondig Dios-jet, omya jabigrrishirii Dios-jet oje jayapinrlauni. Ooshrt boi yashanduutu, jaushiprtya yalica naa ijei iyapin calat.
42010007	Oyat yauligya jatee naa mo-tee yaluug-jurg. Yayecuwaiya cajet, jayawougya naa puncampog idbrg yan. Naa ibeepe jadquedrg jadouglig jabeeb-mü. Yacupoijeu-shoobotya caoolot tojani.
42010008	Yaluugbatya cayan-tee nat yabat-taiat, jayauwougya naa idbrg yan.
42010009	Cadyaujeiconya nat wrrnoligot on. Jayaupin calat brjaliguya Dioat cajuibergshirig nat wrgu tepinot jaepinota caligjee.
42010010	Oyat yaluugbatya cayan-tee nat yabatshantayit, yaucuprtya cashrt mooyeja.i
42010011	Yaumog calat, jabishishrg bishrt naa yayan niti irig bishiirn-jaa, japishiyawaagjee boirig shanditya ishiriibrg yan Dios-jet, japishiyawaagjee yadnarglicat naa jalirm yaiuuglig Dioat moijeuliprn-teja.
42010012	Oyatda yapinr yarn, boi wryulauya Dioat caishipin wrijin, ebupaacashi-nomjricrtya cashrt nat irigotdi Sodoma-tee nat epinot yabatshantaiyit.
42010013	Uubiidprnjinya mam moyan Corazín, uubiidprnjinya mam moyan Betsaida. Jacaminrgu brrt ishanminrri Tiro-tee Sidón-tee poi oje iminrlauni yajewalee, brn cabigshayu cacugcambiarg-om, jadcugyui-om canawa oje saconi irig itagyegprn drrprp-tee jetcadcatadrca cajii-shŕmdig capecado iyecawaaglig.
42010014	Ebupaayashicrtya jijogjet cashrt nat Tiro tepinot, Sidón tepinot poi, oolau wryu-teeya Dioat capecado iishipinya ebupaacacrtjee.
42010015	Oyat mam moyan Capernaum, jayemawaag Dioat mashiwrryrgya shrnoja, ooshrt madshiwonrgya monoja irriprnotjin diiriprn-teja.
42010016	Naa yayerog juiyu yarn ajetwinot, jadpoi-jui ayerog am. Naa jashanjuibri yan, jashanpoi juibrt an. Oyat naa jashanjuibri an, jadshanpoi-juibrt naa acuiyuprnot am.
42010017	Oyat nat setenta itogot, cajii-jái cauprtbat canogprn-shrt. Camog, mam Biŕri, nat demonioot jadjui poi naa ibipin calat matam-jaa.
42010018	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jaluugwi moweijin drglig shrnoat oje iwaalrrlauni.
42010019	Abigshayu jalirbrcat yan shrp yataagjee, shrg yataagjee poi yauya ieb cashiminriiprn yan. Jashirirgya poi bibaat moweijin bigshayu yanamjee yashrt, yadebrg-shrtya yam.
42010020	Yajii cupoijái yayerog cajui-shrm nat mojii iebnogolat, ooshrt yajii-cujái yatam jribinag-shrm naa papera-tee irig shrnoja.
42010021	Oyat oowi jajii jáirig naa Jesús Espíritu Santo-jet. Jamog, ijei abrg man, mam Aii uioat, mam paraíso jriwairüg, naa wryu Jriwairüg poi, jaimajaan-shrmdi naa moyerog cashrt nat bicacauot, oyat mabigtan-mashrtcatpeg nat trrijulolat. Rcaiji Aii, ojerawi imarr jamajeu-shrm imaminrglig oje.
42010022	Aiiat jalirbrcat an wrijin boirig jaligu. Brr-shandit japishiwaja jaWá, jatrmdawi Jali japishiwaja. Brr-shandit japishiwaja brr-jaligu Bii Dios, jatrmdawi jaWá japishiwaja, otpoi nat jaWáat irirgprnot japishicawaagjee.
42010023	Oyat Jesús jewu cadjaluugjee nat idjajuirgprnot, jamog calat brrt-shrt, cajii shijáiya nat jalujut cabig-jet naa iyaluug.
42010024	Dumat yashipinrg, cabagli profetaot iwairügotdi poi, jadjeuli jadduuglig naa iyaluugli, ooshrt yau jadduuliprn. Jadjeuli poicug jadjuirig naa iyajuiri, ooshrt yau jadjuiriprn.
42010025	Oyat itrm Moisés yerog juirg, jajuimig Jesús jarrnjee jabigshayu pishijawaagjee. Jamog jan, mam Bijuirr, boirigjam ishiminrg jalibrgjeeya an wryu ishanbeji.
42010026	Oyat Jesús mog jan, bojerijam Moiséat inaglig japapera-tee. Brjaligu jamog naa imaleeg.
42010027	Oyat jamog jan, manwi jayii mashiruu majri Dios wrijin majiiteat, wrijin majuuyu-jet, wrijin mawairüyu-jet poi, wrijin mabigshayu-jet poi. Oyat majrr yii mauluug ojewi mayii maluulauni maaleat.
42010028	Oyat Jesús mog jan, ijeira naa oodmamog. Imaminrgu ojejri mashijugyawi.
42010029	Oyat naa bon jadjeu jayaadig patjei jajaa naa oodjamog, oyat jamog Jesúat, Brr-jam naa ajrr.
42010030	Oyat Jesús mog jan, itrm bon nog drg-uja Jerusalén-shrt Jerico-teja. Oyat jadwaorg ishegprnotjinolat, wrijin jalapwoo caoug jashrt, jadpai jaaprndigjet, oyat canog jashrt. Jadirmog jarrishucatuwi.
42010031	Oyat itrm saserdote nog naa drg-uye, jadduugbat naa bon, oowi jawuglig jashrt iyaujet.
42010032	Oyat-shri itrm bon nog drg-uye, levitala naa bon. Oyat jadpairuug naa idpayegprnjin, jawug poi jashrt iyaujet.
42010033	Oyat itrm Samaria atwin yug-shri drg-uye, oyat jaduug jashoonoyeglig drg-uu naa bon, jauubiid jaduuglig.
42010034	Oyat jadnarg naa bon, jadwrn jashrt wrijin jajaaprn aceite-jet vino-jet poi. Oyat jajaaprn ijapug yuiot-jet, oyat jadwrryrg jateereijee jaburro-jaa jadrmogjee epinot ouliprn-teja. Onda jadpegjeicon ijeijet.
42010035	Oyat brlemdigu icau palaata jaoug jacatera-teat naa Samaria atwinat jadbrgjee naa mo rriat. Jamog jan, jaimaujeiubrgya an naa bon, oyatya auprt quedyem marnii ashibrgya brjaligu jatog imapatjeijeu.
42010036	Oyat Jesúat carrn, brr-jam capei nat ipoiot ijei-minrr jan naa ishegprnotjinolat ipaiprn oje jajrrbrat iijani jan.
42010037	Oyat jamog Jesúat, naajri bon uubiidjet jalujuprn idminrgbrg jan oje mojrrbrat ijei minrlauni molat. Oyat Jesús mog jan, maunog imaminrgjee oje idijani.
42010038	Oyat Jesús nogbat cajrirü-uye, jaminog boi moyan ishrm-teja. Omda boiriiri den jatam Marta, Jesús batjatai jaot-tee.
42010039	Oyat naa Marta jajáwai-rig jatam María, jateg Jesús shiim cooye jayerog jajuijee.
42010040	Oyat naa Marta jajii nog jashrm naa idbeeb moolee. Oyat jayug Jesu-lica, jamog jan, Aŕri, japishimawajijam-cug ajawaiat alirglig itnnjetwi biwoug aminrglig. Jamaucui jajrija adrgjee.
42010041	Oyat Jesús mog jan, Marta, Marta, mabigmashag wryu tepin-jaa ibagjet.
42010042	Jatrmdawi naa iijeu. Naa Maríajn jajii jalircat jajaa naa ijei iijeu. Boirig shanditya jashiquedrr jadouglig jashrt.
42011001	Boi wryulau Jesús lig boibat Dios japinrgjee. Oyat Dios japinrg quedyem itrm idjuirgprn mog jan, Aŕri bidmajuirg Dios bipinrgjee oje Juanat cajirlauniri idjajuirgprnot.
42011002	Oyat Jesús mo calat, Dios yapinrgbat yaumog jan, mam Bii shrnoja-irig, ijei matarn. Mauyug birica Bijriwairiica maligjee. Jamaulirg mayerog biwaorgjee narn wryu-tee oje mayerog cawaorlauni nat irigot shrnoja.
42011003	Dumat biwoucaboimaubrg, naa ibijeu wryu shitojani.
42011004	Bidmaujeicon majet jashrt naa ieb ibiminrgprn oje cadbijeicondauni bijet nat ieb-minrt birat. Jamacupoirirt brrt biteeshaurlig ieb biminrgjee, ooshrt bidmaushiu jashrt naa iebprnjin.
42011005	Oyat Jesús shri-mog calat, itrm yapei ooat jaliibrgu jajrr, shai-tee jamaiu janog jaot-teja, jamog jan, ajrr jamaubrg an ipoi an jarmolenogjee.
42011006	Itrm ajrr iboonogprn jarninyucat alica, boirig shandit iribrg an jabrgjee jan jawouca.
42011007	Oyat naa jajrr, maucuprt ashrt jashimoijam jan mooleat, ajuiapaacatnira amat, caouot wrijin atrriot. Ashanquedrlat ajuimiglig an abrgjee man.
42011008	Yapinrg yam, yau jaiigu jajuimüriprn jadbrgjee jan naa idjeu jajrrja jalig-shrm. Oyat jajuishimig jadbrgjee jan on jaligjeeat jashrt.
42011009	Ooshrm yapinrg, Dios yaurm oyatya jadshibnr yan naa iyarm jajet. Jayaujeu Dios oyatya jayashitairiir. Jayauág Dios oyatya jaotye juijashiyibrya yan.
42011010	Wrijin nat cairmrt Dios-jet jashiribrgya calat naa idrm jajet. Oyat nat jajewet jadshitairirgya naa idjeuprn. Oyat nat ja-ájat caluugjee jajuijashiyigya calat mooye.
42011011	Itrm yapei trririg, an jarmbat jashrt, jadshibríjain jan jaajou. Yrri jarmbat jaii-shrt, shrp jashibrijam jan.
42011012	Cawa biglig jarmbat jatrriat, jadquedrrijam jadbrgu jan digwr.
42011013	Ooshrt yam iebnogprnotjin, japishiyawaagu ijei yabrglig yatrriat, jaishinomjri-pegya Dioat ishibrg Espíritu Santo calat nat cairmrlat jajet.
42011014	Oyat Jesúat demonio nam itrm bon-shrt, naa jalirrli jayerog rririg. Oyat jayrg quedyem naa demonio jayaalatpeg naa yerogrriprndi. Oyat caom jaduuglig Jesús nat epinolat.
42011015	Oyat itrmnogot mog, naa Jesús, demonioot janam jabigshayujet naa demonioot jriwairücat moweijin.
42011016	Oyat itrmnogolat jajeu Jesús bigshayu caluuglig. Oyat jadrm cadjatadrg jaduugjee itrm brrt ishanminrri shrnoatwin.
42011017	Jesúat japishiwaag brjaligu cabigshayu lig, oyat jamog calat, cabaata caacargu nat iwairügolat, cashibeegya-om. Caacarriryegu caepinot-jet boishiruudya calat idcacuiot. Ojera poi nat mot caot tepinot caacarrirgu caaleolat cashibeegya.
42011018	Ojera poi moweijin, iademonioot janamu ooyawi cabeegshirigjamo, oyat boishiruudya jan idshicui. Ojera amo yan, yam imogot ajaa, demonioot anamdig-cugjin moweijin bigshayu-jet.
42011019	Demonioot acanamu moweijin bigshayu-jet, boirig bigshayujetjam demonioot canam nat idyajuirgprnot. Oodawi yalirt japishiyapoiwaag bŕnwi-bigshayu rriprnotjina yaliglig.
42011020	Ooshrt demonioot anamu Dios bigshayu-jet, japishiyawaagwi jayaa minolicat Dioat cajuiberg-shiricat nat wryu tepinot jáepinota caligjaa.
42011021	Jaot ijajeuu naa bon iwairücat jatat jriat, jaijajeuwi naa jalapwoo ishegot-shrt.
42011022	Oyat boi yugu jalica inomjri-wairüg jashrt jadshiteejogya niti-uja, Oyat jadshiougya jashrt jatat jaa-jajii jalirgprn, oyat jadsheg jashrt jawoojin.
42011023	Naa ishandi ajet, jabaata-adrg. Oyat naajri epinot juishanbe-rri ajet, epinot jatep-yaurg ashrt.
42011024	Itrm mojii iebprnjin jayrgbat bon-shrt, jaboolrg epin-rriya jadjeu jijajaliiriprn. Oyat yau boi jaluuliprn, jamog jaaleat, auushiprt aot-teja ayuuprnot.
42011025	Oyat naa demonio jaminocadu on, jatairirg naa bon ijei oje itrm mo idjeiconprni, ŕri-rriprnjini teecacrprni.
42011026	Oyat naa demonio cadjarmog jajet siete demonioot inomjriebnogot jashrt. Oyat caluug wrijin caligjee jajii-tee naa bon. Oyat janomjri-ebat naa bon jaliiprn-shrt itrm demonio jriat.
42011027	Jesúat jaipinbat naa moyerog, itrm den epinot jewalee irig jamog jijogjet, jajii shijáiya naa den shrt-mayrg, naa mashr-rr jajiimipog-jet.
42011028	Oyat Jesús mog, cashinomjri-jáiya nat Dios yerog juiyut, idminrg poi oje jarnojani calat.
42011029	Oyat ibagjet epinolat cajuibergbat Jesús coo, jajuijawrg cadjajuirglig. Jamog calat, iebnogprnotjinda nat epinot dumatwinot. Adrm jaminrgjee calat brrt ishanminrri, ooshrt jashanminrt calat. Oolawi ishiminrgli ojewi idtjaniri naa Jonáat.
42011030	Oje Jonáat catadrlauniri jadduugjee nat Niniva tepinolat ojeya poi am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee jet-cadatadrcaya nat epinot dumatwinot.
42011031	Oo wryu-teeya Dioat capecado iishipin ebupaacacrtjee, jajuishimigya poi naa sur jriwairügla yaebyu ijashipinya yam epinot dumatwinot. Bŕn jayugli yawaat Salomón bigshayu jajuijee, ooshrt boirig nam yajewalee inomjri-jeirig Salomón-shrt.
42011032	Oo wryu-teeya Dioat capecado iishipin ebupaacacrtjee, cajuishimigya poi nat Niniva tepinot yaebyu iicapinjee. Bŕn cajii-shŕm capecado iyecawaaglig Jonas yerog cajuibat. Oyat boirig nam yajewalee inomjri-jeirig Jonás-shrt.
42011033	Brr-shandit jaquedrr lampara juitaiprn jajaanjee, yau-poi jaiquedrliprn jairirgjee caja-tee. Ooshrt jairirg shrnoye jashooliprnjaa caijáwrrgjee nat iruugot mooleja.
42011034	Naa mobig oolawi motaale shiwryu. Ijeinogot jaligu mabigot, imashiruug ijeijet imabeebjee wrijin mataale-jet. Ooshrt jricaebu mabigot wrijinya mataale shirii ibrrn-tee.
42011035	Ooshrmda jayauluugya yashrt jatrm-shrtya yashrt naa ebushiwryu yajii-tee.
42011036	Naa iribrg man naa ebushiwryu majii-tee, boiruudu ibrru ishrm mabigshayu-tee. Japishimawaagya ijeijet nam wryutee oje moboolauni ijeijet drg-uu ebushiwryu-jet.
42011037	Oyat jayaadbatju Jesús, itrm fariseoat jaág jayugjee jaot-teja jayeiwaijee jajet. Oyat Jesús luug jaot-tee, jateg mesa coo.
42011038	Oyat jaeb jaluug Jesús jalap jashanshrrt-shrm jayeiwai juprtu.
42011039	Oyat Biŕri mog jan, yam fáriseoot yalap yashrg, yanaawa poi oje motasa jaishrglaunitep cajaat-tep. Ooshrt jaapibagprnotjina jaligshicom yajii-tee, yajuituun moteeshauyu-jet jet-epinot pin yasheeca, yajuituun poi yaebyu-jet.
42011040	Yam bicashancowiprnotjin, yau-tejam pishiyawaaliprn, naa jaminrr yataale, naa-poi jalirr yan yabigshayu.
42011041	Ooshrmya yabigshayu yaulirg Dioat oje regaloni, oyatya jaapi-shirriya wrijin naa irig yajii-tee.
42011042	Yauushibiidya yam fariseoot, yam diesmo brrt Dioat wnjin-jaa naa iribrg yan, minta-jaa, ruda-jaa, wrijin mojrmca-jaa poi. Ooshrt jayashanpin naa-jaa Dios bigshayu ijei idirg yan iyaminrgjee ijeijet, rripoi cayajuirlig jayii caluugjee Dios. Yanwi yabigshayu yashirirr Dios-jaa, oyat jayashiminrr oje amojani, oyat yacupoijaap ofrenda yabrglig Dioat.
42011043	Yauushibiidya yam fariseoot, yam jajewet yateglig iinodigot banco-jaa sinagoga-tee. Oyat jayajeu epinot omdig yashrt yadyaadrgbat wad-uu.
42011044	Yauushibiidya yam inaat, fariseoot poi, oitepdigprnotjinda yam. Yaebyulig yajii-tee ijaanjet oje ishijaanprnjin diirauni wadyeg-tee iishanduji. Oyat nat iwuushogot jajaaye yau japishicawaaliprn jajaa.
42011045	Oyat itrrn Moiséat inagprn juirr, jamog Jesúat, mam Bijuirr, jamaebrg bibigshayu jajet naa oodmamog.
42011046	Oyat Jesús mog jan, yauushibiidya yam poi Moisés yerog juirt, jayalirg-shrm ebupaacacrdig Dios yerog-shrm nat epinolat, ooshrt yam yau cajnja cadyarrliprn, yau ishrmjet.
42011047	Yauushibiidya yam caot yaminrg-shrm nat Dios yerog shipinidi bŕn, nat yaloornolat irrirgprnotdi.
42011048	Ooshrmda japishibiwaag itrmjani yabigshayu liglig yaloomotjin-jet. Bŕn cadca-rrirgli, oyat yam durnat jayaminrg calat irriprnotjin olot.
42011049	Ooshrmdi ojeri jamog Dios bŕn, profetaot ashicuiya yan, nat-poi idaougprnot. Oyat cadcashirrirgya itnnnogot capet, oyat cabaata-cadcashirgya brrt.
42011050	Ooshrmya Dioat cashirirgya ebupaacacrtjee nat epinolat durnatwinot camaa prtaya nat profetaot idcarrirgprnotdi wryu juiwrgbatdi dumatpatjee.
42011051	Rjet yapinrg yam, nat epinot durnatwinot ebupaacashicrtya jamaa prtaya naa Abél, natpoi wrijin japrnotwinot ata-on jadrrirca Zacarías, naa idrrirgprndi Dios ot-tee ofrenda iicaberliprn máuu.
42011052	Yauushibiidya yam Moisés yerog juirt, jajuiyaprg-shrm cashrt naa jet-japishiiwaag bojaligu Dios yerog mog. Yam yau japishiyawaaliprn bojaligu jaligu, oyat yau jayalirliprn japishicawaagjee nat jajewet japishicawaaglig.
42011053	Jesúat jaipinbat naa moyerog, jaeb caluug nat Moisés yerogjuirlot, fariseoot poi. Oyat ibagjet jadrm Jesús jadjuijee bojaligu jamog, jainot shicapinjee iebjet.
42011054	Ooshrm jajeicatei jadjuijee Jesús yaadjee-cugjin iebjet cajriwairüg-jaa jainot shicapinjee. Versículo 44, memoria-jet)
42012001	Oyat ibagjet epinolat cajuiberg Jesús-lica, cashiim shicatou caale-jaa calrg cabag-shrm epinot. Oyat Jesúat jaipin-jurg idjajuirgprnolat, jayauluug yashrt naa fariseoot bigshayu, naa idminrt boyajatep jashrt naa idjuirg.
42012002	Boishanduut iiquedrg jaijaandig oirig, ooshrt Dioya jashiyrrgya jadduugjee wrijin. Oyat naa ieb idminrg ijaanjet, japishicashiwaagya jajaa wrijin.
42012003	Ojeya-poiwi wrijin naa oodyamog ijaanjet, jadshijuiya wrglee. Oyat naa iyapin cabutogye brrt-shrt jajuiyapaa quedyern mooyee, jaija-shipinrgya jijogjet mojopocat jadjuijeeya wrijin.
42012004	Yapinrg yam ajrrot, macupoiom cashrt nat yataale rrirt, ooshrm boirig-shandit idquedrg jadminrglig yan yadrrirg quedyem.
42012005	Oyat yapinrg boirig-shrt jaligu yashiom. Yauom jashrt naa jadquedrr iyadnarndig infierno-teja yadrrirg-quedyem. Rcaiji yapinrg, yauom jashrt.
42012006	Jaishanquedrgtejam cadiwendergu sinco wiibot icau moneda muja. Ooshrt Dios bigrrishandit jashrt itrm capei nat wiibot.
42012007	Dioat japishiwaag brjaligu jatog yayuu yajuiyag-jaa, ooshrm macupoiomi, miibagota yalig-shrm ibagjet wiibot-shrt.
42012008	Ooshrmda yapinrg, wrijin nat ainot shipinit ijeijet epinolat cainotshi ashipinya poi ijeijet nat Dios ánjeleolat, am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee.

42019001	Oyat Jesús luug moyan Jerico-teja jawug cayan jamaiye.

43002012	Jesúat jadminrg quedyem oiirig, janog cashrt moyan Capernaum-teja. Janog poi jajet jaiin, jajrrot poi, idjajuirgprnot poi. Oyat calig jajan yai wryuwi. Cristoat cayrrg templo-shrt nat palata yiirujut Dios-shrt
43002013	Oyat janagcadwi judioot juibeeriprn jatam pascua, Jesús nog Jerusalén-teja.
43002014	Oyat cadjaluug nat torroot wendeot templo-tee, ovejaot poi, iitibrmot poi, otpoi nat patata cambiart categ mesa Coo.
43002015	Jesúat caluugbat jadminrg itrm jet-cadjawrgrca drlot-jet. Oyat cadjayrrg wrijin templo-teat caovejaot jriat, wrijin torroot jriat poi. Oyat jadnam capalata cashrt niti-uja nat palata cambiart, oyat cadjateu cashrt wrijin mesaot.
43002016	Oyat jamog calat nat iitibrmot wendeot, cadyaurrnog temploshrt. Jayacupoirirt naa Aii ot yawenderliprna.
43002017	Oyat idjajuirgprnolat jayeewaag naa idnagprndi papera-uu. Ojeri jamo, jijogjeta jajeu jajajeulig maot.
43002018	Oyat nat judioot camog Jesúat, boirigjam imarninrg brrt ishanquedrri jet-birnatadrea jalibrglig moyerog man bidmayrrgjee ternplo-teat.
43002019	Oyat Jesús mog calat, jayanamu naa templo, oyatjri jajuiashimirgya-shri ipoi wryu-jaye.
43002020	Oyat nat judioot camog jan, cuarenta-seis wiig jadminrglig naa templo. Oyatjri jajuimashimirriyajam ipoi wryu-jaye.
43002021	Ooshrt jataalelawi-jaa jamog Jesús.
43002022	Ooshrm jajuimig quedyem morriyu-shrt, jayecawaag naa oodjamoglig nat idjajuirgprnot. Oyatjri cajii calirg jajaa naa idnagprndi papera-uu, jajaa poi naa Jesúat oodmogprn ealat.
43002023	Jesús ligbatju Jerusalén-tee cajuibeeriprn-tee jatam pascua, cabag epinot cajiirirt jajaa jaduugbat jadminrglig ibagjet brrt ishanquedrri.
43002024	Ooshrtjri yau Jesúat jajií-rirrliprn cajaa japishijawaag-shrm bijaligu cabigshayu lig wrijin.
43002025	Yau jadjeuliprn brrt cainot shipindig jan japishijawaag-shrm naa ieb irica cajii-tee nat epinot.
43003001	Oyat itrm bon fariseo jatam Nicoderno, oola capei nat judioot jriwairügot.
43003002	Naa Nicoderno janog Jesús-lica shairei, jamog jan, mam Bijuirr, mapishibiwaagwi mayuglig Dio-licat bidmajuirgjee, ooshrm boiruud jaquedrr jadminrglig brrt ishanminrri oje iimaijani Dios shancalidu jajet.
43003003	Oyat Jesús mog jan, rjeta amog man, naajri ishanyri jajuju-jet yauya jashiquedrliprn jaluuglig Dioat cajuiberliprn-teja jaepinota caligjee.
43003004	Oyat Nicoderno mog jan, brwrnjam quepaat jadquedrg shririg jayrgjee jajuju-jet. Jadshri quedrriwrnjam jaluuglig jaiin narndeja jayrgjee-shri jajuju-jet.
43003005	Oyat Jesús mog jan, rjeta amo man, naajri ishanyri Dios yerogjet Espíritu Santojet poi, jashishanquedrtya jaluugshirig Dioat cajuiberliprn-teja jaepinota caligjee.
43003006	Nat iyrgot wryu tepinot-shrt jaligwi ealat mot bigshayu. Ooshrt nat iyrgot Espíritu-jet jalig ealat Espíritu bigshayu.
43003007	Macupoiyiglrg jashrm naa oodamog man, manwi mashiyrr jajuju-jet.
43003008	Naajri jiim ebujaprg brm jaligui, janoot ijui ooshrtjri yau japishimawaaliprn boiat jaligu jayuu. Yau poi japishimawaaliprn brm jaligu janoo. Ojera poi wrijin nat iyrgot jajuju-jet Espíritu-jet.
43003009	Oyat Nicodemoat jashrirm, brjaliyujam naa oodmamog.
43003010	Oyat Jesúat jayerog waorg, jamog jan, mam israelot juirr, yau-tejam japishimawaaliprn naa-jaa amog.
43003011	Rjeta amog man, biuyaad jajaa naa pishibiwaagprn, biupin jajaa naa ibiruugprn, ooshrt brr-shandit biyerog waorr.
43003012	Yau-jaligu ayerog pishiyawaaliprn wryupinot-jaa, brrwrnjam ayerog yawaorgshirig shrnopinot-jaa.
43003013	Brr-shanditju ijoon shrnoja, oowi naa itnn iwonprn shrnoat, oowi naa shrnoatwin Iyrgli wryu jaluugjee.
43003014	Oje Moiséat jawrryrrlauniri shrp pun-jaa yee-uu, ojeyala poi aashirirglig adwrgyrgjee am Iyrgli wryu aluugjee.
43003015	Carmdrg-shrtya ashrt wrijin nat cajiirirt ajaa, ooshrt ashiribrgya calat wryu ishanbeji.
43003016	Dioat cayii ruug nat wryu tepinot, ooshrmda jadcui calat jaWá itnnwi, carmdrg-shrtya jashrt wrijin nat cajiirirt jajaa, ooshrt jashirirbrgya calat wryu ishanbeji.
43003017	Yau Dioat jaWá cuiriprn wryu-teja cainot shijapinjee ebupaacacrt shirig nat wryu tepinolat. Ooshrt jaWá jacui cadjajeiconjee ebupaacacrt-shrtya canogjee Paraíso-teja.
43003018	Naajri jajiirirrm Dios Wá-jaa, yauya jainotshi cashipindiprn ebupaajaertjee japecado-shrm. Ooshrt naa jajii shandirri jashirigya jajaa naa orden jalirr ebupaajacrdig japecado-shrm, jajii jashandirt-shrm jajaa naa Dios Wá itnnwi.
43003019	Dioat cashinam jashrt ebupaacacrtjee nat epinot ibagot, jayugshrm nan wryu-teja naa Ebushiwryu. Oyat jayii canomjriruug cabigsahyu ibrruprnjin jashrt naa Ebushiwryu, jadjeu-shrm ieb caminrglig.
43003020	Wrijin nat iebminrt, jaeb jadduuglig naa Ebushiwryu. Yau jadnargshuuliprn naa Ebushiwryu cadjatadrg-shrt jajet naa ieb idminrg.
43003021	Ooshrt nat jajewet caliglig jajaa naa moyerog rjetwin, cayug inagjet jalica naa Ebushiwryu cadjatadrgjee jajet naa idminrg Diosjaa.
43003022	Oyat boi wryulau Jesús nog Judea niti-jaa idjajuirgprnot jriat. Oyat; jalig cajet bautisao cadjarg epinot on.

43003024	Ooshrm jadshanju-nam Juan presoja moliiriprnteja.

43003028	Yandawi jayashijui yapinrgli ishalalig-jet, arn shandita naa Cristo Dioat icuiprn. Oolawi adcuirig ayugjee Cristo juprta, jainot shiapinjee jabatyataijeeya.
43003029	Jadminrgbat casamiento, oolawi juujet-uulig pin oo-naa juujetbondig. Oyat jajrr shog jajet, jajii-jái jayerog jajuirig Dumatjri ojera poi am, ajiijái jainot ajuirig naa-jaa amoglig bŕn.
43003030	Dumatya Jesús iinot minjeeya jadjeujeeya wrijin, ooshrt amat ainot shiwonya.
43003031	Naa iyugprn shrnoat jabigshayu inomjri-jeirig wrijin-shrt. Oyat naa wryu tepin, wryu pinda jabigshayu oo, ooshrmda jayaad naa wryu-jaa. Ooshrt naa iyugprn shrnoat janomjri-jeirig jabigshayu wrijin-shrt.
43003032	Ooshrmda jayaad jajaa naa idduugprn idjuiprn poi shrnoja, ooshrt brr-shandit jayerog waorr.

43004001	Oyatjri nat fariseoot Jesús iinot cajui cabajalig idjajuirgprnot Juan-shrt, bautisao idjargprnot poi.

43004003	Jesúat japishiwaagbat jainot cajuiricat, janog Judea-teat jauprtjee Galilea-teja.
43004004	Oyatjri janogbat jawug Samaria niti jamaiye.
43004005	Oyat jamin-nog boi moyan-teja Samaria-tee jatarn Sicar, inagjetwi naa niti-shrt Jacobat irirgli jaWá Joséat.

43004021	Oyat Jesús mog jan, mam den, jamaujui naa oodamog, boi wryulauya yauya yashishri-nooliprn wen-jaja ijei yabrgjeecugjin Bii Dioat, yauya poi-shri Jerusalén-teja.
43004022	Yam Samaria tepinot, yau japishiyawaahprn naa ood-ijei yabrg. Ooshrt bidujri japishibiwaagwi naa ood-ijei bibrg, ooshrm judioot pei naa jet-cadjajeicon ebupaacacrt-shrtya capecado-jaa.

43004024	Mojii ijeira naa Dios, oyatjri nat ijei-brt jan, calatwi ijei cashibrr jan cajii-teat rjet.

43004026	Oyat Jesús mog jan, amdawi naa jeiyateiprn ayuglig, arnwi naa iyaad majet.

43004036	Naajri ibeepe bijuibiberliprn-tee jashiribrgya jan jarnii naa jabeeb. Oyatjri nat juijashugprnot cadjashiruugya wryu ishanbejiteja, jajii jáijeeya naa ijrma jajet naa ebujuishum.
43004037	Rjetwinda naa oodcamoglig, ijrmrla naa itrm, oyat itrm poi naa ebujuishum.

43004051	Oyat jaminocadu inagjet jaot-shrt, cayug jaubata jabatcatai nat jajetwinolat. Camog jan, jajuglawi mawá.

43004054	Jesúat iminrg jacauyujaye naa brrt ishanquedrri jairninrglig, jauprt quedyem Judea-shrt Galilea-teja.
43005001	Oyat jadrninrg itrm cajuicaberliprn nat judioolat, ooshrmda Jesús nog jerusalén-teja cajuibeeriprn-teja.

43005003	Ondi cabaa itaabot iyegshogot jajan, bigrriprnotjin poi, ipeeprnprnotjin poi, imyugprnotjin poi. Jajeicatri rt yaijee.
43005004	Omdi itrm, ángele won itrmnogu, jadirg rt yaijee. Oyatjri naa iruugjurg rt-teja, rt yaibat oowi jajeirig moebyu-shrt.

43005007	Oyat naa iiriyugprnjin mog Jesúat, Áŕri, boirnuda ajrr jet-aluug nan rt-teja jayaibat naa rt. Anogshicom yrmijetwi boi ruug-jurcat ajuprta rt-teja.
43005008	Oyat Jesús mog jan, majuicumig, majeepe mauwao maubog.
43005009	Oowiat jajeirüglig naa bon, jadwao jajeepe jaboocat. Oo wryulau jijacaliiriprn-tee Jesúat jajeicon.
43005010	Oyat nat judioot, camog jan naa Jesúat ijeiconprnot, oo-naa wryujri jijabiiririprn. Jadshandirt man jamarmogjee majeepe jatee naa wryu.

43005013	Ooshrtjri naa Jesúat ijeiconprn, yau japishijawaaliprn boirig jaligu jajeicono, ooshrm Jesús uuprlat cashrt, oyat cabag epinot diglig on.
43005014	Oyat Jesúat jatairirg templo-tee naa idjeiconprn. Jamog jan dumat majeiyatpeg, ieb macushriminrtya mashinomjri ebdajamo maliiprndi-shrt.

43005020	Naa Jaii jayii-jaluug JaWá, ooshrmda jadtadrg wrijin jabigshayu-jet. Oyat jadshishri-tadrgya inomjri-jeirigjet yaomjeeya jayaluuglig.
43005021	Ojewi Jaiiat cabiglewrrlauni irriprnotjin cajugjeeya-shri. Ojera poi jaWáat calirglig cajugjeeya-shri wrijin brjaligu catog idjajeuot.
43005022	Yau Biiat cainot shipindiprn, ooshrtjri jadirg jaWáat cainot shipindig wrijin ebupaacacrtjee caebyu-shrm o ebupaacashanertjee

43005024	Rjeta amo yan, naajri ayerog juiyu, naa jajii-rimn jajaa naa acuiyu nani, jashiribrgya jan wryu ishanbeji. Ebupaajashishancrtya japecado-jaa ooshrm jawucat jashrt naa jalirrli jarririg Dios-shrt. Jalibrgwi jan wryu ishanbeji.
43005025	Rjeta amo yan, boi wryulauya dumatya poi, natjri irriprnotjin jadshijuiya cadjaágrg naa Dios Wáat. Oyatjri cashijugyawi nat jajuiyut.
43005026	Ijuglawi naa Bii, ooshrmda cadjaquedrg cajugwirig nat epinot. Ojera-poiwi jabigshayu jabrglig jaWáat cadjajuurgjee nat irriprnotjin.
43005027	Oyat moyerog jalirbrg jaWáat cainot shijapinjeeya wrijin ebu paacacrtjee capecado prta, o rri-jaligjeeya ebupaacacrdig, oojaligshrm naa Iyrg wryu jaluugjee.

43007048	Itrm iinodigot peiat jajii-rirrijam jajaa, yau-poi itrm fariseot peiat.

43007050	Oyatjri naa Nicodemo, itrm capei nat fariseoot, naa iyugprndi Jesús-lica shairei.
43007051	Jamog calat, Moisés yerocat jalirrijam itrm jainot shibipinjee ebupaajacrtjee jajuprduju jabirmdig jajainot shijapinjee japishibiwaagjee jajaa naa idminrg.
43007052	Oyat camog Nicodemoat, mam-tejam poi Galilea atwin. Jamauleeg mamaujuirg ijeijet idnagprn-tee papera, japishimawaagjee, boiruuda itrm profeta iyug Galilea-teat.
43007053	Oyatjri cauprt caot-teja catojani.
43008001	Oyat Jesús nog wen-teja jatarn Olivos.
43008002	Oyat shaireiju jaushriprt templo-teja, oyat wrijin nat epinot cayug jalica. Oyat jateg banco-jaa cadjajuirgjee
43008003	Oyat nat inaat fariseoot poi, jadnyug Jesú-lica itrm den itairirg inogprn jabon-shrt boi bon-jet. Oyat jadirg jashoglig cajewalee wrijin.
43008004	Oyat camog Jesúat, mam ijuirr, jadtairirg naa den inogprn boi bon-jet jabon-shrt.
43008005	Moiséat inagprn mog birat cadbirrirgjee jaajet nat detpat oiirigot. Oyat mamjri, bojejam mamo jajaa.
43008006	Ojeri camo jan jadjeu-shrm jai-caepindig boyeja-jaligu jamo Moisés yerog-shrt. Ooshrt Jesús woopjog idnagjee niti-uu jalapcarn juprt-jet.
43008007	Oyat yau caquediprn Jesús carmdig brjaligu jashimog jajaa naa den. Oyat Jesús juirniishog jamog calat, naa yapei ebyu-rri jadcujuug-jurg jaa-jet.
43008008	Oyat Jesús shri woopjog idnagjee niti-uu.
43008009	Oyat nat mot jadjuibat Jesúat oodmog calat cauuyig caebyu lig-shrm. Oyat catrmnogpayeg jashrt. Nat quepaat ootda inog jurgot cajuprta. Oyat cabeenog quedyern wrijin orndawi Jesús lii jatrmatwi, oopoi naa den.
43008010	Oyat Jesús juimiishog, boirigshandit iduug oowi naa den. Oyat jamog jan, mam den, brrnjam calii nat mai pinitprnot. Yau-tejam brrt jalirliprn ebupaamacrtdig.
43008011	Oyat naa den mog jan, brr-shandit Arri. Oyat Jesús mog jan, yaula poi jalirliprn ebupaarnacrdig. Dumatjri maunog, ieb macushriminrtya.
43008012	Oyat Jesús shri-yaad nat epinolat jamog, amdawi Wryushiwryu. Naajri ibog ajet, yauya jabigshayu shibrruliprn, ooshrt jashiribrgya jan naa Ebushiwryu jalirr wryu ishanbeji.
43008013	Oyat nat fariseoot camog Jesúat, mainotshi mapinwi ijeijet ooshrmda boirica shandit naa oodmamog.

43008015	Yarnjri brrt iiyaepin oje mot bigshayuat jaliirlauni, ooshrt amjri boirig-shandit iaepin.
43008016	Boi iacaepinu, rjetda acug-mo jajaaom ooshrm ashantnniwi am, ajrrja jalig Aii, naa acuiyuprndi nani.
