43008018	Amjri ai-apin aaleewi, oyat naa Aíi acuiyuprn nani, ai-japoipin.
43008019	Oyat Jesús carm, brm-jam maíi ni. Oyat Jesús mog calat, yau apishiyawaaliprn am, yau-poi Aíi pishiyawaaliprn. Apishiyacawagu amjri, Aíi pishiyacupoiwaag-om.
43008020	Jesúat jaipin calat naa moyerog templo-tee cadjajuirgbat inagjetwi caofrenda ot-shrt, ooshrt brr-shandit preso-jarm, ooshrm jabigye shanjuminui.
43008021	Oyat Jesús shri-mog calat, ashinogya yashrt, oyat ayashijeuya am, oyat yashirriya yapecado-jet. Yauya yayashiquedrrliprn yanoglig on anoca.
43008022	Oyat camog nat judioot, jaaleitejam jashirrirrya, ooshrm jamog, yauya yayashiquedrrliprn yanoglig on anoca.
43008023	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yamdawi binompinot, amdawi shrnoatwin. Yamda naa wryu pinit-tep, amdawi naa wryu-pin shandit.

43008025	Oyat camog Jesúat, brr-jam mam. Oyat Jesús mog calat, amdawi naa oodamogprn yajuirg jurgbatdi dumatpatjri.
43008026	Jabaglaju moyerog ajuprtu jet-yashipinrg, jabag poi yai-apinshirig. Rjetda naa acuiyuli nani, oyat naa moyerog ijuiprn jajet oolawi naa moyerog oodamog calat nat wryu tepinolat wrijin.
43008027	Oyat nat epinot yau japishicawaaliprn Jesús yaadig Bií Diosjaa.

43008029	Jaligdawi ajet naa acuiyuli nani. Naa Aíi yau adirrliprn itrmjetwi jajáirg-shrm oiirig jajet naa iminrg.
43008030	Jesúat jaipinbat naa moyerog, ibagjetda epinolat cajii-rirr jajaa.
43008031	Oyat Jesús mog calat nat judioolat cajii-rirt jajaa, yaliguya jajaa tai-imogjet naa moyerog oodamog yan, rjetda idajuirgprnota yashirii jamo.
43008032	Oyatya japishiyashiwaa brjaliyu jaligu naa moyerog rjetwin, oyat naa moyerog rjetwin yadsnishiuya.

43008041	Yam iyaminrg oje yaíiat irjani. Oyat camog jan, íi-rriprnot shanditda bidu, jaligdawi Bií oola Dios.

43008043	Boirigshrmjam japishiyashanwaji brjaliyu jaligu naa oodarnog. Yau japishiyawaaliprn jaiaa jayashanjeu-shrm jabatyatairig yajiiteat naa moyerog ijuirg
43008044	Yaíira moweijin, japinita yam, ooshrmda jayaujeu iyaminrglig oje jadjeulauni. Epin rrirrla naa moweijin wryu minjurgbatdi dumatpatjri. Yau jaliiriprn moyerog rjetwin-jaa, rjet shandit-shrm jabigshayu. Boiruud rjetwin jajii-tee ooshrm teeshauprnjina jalig. Oola moteeshauyu íi naa moweijin.
43008045	Ooshrt amjri, jaiapin yan moyerog rjetwin, ooshrmda jayashanquedrri ayerog yawaorglig.
43008046	Brr-jam yapei jaquedrm pecado jaluuglig ajaa. Ooshrmda jaiapinu yan moyerog rjetwin, boirigshrmjam ayerog yashanwaorri.
43008047	Natjri Dios pinit, Dios yerog cajui, ooshrt Dios pinit shandita yam ooshrmda jayerog yashanjui shui.
43008048	Oyat nat judioot camog Jesúat, rjet shandit-tejam naa oodbimog, Samaría teatwinda mam, demoniola irig majii-tee.

43008053	Majeiyijam mam biroom Abraam-shrt. Bŕn jarriri, natpoi oyem brrt profetaotdi. Oyat mamjri jamajewijam majeirig wrijin-shrt.

43008055	Yamjri yau japishiyawaaliprn Dios, ooshrt amjri japishiawaagwi. Japishiashanwaat amogu, teeshauprnjincug am-jamo oje yalijani. Ooshrt japishiawaagwi Dios, oyat jayerog awaorg poi.
43008056	Naa yaloom Abraam, ijáijetdí jajeijatei abigye minogjee, oyat jadduug oyat jajii-jái.

43009001	Oyat Jesús wugbat boi moyan-tee, itrm bon jaluug, jabigrriri jaminyrglig jaíin-shrt.

43009004	Andawi jashirninr naa minrg jacui an naa acuiyuat nani iwrgshicomju, ooshrm bishicubya oyat brr-shanditya ishiquedrridbeebdig.
43009005	Amdawi Wryushiwryu ajuligbat naa wryu-tee.
43009006	Jesiíat capinrg quedyem oje, ebushijashrg niti-uu sho jaminrg jacopogjriwao, oyat jadirg jabig-tee naa bigrriprnjin.

43009010	Oyatjri camog jan, bojejam mabiglig-pegli.

43009015	Oyat nat fariseoot jadrm jadjuijee brjaligu jabigliglig. Oyat jamog calat, sho jalirg abig-tee, oyat arnag, ooshrmjri dumat iruucatpeg.
43009016	Oyat itrmnogot fariseoot mog, Dios licatwin shandita naa Jesús, ooshrmda jajayigjarrirg naa wryu jijabiriiriprn. Ooshrt itrmnogot mog, iebprnjin caligu jadquedrrijam jadminrglig brrt ishanminrri. Ooshrm cabigshayu cau nat fariseoot.
43009017	Oyat jadshri-rm naa bigrriprnjin, camog jan, mam-poi bojejarn mamo jajaa naa bon jalirr irnaluuglig. Oyat jamog, jaiashag profetaja jaliglig.
43009018	Nat judioot yau jaicashaaliprn bigrriprnjina jaligli rjet naa biglicat dumat, ooshrm cadcaág jaquepaat cadcarmjee jajaa,

43009020	Oyat jaquepaat mog, japishibiwaagwi bitrria jaliglig oo-naa, Japishibiwaagwi jabigrriliglig jatrtdigli jaíin-shrt.

43009022	Ojera camog nat jaquepat caom-shrm judioot rca, ooshrm nat judioot camogli jabishinamya sinagoga-teat bijaligu Dioat icuiprn imog Jesús-jaa.
43009023	Ooshrm jaquepaat mog, quepaatda naa bitrri jayaurm.
43009024	Oyat jadshri-ág naa bigrriprnjindi, camog jan, dumat ijei maubrg itnnwi Dioat. Japishibiwaagwi iebprnjina jaliglig naa Jesús.
43009025	Oyat naa bigrriprnjindi jamog calat, japishiashanwaat iebprnjina jaliglig. Jatrmdawi pishiawaag, bŕn abigrriprndig, ooshrt dumat abiglicatpeg.
43009026	Oyat camog jan, bojejarn idr man. Bojejam mad-r imaluugjee.
43009027	Oyat jamog calat, yapinrcatni oyat yau ayerog yajuinprn. Boirigshrmjam jayapatjeijeu jainot yajuirig. Jayajewica poi idjajuirgprnota iyaligjee.
43009028	Oyat jadmrn camog, mamdawi idjuirgprn, ooshrt bidujri Moiséat ijuirgprnotda bidu.
43009029	Japishibiwaagwi Dios yaadig Moiséat bŕn, ooshrt naa Jesús japishibishanwaat boyatwin jaligu.

43009031	Japishibiwaagwi Dioat cayerog shanjui nat iebminrt. Ooshrt Dioat cayerogjui nat ijei-brg jan, idminrgu oje jadjeulauni.

43009038	Oyat jamog Jesiíat, mam Arri, ajii alirg majaa. Oyat jateg jautjuiyag-jet ijei jabrgjee Jesúat.
43009039	Oyat Jesús mog, ayug wryu-teja cainot shiapinjee nat wryu tepinot, idduugjee nat bigrriolat, oyat idshanpoiruudjee nat iruuglawi arnat imogot.
43009040	Oyat itrmnogot fariseoot jacoopinot, jadjuibat cadjapinrglig carnog jan, bigrriprnotjin-tejam poi bidu.
43009041	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yabicarriu-om boicugluud yaebyu yajaa-om. Ooshrt yamjri ibiruug yamog, ooshrmda yaebyu lig yajaa.
43010001	Rjetda amog yan, ishegprnjinda naa ijon jaluugjee ovejaat wai-teja ijaanjet, naa ishanduuqui wai-yeiye.
43010002	Ooshrt naa iruug wai-yeiye oola ovejaat ijewet.
43010003	Oyat naa waiyee ijewet jajuijayiibrg jan. Oyat nat ovejaat jayerog cajui naa caijewet. Oyat jaovejaat jaág catam-jet, cadjarrnogjee wai-teat.
43010004	Oyat cadjayrrg quedyem jaovejaat wrijin wai-teat, janog cajúprta naa caijewe, oyat canog japrna jayerog pishicawaag-shrm.

43010010	Naa shegprnjin jayug jashegjee, epin jarrirgjee poi, cadjaebrgjee poi. Ooshrt amjri ayug cajuugjeeyawi ajuuyu-jet cajuituunjeeya awairiyu-jet oiiricawiat.
43010011	Amdawi naa Ebushijewe ijei. Naa Ebushijewe ijei jajalirg jadrrirgjee jaovejaat-shrm.
43010012	Naajri ibeepe jayuiot jaougjee, jadduugbat jayuglig naa yoodan, jacuut cadjanamnogjee nat oveja ebushijeweja shandit-shrm, japinit shandit-shrm. Oowi yoodanat cawaorglig nat ovejaat, cadjaniirei.
43010013	Jacuut ovejaat-shrt naa ibeepe palata-shrm, idbeeb-shrm jayuiot catrm-müja. Boirica shandit jan nat ovejaat.
43010014	Amdawi naa Ebushijewe ijei. Capishiawaagwi nat aovejaat ojewi Aíiat apishiwaalauni.
43010015	Oyat aovejaat apishicawaag poi oje Aíi pishiawaalauni. Oyat aalirg adrrirgjee aoveja-shrm.

43010017	Aíiat ayii-ruu am aalirg-shrm adrrirglig ashrijugjeeya.
43010018	Brrshandit jalirr arrijee, ooshrt aaleira aliirr adrrirgjee. Jaquedrg aalirglig adrrirgjee, jashriquedrg poi aalirglig ajugjee-shri.
43010019	Oyat nat judioot cabigshayu shri-cau jadjuibat naa Jesúat oodmog calat.
43010020	Cabag capet imogot, demoniola irig jan, wryu pishijashanwaat. Boirigshrmjam jayerog yajui.
43010021	Oyat brrt mog, naajri ood-demonio liibrg yau jadquedrliprn jayaadig ijeijet oje jalijani naa Jesús. Demonioat jaquedrrijam jadirglig idduugjee nat bigrriolat.
43010022	Oyat rt-yrgnom jadminr cajuibeeriprn jatarn dedicasión Jerusalén-tee.
43010023	Oyat Jesús bog templo-tee, Salomón colelot-tee.
43010024	Oyat nat judioot cajuicaberg Jesús coo, carnog jan, brrjam japrnshishoo wooja bidmashirg. Dioat icuiprn jaligu mam, bidmaupinrg ishalalig-jet.
43010025	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yapinrcatni ooshrt yau jayajuiriprn naa oodamogli yan. Naa iminrg Aíi tam-jaa jadirgwi apishiyawaagwi Dioat icuiprna aliglig.
43010026	Ooshrt yau ayerog yajuiriprn aovejaata yashandit-shrm oje amojaniri bŕn.
43010027	Aovejaat ayerog cajui, capishiawaagwi, oyat canog aprna.

43010030	Amjri Aíi-jet bi trm wi.
43010031	Oyat nat judioot jamolugot cashri-oug Jesús carrirgjee.

43010033	Oyat carnog jan nat judioot, yaula mabishirrirliprn ijei maminryu-shrm. Ooshrt jajayigmarrirg-shrm Dios jajet naa oodmamog. Bon man, ooshrt jamajeu Dioja maliglig.

43020030	Jesúat jaminrg ibagjet brrt ishanminrri jadduugjee nat idjajuirgprnolat, natjri ashan-nai jatee naa papera.
43020031	Ooshrt janag naa papera japishiyawaagjee Dioat icuiprna jaliglig naa Jesús, japishiyawaagjee Dios Wája jaliglig, jalibrgjeeya yan wryu ishanbeji yajii yalirg-shrm jajaa.
43021001	Oyat boi wryulauya Jesúat jalirg jadduugjee shri nat idjajuirgprnolat. Rt ipeg-coo jatain Tiberias jajalirg jadduuglig.
43021002	Cajuicaberg nat Simón Pedro, Tomás jatam Dídimo poi, Nata- nael poi Cana-Galileaatwin, oyat nat Zebedeo trriot poi, oyat cacan poi Jesúat ijuirgprnot.
43021003	Oyat Simón Pedro mog calat, yrri ashirrir-nogla arnat. Oyat camog jan, bishinog majet. Oowi caluuglig já-teja canogjee, ooshrt yau boi caouliprn oolau shairei.
43021004	Oyat caiwryucatu Jesúat jaalirg jadduugjee mai-jaa, ooshrt nat idjajuirgprnot yau japishicawaaliprn Jesüja jaliglig.

43021007	Oyat naa Jesúat ijuiprn yii-jaluugprn jamog Pedroat, oolawi Biŕri duu. Simón Pedroat jajuibat Biŕri jaliglig, oowi jacamisa jayuirig ooshrm jadruli jashrt jayou janamjee. Oyat jalrrluug rt-teja janogjee mogwaini Jesú-lica.
43021008	Oyat nat brrt Jesúat ijuirgprnot canog já-tee Pedro-prna mai-jaa. Jadjig cayou caprnat jajuituun yrriot-jet, jayryaibrjin sien metro jaligjee mai-shrt.
43021009	Oyat cayrcadu mai-jaa jadduug drr, jadduug poi yrri drr-bigu, an poi.
43021010	Oyat Jesús mog calat, boi yaurryubrg an capeiu nat idyaougprnot.

43021012	Oyat Jesús mog calat, yayeecowayucat. Yau itrm idjajuirg- prnolat jarmdiprn, brr mam, caom-shrm jarea, japishicawaag-shrm poi Caŕri jaliglig naa idduug.
43021013	Oyat Jesúat canaarg jadwao naa an jalap-uu, jadbrg calat, yrri poi.
43021014	Oola jaipoiyu Jesúat jaatadrglig jadduugjee nat idjajuirgprnolat jajuimig quedyem morriyu-shrt.
43021015	Oyat cayewai quedyem Jesús mog Simón Pedroat, mam Simón, Jonás wá, ayii malujijarn ijeijet brrt-shrt. Oyat Pedro mog jan, rcaji Aŕri, japishimawaagwmwi raayii aluuglig. Oyat Jesús mog jan, cawoug maubrg nat acorderoat.
43021016	Oyat Jesúat jashrirm, Simón, Jonás wá, ayii malujijam. Oyat Pedro mog jan, rcaji Aŕri, japishirnawaagwrnwi mayii aluuglig. Oyat Jesús mog jan, caimaujeu aovejaot.
43021017	Oyat Jesúat jashrirm jaipoiyu Simón, Jonás wá, ayii malujijarn. Oyat jajii-shŕm Pedro jadrm-shrm ipoi-jet ayii malujijam. Oyat jamog jan, mam Aŕri, japishimawaagwrni wrijin, japishimawaagwi mayii aluuglig. Oyat Jesús shri-mog jan, cawoug maubrg nat aovejaot.
43021018	Rjeta amog man, trriwaiya majuligbat, jamawrg mawrr mawin- tadye manogjee brm-jaligu jamajeu. Ooshrt quepaja malicatuya, maboo mauyrrnogya. Oyat boiat mashijiipya. Madshirrnogya on mashan-nogshuta.
43021019	Ojera Jesús mog Pedroat japishijawaagjee bijaliguya jarri-shirig Dios-shrm ijei jabrgjee jan. Jesúat jaipin quedyem naa moyerog, jamog jan, mauyucat aprna ebupaamacrtjee oje alijani.
43021020	Oyat Pedro jeuwug japrna jadduug jayuglig japrna naa Jesúat ijuirgprn yii-jaluugprn, naa jajuiyag caaleyeprn Jesús-jaa jadwougbat Pascua-tee, naa Aŕri, boia mashibrrn mabalolat imogprn jan.
43021021	Pedroat jaluugbat jayuglig caprna, jadrm Jesús, boyajam jashirii naa.
43021022	Oyat Jesús mog Pedroat, jajeuu jajugligjri ata-on ashriyuca boirig-yawana shandit man. Ooshrt mam, mauyucat aprna, ebupaarnacrtjee oje alijani.
43021023	Oyat nat jayerog waort camoyeg calat jashanrriyala naa boi Jesúat ijuirgprn. Ooshrt Jesús shan-raot jashishanrriya, oowi jamoglig, jajeuuju jaliglig ata-on ashriyucaya, boirica shandit man.
43021024	Oolawi naa Jesúat ijuirgprn jaipini naa idduugprn Jesús-jet. Oyat idnag jajaa papera-tee, ooshrmda japishibiwaag ijet jaliglig naa moyerog idnagprn.
43021025	Oyat jabagla ijei Jesúat iminrg idduuca, ooshrt jajri-jacanagu wrijin jajainot papera-tee, jaiashag jashan-cugjee togli naa wryu-tee om.
44001001	Mam Teófilo, apapera-tee anag jurg jaiapin wrijin jajaa naa Jesúat iminrg, wrijin poi jajaa naa idjuirg.
44001002	Inag Jesús-jaa wrijin jajuijawrg jurgbadi epinot jajuirglig, ata on jauprta cashrt shrnoja jaijapin quedyem naa moyerog idjajuirgprnolat. Caajapinrg Espíritu Santo-jet brjaliguya idshirg japrnot nat idja-ougprnoladi.
44001003	Oyat jarri quedyem Jesús, jayug calica cadjatadrgjee jajuglicat. Cuarenta jatog wryu jajalirli jadduug-jee jabiglewrg quedyem. Jadminrg ibagjet brrt ishanminrri japishibiwaagjee ijet Dioja jaliglig. Cadjapinrg brjaligu Dioat cajuiberglig jaepinota caligjee nat wryu tepinot.
44001004	Oyat Jesús juuligbat idjacuiprnot-jet cadjapinrg canog-shrt Jerusalén-teat, ooshrt jajeiyautei naa Aiiat oodmogprndi yan, naa iyajuiri ajet poi.
44001005	Bŕn Juanat bautisao carg epinot rt-jet, ooshrt iyai wryu prnotya bautisao iyadshirgya Espíritu Santo-jet.
44001006	Oyat nat ebujuishut Jesús jriat jadrrn, cayaa minyuyatjam nat israelot cadmasínujee cabalot-shrt, jamalirgjee bijriwairüca itrm bipei bidu israelot.
44001007	Oyat Jesús mog calat, boirica shandita yan japishiyawaagjee jajaa naa Dioat ishiminrgya jabigshayu-jet.
44001008	Ooshrt jawonbatya yajaa naa Espíritu Santo, jabigshayu iwairüg shirigya yajii-tee. Oyat yashinogya ainot shiyapinjee rjet wrijin Jerusalén-teja, wrijin Judea-teja poi. Samaria-teja poi, oyat wrijin naa wryu-teja ata on yaminocaya caniti-jaa nat inornjri yauot.
44001009	Jesúat jaipin quedyem naa moyerog, Jaíiat jawrryrg jadrmog shrnoja jadjuluugbat wrijin. Oyat itrm waojribrruat jaiwei cabigshrt.
44001010	Oyat jadyiijeu shogbatju Jesús noglig shrnoja, cacan mottrlot ishogot camauye, ibrgla cayuiot.
44001011	Oyat camog nat ángeleot, yam mot Galileatwinot, boirigshrmjam yanim shrnoja. Naa Jesús inog yashrt, jashiyugya-shri shrnoat ojeyawi jayaluulauni janoglig shrnoja.
44001012	Oyat Jesúat icuiprnot uprt Jerusaléma wen-jaat jatam Olivos, inagjetwi moyan-shrt naa wen-trri, Yaijet canogwi oje Moisés yerocat jalirlauni wryu jijacaliiriprn-tee.
44001013	Oyat caminogbat moyan-teja caluug mooleja, oyat cajón boi piso ishrn-teja, caouliprn nat Pedro, Jacobo poi, Juan, Andrés, Felipe, Tomás, Bartolemé, Mateo, Alfeo wá Jacobo poi, Simón Zelote, oo-poi Jacobo pewai Judas.
44001014	Itrmjanibrla cabigshayu-lii wrijin. Cajuicaberg Dios capinrgjee cajii-teat, cajriat nat Jesús pedwat, jaíin María poi, itrmnogot detpat poi. Yau cajaapdiprn Dios capinrglig.
44001015	Oyat Pedro juimii-shog cajewalee nat jajrrot Jesús yerog-waort, jaishaag ciento-vente catogli nat cajuibert on.
44001016	Oyat Pedro mog calat, ajrrot biyaa minocat jabirninrgjee naa Espíritu Santoat oodmogprndi David papera-tee jajaa naa Judas Iscariote carryuuli Jesús-lica nat jawaortdi.
44001017	Bŕn bijrrjindi naa Judas. Bŕn Jesúat jalirgli janogjee bijet jashrm naa ibibeebdi Dioat.
44001018	Oyat jamii cabrg itrm campo jajet naa plata idougprn jaebyu miija. Oyat jalrg pun-shrt jijog-jet niti-uja. Oyat japanmanog jajamaye, jawinyoot yrg jashrt wrijin.
44001019	Oyat jainot cajui wrijin nat Jerusalén tepinolat, oyat Aceldama jatam carg cayerog-jet naa campo. Oo jaliyula jatam Campo Momaaja irig.
44001020	Oowi idminrglig oje jamojani naa idnagli papera-uu jatam Sal mos. Ojera jamog, jayaulirg boishiruudya epin jacampo-tee, jayacupoirirt boi riglig jajan. Oyat jayaulirg boiat jabeebjee naa jabeebjin.

44001023	Oyat cadcalirg icauot mot, itrm José Barsabas jatam Justo poi, oyat Matías poi.
44001024	Oyat Dios capinrg, mam Biŕri, camog,marn cabigshayu pishiwaja wrijin. Dumat bimautadrg brr-jaligu capei imajeu.
44001025	Brr-jam naa imacuiprn bijet bijrrja bidjargjee jajaa naa ibibeeb man, naa Judas inamnogprndi jaebyu-shrm janogjee on-jalica dumat.

44002001	Oyat jaminogbat naa wryu jatam Pentecostés, cajuicabergbat itrm mo-lee wrijin nat Jesús yerog-waort.
44002002	Oyat boi noot cajui jayuglig shrnoat mogwaibmi noot-shrg oje jiimat iprrlauni jijogjet janoot cajui jijogjet japiip wrijin molee categu.
44002003	Oyat idduug oje drr ibrtni, oyat jajasheu naa drr-brlat jaligjee cajaa tojani itrm drr-brt.
44002004	Oyat cajuituun Espíritu Santo-jet oyat cayaad yawaatwinot yerog-jet oje Espíritu Santoat jalirlauni.
44002005	Omdi calii Jerusalén-tee ibagot judioot ijei-brrt Dioat. Cayucat wrijin caniti-teat.

44002007	Caom ipegjet nat jajuiyut, camog caaleiat, Galilea atwinolat shandit-tejam nat iyaalot.
44002008	Boirigshrmwrnjam jabipoijui cayaadig biyerog-jet bitojani.
44002009	Ooda nat irigot bijewalee iyugprnot Partíateat, Media atwinot poi, Elam atwinot, Mesopatamia atwinot, Judea atwinot, Capadocia atwinot, Ponto atwinot, Asia atwinot poi.
44002010	Calig poi bijewalee nat iyugprnot Frigia-teat, Panfilia-teat poi, Egipto atwinot, Africa atwinot boyaja Cirene-shrt, otpoi nat Roma atwinot inirnyugot birica, judiot poi capet itrmnogot, oyat judiolat ijuirgprnota nat brrt.

44002014	Oyat Pedro juimii-shog cajriat nat once itogot Jesúat icuiprnot. Cayaad ishrgjet, jamog calat, yam mot Judea tepinot, yampoi irigot Jerusalén-tee, jayaulirg ayaadjee yajet japishiyawaagjee ijeijet bijaliyu jaligu naa iyajui yayerog-jet. Jayaujui ijeijet naa oodamog.
44002015	Cashan-wonda nat mot oje carnoolauni nat itrmnogot, oowiju ora-nueve jalig.

44002017	Ojeri jamo Dios, boi wryulauya jashibadya cajaa aEspíritu nat wryu tepinot wrijin. Oyat camashiwaiya Espíritu-jet nat yatrriot mot yalouot poi, oyat nat mot-trrlot jadshiruugya brrt ishanduji, oyat nat quepaat cayrgrri shirigya oje Espírituat jalirlauni.
44002018	Oyat oo-wryulauya jashibat cajaa aEspíritu nat ibeebet an, nat mot detpat poi. Oyat jaicashipinya naa moyerog irirbrg calat cajiitee.
44002019	Cadashitadrgya wryu-uja jajet naa idshanjuduji, iishanduji poi naa wryu-tee. Jadshiruugya mornaa, drr poi, drr-ai poi.
44002020	Oyat jashibrruya naa yamat, oyat jashicrtya naa jrbot jajuprduyaju jayuglig naa wryu ijei jayuulauya naa Biŕri.
44002021	Oyatya wrijin nat ja-ájet Biŕri tarn-jaa, cadjashiougya ieb-shrt, cadjarrnogjee shrnoja.
44002022	Oyat Pedro shriyaad, yam mot israelot, jayaujui dumat naa oodamog jajaa naa Jesús Nazareatwin. Dioat jalirg japishibiwaagjee idcuiprna jaliglig naa Jesús jadminrg-shrm ibagjet brrt ishanduji, brrt ishanminrri poi yajewalee jabigshayu iwairüg-jet, yamdawi japishicuwajat.
44002023	Oyat jadbrg naa Jesús jabalolat jadrrirgjee, ooshrt Dioat jaiwin-shanshot cashrt oid-rglig japishijawaag-shrm bŕnju bjjaliguya idshirg jajet naa paajashicrt. Oyat yam presoja jayargli jayalirgjee calap-uja nat iebnogprnotjin jadrrirgjee crusa-jaa.
44002024	Oyat Dioat jawrryrg naa Jesús, jadshiu morriyu-shrt, ooshrt yau morriyuat jaquedrliprn jadjiipdig.
44002025	Naa biroom David poi-mogli Jesús-jaa, Jaluug Aŕri ajuprta oiirigwi, jashog awireat aorn-shrt boi rca, brrt ashan-quedrtjee adpiiprglig.
44002026	Ooshrmda ajii-jái, ayaad moyerog ijáijet alogjet, ooshrm ataaleat jaquedrg jijajaliglig, ijei jeiateíjee.
44002027	Amashishan-narnnotya irriprnotjin liiriprn-tee, jamashishanpoirirtya jataale cairig naa majetwin ijei.

44002029	Ajrrot, jaquedrg yapinrglig ishalalig-jet jajaa naa biroom David. Bŕn jarriri, oyat jadbrg irriprnjin ot-tee.
44002030	Dios yerog shipiniri naa David, ooshrmda japishijawaag naa Dioat oodmogli jan jijogjet. Ojerijamog, itrmya majriwai ishiteg mabanco-jaa cajriwairüca jaligjeeya wrijin.
44002031	Naa Davirat jaluugli Espíritu-jet naa Dioat icuiprn Cristo jajuimiglig morriyu-shrt. Ooshrmda jarnog jajaa jashishanditya inriprnotjin liiriprn-tee, yauya poi jataalejin shicairiprn.

44002037	Oyat nat epinot jadjuibat naa Pedroat oodmog, cayii-shŕm ipegjet. Oyat jadrrn Pedro, nat-poi brrt Jesúat icuiprnot, camog, yam bijrrot, boirigjam ibishirninrg dumat.

44002039	Naa Espíritu Dioat oodmogprndi biroomolat, dumat yadpoipinrg, nalat poi oyem yawaja irigolat wrijin, nalat poi wrijin nat Biŕriat iágprnot jalica.

44002041	Oyat nat Pedro yerog juiyut cajii-jái, oyat bautisao cadcarg. Oolau wryu jayriyaijin tres-mil catogjee nat iruugot cajet nat Dios yerog waort.

44002044	Oyat itrmjanibr cabigshayu-lig nat cajii-rirt Jesús-jaa, itrmjani jatog poi capin.

44002046	Oyat wryu-shitojani caluug templo-teja wrijin, jatrmwi cabigshayu. Cajuicaberg wrijin mofee poi, an cabrteg, cayewai wrijin jii-jáijet, rjeta cabigshayu wrijin.
44002047	Ijei iicapin Dioat oiirigwi nat jayerog-waort, oyat nat brrt epinot wrijin cadcaluug ijeijet. Oyat wryu shitojani Biŕriat calirg canomjri-bajalig epinot iruugot cajet, nat idjajeiconprnot ishishanrmdriotya jashrt.
44003001	Oyat boi-wryulau canog templo-teja nat Pedro Juan poi jashrm naa culto oración idminrg cuprn.
44003002	Omda boi-rii itrm bon ishanshoiprnjin, japep eb jayrglig jaiin-shrt. Wryu shitojani jajrrolat jarrnog templo otyeja jatam Ijei, jadirg jateglig jarn-u palata jarrnjee cashrt nat iruugot templo-teja.
44003003	Oyat naa ishanshoiprnjin jaduugbat Pedro yuglig Juan poi caluugjee templo-teja, palata jarm cashrt.

44003006	Oyat Pedro mog jan, boiruuda palata alica, rripoi oro, ooshrt jashibrg man naa irig-alica. Dumatjri majuicumig maubog jatam-jaa naa Jesucristo Nazareatwin.
44003007	Oyat Pedroat jalap waorg jawiie-jet jadwrryrg. Oyat oowiat jawairüglig jashiim jatat-jamalag poi.

44003010	Japishicawaag oo jaliglig naa ishanshoiprnjindi, itegli plata jaimbat templo otyee jatam Ijei, ooshrmda caom, boiat boi shanjeicon-shrmdi oje jalijani.
44003011	Oyat naa ishanshoiprnjindi jadjuwaobat naa Pedroat Juanat poi, wrijin nat epinot caman calica templo coredor-tee jatam Salomón-pin. Cadcayiijeu jijogjet caom-shrm carca.
44003012	Oyat Pedroat jaluugbat jadyiijeulig nat epinot ibagolat, jamog calat, yam mot Israel jrdwat, boirigshrmjam yaom bidyaluuglig jajeirüyu shrrn naa bon. Jayashajijam bireí bigshayu-jet jabijeicondig, o bijeinog-shrmtejam Dioat biruuglig.
44003013	Bidu yau jabijeicondiprn naa bon, naa cajri-Dios nat biroomot Abraam, Isaac poi, Jacob poi, oolawi jajeicono japishiyawaagjee inomjri-jeirig wrijin-shrt naa jaWá Jesús, naa iyabrgprndi yajriwáirügolat, naa jayeg-yarrirgprndi Pilatoat inmea. 44003014	ooshrt jayanamdi yashrt naa Dios licatwin ijei, jayarmdi Pilato jadshiujee naa e pin rrirrprn jashrt naa pecado shánminrr.

44007007	Oyat Dios mog jan, jashirirgya ebupaacacrdig nat epinot presoja cashirdya nat majrdwat. Oyatya cashicuut cabalot-shrt, cashiyugya nani, ijei cashibrgya nam an.
44007008	Oyat Dioat boirirg itrm moyerog Abraamat. Jadirg jadminrgjee siconsisón jet-jatadrca jadminrglig jan oje jamojani. Oyat jaminyrg quedyem ja-wá Isaac, Abraamat siconsisao jarg ocho jatog quedyem wryu. Ojeri poi Isaacat ir ja-wá Jacobat. 44007009	Oyat nat biroomot, Jacob itrriot, jaeb caluug capeiwai itrt, caíiat jayiiruug-shrm cashrt. Oyat jadwenderg itrm Ejipto-coot jadrmogjee caniti-shrt, ooshrt Dios shog José coo.
44007010	Oyat Dioat jashiu José jashrt naa paajacrt wrijin, Dioat jalirg bicacoua-jaligjee, ijeijet jaduugjee naa Ejiptoot jriwairücat Faraón. Oyat Faraónat jalirg José caijajeujee wrijin Ejipto tepinot, jaot tepinot poi naa iwairüg.
44007011	Oyat bui paacacrt wrijin Ejipto-tee, Canaa-tee poi. Yau cawau ca boi catairirliprn nat biroomolat.
44007012	Oyat Jacobat jainot juibat jaligwirig trigo Ejipto-tee, cadjaqpinog jatrriot jajan cawouca mii cabrgjee.
44007013	Oyat canogbat shri Ejipto-teja, Joséat jajalirg japishicawaagjee capeiwai-pirica jaliglig. Oyat Joséat jalirg Faraónat capishiwaagjee jajrrota caliglig. Oyat Faraónat japishiwaag israelot pei-ya jaliglig naa José.
44007014	Oyat Joséat cacui jaíi Jacob carryugjee jalica ot-poi nat jajrrot wrijin, setenta-sinco itogot wrijin nat israelot.
44007015	Oyat Jacob nog jaligjee Ejipto-tee, oyat jarri on, oyat wrijin biroomot poi.
44007016	Ooshrt cataalejin carmog Siquem-teja cadcabrgjee irriprnjin ot jaacon-tee, naa Abraámat mii brgprndi plata-jet cashrt nat Hamor trriot Siquem-tee.
44007017	Oyat janaacadu jayaa naa Dios oodmogli Abraamat, cabacat nat jajrdwat Ejipto-tee, ooshrm cabag itrriot nat israelot jajan.

44007019	cateejashaurg biroomot, ieb jaminrg calat. Oyat Faraónat cacui catrriot canamjee carrijee nat jujet iminyrgot.
44007020	Oobatdi Moisés minyrr wryu jaluugjee. Ijeijeta Dioat jaluu, oyat jaíijirat jabigshugrg ipoi jrbot caot-tee ijaan-jet.
44007021	Oyat jadnamnog cashrt jatairirgjee naa cajriwairüg louat, oyat naa den jabigjashugrg jatrria naa Moisés.
44007022	Oyat jadjuirg naa Moisés wrijin ejiptoot bigshayu-jet, oyat iinodig iwairücatpeg, ijeira jabigshayu.
44007023	Oyat cuarenta años jancadu naa Moisés, janimnog calica nat jajrrot israelot.
44007024	Oyat jaduug itrm ejiptoat japairig itrm israelotpei, oyat Moiséat jajrrja-jarg naa israel, jadpai naa ejipto, jadrrirg.
44007025	Moiséat jaishaag japishicawaaglig Dioat jalirg-shirig cadjashiujee Ejipto-shrt nat jajrrot israelot, ooshrt yauju japishicawaaliprn.
44007026	Oyat brlemdicat Moiséat cashritairirg icauot israelot caprrtoglig. Oyat jadjeu cacajeicondig caaleolat, jamog calat, yam molí, jatnndawi yaloom, boirig-shrmjam ieb yaminrg yaaleat-tep.

44007030	Oyat cuarenta años prnat Moiséat itrm ángele duug punyunot ibrrlot-tee jaligbat brgu-tee wen mauu jatam Sinaí.
44007031	Moiséat jaluugbat naa ángele, oyat jadnargbat jadduuglig ijeijet, jadjui Biŕri moglig jan,
44007032	Amdawi maloomot jri-Dios. Amdawi Abraam jri-Dios, Isaac jri-Dios poi, Jacob jri-Dios poi. Oyat Moisés piip jaom-shrm, jabig shi-jawao jalap-jet ángele-shrt.
44007033	Oyat Biŕri mog jan, ca mau-oug mashiim-shrt masapatoot ooshrm apinda naa niti jaa-mashog.
44007034	Rjeta cadaluug aepinolat ebupaacrdig Ejipto-tee, jajuiwi caquiglig cajii shŕm-shrm, ooshrmda awonat cadashiujee. Dumat mauyucat mashicui nog Ejipto-teja.

44007041	Oyat boi caminrg becero oro-con, oyat cajiu carrirg naa ídolo oro-conat. Oyat caacajáirg jajet naa idminrgprn calap-jet.

44007043	Yaula ayeyawaalipin am idyarrirgprnot-jet. Bŕn cadyarmog yajiíprta yajri-dios Moloc liiriprn, yajri-dios Renfán crt, nat idoloot idyaminrgprnot yalap-jet ijei yabrgjee calat. Ooshrmya yashi-oug yaniti-teat, yadshirirgya yadrrnogjee inomjri-yawaligjet Babilonia-shrt.

44007050	Am shandit-tejam naa Iminrr wrijin boirig jaligui abigshayu-jet.
44007051	Oyat naa Esteban, cadjapinrg quedyem caloomotjin-jaa, jamog calat nat judioolat, yam juiyag shaatprnotjin, yam bigshayu jaapibagprnotjin, yabotog prr Dios yerog-shrt. Oiriglawi yabata jayarglig naa Espíritu Santo oje calijani nat yaloomotjin.

44007053	Jalibrgwi yan naa moyerog ángeleat ibrgprn yan ooshrt yau jayawaoliprn.

44008001	Oyat naa Saulo, jajei jaduuglig jadrrirglig naa Esteban. Oyat oobat wryu-laula jajuicawrg-jurr cabata-jadrglig jajogjet nat iglesia-atwinot Jerusalén-tee. Oyat caniinopayeg wrijin Judea-teja, Samaria-teja poi. Oodwi nat Jesúat icuiprnot ijuuligot Jerusalémtee.

44008026	Oyat itrm Biŕri ángele mog Felipeat, majuicumjg maunog noma inog drg-uye Jerusalén-shrt Gaza-teja, naa drg iwug brg-uye.

44009001	Oyat naa Saulo yau jajaapdiprn cadjaomrg nat cajiirirt Biŕrijaa. Caeb jaluug, jadjeu cadjarrirglig ooshrmda janog jalica naa sacerdoteot jriwairüg,
44009002	orden jarm jashrt sinagoga ijewerat Damasco-tee, cadcabrgjee jan wrijin nat moyerog-juju waorlat, mot detpat poi, cadjarrnogjee ijiipjet Jerusalén-teja.

44009006	Oyat Saulo piip jaom-shrm ipegjet, jamog jan, Aŕri, boirig imajeu jaminrglig man. Oyat Birri mog jan, majuicumig maunog moyan-teja, onya mashipinr boirig jaligu imashirrbrg an.

44009020	Oyat Sauloat cajuirg-jurg sinagoga-tee Jesús-jaa, jamog calat, Dios Wála naa Jesús.

44009022	Oyat Sauloat cajuirg jijogjet patjei. On cadjarg nat judioot Damasco-tee. Cadjatadrg capapera-uu Jesúla naa-jaa idnaglig bŕn. Oolawi naa Dioat icuiprn jeicatei jayuglig nan wryu-teja, jamog calat.

44009026	Oyat Saulo minogbat Jerusalén-teja, jadjeu jajrrja cadjarglig nat iglesia atwinot jajan, ooshrt caom jarea wrijin jaicashag-shrm cajrr shandit rjet.
44009027	Oyat Bernabéat Saulo rrnog calica nat Jesúat icuiprnot. Cadjapinrg brjaligu Sauloat jaluuglig Biŕri drg-uu, cadjapinrg poi brjaligu Biŕri mog jan. Bernabéat jaipin poi brjaligu cadjajuirglig uuyig-rrijet Jesús tam-jaa Damasco-tee.
44009028	Oyat Saulo lig Jerusalén-tee, jabog bigtanshrgjet cajet nat Jesús yerog-waort.
44009029	Epinot jajuirg uushanyiijet Biŕri Jesús tam-jaa. Jayaad cajet ibagjet nat judioot iyaalot griegoot yerog-jet, oyat jadjeu jadnrirglig.
44009030	Oyat nat Saulo jrrot Cristo-jaa, jadjuibat jadjeulig jadrrirglig, jadrrnog Sesarea-teja, oyat jadcuinog Tarso-teja.
44009031	Oyat cabigrririg wrijin nat iglesia atwinot Judea-tee, Galilea-tee poi, Samaria-tee pon Oyat caacawairürg Dios-jaa, caom Biŕri rca. Oyat canomjri-bajalicat nat iglesia atwinot cajrrja jalig-shrm naa Espíritu Santo, cadjalirg cajii-jaijee.
44009032	Oyat Pedroat caluubogbat nat jajrrot, japoinimnog calica nat iglesia atwinot moyan Lida-teja.

44010001	Omdi boirii Sesarea-tee itrm bon jatam Cornelio, cajricapitán nat sodawaat Italia atwinot.

44013007	Naa ijiig jalig cajuiwairüg ot-tee jatam Serjio-Paulo, bicacoula naa cajriwairüg, oyat cadja-ág jalica Bernabé Saulo poi. Jadjeu jadjuirig naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn jadjuirglig.

44013009	Oyat naa Saulo jatam poi Pablo, jajuituun Espíritu Santojet, jadyiijeu jijogjet naa ijiig.
44013010	Oyat Pablo mog jan naa ijiig, mam teeshauprnjin iebprnjin, mam moweijin wá, mam jabata jannprnjin wrijin naa ijei. Boirigshrmjam mashanjaapi Birri jririi maebrglig naa inog ishalaligjet shrn oja.
44013011	Dumat Biŕriat mashirirgya ebupaamacrtjee, mabigshirriya itrm wiig, yauya yamat mashiruuliprn. Oyat oobatwiat ibrruat iduuglig wrijin, boirigshandit iduug, oyat jadjeu brrt jarmoglig jalap-jet.
44013012	Oyat naa Pafoot jriwairüg jadduugbat jabigrririg naa ijiig, jajii jalirg Dios yerog-jaa jaom-shrm jadjuirig naa ijuirg Biŕri-jaa.
44013013	Oyat Pablo nog Pafos mau-teja jajrrot-jet. Oyat caluug itrm Iancha-tee canogjee moyan Perga-teja niti Pamfilia-tee, ooshrt Juan Marco uprt cashrt Jerusalén-teja.
44013014	Oyat cawug Perge-shrt ishalaligjet-tep canogjee Antioquía Pisidia-teja. Oyat caluug sinagoga-teja wryu jijacahiriprn-tee, categ banco-jaa.
44013015	Oyat nat sinagoga iinodigot, jadleeg quedyem Moisés papera-teat, capapera-teat poi nat brrt profetaot, carnog Bernabéat Pabloat poi, ajrrot jaligu yan itrm moyerog cadyaujuirg nat epinot, bidyaupinrg.
44013016	Oyat Pablo juimii-shog on-cadjarg jalap-jet, jamog, yam niot israelot, yam poi iomot Dios rca, ayerog yaujui.
44013017	Naa israelot jri-Dios, cadjaougli biroomot, oyat cadjalirg cabagjee catrriot caligbatdi Egipto-tee, oyat cadjarmog Egipto-teat jabigshayu iwairügjet.
44013018	Dioat jajricacouli naa idminrgli brg-uu cuarenta wiig,
44013019	Oyat cadjanam siete tribu Canaa tepinot caniti-teat jadirbrgjee biroomolat naa caniti wrijin.
44013020	Oyat cuatro ciento años jatogjee Dioat jalirg iinodigolat caijeujee ata on jamiyrca naa profeta Samuel.
44013021	Oyat jadrrn jadirgjee itrm iwairüca. Oyat Dioat jalirg cajriwairiica naa Sis wá jatam Saúl. Benjamín jriwaira naa Saúl, oyat cajriwairiica jalig cuarenta anos.
44013022	Oyat Dioat jalirg cajriwairiica jaligjee naa David Saul-shrt, naajaa Dios mogli, jatairirg naa Isaí wá David, ijeijeta jaluu ooshrm idshiminrgya oje jajeulauni.
44013023	Oyat itrm capei nat David jrdwat oola Jesús, naa Bijeicono ieb-shrt, naa Dioat icuiprn nat israelolat oje jamojaniri bŕnju.
44013024	Jajuprduju Jesús yuglig epinot jajuirgjee, Juanat cajuirg wrijin nat israelot bautisao caacarg jet-jatadrca cabigshayu cacambiarglicat capecado-shrt Dios-jaa.
44013025	Oyat Juanat jaquedrg quedyern naa jabeeb Dioat narn wryutee, jamog epinolat, am-shandita naa jeiyatei jayuglig. Boi shiyugya aprnat inomjri-jeirig ashrt. Ijei-shandita am cadashiujee-cugjin japargataot jashim-shrt.
44013026	Yam ajrrot Abraam jrdwat, Pablo mog calat. Yamda iornot Dios rca, yamata naa moyerog jet-Dioat bijeicon jajet epupaabishancrtjeeya biebyu-shrm.
44013027	Nat irigot Jerusalén-tee, bŕn yauli japishicawaaliprn brr-jaligu naa Jesús, yau poi cajriwairügolat japishiwaaliprn, yau japishicawaaliprn brjamoyu-jaligu naa profetaolat inagprndi naa idleegli sinagoga-tee wryu jijacaliiriprn shitojani. Jadirgbat jadrrirglig naa Jesús, oowi idminrg ojewi idnaalauniri jajaa bŕn capapera-uu.
44013028	Boirigshandit ieb idtairirg jajaa jadrrirgjee-cugjin, ooshrt Pilato carm jadirgjee jadrrirglig.
44013029	Oyat jadminrg quedyem wrijin naa idnagprndi jajaa, jadwonrg cmsa-jaat jadbrgjee wadyeg-teja.
44013030	Oyat Dioat jawrryrg momyu-shrt.
44013031	Oyat ibag wryu jajalirg jaduugjee jajugwirig nat iyugprnolat jajet Galilea-teat Jerusaléma. Otdawi jainot shipinit nat epinolat dumat.
44013032	Dumat jabirryubrg yan naa moyerog ijei Dioat oodmogprndi biroomolat.
44013033	Dioat jarninrg birat cajrdwat oje jamojaniri calat, jadwrryrg naa Jesús morriyu-shrt. Ojeri jamog idnagprn-tee, Salmos 2:7, jaWáala mam, dumat mashirirg maminyrglig wryu maluugjee.
44013034	Bŕndi Dios mooli Jesús-jaa jadshiwryrgya morriyu-shrt jataale shancaijeeya. Ojeri jamo idnagprn-tee, jashirirbrgya yan naa ijei oodamog Davidat.
44013035	Oyat jashri-mog Salmo-tee (16:10) yauya mashirirliprn jataale cairig naa Majetwin ijei.
44013036	Naa David, bŕn jarri jadminrg quedyem naa Dioat irirgli idminrg jaepinolat. Oyat jataale cabrg jaloomotjin taalejin mauye, oyat jataale cai.
44013037	Ooshrt naa Jesús, Dioat iwryrgprn jajugjeewi wadyeg-shrt, yau jataale cairiprn.
44013038	Ooshrm ajrrot, yandawi japishiyashiwaa, oowi jatam-jaa naa Jesús jabiquedrg yabipinrglig, Dioya jashinama yaebyu yashrt jashrm naa Biŕri Jesús.
44013039	Oyat wrijin nat cajiirirt jajaa cadjashishiuya jashrt naa ieb Moisés yerocat ishanquedrri jadnamdig.
44013040	Ooshrmda jayauluug yashrt brjashirii jalrgu yajaa naa oodcamogli nat profetaotdi.
44013041	Ojeri camo, jayacaluu yam jatam shiyoiot, yasniomya jayaluuglig oyat yashirmdrgya, ooshrm jaminrg iyaluuca itrm ijei yajewalee, ooshrt yauya yajii yashirirliprn jajaa yadcug-pinrgshicom.
44013042	Oyat Pablo yrg sinagoga-teat jajrrot-jet. Oyat nat judioolat ijuirgprnot, cadcann cashriyugjee cadcajuirgjee naa moyerog-jet boi wryu-lauya jijacahiriprn-tee.
44013043	Oyat cauprtbat sinagoga-shrt nat Pablo Bernabé poi, cabag judioot inogot caprna, ibagot idcajuirgprnot poi. Oyat Pabloat capinrg caligjee dai-imogjet jajaa naa ijei Dioat iminrg birat biyii jaluug-shrm.
44013044	Oyat boi wryu-tee jijacaliiriprn, jayryaijin nat moyan tepinot wrijin cajuibeegjee Dios yerog cajuijee.
44013045	Oyat nat judioot cadcaluugbat nat epinot ibagot, jaeb caluug Pablo Bernabé poi, caucacajeu, jadjeu cayerog jayigcarrirglig, ca-jayeg carrirg poi.
44013046	Oyat nat Pablo Bernabé-jet cadcapinrg uushanyijet, biradawi yabishipinrg-jur yam judioot naa moyerog juju Dioat irirbrgprn birat, ooshrt jayatepnam yashrt. Yaaleilawi jashantepjewit naa wryu ishanbeji, ooshrmda dumat bishinogya calica nat judioja ishandiot.
44013047	Ojerawi Biŕriat bicuiri ibiminrgjee, malirg cai-wryuja maligjee nat judioja ishandiot, jamog. Jamarmogjee wrijin wryu tepinolat naa moyerog jet-moijeicon Dios-jet, ebupaacacrt-shrtya jashrm naa ieb idminrg, canogjee paraiso-teja.
44013048	Oyat jadjuibat naa moyerog cajii-jái nat judioja-ishandiot. Ijeira naa moyerog Biŕri Jesús-jaa, camog. Oyat cajii-calirg Jesúsjaa wrijin nat ood-jashiribrgotya wryu ishanbeji.
44013049	Oyat jadjuirg naa moyerog Biŕri-jaa wrijin caniti-jaa Pisidia-tee.
44013050	Ooshrt nat judioot cadcanrmrg itrmnogot detpat irigot Moisés yerog-jaa, otpoi nat iinodigot moyanot-tee. Oyat cabatajadrg nat Pablo Bernabé poi, cadcanam caniti-shrt.
44013051	Oyat nat Pablo Bernabé poi, jadnam cashim-shrt niti jetcadcatadrca boirig shanditya ishiribrg calat nat cayerog shanwaorríot Jesús-jaa. Oyat canog moyan Iconio-teja.
44013052	Oyat cajii-jái ipegjet nat cajiirirt Biŕri-jaa, cajuituun Espíritu Santo-jet.
44014001	Oyac moyan Iconio-tee caluug judioot sinagoga-tee nat Pablo Bernabé poi, jijogjet cadcajuirg ooshrm ibagjet judioolat cayerog-jui, capoibag nat judioja-ishandiot.
44014002	Oyat nat judioot cayerog shanwaorriot, cadcanrmrg nat judioja-ishandiot. Cabigshayu caebrg caúbata nat cajiirirt Jesús-jaa.
44014003	Calig jajan prnpatjet nat Pablo Bernabé poi, cauushanyit idjuirglig Biŕri-jaa cadjawairirg-shrni. Oyat jadirg jadminrglig ibagjet brrt ishanminrri jadduug nat epinolat japishicawaagjee rjet jaliglig naa oodcamog Dios-jaa, ijei jaminrg birat biyii jaluug-shrm, camog.
44014004	Yau itrmjani cabigshayu liiriprn nat Iconio tepinot, itrmnogolat judioot yerog waorg, oyat itrmnogolat cayerog-jui nat Jesúat icuiprnot.
44014005	Oyat nat judioot cayerog shanjuiyit, otpoi nat judioja ishandiot, cajuicaberg cajriwairügot-jet, canog caprna nat Pablo Bernabé poi cadcarrirgjee jaa-jet.
44014006	Oyat naa Pablo Bernabé poi cabalolat iinot cajuibat, cacuut Listra-teja, Derbe-teja poi, nat moyanot Licaonia-tee. Cadcaluug poi wrijin nat moyanot inagot,
44014007	jadjuirgjee naa moyerog jet-epinot ijeicon Dios-jet.
44014008	Omda Listra-tee jalii boi bon ishanshoiprnjin. Ojeri jayrgwiri jaiin-shrt, brlau-shandit jaboo.
44014009	Oyat naa bon Pablo yerog jajui epinot jajuirgbat. Oyat Pabloat jayiijeu jijogjet, japishijawaag jadquedrglig jadjeicondig jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa naa moyerog Jesúsjaa.
44014010	Ooshrmda Pablo mog jan jijogjet, majuicumii-shog ishalaligjet mashiim-jet. Oyat naa bon jalryrshog, oyat jabog.
44014011	Oyat nat epinot jaduugbat naa Pabloat irninrg cawrr-ág jijogjet Licaoni yerogjet, nat bijri-dioot cawon birica oje boni camog.
44014012	Oolawi bijri-dios Júpiter camog Bernabé-jaa. Oolawi bijri-dios Mercurio camog Pablo-jaa, ooshrm oola naa iyaad.
44014013	Oyat naa Júpiter sacerdote jayrg ídolo ot-teat irig moyan mauu, jadrryug nat torroot, putiraat poi. Jadjeu cadjarrirglig nat torroot, jaepinot jriat, ijei cabrgjee Pabloat Bemabeat poi.
44014014	Oyat nat Jesúat icuiprnot, jadduugbat naa idjeu jadminrglig calat, cajii-shŕm. Caman calica nat epinot, cashog cajewalee.
44014015	Camog calat, yam mot, boirigshrmjam ijei yabrr birat, motda bidu oje yalijani. Biyug nani yabipinrgjee jajet naa moyerog ijei cadyanamnogjee yashrt nat yacostumbre mii-rri, yabigshayu yalirgjee jajaa naa Dios ijug, naa iminrr wrijin boirig jaligu shrnoja, naa wryu-tee poi, rt-tee poi.
44014016	Bŕndi Dioat cajulirgli cabogjee cajrirüot-tee catojani.
44014017	Ooshrt jadirg japishicawaagjee jajaa jajet naa ijei idminrg calat. Jadirg wao Irgjee bijrmca-jaa cacabot-digjee ipegjet. Jadirg birat biwoug ijeijet bijii-jáijee.
44014018	Naa Pablo Bernabé-jet, cayaad ijeijet epinolat, ooshrt jayryaibrjin jadshanquedrtjee cabigshayu cacambiarglig nat epinot, jijogjeta jadjeu cadcarrirglig nat torroot ijei cabrgjee calat nat Pabloat, Bernabeat poi.
44014019	Oyat cayug itrmnogot judioot Antioquía atwinot Iconio atwinot poi. Oyat cadcanrmrg nat epinot cabata-jadrgjee Pablo Bernabé poi, oyat jadrrirg Pablo jaa-jet. Oyat jadjigquinog cayan-shrt jaicashacat-shrm jarririg.
44014020	Oyat nat idjajuirgprnot cashooyug Pablo mauu, jadyiijeu-shog. Oyat oowi jajuirnii-shoglig, oyat jashri-ruug moyan-teja. Oyat brlerndigu janog Bemabé-jet Derbe-teja.
44014021	Oyat idjuirgbat Derbe-tee naa moyerog jet-moijeicon Dios-jet, ibag epinot cajiirirt jajaa. Oyat cauprt Iistra-teja, Iconio-teja poi, Antioquia-teja poi.
44014022	Cadcawairürg nat idcajuirgprnot moyan tojani, cadcacui caligjee dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog idwaorg. Cadcapoipinrg ebupaaicrdig prnpatjet moluugjee Dioat moijeuliprn-teja.
44014023	Oyat cadcalirg ancianoja caligjee nat mot iglesia tojani epinot icajeujee. Oyat Dios carm cajaa cayeishanjuwaibat. Oyat jadirg Biŕriat caijeulig naa-jaa cajii-calirg.
44014024	Oyat cawug niti Pisidia jarnaye canogjee niti Panfilia-teja.
44014025	Oyat jadjuirg quedyern naa moyerog moyan Perje-tee canog Atalia-teja.
44014026	Oyat caluug já ipeg-teja canogjee Antioquía-teja, naa moyan cayug jurprnot canogjee Dios-jet jadminrgjee naa minrgcacuiri calat nat iglesia iinodigolat.
44014027	Caminogbat Antioquía-teja nat Pablo Bernabé poi cajuicaberg nat iglesia-atwinot cadcapinrgjee caviaje-jaa brjaligu Dioat jalirgli ijei caminrglig, jajuijayig calat moluugliprn calica nat judioja ishandiot cajii calirgjee jajaa naa moyerog ijei Jesús-jaa.
44014028	Oyat nat Pablo Bernabé poi, calig Antioquía-tee ibag wryu cajet nat iglesia atwinot.
44015001	Oyat itrmnogot mot Judea atwinot yug Antioquía-teja ID iglesia atwinot cajuirg on, yadshanconsisaordu oje Moisés mojaniri, yauya Dioat yashijeicondiprn-jamo, camog calat.
44015002	Oyat Pablo yaad cajet cayerog ubata Bernabé poi, rjet shandit naa iyajuirg, camog calat. Oyat nat iglesia atwinot Ántioquía-tee jadcuinog Pablo Jerusaléna Bernabé-jet, itrmnogot cajrrot poi, cadcarmjee Jesús icuiprnot, ansianoot poi, jajaa naa idjuirg nat judioolat.
44015003	Oyat nat iglesia atwinot jadirg canogjee Dios carm quedyern cajaa. Oyat cawug Fenisia niti jarnayei, Samaría jarnayei poi. Canogbat cadcapinrg wrijin iglesia-tee cajaa nat judioja ishandiot brjaligu cabigshayu cacambiarlig idoloot-shrt Jesucristo-jaa. Oyat cajii-jái wrijin nat iglesia atwinot moyan tojani.
44015004	Oyat caminogbat Jerusalén-teja nat Pablo Bernabé poi, cabatcatai ijeijet nat iglesia-atwinolat, Jesúat icuiprnot poi, ansianoot poi. Oyat cadcapinrg caviaje-jaa brjaligu Dioat jalirglig idrg cajewalee nat judioja-ishandiot.
44015005	Oyat itrmnogot iglesia atwin fariseoot-peit, cajuimii-shog camog, yandawi siconsisao cadyashirr nat judioja ishandiot, yandawi Moisés yerog waorg yashicui calat.
44015006	Oyat Jesúat icuiprnolat cajuiberg ansianoot-jet cadcapinrgjee jajaa naa judioot icostumbre.
44015007	Oyat cayaad quedyern ipegjet Pedro juirnii-shog, jamog calat, ajrrot japishiyawaagwi Dioat aágli arn yajewaleat bŕn jajuirgjee naa moyerog ijei nat judioja ishandiolat cajii calirgjee jajaa.
44015008	Oyat naa Dios cabigshayu pishiwaja wrijin, jadirg japishibiwaagjee cadjaouglicat japinita caligjee jadirbrg-shrm calat naa Espíritu Santo ojewi jadirbrlauniri birat.
44015009	Itrrnjanibrlawi Dioat biruuglig cajet nat brrt epinot. Cabigshayu jacambiarg jaapi-rrijet ojewi idrjani birat, bijii birirg-shrm Jesucristo-jaa.
44015010	Oyat dumat boirigshrmjam yabigshayu cau jajaa naa Dioat iminrg birat. Boirigshrmjam jayalirg bicostumbre imrm cajaa nat idbijuirgprnot, naa ibishanquedrri jajricabicoulig, yau-poi biroomolat jaquedrliprndi jadminrgli.
44015011	Japishibiwaagwi Biŕri Jesúat bijeieondig binogjee shrnoja oje cadjajeicondauni nat brrt epinot jajet naa ijei idminrg birat miirrijet cruza-jaa biyii jaluug-shrm.
44015012	Oyat Pedroat capinrg quedyern on-cairig jashrt wrijin. Oyat Pablo yerog cajui ijeijet Bernabé poi cadcapinrgbat bijaligu Dioat jalirglig idrninrgli cajewalee nat judioja ishandiot, ibag brrt ishanrninrri, iishanjuduji poi.
44015013	Oyat cayaad queyernat Jacobo mog calat, ajrrot ayerog yaujui.
44015014	Simón Pedroat bipinrcat brjaligu Dioat caluuglig dumat nat judioja ishandiot cadjaágjee jaepinota caligjee capet poi.
44015015	Ojeri poi idnagli capapera-uu nat profetaodi Espíritu-jet.
44015016	Ashiyugya-shri jawrryrgjee naa David templo iyrglig, japeijin juiashimiirg shri,
44015017	jadjeujeeya Biŕri wrijin nat epinolat, wrijin poi nat brrt epinolat iyarmprnot atam-jaa.
44015018	Oyat Jacobo shri-mog calat, ojera jamo Biŕri, naa jalirrli japishicawaagli bŕnju jajaa naa idminrg dumat brrt epinot jewalee.
44015019	Ooshrmda yapinrg, jajeirawi cadbirirgu cabigrririgjee judioot costumbre-shrt nat judioja ishandiot, cabigshayu cambiart Diosjaa.
44015020	Oowi ibishinaabrg calat papera jadshanwoutjee mojiu taa idcarrirgprnot idoloolot, ieb cashanminrgjee cataale-jet poi, rri-poi jadwouglig jrrlug taa maa-cashannami, rri-poi momaa.
44015021	Japishicawaacatwi boirig jaligu idshiminrg ooshrm jairuug wrijin moyantee nat Dios yerog juirt, jadleeg cajuibeeriprn-tee jatee naa wryu jijacaliiriprn. Cadcalirg cabigrririgjee judioot costumbre-shrt
44015022	Oyat nat Jesúat icuiprnot, ancianoot poi, wrijin iglesia atwinot poi, jaicashag jajeirig itrmnogot capet cacuinoglig Antioquía-tee cajet nat Pablo Bernabé poi. Oyat jadcuinog Juda Barsabas, itrm poi iinodig capei jatam Silas.
44015023	Jadcuinog cajet itrrn papera idnagprn calat, ojeri carno, bidu yajrrot Jesúat icuiprnot, ancianoot poi, iglesia atwinot poi, memoria bicui yan, yam bijrrolat judioot ishandiot irigot Antíoquatee, Siria-tee poi, Silicia-tee poi.
44015024	Bŕn cainot bijui caminoglig yalica nat ibishancuiyit yabigshayu caebrg caaleiot yerog-jetep. Yadcui yayasiconsisargjee, jayapoiwaorg naa moyerog bŕnwinjin.
44015025	Ooshrm bijuibergbat jaibishaag cadbicuinog shirig yalica Pablo-jet Bernabé-jet poi itrmnogot bipet,
44015026	nat mot jaawrgot carrijee Biŕri Jesucristo-shrm jayerog cajuirgjee.
44015027	Cadbicuinog poi yalica nat Juda Barsabas, Silas poi. Yadshipinrgyawrn cacooleat jajet naa ibinagprn papera-uu.
44015028	Naa Espíritu Santo jadirg yabipinrglig, jabishanjeu yabigshayu mrmdig jashrm nat judioot costumbre, oolawi iyawaorgya naa oodbimog yan papera-tee.
44015029	Jayacupoi-wout mojiu taa idrrirgprn idoloolat, rri-poi jrriug maa, rri-poi idcarrirgprnot taa maa-cashannamit, rri-poi ieb yaminrglig yataale-jet. Jayawaorgu naa oodbimog omda yashijeiyaoicom. Durnat yaulig ijeijet.
44015030	Oyat nat idcacuiprnot canog Antioquía-teja, caminogbat jajan cajucaberg nat iglesia atwinot, jadbrg calat naa papera idcuiprn.
44015031	Oyat jadleeg quedyern cajii-jái, jawuucat cashrt cabigshayu imrmprnjin.
44015032	Oyat naa Juda Barsabas, Silas poi, japishicawaag ijeijet jadjuirgjee naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn cajii-tee, ooshrmda cadcawairürg nat iglesia-atwinot cayerog-jet, ijáijeta cayerog cajui.
44015033	Oyat ibag wryu calig cajet, oyat nat iglesia atwinot cadcalirg caúprtjee ijeijet calica nat cacuinotprnot.
44015034	Oyat Silaat jajujeu jaliglig cajet Antioquía-tee,
44015035	oo-poi Pablo, Bernabé poi, jadjuirgjee naa moyerog ijei Biŕri-jaa cajriat nat brlat ijuirgprnot ibagot.
44015036	Oyat boi wryulau Pablo mog Bemabeat, shog biunog binimnojet calica nat bijrrot wrijin moyanot-teja jabijuirprnali naa moyerog Biŕri-jaa. Cadbiuluunog brjaligu caliglig jajaa naa jet-cadbijuirgli.
44015037	Oyat Bemabeat jajeu jadrrnoglig cajet naa Juan Marcos.
44015038	Ooshrt Pabloat jaishag jashanjei cadirrnogu ooshrm jaúprtdi cashrt Panfilia-teat. Jashan-nodi cajet idbeebjee Biŕriat.
44015039	Ooshrm itnnjani cabigshayu shandit, oyat cayaad caaleat ibagjet, oyat caacasheu cashrt. Bernabéat jarmog jajet naa Marcos, oyat caluug itrrn lancha-tee canogjee Chipreja.
44015040	Oyat Pabloat jaoug naa Silas janogjee jajet. Oyat nat iglesia atwinot Biŕri carm cajaa caijajeujee ijeijet caviaje-tee.
44015041	Oyat Pablo boolrg wrijin Siria-tee, Silicia-tee poi, cadjawairürgjee nat jajrrot iglesia atwinot wrijin.

44018027	Oyat Apoloat jajeubat janoglig Acaya-teja, nat iglesia tepinot papera canag cajrrolat Acaya-tee jabatcataijee Apolo ijeijet. Oyat jaminogbat Acaya-teja cajrrja jalig ijeijet nat Dioat irirgprnot jayerog cawaorgjee cayii jaluug-shrm.

44019001	Apolo ligbat Corinto-tee, Pablo nog drg-uye ibog niti ly shrnjaat-jaye jaminogjee Efeso-teja. Onda brrt jatairir itrm nogot idjajuirgprnot.
44019002	Oyat Pabloat carm, Espíritu Santo wonijam yajaa yajii yalirgbat. Oyat camog jan, jabishanjuiju oo-jaligu naa Espíritu Santo.

44019005	Oyat nat epinot jadjuibat naa Pabloat iipin calat, jadirg bautisaocacargjee Biŕri Jesús tam-jaa.
44019006	Oyat Pabloat jalap dirgbat cajaa, naa Espíritu Santo won cajaa. Oyat cayaad yawa-atwinot yerog-jet, jaicapoi-pin itrrn moyerog Dioat irirgprn cajii-tee.
44019007	Doce catog nat mot wrijin.
44019008	Oyat Pablo luug sinagoga-tee, cajajuirg jijogjet jajan ipoi jrbot. Jauushanyit caacajauyeglig cajet nat judioot ishiigjeta cadjapinrg brjaligu Dioat cajuiberglig nat wryu tepinot jaepinota caligjee.
44019009	Oyat nat itrmnogot cajuiyag cashaatrg jayerog-shrt. Yau jadjeuliprn jayerog cawaorglig, ooshrt cayaad iebjet epinolat jajaa naa moyerog ijapin Biŕri jrirü-jaa. Oyat Pabloat jayaujignog cashrt, cadjarrnog jajet nat jayerog juiyut jaescuela-teja naa bon jatam Tirano, onda Pabloat cajuirr wryu shitojani.
44019010	Ojerawi Pabloat ir icau anos, oyat wrijin nat irigot Asia-tee jadjui naa moyerog Biŕri Jesús-jaa, wrijin nat judioot, wrijin poi judioja-ishandiot.
44019011	Dioat jaminrg ibagjet brrt ishanminrri jalap-jet naa Pablo.
44019012	Oyat nat panueloot camisaot poi Pabloat imaapaiprnot cadcarrnog itabot-dica, oyat ishiyuat canaamnog, oyat demonioot capoiyrg epinot-shrt.
44019013	Oyat itrmnogot judioot demoniot canambog cajiigyu-jet, jadpoi-jeu demonioot canamdig Biŕri Jesús tam-jaa. Oyat camog calat nat demonioolat, yabicui yayrgjee epinot-shrt jatam-jaa naa Jesús, jaa-Pabloat ijuirg.
44019014	Ojera idr nat siete itogot jawaot naa sacerdoteot jriwairüg jatam Esewa.
44019015	Ooshrt jadcuibat naa demonio, oowi jarnoglig calat, japishiawaagwi Jesús, japishiawaag poi Pablo, ooshrt yarn, boirigotjam yarn.
44019016	Oyat naa bon demonio-lig jalrmog cajaa jijogjet, cajajan wrijin nat siete itogot. Cadjapai jijogjet janrmshicom, jadjouteinog cashrt cayuiot, oyat cacuut jashrt mooyeja jequewitep, cajaaprnot poirig.
44019017	Oyat cainot cajui nat irigolat Efeso-tee wrijin nat judioot, natpoi judioja ishandiot. Oyat caom ipegjet, ijei icapin Biŕri Jesús tam-jaa.
44019018	Oyat cabag nat cajiirirt Biŕri-jaa, cayug jaicapinjee wrijin naa ieb idminrgprndi.
44019019	Oyat cabag ijiigot cadcarmog capaperaat jet-mojigyu caminrgot, cadcatai idduugjet wrijin. Sincuenta mil palata carnii-togli nat libroot idcataiot iyaalot mojigyu-jaa.
44019020	Oyat naa moyerog Biŕri-jaa jainocat wrijin jajuprta shirigyau cabigshayu jacambiarg nat epinot.
44019021	Oyat naa Espíritu, Pablo japinrg jajii-tee janimnogjee Macedonia-teja, Acaya-teja poi janogbat Jerusaléna. Oyat Pabloat capinrg jajrrot, Anog quedyemya Jerusaléma oyatya ashinoo Roma-teja poi.
44019022	Oyat Pabloat cacuinog icauot jajrrot Macedonia-teja, naa Timoteo, Eraste poi, ooshrt Pablo julig Asia-tee.
44019023	Oyat itrmnogot Efeso tepinot jajuicawrg caacamrndig jajaa naa moyerog Biŕri-jaa.
44019024	Omda boirü itrm bon jatam Demetrio idoloot liiriprn beepe palata-con, naa cajri-diola Diana shogot. Naa Demetrio jad-oug ibag jalapwoo jajet naa idbeeb, otpoi nat ibeebet jajet.
44019025	Oyat naa Demetrio cajuijaberg nat ibeebet jajet, otpoi wrijin nat idoloot ibeebet. Jamog calat, ajrrot, japishiyawaagwi jabaglig bipin jajet naa ibibeeb.
44019026	Jainot yajuiwi naa Pablo, jayaluug poi brjaligu jamoobog Dioot shandit nat idbiminrgprnotep birap-jet, oyat ibagot epinot jayerog waort. Efesio-teebr shanwirit cadjajuir ooshrt wrijin poi Asia-tee.
44019027	Dumatya bishieb, naajri bibeeb jashibeegya, jet-naa bipinbioug ooshrm boi-tep cashimogya jajaa naa jaliiriprn bijri-diola Diana. Oyat jainot ijei jashirmdrgya, naa ood-ijei cabrg wrijin moyanot Asia-tee, wrijin wryu-tee poi.
44019028	Oyat canrm nat mot jadjuibat Demetrioat oodmog, cawrr-ág jijogjet, ijeira naa Diana, naa Efesioot jri-diola.
44019029	Monrmyujet cawrr-ág wrijin moyan-yecani. Oyat jadwaorg calap-jet naa Gayo, Aristarco poi, nat Macedonia atwinot iyugprnot Pablo-jet. Oyat caman cajuibeeriprn-teja wrijin, cadcajig cajet nat Pablo jrrot.
44019030	Oyat Pabloat jajeu jaluuglig cajuibeeriprn-teja jayaadjee cajet, ooshrt jaiwincashog jaluuglig nat idjajuirgprnot.
44019031	Oyat itrmnogot Asia tepinot jayii-caluug Pablo, moyerog cacui jan jashanduu-jee cajewalee nat iwrr-ágot.
44019032	Omda cajuibeeriprn-tee, itrmnogot wrr-ág boi moyerog-jet, oyat itrmnogot boi-poi moyerog-jet boyeja poi brrt-shrt. Oowi catewrr-ág jequewitep wrijin. Ibagot capet japishanwajit boirigshrm jaligu cajuicaberg.
44019033	Oyat itnnnogolat Alejandro cui jayaadjee calat, ooshrm jatounog nat judioolat. Oyat Alejandroat on-carg jalap-jet, jadjeu jaalei iinot shijapindig nat epinolat.
44019034	Oyat jadduugbat judioja jaliglig naa Alejandro canomjri wrr-áalica jijogjet itrmjanibr. Cau orala cawrr-ág, ijeira naa Diana Efesioot jri-diola, camog.
44019035	Oyat naa gobierno secretario on-cadjarg quedyem nat epinot ibagot, jarnog, calat, yam mot Efeso tepinot, wrijin nat wryu tepinot wainot pishicawaag bidu Efeso tepinot, jaibijeujee jatemplo naa bijri-diola ijei Diana, jayaajin poi, naa ilrgprndi shrnoat.
44019036	Brr-shandit jaquedrr jainot shijajaandig naa bijri-diola, ooshrmda on-yairig, yabigyaushag ijeijet ieb yaminrgcu monrm-shicom.
44019037	Ooshrm nat mot idyarryugprnot narn, yau ieb carninrliprn naa bijri-diola, rripoi ieb icapindig jajaa.
44019038	Oyat naa Demetrio, otpoi ibeebet jajet, jadjeuu boi-iinot shicapindig iebminrg calat, caladwi caicashipin nat iinodigolat. Omda cairii cadearmdiprn-tee nat iwairügot japishiwajat bijaa brrt iebminrg-shrt brrlat.
44019039	Oyat jayajeuu cadyarmdig boirig-jaa jaligu cadyaurm nat iwairügot cayaadiprn-tee.
44019040	Oyat jayauluug yashrt dumat bijainot capin-shrt iebjet jashrm naa yawrr-aliprn iyaminrg. Bidcarmu jajaa naa iyaminr, yau biquedrliprn jaibipinu boirig-shrm jaligu.
44019041	Oyat jaijapin quedyem naa moyerog, caujaprt-cui nat juibeegprnot jajan.
44020001	Oyat cawrr-ág quedyem nat idoloot yürujut, Pabloat caág jalica nat idjajuirgprnot, jijogjet cadjapinrg moyerog ijeijet caligjee dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog Biŕri-jaa. Oyat cadjawai-riirg quedyem cadjajoolig jainot shijapin, oyat janog cashrt Macedonia-teja.
44020002	Oyat Pablo boolrg wrijin caniti-jaa, cadjawairürg nat iglesia atwinot ibag moyerog-jet, oyat janog Grecia-teja.
44020003	On jalig ipoi jrbot cajet nat iglesia-tepinot. Oyat jadjeu janoglig Siria-teja lancha-tee ooshrt judioot iinot-jajui jajeicateirig jaanajet jadrrirgjee, ooshrmda jaúprt drg-uye jashri-wug Macedonia-tee jaamaye.
44020004	Oyat itrm nog Pablo-jet Berea atwin jatam Sopater, nat poi Tesalonica atwinot Aristarco, Segundo poi, oyat naa Derbe atwin jatam Gayo, Timoteo poi, oyat nat Asia atwinot Tiquico, Trofímo poi.
44020005	Nat bijrrot canog bijüprta, oyat bijeicatei moyan Troas-tee.
44020006	Oyat bijuulig on jibiruug cajuibeeriprn jadwouglig naa pan levadura-rri. Oyat biruug lancha-tee binogjee Filipo mau-shrt, oyat sinco-itog wryu prnat bijripao Troasa drjogu, onda bijuibiber bijrrot-jet.
44020007	Oyat domingo-tee bijuibeeg an-bimogpig Santa Cena-tee, oyat Pabloat cajuirg. Jadjeu janoglig cashrt briemdicat ooshrmda jayaad prnpatjet ata shaite jamaya.
44020008	Bijuibeeg mo-tee ipoi piso-teye shrnoja, ornda cabag lampara biwryuot.
44020009	Oyat itrm bon-trri jatam Eutico jateg ventana-ye, jaou-shug, oyat jaou jayaad-shrm prnpatjet naa Pablo. Oyat jalrg ventana-teat ipoi piso balat-yau jalrg nitu-uja. Oyat jadwrlayrg jacomrri.
44020010	Oyat Pablo won jalica nat bon-trri calera-jaye, oyat jawopjog jalica jadjoolagyrg. Oyat jamog nat epinolat, yacupoiorn jajugwi.
44020011	Oyat Pablo shri-jon caleraat-jaye ipoi piso-teja. Oyat an japig jadwoug cajet, oyat japatjri-yaadju calat ata-on iwryuca, oyat janog cashrt.
44020012	Oyat naa trriwai jrrolat jadrmog cajet jajugwi, cajii-jái ipegjet wrijin.
44020013	Oyat binog Pablo juprta lancha-tee, binogjee Asón-teja, Pablo bitairirgee jajan, ooshrm oje jamogli birat jadjeu janoglig on drguye.i
44020014	Oyat Asón-tee Pablo Iuug bijet Iancha-tee, binogjee Mitilene-teja.
44020015	Oyat binog Mitüene-shrt, oyat brlemdigu biwug Quio yabalat, oyat brlemdigu shri bijripau Somos maua, oyat boi wryulau biminog Mileto-teja.
44020016	Ojera biwugli mogwaijetep, Pablo shandigshutshrm prnpatjet Asia-tee. Jadjeu jawugjee Efeso mauye janogjee mogwaini Jerusalén-teja jaduugjee cajet wryu Pentecostés jadpoiquedrgu-om.
44020017	Oyat Pablo ligbat Mileto-tee, caág jacui nat ancianoot iglesiaat ijewet Efeso-tee.
44020018	Oyat cajuicabergbat jalica, jamog calat, yamdawi japishiwajat brjaligu aliglig yajewalee oüriglawi ayug jurgbati nam Asia-tee dumat-patjri.
44020019	Uubiidprnjini ibeebdig Biŕriat oiirigwi aligbat yajet, jaibagli aquig yashrm, oyat ipegjet ebupaa-acrt canog-shrm aprna nat judioot ieb caminrgjee an.
44020020	Ooshrt yau ajaapdiprn yajuirglig wrijin jajet naa moyerog jet-yaijeicon jaligjee ijeijet, cadajuiig wad-uu iduugjet wrijin, mooíee poi.
44020021	Cadajuirg nat judioot, ot-poi nat judioja shandiot cabigshayu cacambiargjee Dios-jaa caebyu-shrt, cabigshayu calirgjee Biŕri-jaa.
44020022	Dumat naa aEspíritu adcui anogjee Jerusalén-teja, yau japishiawaaliprn brjaligu awug-shirig on.
44020023	Oowi japishiawaag Espíritu moglig an wrijin moyan-tee adshinamya presoja moliiriprn-teja Jerusalén-tee, ebupaa-ashicrtma ipegjet jajan.
44020024	Oyat abigashag jajaa naa paa-shicrtya. Boirica-shanditya an ajuuligu narn wryu-tee. Oowi ijeu jaberglig ijáijet naa Bíŕri Jesúat irirgprn an jabeebjee. Jajeu jaiapindig jajaa naa ijei Dioat iminrg birat biyii jaluug-shrm.
44020025	Dumat japishiawaagwi yauya a-ú yashiruuliprn-shri yam idajuirgprnot jajaa naa Dioat cajuiberliprn jaepinota caligjee.
44020026	Dumat yapinrg, boi rmdrgu itrm yapei Dios-shrt, am culpa shanditya,
44020027	ooshrm yajuireat wrijin Dios yerog-jaa, boirig shandit ajaan yashrt.
44020028	Dumat jayauluug yashrt wrijin ieb. Cayaujeu ijeijet nat Espíritu Santoat irirgprnot cayajeulig. Cadyaujuirg ijeijet nat Biŕri iglesia tepinot, nat mii-jabrgprnot jaalei maajet.
44020029	Japishiawaagwi anog quedyernya yashrt cashiyugya yalica nat jajewet cadcarmdrrglig nat iglesia tepinot oje yoodanot inrmolat carmrlauni nat ovejaot.
44020030	Oyat cajuishipoimigya yajewaleat nat moteeshauyu juirt jashrt naa moyerog rjetwin, cateecashaurgjeeya nat iglesia tepinot canogjee caprna Dios yerog-shrt.
44020031	Ooshrmda cadyauluug yashrt nat oiirigot, jayeyawáag naa ipoi wiig ipoi rt-yrg poi, yau ajaapdiprn yajuirglig abigpog jriat wrglei shairei poi.
44020032	Dumat yam ajrrot, jalirg Dioat yaijeujee, jalirg yajrijawaoteg: jee naa moyerocat oodmog jajaa naa ijei Dioat iminrg birat biyii jaluug-shrm, naa jalirr yaligjee dai-imogjet jalibrgjeeya yan ijei cajriat nat idjaougprnot jan wrijin.
44020033	Yau palata armdiprn boi-shrt, rri-poi alapwooja.
44020034	Japishiyawaagwi ibeebdig alapjet jarnii abrgjee naa boiruudbrg an, oolat poi nat ibogolat ajet.
44020035	Oiiriglawi yajuirglig yabeebjee oje alijani cajrrja yaligjee nat uubiidot. Jayeyauwaag naa Biŕri Jesúat oodmog birat, jashinomjri jáiya naa jalapwoo-bŕn jashrt naa jajeiteiye boiat boi-brglig jan.
44020036	Oyat Pabloat jaipin quedyem naa moyerog jashog jautjuiyagjet Dios jarmjee wrijin cajet nat ansianoot.
44020037	Oyat caquig jajaa wrijin, jadjoolag Pablo, ja-ú cabesorg jetjatadrca jayii-caluuglig.
44020038	Cajii-shŕm ipegjet jamog-shrm calat, yauya a-u yashiduuliprn shri. Oyat canog jajet drjoca lancha waaca.
44021001	Oyat cadbinamnog quedyem nat bijrrot iglesia tepinot biruug lancha-teja. Oyat binog ishalalig-jet Cosaja, oyat brlemdigu binog Rodaja, oyat binog Pátaraja.
44021002	Omda boi bitairir lancha ŕri inog Feniciaja, oyat biruug binogjee jajet.
44021003	Oyat jabiruugbat iporn Chipre biwug jashrt bishaat binogjee Siriaja. Oyat bijripao Tiro drjoca boi biyrrgjee lancha tepin-jarno.
44021004	Oyat cadbitairirg Tiro-tee nat iglesia tepinot, oyat birig cajet siete-jatog wryu. Oyat Pablo capinrg Espíritu Santo-jet jashannotjee Jerusalén-íeja.
44021005	Oyat siete-itog wryu prnot binog cashrt, oyat cayug bijet moyan drjoca wrijin nat bijrrot iglesia tepinot, wrijin ca-ujut poi, wrijin catrriot poi. Oyat bishog biutjuiyag-jet mai-jaa Dios birrnjee.
44021006	Oyat bibijoolat quedyem bidcalirg binogjee Dios-jet. Oyat biruug lancha-teja, oyat eauprt caot-teja.
44021007	Oyat binog Tiro dijocat Tolemaida-teja, onda jabee naa binooyu rt-teye. Oyat binimnog calica nat bijrrot iglesia tepinot on, birig cajet itrm wryu.
44021008	Oyat brlemdicat biúprt cashrt binogjee Cesarea-teja, oyat biriinog jaot-teja naa ijuirr iwairüg jatam Felipe, oola boi-capei nat siete itogot deaconoot.
44021009	Cacaunogla jalouot yrgrg shanjuebit jaipinit moyerog Dioat irirgprn cajii-tee.
44021010	Oyat birig quedyem cajet itnnnog wryu, jaminyug itrm profeta Judea atwin jatam Agabo.
44021011	Oyat naa Agabo janimnog birica, jadwaorg Pablo isintaron oyat jashiim ijajiip jajet, jalap poi. Oyat jamog, naa Espíritu Santo mog, ojeya jadjiipshirig naa sintoron-ŕri Jerusalén-tee nat judioolat, oyat jadshibr nat yawa-atwinolat.
44021012	Jadjuibat naa Agaboat iipin Pabloat, jabipinrg ishiigjet cajet nat Cesaría tepinot, jashannotjee Jerusalén-teja.
44021013	Oyat Pablo mog birat, boirigshrrnjam yaquig ajaa, boirigshrrnjam ajii yashŕmrg. Ajaawrgla am adjiipjee, ajapoiwrg arrijee Jerusalén-tee Biŕri Jesús-shrm.
44021014	Oyat yau jabiquedrliprn jabigshayu bicarnbiarglig, on-birig jashrt. Oyat birnog jan, imaurninrg oje Biŕriat jajeulauni.
44021015	Oyat bilapwoo bijeicon binogjee Jerusaléna.
44021016	Capoinog bijet itrrnnogot bijrrot Cesárea atwinot, itrm capei Chipre atwin jatam Masón, ibag wiig jajii jalirg Biŕri-jaa, oyat bidjacui bioujee jaot-tee.
44021017	Oyat biminogbat Jerusalén-teja, cajii-jái bibaatcatairi nat iglesia tepinolat.
44021018	Oyat brlemdicat Pablo nog bijet Jacobo-lica, omda cajuicaber wrijin nat iglesiat iinodigolat.
44021019	Oyat Pabioat casaludarg quedyem, cadjapinrg jajet naa Dioat irirg jadrninrglig cajewalee nat judioja ishandiot.
44021020	Jadjui quedyem naa Pablo oodmog, ijei cabrg Dioat. Oyat camog jan, bijrrjapishimawaagwi cadiruuglig miles itogot judioot cajiirirt Jesús-jaa, oyat camog jajeirawi moligu Moisés yerog-jaa poi.
44021021	Oyat carnog majaa cadmajuirgma wrijin nat judioot irigot boyaja, Moisés yerog cashanwaortjee, rri-jaligjeema poi cadcasiconsisarglig catrriot, rri-poi bicosturnbre caminrglig.
44021022	Boyajam ibishir, ooshrm cajuishibegya birica mainot cajuibat marninyuglig.
44021023	Jajeirawi imaminrgu oje bimojani man. Omdawi calii bijewalee icaunogot mot jajewet idminrglig itrm voto oodcarnog Dios-jaa.
44021024	Oyat cadmaurrnog majet, oyat mamaujeicon, ot-poi. Oyatjamii maubrg cajuu cacugjee japishicawaagjee wrijin rjet shandit naa oodcarnog majaa, ooshrt imaminrg poi oje Moisés mojani.
44021025	Oyat nat bijrrot judioja ishandiot, ibinacatni calat papera-tee cabigrririgjee judioot costumbre-shrt. Oowi idshanwoi jataa naa idrrirgprn idoloolat, rri-poi jadwouglig jrrlug maa, rri-poi jataa naa maa shan-narniprn, rri-poi ieb caminrglig cataale-jet.
44021026	Oyat Pabloat carmog jajet nat icaunog mot, oyat brlemdicat jajajeicon, ot-poi. Oyat jaluug templo-teja cadjarmjee bijaligu jayeitog wryu jajuprdu caacajeiconjee caofrenda calirgjee catojani.
44021027	Oyat jayryai jabergjee siete wryu, Pablo caluug templo-tee nat itrmnogot judioot Asia atwinot. Oyat cawrr-ág jijogjet cadcannnrg wrijin nat epinot templo-tee. Oyat jadwaorg Pablo calap-jet.
44021028	Cawrr-ág carnog, mot israelot bijnja bidcarg. Oolawi naa bon iboolrgprnjin wrijin moyan-tee cadjajuirg brrtep jamog bijaa bidu judioot, Moisés yerog-jaa poi, naa templo-jaa poi. Oyat durnat cadjarmog templo-teja nat griegoot jad-ebrg naa Dios ot ijei.
44021029	Ojeri carnog Pablo-jaa jadduug-shrm jaboglig moyan-tee jajet naa Efeso atwin jatam Trofirno, ooshrm jaicashag Pabloat jarryuglig jajet templo-teja.
44021030	Oyat canrm wrijin moyan tepinot. Carnan calica wrijin jadwaorgjee Pablo, jadjigyrmog templo-teat. Oyat juicapag templo-otye.
44021031	Oyat Pablo capai, jadjeu jadrrirglig. Oyat naa sodawaot comandanteat cainot-jui cawrr-áglig wrijin nat Jerusalén tepinot.
44021032	Oyat cajuijaberg jasodawaot cacapitanot poi, oyat carnan cajewalee nat epinot. Oyat jadduugbat naa comandante, sodawaot poi, caqued Pablo capairig.
44021033	Oyat naa comandanteat Pablo jaoug cashrt, cadjacui sodawaot jadjiipjee icauot cadena-jet. Oyat jadrm Pablo jatam-jet, jadpoi-rm boirig jaligu ieb idrninrg.
44021034	Oyat nat epinot ibagot cawrr-ág jijogjet, itrninogolat jaipin boi moyerog, boyeja poi brrt yaad. Oyat naa comandante yau jadquedrliprn jadjuirig boirigshrm jaligu cawrr-áa, ooshrmda jarmog jacui Pablo sodawaot ot-teja.
44021035	Oyat nat sodawaot cajonbat caluugjee caot-teja, oowi Pablo cawrryrg calap-jet epinot-shrt ooshrm canrm nat ibagot, jadjeu jadouglig Pablo sodawaot-shrt.
44021036	Cayug wrijin Pablo prna, cawrrág carnog jayaurrirg.
44021037	Oyat jajuprduju Pablo caluugrglig cuartel-teja, jamog naa comandanteat, jamalirrijam ayaadig majet. Oyat comandante mog jan, japishimawajijam griegoot yerog.
44021038	Mam shandit-tejarn naa Egipto atwin carryuuli cuatro mü itogot mot epin-rrirt brgu-teja Cabata bidcargjee.
44021039	Oyat Pablo mog jan, judióla arn, Tarso-atwinda arn, naa moyan ijei Cilicia-tee. Durnat marrn jamalirgjee ayaadig nat epinolat.
44021040	Oyat naa comandante jadirg Pablo yaadig nat epinolat. Oyat Pablo shog cuartel-yee ishrnjet jadduugjee wrijin, jalap jaoonog on-cadjargjee nat epinot. Oyat on-caligbat jayaad calat hebreoot yerog-jet.
44022001	Oyat Pablo mog calat, yarn ajrrot, aiijit poi, durnat jayaujui naa iashipin aalei-jaa.
44022002	Oyat nat judioot jadjuibat Pablo yaadig hebreoot yerog-jet, on capatjririg jadjuijee jan.

45001001	Am Pablo, ibeepe Jesucristoat, ad-ág am idcuiprna aligjee jajuirgjee naa moyerog-juju jet-bidjajeicon ieb-shrt.

45001003	Oolawi naa moyerog ijapin Birri Jesucristo-jaa, naa Dios Wá iminyrgprn wryu jaluugjee David jrimala-shrt bona jaligjee naa Jesucristo.

45001008	Dumat jajuiawrg jabrglig jan ijei naa ajri-Dioat yajaa yam bijrrot wrijin jatam-jaa naa Jesucristo, ooshrm yainot shicapin ijeijet wrijin nat wryu tepinolat yajii yalirg-shrm ijeijet Jesús-jaa.
45001009	Ooshrmda naa Dios,am ibeebrg jan wrijin ajii-teat jaiapinjee naa moyerog-juju jaWá-jaa. Japishijawaagwi ajaa brjejaligu yayeawaaglig oiirigwi ai-annbat jajet.
45001010	Dios arm oiiricawiat jadirgjee anirnnoglig yalica boirigbat jaligui jadjeuu poi oje.
45001011	Jajeu yaluuglig yajrrja yargjee jajeijeeya yabigshayu Espíritujet, yaligjeeya dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog iyawaorg.

45001014	Ooshrmda anwi cadashijuirg wrijin, nat irigot moyan-tee, nat iboolrgot poi jugletaja, nat bicacouot poi, nat bicashancowit poi.

45001016	Auu-shanyiit jaiapindig naa moyerog-juju, ooshrm jawairüg Dioat cajeicondig jajet naa moyerog Cristo-jaa, ebupaacacrt-shrtya capecado-shrm canogjee paraíso-teja nat cajiinriat jajaa, nat judioot jajui-jurdi, otpoi judio ishandiot.
45001017	Ooshrm naa moyerog-juju jadirg japishibiwaagjee ijeinogotni Dioat biruuglig jashrm naa idminrg bishrm bijii birirg-shrm jajaa. Ojeri japoi-mo naa Idnagprn bŕn, jashijugyawi naa Dioat irug oje ijeini jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa.

45001019	Japishicawaagwi ijeijet jajaa naa jet-japishiiwaag Dios-jaa, ooshrm Diolawi jalirnn jaduuglig jabigshayu.

45001022	Camog, ebupishiwajata bidu, ooshrmda eabigshayu biguwi.

45001029	Cajuituun ieb-jet wrijin, cabutugrri boiquejetep cataale-jet, canai boi pin-jet, cabigshayu eb. Caeb caluug wooligot, epin carrirg, caacamrnyeg, cateeshau, cabata cacaryeg, cayeicawaag brrt iebjet.

45001031	Cabigcashancou, idshanminrg oje cayaadauni, cayii cashanduut brrt. Cadcashanquedrt cadeajeicondig cajet nat ieb-minrt calat, cauubiid cashanduut brrt.
45001032	Japishicawaagwi ijeijet naa Dioat oodmogli bŕn. Japishicawaagwi carmdrg snirigya Dios-shrt nat irninrt oje, ooshrt jadpatjri minrgju caebyu. Oyat ijáijet poi cadcaluug nat ieb-minrt oje calijani.
45002001	Oyat mam, jaipini itrm ebyu, jamashanquedrt mamogu japishiashanwaat boirig jaligu ieb, ooshrt mainot shirnapin jajet naa iebjet mayaadyu boi-jaa, ooshrm jamapoirninrg naa ieb imaluug jajaa.
45002002	Ooshrm japishibiwaagwi Dioat jalirg-shirigya ebupaacacrd-shirig caebyu prta oje jamojani jayerog rjetwin-tee.

45002006	Oyat Dioat shirirgya calat catojani jamiijaya naa idminrgprn.

45002008	Ooshrt monnnyu-jetya Dioat jashirir ebupaacacrtjee nat jayiirujut cabigshayu-caaleiat, nat jashanwaorriot naa moyerog rjetwin, ooshrt cayerog cawaorg nat iebnogprnotjin.
45002009	Oyat ebupaacashicrtya, cajii shishŕmya wrijin nat iebminrt. Jajuicawrg ebupaacacrtjee nat judioolat, oyatya poi nat judio ishandiot.
45002010	Oyat nat ijei minrt, Dioya jashirirm cataale ijei brtbrtirig. Cainot shijashipinya ijeijet, jadshirirgya cabigrririgjee ijeijet nat judioot jajui-jurt, otya poi nat judio ishandiot.
45002011	Ooshrm Dioat cashan-áat itrrnnogot epinot itrmnogot-shrt.

45002013	Jashanjei Dioat caluuglig nat jayerog juiyut ojewitep, ooshrt oje ijei-nogotni Dioat caluuglig nat jaminrg oje jarnojani.

45002015	Jajet naa ijei iarninrg jadirg japishibiwaagjee jaliglig cajii-tee naa moyerog ijei, ooshrm cajii-teat japishicawaagwi jajeirig jaiwaorglig. Oje cabigshayuyawi cainot shipini japishicawaagjee o ijei o ieb naa idrninrg.
45002016	Boi wryulauya Dioat cainot shishipinya Jesucristo cooleat wrijin naa ieb icajaanprn brrt-shrt. Cainot shijashipinya jajet naa moyerog-juju idjuiri.
45002017	Oyat mam, judióla arn imog, alig Moisés yerog-jaa imog, alig poi ijeijet Dios-jet imog.
45002018	Japishimawaagwi brjaligu Dioat jajeu ibiminrglig, ooshrm naa moyerog idirgprn bŕn madjuircata mam jaminrgjee naa biradwi ibishiminrg.
45002019	Mam jaisham japishimawaaglig cadmajuirglig nat bigshayu rriprnotjin. Mam jaisham jamaquedrglig imayrglig cajuiyag-tee nat bigshayu br ruot.
45002021	Mam cajuirrm brrt, boirigshrmjam mamashanjuirr maaleat. Mam, macupoishet imog, boirigshrmjam masheg.

45002023	Mam, alig ijeijet jajaa naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprndi imog, jamalirg mii rriprnjin camoglig Dios-jaa imashanminrt-shrm oje jayerog mojani.
45002024	Ojera jamo naa Idnagprndi, nat iyawawinot cayaad iebjet Dios-jaa jashrm naa ieb iyarninrg.

45003001	Oyat boirigjam ijei iribrg judioolat brrt-shrt. Dioat jaminrririjam calat ijei brrt-shrt.

45003003	Oyat bojejam bishimo cajaa nat itrmnogot. Cashanditu daiimogjet Dios yerog-jaa, Dios shandit-tejam dai-imogjet jajaa naa ood-jamogli.
45003004	Dioat jashishan-namnotya naa ood-jamogli bŕn. Teeshauprnotjinda wrijin nat mot, ooshrt Dioat ishiminrgya wrijin oje jayerog rjetwin mojani. Ojera jarnog naa Idnagprndi, mayii cashiruugya mayerog-shrm, oyatya mapishicashiwaa ijeiya maliglig mainot shicapinbatya.

45003006	Jashan-ebda Dios, yau ishrmjet. Jacaebu naa Dios, jadcugquedrriwrnjam-om cainot cainot shijapindig nat wryu tepinot.

45003008	Oyat boirigshrmjam jabishishanminrri oje cateeshaulauni bijaa. Camog, biebyu biuminrg jaminyrgjee ijeijet brrlat. Dioya cashirirr ebupacacrtjee nat iyaalolat oje.
45003009	Oyat bojejam bidu judioot. Bijeyijam bidu brrt-shrt. Yau ishrmjet, ooshrm biquedrcat cainot shibipindig nat judioot oje cainot shibipindauniri nat brrt epinot, naa ieb ibiminrgprn wrijin bitojani jadshirigya bijaa.
45003010	Ojera jamo naa Idnagprn bŕn, boiruud ijei, boiruud itrm.

45003020	Oyat boirig shandit Dioat ijeijet iruug calig-shrm jayerog bŕnwinjin-jaa, ooshrm jayerog cashanwaorri rjet. Oowi jayerog bŕnwinjin jadirm japishibiwaaglig iebnogprnotjina biriglig.
45003021	Ooshrt dumat Dioat jalirg japishibiwaagjee ijeinogotni bidjaluuglig Cristo-shrm, yau jayerog bŕnwinjin shrm. Ojeri poi jamooli naa Moisés, nat poi brrt Dios yerog shipinidi bŕn.
45003022	Oowi ijeinogotni Dioat caluuglig wrijin nat cajiirirt Jesucristojaa. Cadjashan-áat itrrnnogot brrt-shrt.
45003023	Caebyu carninrg wrijin, yau jadquedrliprn jadnarglig naa Dios ijei caalei bigshayu-jet.

45003025	Dioat jalirg jarrijee Cristo bishrm jadnamjee bishrt biebyu jamaa-jet, bijii birirg-shrm jajaa. 45003026	Ojeri idminrglig naa Dioat japishibiwaagjee ijeija-jaliglig naa Dios, japishibiwaagjee ijeinogotni Dioat caluuglig nat cajiirirt Jesús-jaa.
45003027	Ooshrmda jabidquedrrijam ijei bibrglig bireiot-jaa. Yau ishrmjet. Boirigshrmjam jabishishanquedrri ijei bibrgli bireiot-jaa. Ooshrm jashanjei Dioat biruuglig jashrm naa ibiminrg jan, ooshrt ijeinogotni Dioat biruuglig bijii birirg-shrm Jesús-jaa.

45003029	Oo tejarnwi judioot jri-Dios naa Dios. Cajri-Dios shandittejam poi nat judio ishandiot. Rcaiji, oolawi cajri-Dios poi nat judio ishandiot.
45003030	Jatrrnwi naa Dios, oyat ijeinogotni Dioat caluuglig nat judioot cajii calirg-shrm Jesús-jaa, natpoi judio ishandiot cajii calirg-shrm jajaa.
45003031	Oyat jabishirirrijam mii rriprnjina jaliglig naa moyerog bŕnwinjin jabiwaorg-shrm naa moyerog juju. Yau ishrmjet, ooshrt jayerog bŕnwinjin-jet japishibiwaag jabijeuligli Bijeicono.
45004001	Oyat bojejam bishimo jajaa naa biroom Abraam. Boirigjam naa ijei idtairirg.
45004002	Epinolat jaluugu ijeijet naa Abraam jashrm naa idminrglig, jadquedrg jainot shijapindig ijeijet moolat, ooshrt Dioat jashandit.
45004003	Bojejam jamo naa Idnagprndi. Naa Abraam jajii jalirg Dios-jaa ooshrmda ijeijet Dioat jaluug.
45004004	Naa bon ibeepe jaŕriat, mii rriprnjin shandit naa jaŕriat ibrg jan. Ooshrt jamii jashibrgya ooshrm jamii jarrirg jajet naa idbeebbrg jan.
45004005	Oyat naa jajii shandirri jabeeb-jaa, ooshrt jajii jalirg jajaa naa cajeicono iebnogprnotjin, ijeijet Dioat jaluug jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa.
45004006	Bŕndi David jaipin poi, jashijáiya naa bon Dioat iruug oje ijeini jajejeicon-shrm mii-rrijet, naa ebupaashancrli jashrm naa ieb iminrgprn.
45004007	Ojeri jamog David, cashijaiya nat Dioat ebyu namprnot cashrt, nat Dioat ebyu iweiprnot cashrt.
45004008	Jajii shijáiya naa bon Dioat ebyu shandirri jajaa naa ieb iminrgprn.
45004009	Dios moijam cashijaiya nat judioot siconsisaoot brrt-shrt. Caijapinirijam poi cajaa nat judio ishandiot. Jabiquedrcat yabipinrglig, ijeijeta Dioat jaluug Abráarn jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa. Yau cacosturnbre-shrm.
45004010	Brrlaulijam ijeijet Dioat jaiuu Abraam, o cacostumbre siconsison prnot o jajuprtuju. Yau japrnot ooshrt jajuprduliju.
45004011	Dioat jalirg Abraam jaminrgjee naa siconsison ijeijet idduugprnat jetjaatadrg pecado-rrijet Dioat jaluuglig jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa. Ooshrmda caíija jalig naa Abraam wrijin nat judio ishandiot poi nat cajiirirt Dios-jaa, oyat Dioat cainot shipin ijeinogota caliglig.
45004012	Caíija jalig Abraam nat judioot cajii shandirriot jajaa naa idminrg wiuyu-jet, nat cajii-rirlat Dios-jaa oje jalijani naa Abraam.
45004013	Bŕn Dioat japinrg Abraam jajrdwat poi, capina jaligjeeya naa wryu, yau jashrm naa moyerog idbrgprndi, ooshrt ijeinogotni cajaluuglig cajiicalirg-shrm jajaa.
45004014	Jalibrguli calat naa ijei Dioat oodmogli calat calig-shrm jayerog bŕnwinjin-jaa, boirica shancuglit-om bijii birirr Cristo-jaa-om boirica shancugpoirit-om naa ijei Dioat oodmoglig birat bŕn.
45004015	Ooshrm naa moyerog mog birat, Dioya jashirirm ebupaacacrdig caebyu-shrm. Oyat nat oolat boiruudbrgotcug naa moyerog bŕnwinjin jadminrg poi iyaujet jashrt.
45004016	Ooshrt uubiidjet Dioat caluug, ooshrmda jamog jashibrgya calat naa ijei mii-rrijet, cajii calirg-shrm jajaa. Ojeri jamog calat jadtairirgjeeya naa ijei oodjamoglig calat wrijin nat Abraam prnatwinot. Jaijashanpin calat nat oolat jalibrgot jayerog bŕnwinjin brrt-shrt, ooshrt jaijapin poi calat wrijin nat cajiirirt jajaa oje jalijani naa Abraam, ooshrm biíja-jalig wrijin bidu.
45004017	Ojera jamog Abraam-jaa naa Idnagbrndi, malirg caíija maligjee nat epinot ibagot jadduugjee naa Dios, naa-jaa jajii-jalirg, naa calimn cajuglig nat irriprnotjin, naa iminrr wrijin naa iishandujiriju.
45004018	Abraarnat jajeitei prnpatjet naa ishanquedrri jajeiiteirig. Japishijawaagliwi jajii-teat caíija jalig-shirigya ibagot epinot oje Dios mojaniri jan. Ojeri jamog, ojeiya cashitoo majrdwada maat maini.
45004019	Jalibrg-shucat jan sien wiig naa Abraarnat, yau jacairiprn jajii jalirglig Dios-jaa quepaja jalica-shrm oje irriprnjini. Oje poi ja-u Sara, jabigyeg wuucat jatrririgjee, ooshrt Abraamat japishiwaagwi jatrririg shirigyawi oje Dios mojaniri jan.
45004020	Yau jacauliprn jabigshayu jajaa naa Dios mooyu jan. Dios yerog shanwaorriprnjin-shandit naa Abraam, ooshrt jijogjet jajiijalirg Dios-jaa, ijei jabrg jan.
45004021	Jabigrririg naa Abraam pishijawaag-shrm iwairügjet Dioat jaminrg-shirigya jan wrijin naa oodjamogprn jan.
45004022	Ooshrmda ijeini Dioat jaluugli Abraam, jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa.
45004023	Jajricashan-nadi oowi naa Abraam brrt-shrt jijeijet Dioat jaluuglig jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa.
45004024	Ooshrt bishrm poi jajri-canaa oje, ooshrm ijeijetya poi Dioat bishiruug bidu bijiirirg-shrm jajaa naa jawryrrprndi Biŕri Jesús morriyu-shrt.
45004025	Dioat jalirg jarrijee Jesucristo jadnamjee bishrt naa ieb ibiminrg, oyat jajuijamirg morriyu-shrt bidjalirgjee ijeinogotni bidu jashrm naa idminrgli bishrm.
45005001	Ooshrmda ijeinogotni Dioat biruuglig bijii birirg-shrm jajaa. Bidjajeicon jajet jashrm naa Biŕri Jesucristoat iminrg birat.
45005002	Cristo tam-jaa jabinarg naa Dios, bijii birirg-shrm jajaa. Ooshrmda biulig dai-imogjet jajaa naa ijei idminrg birat mii-rrijet. Oyat biulig ijáijet jajeibiteibat birigjeeya Dios-jet ijeijet brtbrtirig-teja.
45005003	Oocatrm shandit bijái jajeibitei-shrm ijeijet, ooshrt bijii-jái poi ebupaabicrtbat jashrm, japishibiwaag-shrm naa ebupaaicrtyuat jalirglig dai-imogjet biriglig prnpatjet jajet naa paabishicrt nam wryu-tee.
45005004	Ebupaabicrduya prnpatjet, bibigshayu shijeiya-jamo. Oyat jajeiuya bibigshayu jajeibishiteiya jabiruugjee naa ijei idshirirgya birat.
45005005	Oyat jajeibiteiuya jabiruugjee naa ijei, yauya biuushiyiiriprn, ooshrm Dioat jalirg biyü biruuyeglig jajet naa Espíritu idirgprn bijii-tee. Japishibiwaagwi Cristoat biyii ruuglig jarrishrrndi bishrm
45005006	Bŕnju bijurriyugbadiju, Cristo bigyeg minocat jarrijee iebnogprnotjin-shrm.
45005007	Brr-shandit jajewe jarrijee boi-shrm. Jashanjeu poi jarririg ijeinogot-shrm. Ooshrt jadiritep-pawi jajewe jarririg ijei-shrm.
45005008	Ooshrt Dioat jalirg japishibiwaagjee biyii jaluuglig jarri-shrm Cristo bishrm biebnogbatdiju.

45005010	Bŕnju bibaata jabirgli Dios, bidjajeiconwi jajet jarri-shrm jaWá bishrm. Oyat dumat iwairüg-jet jaiquedrg bidjajeieondig ieb-shrt jaWá biglewrg-shim morriyu-shrt.
45005011	Oyat ijáijet jayebiwaag Dios jashrm naa Biŕri Jesucristoat iminrg birat. Ooshrm Cristo-jet jabiquedrg bibijeicondig Dios-jet.
45005012	Bŕn itrm bon-shrm mobig-shayu iebprnjin yuglig naa wryu-tee, oyat jaebyu-shrm morriyu yug jalica. Oyat morriyu yug poi calica wrijin nat wryu tepinot caebyu caminrg-shrm wrijin.
45005013	Caebyu caminrg jajuprduju Dioat jalirglig Moiséat naa moyerog jet-jaiwinjashog ieb caminrglig. Ooshrm jashandirdiju ebupaacacrdjee caebyu-jaa, jashandit shrmju cajaa naa moyerog jaiwinshomdi ieb caminrglig.
45005014	Oyat morriyu yug Adan-lica, calica poi wrijin japrnotwinot ata-on Moisés-lica cajewalee caebyu caminrg-shrm. Ooshrt nat Adán prnatwinot boiraudiju calat itnn moyerog jadwaorgjee oje jalijani. Ooshrm Adan-jet jabiminrg comparación jajaa naa iyugprn japrna.
45005015	Oyat Adán ebyu-jet jabishanquedrt jabiminrgu comparación qet jajaa naa ijei Dioat iminrg birat. Morriyu yug calica nat ibagot jaebyu-shrm naa itnn bon, ooshrt jashrm naa itrm Bon Jesucristo, Dioat bijeicon mii-rrijet ieb-shrt. Jajeirig naa idminrgprn caligjeeya ijeijet nat ibagot.
45005016	Oyat naa Dioat irirgprn birat, jadshanminrt birat ieb oje Adán ebyuat iminrlauni. Caebyu lig cajaa nat wryu tepinot wrijin jashrm naa ieb idminrg itrmjetwi naa Adánat. 45005017	Morriyu yug calica jijogjet jaebyu-shrm naa itnnwi bon, ooshrt iwairügjet Dios bigshayu ijei ruug cajii-teja cashijugya oiiricawiat nat jaluujut ijeijet jashrm naa itrm Bon Jesucristoat iminrg birat mii-rrijet.
45005018	Oyat jaebyu-shrm itrm bon Adán, caebyu lig cajaa wrijin nat wryu tepinot. Oyat naa itrm bon Jesucristo, ijeijet Dioat jaluug naa Cristoat irninrgprn calat, ooshrmda ijeinogotni Dioat caluuglig jadirg-shrm calat jabigshayu ijei cajugjeeya oiiricawiat.

45005020	Oyat jayug calica naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprn Moiséat japishicawaagjee jaebdig naa idminrg. Ooshrt caebyu caminrgbatju ibagjet, iwairügjet Dioat jaminrg calat naa ijei mii-rrijet.
45005021	Caebyuat calirg canndrglig, ooshrt Dios bigshayu ijeiat jalirg ijeinogotni cajaluuglig jalibrgjeeya calat wryu ishanbeji jashrm naa Biŕri Jesucristoat iminrg calat.
45006001	Oyat bojejam bishimo. Jabishiminrrijam-patjei biebyu Dioat jadnamjee bishrt jabiruugjee-patjei jabigshayu ijei.

45006003	Japishiyashanwat-tejam wrijin bidu bautisao idcargprnot Jesucristo tam-jaa, bautisao bicarg birigjee dai-imogjet Cristo-jet, jet-bibitadrg jarririg bishrt bibigshayu bŕnwinjin Cristo-jet cruza-jaa.

45006015	Oyat bojejam bishirii. Biebyu biminrrijam birig-shrm jajaa naa ijei Dioat ibrgprn birat mii-rrijet jashrt naa moyerog idirglig bŕn. Yau ishrmjet ieb biminrliprn.
