45006017	Durnat ijei ibrg Dioat yajaa. Bŕn yaebyuat yajiipdig, ooshrt jayawaorcat yajii-teat naa moyerog jet-yabijuirg, ooshrmda jayauminrg oje jamojani.

45006020	Bŕn yaebyuat yajiip yaligbatju yaujet jashrt naa ijei Dioat irirg bijii-tee.

45007001	Ajrrot, yam japishiwajat Moisés yerog, japishiyawaagwi naa moyerocat cacuirig nat epinot cajujugbatju.

45007003	Ooshrt jaligu boi bon-jet jabon-shrt jajujugbatju jabón, iigprnjinda oo. Ooshrt jarriu jashrt jabón jashiwugya jashrt naa moyerog jajiipiprndi. Oyat jabondigu-shri oyem iigprnjin shandita oo.

45007015	Japishiashanwaat boirigshrm jaligu jaminrg naa iminrg. Jashanminrt oje jajeulauni, ooshrt jaminrgju naa ishanjewi jaminrglig. Naa iruugprncug ieb-jet, oolawi iminrg.
45007016	Oyatjri jaminrgu naa ieb ishanjewi, japishiyawaagwi ijeiya jaliglig naa moyerog jaiwinshom ieb biminrglig.

45008001	Dumat caebyu shandit cajaa ebupaacacrtjee-cugjin nat irigot dai-imogjet Jesucristo-jet, nat ishanminrriot oje cataaleat jajeulauni, ooshrt idminrg oje Espírituat jajeulauni.
45008002	Oyatjri naa moyerog irig birat Espíritu-jet, jadirg birat wryu ishanbeji birig-shrm dai-imogjet Jesucristo-jet. Oyatjri adshiu jashrt naa moyerog jalirr aebyu liglig ajaa, morriyu poi.
45008003	Ooshrm Dioat jaminrg birat naa Moisés yerocat ishanquedrri jadminrglig. Naa moyerog bŕnwinjinat jashandirt jabiwaorglig. Ooshrmda Dioat jacui jaWá nam wryu-teja. 45008004	Dios Wáat iminrg wrijin bishrm oje Jaii mojaniri bŕn. Jamii jabrg wrijin bicuenta jabishanminrgjee oje bitaaleat jajeulauni, ooshrt jabiminrg oje Espírituat jajeulauni.
45008005	Natjri iminrt oje cataaleat jajeulauni jaicashaat wrijin jet-cataale cajáirca. Ooshrt nat jarninrt oje Espírituat jajeulauni, jaicashag wrijin jet-Espíritu Cajaírca.
45008006	Nat jajewet cataale cajáirglig cashirriya Dios-shrt, ooshrt nat jajewet Espíritu cajáirglig jashirirbrgya calat wryu ishanbeji, cabigrri-shirigya jashrt naa wryu ebyu.
45008007	Nat jajewet cataale cajáirglig cabatajadrg Dios, ooshrt jadshanjeu Dios yerog cawaorglig. Jadshanquedrt jadminrglig oje jamojani.
45008008	Ooshrm nat jajewet cataale cajáirglig, jadshanquedrt jadjáirglig Dios.
45008009	Jaligu yajii-tee naa Espíritu, iyashishanminrtya oje yataaleat jajeulauni, ooshrt yaurninrg oje Espírituat jajeulauni. Naa ood boiruudbrg Espíritu jajii-tee, Cristo pin shandit.
45008010	Oyatjri Cristo ligu yajii-tee, jashirriya yataale yaebyu-jet ooshrt jashijugyawi yajii Dioat yadduug-shrm ijeinogotni.

45008014	Dios trriota calig wrijin nat jajewet Espíritu Santoat calrmwaoteglig.

45008019	Wrijin nat Dioat iminrgprnot shrnoja irigot nam-poi wryu-tee, iajeicatei jijogjet jadduugjee bojejaliguya calig-shirig shrnoja nat Dios trriot.
45008020	Wrijin nat Dioat iminrgprnot idbiruugot cashirmdrgya. Cadjashan-cugjeu carmdrglig, ooshrt Dioat caminrglig oiirigota. Ooshrm bŕnju dumat-patjei jajeicatei jadduugjee naa ijei ishanbeji oodjamogli calat.
45008021	Ooshrm Dioya cashishiuwi nat idjaminrgprnot jashrt naa cajiipiri naa jalirr carmdrglig. Cadjashishiuya jaliibrgjeeya calat naa ijei idshiriiya calat nat jatrriot.
45008022	Capishibiwagwi wrijin nat Dioát iminrgprnot iiyaishrmwíat calii bŕnju dumat poi, ebupaacacrt oje denat ebupaacrdauni jatrri jawaobat.
45008023	Ood-shanwirit nat idjaminrgprnot, ooshrt ebupaabicrt poi bidu oolat jalibrgot naa Espíritu. Oolawi naa Espíritu Dioat irirg jurgprn birat. Itrmjaniwi biquigligju bijii-tee jajeibiteibatju bidjalirgjee jatrriota birigjee shrnoja, jajeibitei jadshiujee bitaale morriyu-shrt.
45008024	Dioat bijeicon ieb-shrt jajeibitei-shrm jabiruuglig naa-jaa bijii birirg. Jaishanquedrt jajeiiteirig naa iiruug dumat. Dioat jalirgu jabiruulicat dumat, jabiquedrrijam-patjee jajeibiteirigju jabiruugjee.
45008025	Ooshrt jateibiteiu jabiruugjee naa ibishanduujiju, prnpatjet jajeibiutei jabiruugjee.
45008026	Ojeri poi naa Espíritu, bijnja jalig bidu ishanwairügprnotjin, ooshrm japishibishan-waat biibirmdig Dios-jet oje jajeulauni. Ooshrt naa Espíritu Santo, Dios rma bijaa jijogjet. Jaishanquedrt jaipindig moyerog-jet naa Espírituat oodmog.
45008027	Oyat naa Dios japishiwaja brjaligu bibigshayu lig, japishijawagwi brjaliyu-jaligu naa Espírituat irm cajaa nat Dios pinit oje Dioat jaieulauni.
45008028	Japishibiwaagwi Dioat jaminrgli ijei calat nat jayurujut jajet naa ieb iyug calica, nat idjaagprnot iminrt oje jamojani.
45008029	Dioat japishiwacadiwi japinit-jaa jajuprduju wryu caluuglig. Bŕnju jamogli cadjawawug jaaleatwi cabigshayu jacambiargjeeya, cataale poi ojewi jaWáani, capeewaiya jaligjeeya jaWá cajewaíee nat jajrrot ibagot.
45008030	Oyat nat Dioat iwawugprnot jaaleatwi bŕnju, cadjaág poi. Oyat nat idjaagprnot, cadjalirg ijeinogota caliglig. Oyat nat idjaluugot oje ijeinogotni, cataale jacambiarg ijeijet brtbrt-irigjet.
45008031	Oyatjri bojejam bishimo Dios-jaa. Dios ligu bijet, brryajarn bishiquedrrm bidjanarndig.
45008032	Naa jaiwinshanshoi jaWá bishrt, jadirg jarrijee bishrm wrijin, jadshishanbrt-teyajam birat poi wrijin naa ijei idirg jaWáat.
45008033	Brrjarn jadquedrm iebjet jayaadig cajaa nat Dioat jougprnot janwi. Oolawi naa Dios calirr ijeinogota caliglig.
45008034	Ooshrm brr-jam jadquedrm cainot shijapindig ebupaacacrtjee caebyu prta. Oolawi Cristo irri cashrm, oowi ijuimigprndi morriyushrt, oyat jateg Dios wireat bijaijarmjee Dios-shrt.
45008035	Boirigjam jadquedrr jadcairglig biyii jaluuglig naa Cristoat. Jacayijam biyii jaluuglig ebupaabicrtbat, o bijii shŕrnbat poi, o bibata bicargbat poi, o ebupaabicrtbat bui-jaa poi, o biuubiidbat poi, o rrglig yugbat birica, o morriyu yugbat.
45008036	Ojera jamo naa Idnagprndi, jadjeu bidcarrirglig wryú-shitojani mayii bimug-shim. Bidcaluug oje oveja irriyawani.
45008037	Ooshrt jijogjet jajricabicou wrijin naa ieb iyug birica, ooshrm biwairüyu jabrg naa biyiirujuat.
45008038	Ooshrmda japishiawagwi boirig-shandit jadquedrr jacaijee bishrt biyii jaluuglig naa Dioat. Morriyuat jashanquedrg jadwawuglig bishrt, bidjashanwawut jashrt bijugbatju, ángeleolat jashanpoiquedrt bidjawawuglig jashrt, rri-poi iwairügolat, rri poi dumatwinolat, rri poi nat ibishiruugolatya.
45008039	Binogu shrnoja jashishancayiya Dioat biyii-ruuglig, rriya poi binogu monoja. Boirig-shandit capei nat Dioat irninrgprnot jadquedrr jadirglig biyii jashanduugjeecugjin birig-shrm Biŕri Jesucristo-jet.
45009001	Yapinrg rjet am ajiirirat Cristo-jaa, ateishanshau. Japishiawagwi ajii-tee Espíritu Santo-jet ijetwina jaliglig naa oodamog.
45009002	Ipegjeta ajii-shrm, ebupaa-acrt oiirig ajii-tee.
45009003	Yaibrjin armdrriu Cristo-shrt ajrrot-shrm cayii aluug-shrm. Oodwi aloomotjin jrdwat oje alijani.
45009004	Israeli jrdwata caliglig. Bŕn Dioat cabatai jatrrijulota caligjee. Bŕn Dios liglig cajewalee idyrgli cajaa ijeijet. Jaijacugpindi calat ijei jayerog cacawaorguli. Dioat jacuglirgli calat naa moyerog jetjaiwinjashog ieb caminrglig, jadirg calat naa culto templo-tee poi. Oyat cadjapinrg jajaa naa ijei idshiminrgya calat Cristo-jet.
45009005	Cajrdwata yam nat biroomot bŕnwinot, oyat Cristo minyrg wryu jaluugjee cajewalee oje boni. Oolawi cajri-Dios wrijin, oowi caijewe wrijin boirig-jaligu. Ijei biubrg jan oiiricawiat, Amén.
45009006	Jabishanquedrt bimogu, Dioat jashanminrt oje jamojani bŕn calat nat israeliot, ooshrt israeliot-shandit wrijin nat Israelot jrdwat.
45009007	Abraam trriot shandit Espíritu-jaa wrijin nat Abraam jrdwat. Ojeri jamo Dios jan, majrdwatya nat iminyrgot Isaac-shrt.
45009008	Ooshrmda capishibiwagwi Dios trriot shandit caminyrg-shrm jayerog waort-shrt. Ooshrt Abraam jrdwata calig nat Dioat irirgprnot jatniota caligjee calig-shrm jajaa naa oodjamogprndi Abraamat naa Cristo.
45009009	Ojeri Dios mo Abraamat, boi wiyulauya majrrja mashirr, oyatya jatrri-shirii ma-u Sara.
45009010	Dioat jaishanpindi Sara trri catrm-jaa, ooshrt cajaali poi nat Rebeca trriot icauot. Jatrmdiwi caíi nat biroom Isaac.
45009011	Jajuprduju catrrdig Rebeca-shrt, jadshanminrtju ijei, rripoi ieb, ooshrt Dioat jaág itrrn capei japishiiwagjee Dioat jaquedrglig jadáglig brr-jaligu idjeu.
45009012	Oyat Dios mo Rebecaat, naa ipaagprn japeewai-itrt yerog jashijuiya.
45009013	Ojeri poi jamooli naa Idnagprndi bŕn, jayii aluug Jacob ooshrt jaeb aluug Esau.
45009014	Oyatjri bojeyajam bishimog, ieb jaminrrijam naa Dioat. Yau ishrm-jet.
45009015	Ojeri jamooli Moiséat, jajrija-jarg brr-jaligui idjeu. Uubiidjet jaluug brr-jaligui ijeu uubiidjet jaluuglig.
45009016	Uubiidjet Dioat biruug, rri-jashrm naa ibiminrgcug ijei, rri-poi biebyu-shrm. Ooshrt uubiidjet bidjaluug biyii jaluug-shrm.
45009017	Bŕn poi jatee naa papera Idnagprndi, ojeri jamo Dios jajaa naa Ejiptoot jriwairüg. Mashirirgya cajriwairüca maligjee jatadrgjeeya abigshayu, jadduugjeeya jajet naa ishiminrgya man, cayaadjeeya ajaa wrijin wryu-tee.
45009018	Ooshrmda japishibiwaagwi uubiidjet Dioat jaluug brr-jaligu idjeu. Oyat jadirg cajii-shaadig jashrt brr-jaligu idjeu.
45009019	Oyat maupinrgya an, jadminrgu oje naa Dioat, boirigshrmjam cainot shijapin nat epinot. Brr-jam jadquedrr jadminiglig naa Dioat ishanjewi jabiminrglig.
45009020	Mam bon, itrmjanitejam malii Dios-jet jamaquejargjee-cugjin Dios. Itrm wam jaquedrrijam jayaaddig jaminrprnot, boirigshrmdijam amarninrg oje.
45009021	Naa jaminrr ishoocon, jadquedrg idrninrglig oje jadjeulauni. Jaquedrg jadminrglig itrm wam ijei, oyat itrrn wam iebprnjin jajet naa jricabinprn wamshou-jet.
45009022	Oyat bojejam bishirno Dioat jad-jeuu bidjatadrglig janrmyu-jet jabigshayu-jet poi cajuicajacou-shrm prnpatjet nat irmdrgyawanot jashrt capecado-shrm.
45009023	Dioat iminrg oje japishibiwagjee ijeiya jaliglig naa jaminrgprn birat bidu idjaluugot uubiidjet bŕnju dumat poi, jalibrgjeeya birat naa ijei oodjamogli bŕn.
45009024	Oodawi bidu Dioat iágprnot capet nat judioot, capet poi nat judio ishandiot.
45009025	Ojeri Dios mooli papera-tee Nat aepinota ishandiot capishiashiwaagya aepinota caliglig. Oyatya nat idashanjewidi capishiashiwaagya idajeuprnota caliglig.
45009026	Oriidi Dioat capinrprndi aepinot shandita yarn, omyawi poi japishicashiwaaya jatrriota caliglig naa Dios ijug.
45009027	Oyat Isaías mooli cajaa nat israelot. Cashibagya oje darnatmaini cashitogya nat israeli jrdwat, ooshrt cashiyaiyawi Dioat ishijeiconot ebupaacacrt-shrt jayerog cashanwaorg-shrm.
45009028	Mogwainiya Dioat jashiminrg nam wryu-tee wrijin oje jabigshayu rjetwinat jalirlauni.
45009029	Jadshirninrgya oje Isaías mojani bŕnju. Ojeri jarnog, cadjashandirtu bitrriot naa ibagot-Rri, bicugbeegtete-om oje Sodoma beerauni, Gomorra poi.
45009030	Oyatjri bojejam bishimo cajaa nat judio ishandiot, nat jashanjewitdi ijeijet Dioat caluuglig. Dumat ijeijet Dioat caluug cajii calirg-shrm jajaa.
45009031	Ooshrt nat israelot jajewet ijeijet Dioat caluuglig calig-shrm jayerog bŕnwinjin-jaa, ooshrt jadshanquedrt jadminrglig naa minrgjacuiprn.
45009032	Boirigshrmjam Dioat cashanduji oje ijeinogotni. Ooshrm cajii cashandirt jajaa cadjajeiconjee-cugjin, ooshrt jadjeu ijeinogotni Dioat caluuglig jashrm naa idminrg caalei bigshayu-jet. Ooshrm calrg jashrt naa jet-bidjajeicon oje moshiim shiitoulauni jáa-jaá molrgjee.
45009033	Jadminrg oje idnaalauniri brn. Oowi nam Sion-tee jalirr naa Jaa, jaá-cashiim shicatou calrgjee nat judioot. Ooshrt nat cajiirirt jajaa cauushi-shanyitya.
45010001	Ajrrot ajii-teat jajeu Dioat cajeicondig nat israelot ebupaacacrt-shrt caebyu-shrm. Ooshrm Dios arrn cajaa ajii-teat.
45010002	Japishiawaag jadjeulig ijei caminrglig Dioat, ooshrt japishicashanwaat jadjáirglig Dios.
45010003	Japishicashanwat bijaligu idminrgshirig Dioat ijeinogotni cadjaluugligjee. Ooshrt jadjeu ijeijet Dioat caluuglig jajet naa idminrg caalei bigshayujet.
45010004	Cristoat jaquedrcat jadminrglig oje Dios yerog bŕnwinjinat bicuirauni jawugjee cashrt nat cajiirirt Cristo-jaa, ijeinogotni Dioat caluugligjee.
45010005	Bŕndi Moisés mog jajaa naa moyerog Dioat irirgprndi. Ojeri jamo, naa iminrr oje naa moyerog mojani jashirigyawi jajaa naa idminrgprn.
45010006	Ooshrt ojeri jamo jajaa naa jajewe ijeijet Dioat jaluugjee jajii jalirg-shrm jajaa. Jaimacupoipin majii-tee brryajarn ishinoo shrnoja Cristo jawonrmogjee.
45010007	Jaimacupoipin brrjaligu iwon monoja jadwryrgjee Cristo imprnotjin-shrt.
45010008	Oyatjri bojejam jamo. Ojera jamog, janagwi mashrt naa moyerog, jaligwi macoolee majii-tee poi. Naa moyerog oolawi jet-cadbijuirg cajii calirgjee Cristo-jaa.
45010009	Jaimapinu macoole-jet Maŕriya jaliglig naa Jesús, oyat japishimawaagu majii-teat Dioat jawrryrprn morriyu-shrt, madshijeiconya-jamo jashrt naa paacashicrtya caebyu-shrm, madrrnogjee paraíso-teja.
45010010	Oowi bijii-teat bibigshayu birirglig Cristo-jaa, ijeijet bidjaluugjee jashrm naa idminrg birat. Oyat biyee-jet testimonio ibipin Jesucristo-jaa bidjajeiconjee ebupaabicrt-shrt biebyu-shrm binogjee paraíso-teja.
45010011	Ojeri jamo naa Idnagprndi, naa jajiirirg jajaa jauushishanyitya.
45010012	Ooshrm Dioat cashanjeu nat judioot brrt epinot-shrt. Naa Biŕri oola poi Caŕri wrijin. Oyat jadirg ibag ijei calat wrijin nat cairmrt jashrt.
45010013	Wrijin nat cairmrt Biŕri tam-jaa cadjashijeiconya ebupaacacrtshrt caebyu-shrm canogjee paraíso-teja.
45010014	Ooshrt bojeyawrnjam jadquedrgshirig caicarmdig jashrt yaujaligu cajii calirliprn jajaa. Oyat bojeyawrnjam jadquedrg-shirig jainot cajuirig boiat cashanjuirgu.
45010015	Oyat bojeyawrnjam jadquedrg shirig cadcajuirnoglig boiat cashancuinotu cacajuirgnogjee. Ojera jamo naa Idnagprndi, jajeira cashiim nat inogot jadjuirgjee naa moyerog jet-cacajeicon Dios-jet.
45010016	Ooshrt wrijin shandit epinolat jawaorr naa moyerog ijei. Ojeri jamog Isaías, mam Aŕri, brm-jalii naa jawaorr naa moyerog ibijuirg.
45010017	Dios yerog-jet cajii calirg jajaa. Oyat naa moyerog idjui, oolawi moyerog Cristo-jaa.
45010018	Oyat yarm, jadshanjui-tejamju naa moyerog. Rcaiji jayerog cajuiat. Ojeri jamog naa Idnagprndi bŕn, jadjuiat jayerog wrijin naa wryu-tee. Cayerog minocat wrijin caniti tojani.
45010019	Oyat cadarm shri, japishicashanwaat-tejamju nat israelolat jajaa naa Idnagprndi. Moiséla naa jaipin-jurm calat, jashirirgya cabigshayu naijee nat Dios epinota ishandiot. Cadshirirgya cabicacoujee yashrt yadnrmrgjeeya nat japishishanwajidi bŕn,
45010020	Oyat ishan-omijet Isaíasat capinrglig, aatairircata am nat ashanjewiradi, aatadrbrg calat nat ainot shan-rmiradi jadjuijee ainot.
45010021	Oyat Isaías yaadbat cajaa nat israeliot, ojeri jamog, wryu shitojani cadaág nat epinot ayerog shanwaorriot nat jajewet cabata adrglig.
45011001	Oyatjri jarm jajuijee, Dioat canamijam jaepinot jashrt. Yau ishrmjet, ooshrm ampoi israelot peira am. Abraam jrrwaira am. Benjaminat peira am.
45011002	Dioat cashannamnot jaepinot, nat pishijawagot jaepinota caliglig bŕn. Japishiyashanwatejamju bojejaligu Idnagprn mo Elíasjaa, cainot shijapinbat israeliot Dios jarmbat.
45011003	Ojeri jamog Elias, mam Am, bŕn cadcarrirg nat imacuiprnot mayerog shipinit. Bŕn cadcanam nat caaltaot on ijei cabrliprn man. Oyat ayritrmbr am irig. Oyat jadjeu poi adrrirglig.
45011004	Ojeri Dios mo Elíaat, cadawawucat an siete-mil mot ishanshoiot cautjuiyag-jet jayaatnaa cajri dios jatam Baal.
45011005	Ojera poi dumat, caligwi cajewalee nat Dioat iwawugprnot jan cayii jaluug-shrm oje jabigshayu ijeiat jalirlauni.
45011006	Oyat Dioat cawawugu jaaleatwi cayii jaluug-shrm, cadjashanwawut jan idbeeb-shrm jan brjashirii cadjashanjeicon mii-rrijet.
45011007	Oyatjri bojejam bishimog, jadshantairirt naa idjeucug nat israeliolat, ooshrt jatairircat nat Dioat iwawugprnolat jan cayii jaluugshrm mii-rrijet. Oyat nat brrt cabigshayu shaalat Dios-shrt.
45011008	Ojera jamo Idnagprndi, Dioat jalirg cabigshayu oje ioushugni idduug-shrt cabig-jet, idjui-shrt poi cabutog-jet bŕnju dumat poi.
45011009	Ojeri David poi mo, cadyaulirg cafiestaat cateeshaurgjee calrgjee yeem-teja Dios-shrt ebupaacacrtjee jashrm naa íeb idminrg.
45011010	Jayaulirg cabigshayu brrujee oje mobigu brrulauni nat jashanquedrriot iduulig. Oyat cayaulirg cajrrm-boglig oiiricawiat jayeicawaagjee naa iminrgli caalei bigshayu-jetep.
45011011	Oyat jann jajuijee, cashiidrrijam Dios-shrt wrijin nat israelot jadshanquedrt-shrm jayerog cawaorglig. Yau ishrmjet, ooshrt capecado-shrm jadrmog brrt epinot-dica naa moyerog jet-rnoijeicon cajaawrgjee nat israeliot jayerog cawaorgjeeya oje calijani nat judio ishandiot.
45011012	Oyat jalibrgu calat ijei nat wryu tepinot, jayerog cashanwaorgshrm nat israeliot. Jalibrgu ijei nat brrt epinolat jayerog cashanwaort-shrm nat israelolat, oyatya shri jashiribrgya calat inornjrijei jayerog cashiwaorgprnya shri.
45011013	Ooshrt yapinrg yam judio ishandiot, Dioat acui calica nat judio ishandiot, ooshrm ayaad ijeijet jajaa naa ibeeb Dioat.
45011014	Ojera poi jajeu cajawrgjee nat ajrrot jayerog cawaorgjee oje yalijani, Dioat cajeiconjee ebupaacacrt-shrtya cajet nat irmdrgyawanot.
45011015	Dioat cajeiconu jajet nat wryu tepinot cadjawawug-shrm jashrt nat judioot, bojeyajam cashirii cabatjataibatya. Ooyawi cajuimiglig caebyu-shrt cajugligya oje irriprnotjin juimiirauni-shri morriyu-shrt.
45011016	Jajeiu naa an idoug-jurgprn calrt-umta shrt, jashijeiya poi naa idougprnat japrnot. Jajeiu jatat-shut naa pun, oyatya cashijeinogya poi jalouot.
45011017	Dioat capan jashrt itmrnogot judioot oje jaipandauni jalou pun-shrt, oyat jalirg maligjee jajet dai-imogjet oje jairirshoo boi pun-dou boi pun-jaa, oyatya jamaa jashishrr. Ojeyala poi mam, mashijugyawi jadirg-shrm man jawairiyu, jabigshayu ijei poi naa Pun ijucat.
45011018	Maimacupoishaat majeririg cashrt nat jalouot bŕnwinotjin. Jaimashagu majeirig cashrt jashirirgya japishirnawagjee, mam shandit naa jawaowa naa Pun, ooshrt naa Pun oola mawaowa.
45011019	Jaimashipiniyajam, rcaiji jaquedrcat japandig jashrt itrmnogot jalou bŕnwinotjin aluugshogjee am japrnjinye.
45011020	Rcaiji, Dioat capanat jashrt cajii cashandirt-shrm jajaa, oyat jalirg maligjee jajet majii malirg-shrm jajaa. Ooshrmda jaimacupoishai majeirig, ooshrtya mauom jarea.
45011021	Dioat cashanjeiconu jajet nat japinit jurgotdi, madshishanjeiconya poi jajet-jamo majii mashandirtu jajaa.
45011022	Jamacaluug brjaligu jajeirig naa Dios, oyat jijogjet poi cadjapinrg jajaa naa ieb idrninrg. Iwairüg-jet cadjapinrg caebyu-jaa nat ilrgprnot jashrt. Ooshrt ijeijet madduug mam maligu dai-imogjet jajet. Mashanditu jayerog-jaa madshipanya poi mam jashrt.
45011023	Oyat nat judioot, cajii calirgu-shri jajaa, cadjashirirgya shri japinita caligjee, ooshrt jawairüg naa Dios cadjalirgjeeya shri jaepinota caligjee.
45011024	Madpanu pun iebprnjin-shrt madirr-shogjee Pun ijei-jaa, ojeyala poi cadjalirgjee caliglig shri Pun ijei-jaa nat jalouot bŕnwinotjin.
45011025	Ajrrot, jajeu japishiyawaagjee naa Dioat ijaanprndi yashrt brn. Dumat yashipinrg jajaa jayashag-shrt yajeirig brrt-shrt. Bigrriprnjinda cabigshayu nat itrmnogot israelot ata-on brrt epinolat cajii calircat Dios-jaa brjaligu catog idjajeuot.
45011026	Oyatya cadjashishri jeicon ebupaacacrt-shrtya caebyu-shrm wrijin nat israelot oje jamojani naa Idnagprndi bŕn. Ojeri jamo Isaías, jashiyugya Zion-teat naa Bishishiiwi jadshinamya cashrt caebyu nat Jacob jrdwat.
45011027	Oolawi naa oodamog calat janambatya cashrt capecado.
45011028	Nat judioot cabata jadrg Dios jashrm naa moyerog juju, naa jet-bidjajeicon. Ojeri Dioat jalirglig yashrm yam judio ishandiot jayerog yawaorgjee poi, ooshrt Dioat iágprnota calig cayii jaluugshrm caloomotjin-shrm.
45011029	Dioat jaushanprtrtya bishrt naa idirgprn birat mii-rrijet. Cadjashan-namya poi jashrt nat idjaágprnotdi.
45011030	Yam, Dios yerog shanwaorriotdi bŕn, ooshrt dumat uubiidjet Dioat yaluug jayerog cashanwaort-shrm nat judioolat.
45011031	Ojera poi dumat Dioat yauubiid-duug jayerog cashanwaortshrm, oyat uubiidjeta poi cajashiruu.
45011032	Dioat jalirg japishibiwaagjee jayerog shanwaorriot wrijin, uubiidjet bijaluugjee wrijin.
45011033	Ipegjeta jajei naa Dios, jabigshayu ijei, japishijawaag wrijinshrt. Yau jaiquedrliprn japishiiwaalig boirica jaligu jadminr oje idminrlauni. Yau poi jaiquedrliprn japishiiwaaii naa jet-idrninrg.
45011034	Ooshrm brr-jam jaquedrr japishijawaagjee Biŕri bigshayu. Brrjam jaquedrr jadjuirglig Dios.
45011035	Brr-jam jajuiwnn ijei jalirglig. Biŕriat jadougjee jajet jamiijá.
45011036	Dios licatwin wrijin boirig jaligu, idjaminrgprnota wrijin, janwi wrijin. Ijei biubrg jan oiiricawiat. Amén.
45012001	Ajrrot, uubiidjeta bidjaluug naa Dioat, ooshrmda yapinrg jijogjet yayaubrg jan oje ofrenda ijugni ijeini, jiijáijet yadduugjeeya naa Dioat. Ojera iyaminrgculig yajii-teat.
45012002	Iyacupoiminrt oje calijani nat wryu tepinot, ooshrt yabigshayu yaucambiarg jajuju-jet japishiyawaagjee boirig jaligu Dioat ijeu jayaminrglig ijeijet jet-jayajáirca.
45012003	Dioat jalircat an ijei, ooshrmda yapinrg wrijin yabigyacupoishat yaalei-jaatep jayashag-shrt yajeirig brrt-shrt. Ooshrt yabigyaushat ishalalig-jet oje Dioat jalirlauni yajii yalirg-shrm jajaa.
45012004	Jabag bitaale lou, ooshrt jalibrg calat cabeeb catojani.
45012005	Ojera poi bidu, bibag-cug, ooshrt jatrmwi biriglig Cristo-jet wrijin. Ojera poi bitaale, cabag jalouot ooshrt jatrmwi bitaale.
45012006	Dioat jalirg bitojani naa pishibiwaag jabibeebdig jan oje jadjeujauni. Biratwi jabishiminrg ijeijet jabigshayu-jet idirbrg birat. Dioat jalirgu jaibipindig itrm moyerog idirgprn bijii-tee, biratwi jaibishipin ijeijet japishibiwaagu Dioat jalirgprn.
45012007	Jadirgu cajrrja birigjee brrt, biratwi cajrrja bishirii ijeijet. Naa japishiwaja brrt jajuirglig, janwi cadjashijuir jajii-teat.
45012008	Naa japishiwaja jaijapindig capecado-jaa janwi cadjapinrg ishalaligjet. Naa cayuiot bŕn uubiidot, janwi jadshibr jajii-teat naa idjeu. Naa iglesia ijewe, janwi caijashijeu ijeijet. Naa jajrr perdonarm, janwi jashiperdonar jii-jáijet.
45012009	Cayii yauluug brrt yajii-teat, jaeb yauluug wrijin naa ieb idminrg. Oyat yarn, jijogjet jayaujeu ijei yaminrglig.

45012017	Ieb yacupoiminrg jan naa ieb minrat yan, yauwairüg jayarninrgjee ijei jadduugjee wrijin nat epinolat.

45012020	Oyat jamog shri, mabaalat ebupaajacrtu bui-jet jawoug maubrgya. Jajii jrauya jamaubrg jan jawóca. Jamaminrguya jan ijei jauushigyigya-jamo jashrm naa ieb idminrg man.
45012021	Macupoirirt caebyuat jabatshiwugjee mabigshayu juju, ooshrt caebyu batshimawug jajet naa ijei imaminrg calat.
45013001	Calatwi cajriwairüg yerog cashijui nat epinolat wrijin, loooshrm boiruud ebushijewe Dioat ishandirriprn. Oyat nat yaijewe dumat, Dioat irirgprnota yaicajeujee.
45013002	Naa jabata carm gobiemoot, cabata-cadjarg nat Dioat irirgprnot cajriwairüca. Oyat nat cabat-jart cajriwairügot ebupaacashicrtya jashrm naa idminrg.

46001003	Jabijeu Bií Dioat jalirglig ijei yajii-tee. Jabijeu yadirgjee yabigrririgjee, oopoi Biŕri Jesucristo.
46001004	Ijei abrg yajaa Dioat oiirig jadirgshrni yan ijei jashrm naa Cristo Jesúat iminrg birat.
46001005	Dioat jalircat yatrmwijeeya Cristo-jet, ooshrmda jadirg naa miibag yajii-tee yayaadjee ijeijet, japishiyawaagjee ijeijet poi.
46001006	Ooshrm naa ijei ood-bimog Cristo-jaa, bŕn jadircat yajii-tee japishicawaagjee wrijin ijet jaliglig naa ood-bimog.
46001007	Ooshrm boirig shandit iyajeu, jaligwi yajii-tee naa ijei Dioat irirg jajeiyateishicomju boi wryulauya jashiyuu Biŕri Jesucristo.
46001008	Jadshirirgya yaligjee dai-imogjet jajet on jabeegcaya wryu, brrt yainot shipin-shrtya ieb-jet, yashogbatya iduuca naa Biŕri Jesucristoat.
46001009	Dioat ishiminrgya oje jamojani, oolawi yaája yam jaligjeeya yan ijei jaWá-jet, naa Jesucristo.
46001010	Ajrrot, ishiigjeta yapinr jatam-jaa Biŕri Jesucristo yayaadshrtya boyeja yashrt, jatnnjanijeeya yabigshayu, yayerog poi.
46001011	Ojera amo yan yam ajrrolat, ooshrm nat Cloé jrrot yai capin yai-yamrndig.
46001012	Camog yajaa yayaadyeg boyeja yashrt. Itrmnogot mog Pablo pinda am, itrmnogot mog Apolos pinda am, itrmnogot mog Pedro pinda am, itrmnogot mog Cristo pinda am.
46001013	Jabajijam naa Cristo. Pablo ucabamirijam cruz-jaa yashrm. Bautisao yadrrijam Pablotam-jaa.
46001014	Ijei abrg Dioat bautisao yashanrt-shrm, oowi bautisao irg Crispo, Gayo poi.
46001015	Ooshrm brr shandit jaquedrr jai japindig bautisao yarglig aalei tam-jaa.
46001016	Rcají, bautisao cadjarg Estefanas ot tepinot poi. Jaiashag boiruud itrmu-shri.
46001017	Cristoat ashancui bautisao cadargjee epinot, ooshrt adcui jajuirgjee naa moyerog jet-moijeicono. Cadashanjuirt aalei bigshayujet, jamiirri-shrtya naa Biŕri Jesucristoat iminrg bishrm cruz-jaa.
46001018	Nat biguwiot Dios-shrt jaicashag iigprnjin yeroca jaliglig naa moyerog cruz-jaa, ooshrt naa moyerog cruz-jaa jadirg birat Dios bigshayu iwairüg, bidu idjajeiconprn ieb-shrt bidjashirmogjeeya paraíso-teja.
46001019	Ojera idnaglig brn papera-tee, jashirirgya cabigshayu rmdrgjee nat bicacouot. Jashirirgya japishicawaaglig mii rriya jaliglig cabigshayu nat juituunot mot bigshayu-jet.
46001020	Boirigjam jamii birat jabigshayu naa ebupishiwaja. Boirigjam jamii birat idjuiyu naa ijuirr. Boirigjam jamü naa japishiwaja jayaadig jajaa naa wryu. Dioat jashandirt-tejam japishibiwaaglig iigprnjini jaliglig cabigshayu nat wryu tepinot.
46001021	Naajri Dios japishijawaagwi jajaa naa idminrg, ooshrmda jadshandirri japishicawaaglig Dios-jaa cabigshayu-jet nat wryu tepinot, Ooshrt jajet naa moyerog jaa-camog iigprnjin yerog, Dioat jajeu cadjajeicondig nat jawaort, ebupaacacrt-shrtya capecado-shrm canogjee paraíso-teja.
46001022	Nat judioot jadjeu jadduuglig jabirninrglig brrt ishanminrri, oyat nat griegoot jadjeu japishicawaaglig wrijin mot bigshayu.
46001023	Ooshrt bidu, ibijuirg jajaa naa Cristo iicabamdi cruz-jaa. Oyat nat judioot caom jadwaorglig naa moyerog cruz-jaa, oyat nat judioota ishandiot jaicashag iigprnjin yeroca jaliglig.
46001024	Ooshrt nat Dioat iágprnot capet nat judioot, brrt epinot poi, jalibrgwi calat Dios wairüyu cajii-tee, jabigshayu poi, jajet naa moyerog ibijuirg Cristo-jaa.
46001025	Oyat naa Dios bigshayu, naa moolat iruug oje iigprnjin bigshayuni, oola ebupishiwaja wrijin mot bigshayu-shrt. Oyat naa Dios wairüyu, naa moolat iruug oje irriyugprnjirn, jawairüg wrijin mot wairüyu-shrt.
46001026	Ajrrot, jayacaluug brjaligu Dioat yaáglicat. Cadjashan-áat ibagjet bicacouot mot bigshayu-jet, rripoi cadjaáglig ibagjet iinodigot iwairügot, iwooligot poi.
46001027	Ooshrt Dioat caág nat moolat iruugot oje bicashancowitni, cadcalirgjee cauuyiglig nat bicacouot. Oyat cadjaág nat idcaluugot oje irriyugotni cauucayiirgjee nat iwairügot.
46001028	Dioat caág nat uubiirot, nat idishanjewit, nat rca-shanbriot nam wryu-tee. Dioat caág nat oiirigot canomat cadjalirgjee nat iyiijet idcaluugot nam wryu-tee.
46001029	Dioat caág oiirigot boiat jaishag-shrt jajeirig Dioat jaluuglig jabicacouyu-shrm.
46001030	Oolawi Dios jalirrm yatrmwijee Jesucristojet jabigshayu ligjee yajii-tee, pecado rriotni bidjaluugligjee, jajetwina birigjee. Jadirg Cristoat bimii-brgjee biújaprtrgjee jaaleat.
46001031	Ooshrm ojeri idnaglig bŕn, naajri jajewe ijei ijapindig jaaleijaatep, jayaulirg ijei ijapindig Biŕri-jaa.
46002001	Ajrrot, brn ayugbadi yalica yajuirgjee jajet naa moyerog rjetwin Dios-jaa, yau yajuirliprn jajet naa moyerog ipaag japishiiwaagjee oje idrjani nat ebupishiwajalat.
46002002	Ooshrt aligbadi yajewalee boirig-jaa shandit jajeu ebu-ajuirglig jashrt naa Jesucristo, naa idminrgprn bishrm cruz-jaa.
46002003	Arriyuglig aligbat yajet brn, aomdi apiipdi.
46002004	Oo-jet yajuirgbadi jashanjeu yabigshayu ajiipdig abigshayu-jet oje bicacouni. Ooshrt yajuirg Espíritu-jet, Dios bigshayu iwairüg-jet poi,
46002005	yabigshayu yalirg-shrt mot bigshayu-jaa ooshrt yabigshayu yaulirg Dios iwairüyu-jaa.
46002006	Oyat nat japishiwajalat naa moyerog idwaorg, jabijuirg cajewalee naa moyerog ipaag-jet japishiiwaagjee. Ooshrt wryu tepinot bigshayu shandit naa ood-bimog, rripoi gobiernoot bigshayu, ooshrm jashiwugya cabigshayu wrijin.
46002007	Ooshrt jaibipin epinoíat naa Dioat iijaandig cashrt brn, naa ijei jaa-Dioat jabigshagli wryu juprduju, naa idjeu jadminrglig birat bidjajeiconjeeya ebupaabicrt-shrtya bipecado-shrm binogjee paraíso-teja.
46002008	Nat wryu jriwairügot, boiruuda itrm capei japishiwaja jajaanaa Dioat ijeu jadminrglig. Japishicacawaagu jajaa jaicashancugbam-om cruz-jaa naa Biŕri shrnoatwin.
46002009	Ojeri idnaglig brn, mobicat ishanduudiju, rripoiju mobutocat ijuiriprn, rripoi jaluuglig mobigshayu-tee naa ijei Dioat iminrg calat nat jayii-rujulat.
46002010	Oola naa ijei Dioat oodmoglig calat, dumat jadirg japishibiwaagjee jajaa Espíritu-jet, ooshrm naa Espíritu jadduugwi wrijin, japishijawaagwi wrijin jaa-Dioat jabigshag jajii-tee.
46002011	Nat mot, yau itrm bonat japishiiwaaliprn itrm bon bigshayu jaa-jabigjashag jajii-tee, oowi pishicawaag caalei bigshayu catojani. Brr-shandit japishiwaja bijaligu Dios bigshayu lig, oowi Dios Espí ritu japishiwaja.
46002012	Bidu Dioat jashandirt bibigshayu calijani nat wryu tepinot, ooshrt jadircat birat naa Espíritu, naa Dios licatwin, japishibiwaagjee brjaliyu jaligu wrijin naa ijei Dioat irirbrg birat.
46002013	Oyat yabipinrg jajaa naa moyerog ijei oje Dios Espírituat bijuirlauni. Molat bishanjuirt jajaa naa ood-bimog. Oyat cadbijuirg nat ood-jalibrgot naa Espíritu jajet naa moyerog Espírituat irirg birat.
46002014	Naajri ood-boiruud Espíritu, yau jadquedrliprn japishijawaaglig jajaa naa Dios Espírituat irirg bijii-tee, ooshrm jaijashag iigprnjin bigshayuja jaliglig. Yau japishijawaaliprn brjaliyu jaligu Dios yerog, ooshrm jatrmwi Espíritu jalirrm japishiiwaaglig.
46002015	Naa ood Espíritu lig jajii-tee, jadquedrg japishijawaaglig brja- liyu jaligu Dios yerog. Ooshrt brr-shandit japishiwaja brjaligu jabigshayu lig naa ood-Espíritu lig.
46002016	Ojeri idnaglig bŕn, brr-jam pishiwaja brjaligu Biŕri bigshayu. Brr-jam jadquedrr Dios jajuirglig. Brr-shandit jaquedrr, ooshrt jalibrgwi birat Cristo bigshayu.
46003001	Ajrrot yau jaquedrliprn yajuirglig oje cadajuirlauni nat Espíritu yerog juiyut, ooshrt yajuirt oje cadajuirlauni nat iminrt oje cabigshayu bŕnwinjinat jalirlauni, nat jujet irigot Cristo-jet.
46003002	Bŕn yajuirglig jajet naa ishanpaji jaiwaorglig, oje jirnigpog jashrrlauni taacrlat, Yau jadquedrliprn jataa cawouglig. Ojera poi yam bŕn jayashan-waordiju naa ipaag japishiwaaglig, oyat dumat poi jayashag jayashanpoi-quedrtju jayawaorglig.
46003003	Ooshrmda iyaminrgju oje yabigshayu pegjinat jalirlauni, yaeb yaluuyeg, yayamrnju, yabigshayu yauyeg yashrt, ooshrmda japishibiwaagwi yajuliglig yabigshayu bŕnwinjin-jaa calijani nat wryu tepinot wrijin.
46003004	Itrm yapei imogu Pablo pinda am, oyat boi mog Apolos pinda am, idrninrg calijani nat wryu tepinot irigot mot bigshayu-jaa.
46003005	Brr-irigjam naa Pablo. Brr-irigjam naa Apolos. Oodawi yajuirt yajii yalirgjee Birri-jaa, oowi ibijuirg naa Biŕriat irirg jabijuirglig.
46003006	Am jarrnat naa mojrmca, oola Dios yerog, oyat Apoloat jatat trurg rt-jet, oola Espíritu Santo. Ooshrt oolawi Dios jalirr jarnindig yajii-tee naa mojrmca ijei.
46003007	Boirica shandit naa jajrmrr, oje-poi paa jatat trurr Rt-jet, oolawi ijei naa Dios jalirr jaminjee.
46003008	Itrmjanirawi jalii naa ijrmr jajet naa Rt nama jajaa, oyat Dioya camii shibrm jamiija naa idbeeb jan.
46003009	Ibeebeda bidu Dios-jet. Yamdawi Dios jrmcaat, yamdawi ojeirigot itrm mooni Dioat iminrgprn.
46003010	Jajuiawrg naa iglesia oje carpinteroat jaminriauni mo liiriprn simento-jet. Dioat jalirg jajuiawrglig jaiglesia, oyat brrlat ibeeb aprna, ooshrm calatwi jadshiruu cashrt jadebrg-shrt naa iglesia,
46003011	ooshrm brr-shandit jaquedrrm jadirglig itrm iglesia liiriprn jashrt naa Dioat irirgprn bŕn. Oola Cristo naa Iglesia liiriprn.
46003012	Dumat nat itrmnogot jamii-rigwi naa idminrg Cristoat oje oroni, palatani poi, jaa ibrtni poi. Oyat nat itrmnogot jamii-rri naa idminrg oje puni, shooni poi, oje poi shonyoni.
46003013	Japishibishiwaagya brjaligu idrg nat epinolat catojani jayugbatya Jesús cainot shijapinjeeya. Jashiyugya oje drmi, oyat naa drr jadshirirgya japishibiwaagjee boje-jaliguli idr catojani, o ishanbeji jaligu naa idminrg o ibeeg jaligu.
46003014	Ishanbeji jaligu naa idminrg Cristo tam-jaa, Dioya jamii-shibrm.
46003015	Ooshrt ibeeg jaligu naa idminrg Cristo tam-jaa, yauya Dioat jamii shibrrliprn. Ooshrt cadjashiougyawi ieb-shrt oje epin ioulauni drr-shrt.
46003016	Japishiyashanwaat-tejam Dios ota yaliglig. Japishiyashan waat-tejam Dios Espíritu liglig yajii-tee.
46003017	Itrmat jaeb-rgu Dios ot, Dioya jashirirr jarmdrglig, ooshrm Dios pina jalig naa ja-ot. Yamdawi naa Dios ot.
46003018	Yateeyacupoi-shauryet yaaleat, naajri jaishamat ebupishijawaaglig jaalei bigshayu-jet, janwi jadshinamnog jashrt jajuijawrgjee jajajuirglig oje trriwaini jatairirgjee Dios bigshayu rjetwin.
46003019	Oje iigprnjin bigshayuni Dioat jaluugrg cabigshayu nat wryu tepinot. Ojeri idnaglig brn, Dioat jashirirgya ebupaacacrdig cabigshayu-shrm nat bicacouot oje molrrlauni jaalot-teja.
46003020	Oyat idshinag shri, Birri japishiwaagwi mii-rriprnjina jaliglig cabigshayu nat bicacouot.
46003021	Ooshrmda brr-shandit jaquedrr jai jashaglig jajeirig brrt-shrt jajajuirg-shrm bicacou-jet, ooshrm yapina jalig naa Dioat irirg calat wrijin.
46003022	Yapinda poi naa Pablo pin, Apolos pin poi, Pedro pin poi, naa wryu pin poi, mojuuyu poi, morriyu poi, shiruu wryu poi, wrijin wryu ishiyugya poi, yapina jaligligjeeya wrijin.
46003023	Oyat Cristo pinita yalig, oyat Dios pina jalig Cristo.
46004001	Ojerawi bipishiyawaacurg, oodawi bidu ibeebet Cristoat. Jalirg jabijuirgjee naa moyerog pishicashanwaji Dios-jaa.
46004002	Ooshrm nat iglesia ijewet calatwi caepinot icashijeu ijeijet cargcabrgjee.
46004003	Ooshrt boirica shandit an naa ood-yamog ajaa, nat-poi brrt wryu tepinot. Rri-poi ainot shiapindig aalei-jaa.
46004004	Yau japishiawaaliprn ieb ajaa, ooshrt jashanquedrt jai-ashaglig ajeiríg Dioat imugjet jashrm naa iminrg. Oowi Birri japishiwaja ajaa.
46004005	Ooshrmda boi imacupoiprn Birri yug juprdu. Oolawi bishitadrrya wrijin idjaanjet bibig-shrt. Jadshirirgya japishibiwaagjee boirigshrm jaligu jadminrg oje jadminrlauni. Oyat Dioya ijei ishipini calat nat ibeeberat jan wrijin catojani.
46004006	Ajrrot, ojera amo ajaa, Apolos-jaa poi, japishiyawaagjeeya yaliglig ijeijet oje birijani jajaa naa ibinag, ijeijet jayaluug-shrt itrm ijuirr itrm-shrt.
46004007	Brr-jam jalirrm majeirig brrt-shrt. Boirigjam iriibrg man Dioat ishandirbriprn man. Dioat jalibrgu man mabigshayu, boirigshrmjam jaimashaa jamatairirglig maalei wairüyu-jet.
46004008	Jaiyashag japishiyawaagligwi wrijin, jaiyashag jaligwirig yan wrijin iyajeu. Jaiyashag iinodigota yaliglig birshrt. Boirica shandit yan bidu. Jajeu iinodigota yaliglig rjet bijrrja bidyargjee epinot iyajeujee.
46004009	Jaiashag Dioat birirglig uubiidjet wrijin-shrt bidu idjacuiprnot. Bidjalirg oje presootni idcarrirg-yawanotni. Jadirg bidcaluugjee ebupaabicrdig wrijin nat wryu tepinot, ángeleot poi, epinot poi.
46004010	Cristo-shrmda jaicashaa wryu pishibiwaaca shandit. Oyat yarn jayashag ebupishiwajata yaliglig Cristo tam-jaa. Bidujri irriyugot, ooshrt yam jayajeu iwairügota yadduuglig. Mii-rriprnjinjet bidcaluug ooshrt yarcabrg yam.
46004011	Dumatju bui paabicrt, bijii jrro, boiruud bilapwoo, bidcapai, boiruud biriiriprn.
46004012	Tbibeeb bilap-jet biwoug shibibeebjee. Cayaad iebjet bijaa nat epinot ooshrt cadbibenisiarg. Cabata bidcarg ooshrt jricabicou naa paabicrt.
46004013	Ebuteecashaurg bijaa ooshrt cadbijuirg yrnijetwi ishan-nnnijet. Nat wryu tepinot bidcaluug oje woohyrrni, bidcanam cashrt oje ishijaanprnjin inarndauni.
46004014	Ishan-naabrt yan yauuyigjee, ooshrt jajeu japishiyawaagjee ijeijet ooshrm atnijulot yalig, idajeuprnota yam.
46004015	Caliibrgwi yan ibagjet nat ebujuirt Cristo-jaa yajewalee, ooshrt cashanbaat yaíijit Cristo-jaa. Yaira am Jesucristo-jaa jajet naa moyerog jet-moijeicon,
46004016	ooshrm yapinrg iyauminrg oje naa injani.
46004017	Dumat jashicui yalica naa Timoteo, oolawi atrri ijeuprn Biŕrijaa, naa irig dai imogjet Biŕri-jet. Jadshirirgya jayeyawaagjee shri brjaligu aliglig Cristo yerog-jaa. Jadshirirgya japishiyawaagjee brjaligu ebu-ajuirglig wrijin iglesia-tee moyan tojani.
46004018	Itrmnogot yapet jaicashag ebupishicawaaglig bishrt, jaicashag ayuca shishandi-shri yalica.
46004019	Jaiashag ooshrt mogwainia ishiyuu yalica Dioat jajeuu. Oyat jashiruugya brjaligu idrg Dios bigshayujet nat jaishaialot ebupishicawaaglig bishrt. Boirica shandit an naa ood-camog cayee-jet.
46004020	Brr-shandit iruug Dioat cajuiberliprn-teja shrnoja jajet naa moyerog ood-jamog jayee-jetep, jajii-teatwin jashandidu. Ooshrt cashiruugya Dioat cajuiberliprn-teja jabigshayu iwairügjet cajiitee.
46004021	Boirigjam iyajeu. Jayajewijam ayuglig monrmyu-jet o jayajeu yaluuyuglig ijeijet oje yii-aluugotni.
46005001	Bŕn jainot ajui itrm yapei, ieb jaminrg boyequejetep jataalejet. Ieb jaminrg ibajaligjet cashrt nat Dios pishishanwaji. Boirauda itrm capei irig jaíi u-jet.
46005002	Oyat yam, yaiyashag yajeirig brrtshrt. Boirigshrmjam yajii shanshrmi. Oyat dumat yanwi jayashiwaowu yashrt naa ieb-minrr ipegjet.
46005003	Dumat ashishandi yajewalee ataale-jet, ooshrt yayeashiwaag ajiiteat. Ooshrmda yapinrg ojewi alirauni yajet, yapinrg brjaligu yashirg jan na t ieb-minrat.
46005004	Yajuiyauberg jatam-jaa Biŕri Jesucristo, oyat am ashirigya yajet abigshayu-jet, oyat Biŕri Jesucristo iwairiiyu yajii-tee.
46005005	Oyat yanwi jaúuyashiprdr moweijinat naa bon, jataale nndrgjee, ooshrt jajuuyujin jeijeeya ebupaajacrt-shrtya jayugbatya Biŕri Jesús.
46005006	Yam, yau jayaquedrliprn yaiyashaglig yajeirig jayalirgu jaliglig yajewalee naa oirigprnjin. Japishiyashanwaat-tejam ishrmwi ieb oje levadurani jadshieb-rgya wrijin.
46005007	Ooshrmda jayauwawu yashrt naa levadura bŕnwinjin yadebrgshrt jajujuja yaligjeeya oje pan Ievadura-rrini idwoug pascua-tee. Ooshrm bŕn jarn bishrm bicordero Cristo jawugjee bishrt naa biebyu jalirr birmdrglig.
46005008	Ooshrmda biratwi biyeeshiwai jajaa naa biCordero Cristo bigshayu ijei jriat, rjet jriat, oje pan ishiigni. Rri jabiwouglig bicostumbre bŕnwin jriat.
46005009	Bŕn papera anaabrgli yan cajnja yalig-shrt nat ieb-minrt cataalejet.
46005010	Oo ashan-moot cajaa nat Dios yerog shanwaorriot iebminrt boyequejetep, inaiot poi, ishegot poi, idolo-jet cairmrot poi. Ooshrm jayajeuu yaliglig yaujet cashrt nat oiirigot, yanwi yashinoo wryu-shrt.
46005011	Ooshrt inaabrg yan yajrrja cadyarg-shrt nat iglesia atwinot iebminrt cataale-jet, inaiot poi cairmrot idolo-jet poi, yowan-ebot poi, iwónot poi, ishegot poi. Yayeecupoiwai cajet nat iminrt-shri oje.
46005012	Cainot shibishanpin nat iglesia atwinota ishandiot, ooshrt caibishipin nat bijrroh
46005013	Ooshrm Dioya cai-shipini nat irigot jaiglesiashrt. Oyat dumat jayauwawug yashrt naa iebprnjin.
46006001	Ieb jaminrgu yan naa yajrrat, boirigshrmjam jai-yapin calat nat iwairiigot jashanwaorriot naa moyerog ibiwaorg. Boirigshrmjam jai yashanpini calat nat Dios epinolat.
46006002	Japishiyashanjuwaat-tejam Dios jetwinolat cainot shipindigya nat wryu tepinot wrijin. Japishiyawaaguya cajaa nat wiyu tepinot, jayashanquedrt-tejam capecado iyapindig nat yajrrot.
46006003	Japishiyashanjuwaat-tejam ángeleot-jaa pishibiwaagya. Capishibiwaagu-om ángeleot-jaa, epinot-jaa pishibicugpoiwag-om nam wryu-tee.
46006004	Jayajeuu boi iyapindig, boirigshrmjam cai-yapin calat nat bijrrja ishandiot iglesia-tee.
46006005	Ojera amo yan yauu-ayiirgjee. Itrrn bon yapeat jashanquedrttejam jai-japindig capecado nat yajrrot.
46006006	Boirigshrmjam cajrrot ii-capin nat iwairügot Dios yerog shanwaorriolat.
46006007	Yarn jajewet yaiyarnrndig yajrrot-jet, jayashirirgya yapishibishiwaagjee jayashanquedetju Dios yerog yawaorglig. Boirig-shrmjam on yashandi ieb caminrgbat yan. Boirig-shrmjam jayashandirri jadouglig yashrt yalapwoo moteeshauyu-jet jadjeuu.
46006008	Ooshrt yam, ieb yaminryeg yan, cateeyashaurg yajrrot calapwoo yaougjee cashrt.
46006009	Japishiyashanwaat-tejam Dioat cashishandirtya caluuglig cajuijaberliprn-teja shrnoja nat iebnogprnotjin. Yateeyacupoishauiyet yaaleat, Dioat cashishandirtya jaepinota caligjee nat ieb-minrt cataale-jet, rri-poi cairmot idolo-jet, rri-poi iwoojeoot caujut-shrt, rri-poi nat mot ieb-minrt cabon calii-jet.
46006010	Rrr-poi ishegot, rri-poi inaiot, rri-poi iwónot, rri-poi youwanebot boyequejet, rri-poi ebuteeshaurt boi-pin caougjee, Dioat cashishandirtya jaepinota caligjee oiirigot.
46006011	Bŕn ojeri idminrglig itrrnnogot yapet, ooshrt Biŕriat yashrrcat. Yadirg Dios jetwinota yaligjee. Pecado rriotni Dioat yaluugrg Birri Jesucristo tarn-jaa, bijri-Dios Espíritu-jet poi.
46006012	Jaquedrg jarninrglig wrijin boirig jaligu ijeu, ooshrt wrijin yau ijei jaminrliprn an. Jaquedrg jarninrglig wrijin boirig jaligu ijeu, ooshrt jashandirt abigshayu jajiipdig naa iminrcat.
46006013	Biwoug oola binamde yawan, oyatjri binamde oola biwoug liiriprn. Ooshrt Dioya jashirirr jarrndrglig naa biwoug, bitaale poi. Dioat jashandirt bitaale ieb biminrgjee boyequejetep, ooshrt Birri pindawi naa bitaale, oyat naa bitaale jeicono naa Birri.
46006014	Bŕn Dioat jawrryrg Birri wadyeg-teat, oyat bidjashipoiwrryrgya bidu jabigshayu iwairüg-jeh
46006015	Japishiyashanwaat-tejamju Cristo pina naa yataale, ooshrm jayeyiwrnjam-om jaougu Cristo-shrt japin jabrgjee naa den iwoojeuprnjinat. Yau jaiquedrliprn jairninrglig oje.
46006016	Japishiyashanwaat-tejamju, naajri irig iwoojeuprnjin-jet jatrmwi cataale, oje idnaglig bŕn, catrmdawi naa icauot.
46006017	Ooshrt naa ishog Biŕri-jet itrrn Espíritu-jetwi.
46006018	Yaucuut jashrt naa ieb idminrg cataale-jet. Wrijin naa boi pecado idminrg nat epinolat, jadminrg boyaja cataale-shrt. Ooshrt naa ieb-minrr jataale-jet jadébrg jataalewi jaaleat.
46006019	Japishiyashanwaat-tejamju, Espíritu Santo ota jaliglig naa yataale. Jalig yajii-tee naa Espíritu Dioat irirgprn yan, ooshrmda yapin jashandit, yataale ŕriot shandit yam.
46006020	Mii-bagjet Cristoat yámii-brg bŕn, ooshrm ijei yaubrg Dioat yataale-jet yajuuyu-jet poi, ooshrm Dios pina jalig naa yataale yajuuyu poi.
46007001	Dumat yashipinrg jajaa naa iyajeu pishiyawaaglig. Rcaji jajeiwi casaaja cashanditu nat mot jadshanjeuu.
46007002	Ooshrt cabag nat ieb-minrt cataale-jet, ooshrmda cayaulirg moolat caujuta brrt caougjee catajani. Jayaulirg detpat mot-digjee catojani.
46007003	Naa bon, janwi jashirii ijeijet ja-u jet. Oje poi naa den jashirii ijeijet jabon-jet oje jadjeulauni.
46007004	Jabón pina jalig naa ja-u taale, japin-shandit. Oyat ja-u pinda naa jabón taale, japin-shandit.
46007005	Ooshrm jaiwin macupoishoot mabonshrt, jaiwin macupoishoot ma-u shrt. Itrmjani jaligu jayajeulig yayauryeglig yashrt Dios yapinrgjee, omya jashijeiwi. Ooshrt yayacupoiyauryet prnpatjet yashrt, moweijinat yateeshaurg-shrt ieb yaminrgjee.
46007006	Ojera jajei yaligu jajajeuu, ooshrt yashancui casaja yaligjee.
46007007	Jajeu yaliglig oje alijani y-rrijet ooshrt Dioat jalirg bibigshayu bitojani, itrmjani shandit.
46007008	Cad-apinrg nat ujut-rriot, nat-poi detpat mot-rriot jajeiwi cal gu itrmjetwi oje alijani.
46007009	Ooshrt yau jaligu jadquedrliprn cabigrririglig detpat-shrt, jajeiwi ca-ujuta brrt caougu canai-shrt detpat-jet.
46007010	Cad-ashipinrg nat ujut-digot, am shandit oje imog ooshrt Bírrira imog calat, naajri bon-dig yauya jabon jashinamnoliprn.
46007011	Jabon janamnogu, janwi jashirii itrmjetwi. Rri-shri jabon diglig boi-jet ata-on jabonat jashri-jeiwaowa. Oyat naa uulig yauya jadshiquedrliprn ja-u janamdig.
46007012	Durnat Biŕri yerog shandit naa, ooshrt cad-apinrg nat brrt epinot, yau jaligu Dios yerog jawaorliprn naa bijrr uuat, yauya jadshiquedrliprn jadnamnogrg jadjeuu jaliglig jajet.
46007013	Dios yerog shanwaorri jaligu jabón naa bijawai, yauya jadshinamnoliprn jadjeuu jaliglig jajet.
46007014	Ooshrm naa jabón Dios yerog shanjewe, ja-u pina jalig. Oyat naa den Dios yerog shanjewe, jabón pina jalig. Oo cashancaliiduom catrriot dig oje catrriotni nat Dios shanjewet. Ooshrt durnat Dios pinita calig nat catmot.
46007015	Ooshrt ja-u janamnogu naa Dios yerog shanwaorriat jayaulirg janogjee. Oje poi bijrr, jadnamnogu naa den Dios yerog shanjuiprnjinat jayaulirg janogjee jashrt. Oowi cacawaowuyeg shirig cashrt, ooshrm Dioat biáacat bibigrririgjee.
46007016	Mam bondig, yau japishimawaaliprn mabon bigshayu macambiargu jajeijeeya-cugjin jashrt naa paacashicrtya capecado prta. Mam poi uulig, yau japishimawaaliprn ma-u bigshayu macambiargu jajeijeeya-cugjin ieb-shrt janogjee paraíso-teja.
46007017	Oowi cadyaulirg-culig catojani oje Birriat jaliirlauni, ojewi caliilauni Dioat caágbat. Ojera cad-apinrlig iglesia tojani.
46007018	Naa idconsisargprn jajuprdu Dioat jaáglig, jayaulirt jaligjee ojewi. Oyat nat idshanconsisarriprn jajuprdu Dioat jaáglig, jayacupoirirt jadshiconsisargjee,
46007019	ooshrm boirica shandit jaiminrg naa siconsision, oowi ijei jairninrgu oje Dioat mocuilauni.
46007020	Cadyaulirg caligjee ojewi caliilauniri Dioat caágbat.
46007021	Boi jetwina maliirijam Dioat maágbat maju-cupoinot, ooshrt jamaquedrgu jarnii mabrglig madshiujee, omda jashijeiyawi.
46007022	Naa preso Dioat iágprn jaju jalirgjee Birri-jaa, dumat Birriat ishiuprna jalicat idbeebjee Dioat. Oyat naa presoot ishandi Dioat iagprn,dumatya Cristoat presoja irgprna jashini.
46007023	Cristoat jarnii-brg mii-bagjet, ooshrmda jayacupoirirri presoja yadrglig nat moolat.
46007024	Ooshrm ajrrot, yaulig ojewi yaliirauniri Dioat yaágbat yatojani, ojerawi yaliculig Dios-jet.
46007025	Yau Birriat apinrliprn cajaa nat casaaja ishandiot, ooshrt yapinrg abigshayu-jetep. Jayaquedrg jayaujuibrgu an jashrm naa ijei Birriat irirbrgprn ajii-tee.
46007026	Jasniebya iyug birica ooshrmda amog jajeiwi yaligu oje dumatju.
46007027	Ma-u liijam, jamacupoijeu jamanarnnoglig. Ma-u rrijam, jamacupoijeu ma-u ligjee.
46007028	Ooshrt pecado mashishanminrtya ma-uuja boimaougu, rriya poi japecado jaminrglig jabon-digu naa den. Ooshrt yau jadquedrliprn cabigrririglig nat casaaja irigot, ooshrmda yapinrg yajii shŕmshrtya.
46007029	Yapinrg yam ajrrot boiruuda wryu ibag birat ibibeebjee Dioat, ooshrmda jayaulirg cabigcashagjee oje ujut-rnotni nat ujut-digot.
46007030	Jayaulirg cabigcashagjee oje ishanquiiotni nat jii-shŕmot. Jayauliig cabigcashagjee oje iishanyoiyitni nat iyoiot. Jayaulirg cabigcashagjee oje japwoo rriotni nat wooligot.
46007031	Jayaulirg cabigcashagjee oje ishanbeebitni nat ibeebet wryutee, ooshrm jashiwugya bishrt naa wryu.
46007032	Jajeu yabigrririgjee. Naajri u-rri oowi iyeijawaag naa Birri beeb. Jadjeu Birri jajáirglig.
46007033	Ooshrt naa uulig, oowi iyejawaag naa wryu tepin. Jadjeu ja-u jajáirglig.
46007034	Ojera poi nat detpat, naajri bon-rri jayejawaag naa Birri beeb. Jadjeu jajetwina jaligjee wrijin jawairiiyu-jet wrijin jabigshayu-jet poi. Ooshrt naa bon-dig jayejawaag naa wryu tepin, jadjeu jabón jajáirglig.
46007035	Ojera amo yan yaligjee ijeijet. Jashanjeu yabigshayu ajiipdig, ooshrt jajeu ijei yaminrglig, yajrrja jayargjee Biŕri wrijin yajii-teat, naa wryuat yaipejocu Birri-shrt.
46007036	Naa bon jadjeuu jabón diglig naa jalou dena jalig-shrm ibag wiig, jayaulirgya idrninrglig oje jadjeulauni. Jabón digujri jaebyu jashishanminrtya.
46007037	Ooshrt naa itrm bon japishijawaagu jajii-teat jadshanjeuh jabón diglig jalou, omda jadshijeiwao jalou oje yrgrrishan-ebini jadjeuu.
46007038	Ijei jashiminrgya naa bonat jaíirr casaaja jaligjee naa jalou. Oyat naa bon jashandirri, ijei jaminrglig jashrt.
46007039	Naajri bondig jashirigya jabon-jet jajujugbat, ooshrt jarrirau jashrt jadquedrg casaaja jaligu-shri bijaiigu idjeu capet nat Cristo epinot.
46007040	Ooshrt jaiashag jajii shijáiyajaligu itrmjetwi. Ojera yapinrglig amat, ooshrt jaiashaat Dios Espírituat jalirglig yapinrglig oje.
46008001	Dumat yashipinrg jajaa naa jrrlug taa idwoug idoloot-jaa. Japishibiwaagwi jaliibrgwi birat bibigshayu bitojani. Ebupishibiwaagu ijeijet brrt-shrt, bijai-bishishagya bijerig-jamo brrt-shrt. Cayii biruugu brrt, Dios bigshayu shiminya bijii-tee.
46008002	Naa jaishaam ebupishijawaaglig brrt-shrt jadshirirgya japishibiwaagjee jajaa boirig-shandit pishyawaag ijeijet oje jaijeulauni.
46008003	Ooshrt naa jayiiruju Dios, oolawi Dioat pishiwaagprn.
46008004	Dumat yashipinrg jajaa naa jrrlug taa idrrirgprn idoloat. Capíshibiwaagwi boirica shandit nat idoloot wryu-tee. Japishibiwaagwi boiruud-dig itrm Dios jashrt naa itrmwi Dios.
46008005	Jaica shag jabaglig cajri-dioot shrnoja nam poi wryu-tee, ooshrm cabag cajri-dioot idcaminrgprnot calap-jet caŕriot poi.
46008006	Ooshrt bidu, jatrmdawi bijri-Dios, oowi Bií shrnoja irig. Oolawi jaíirr wrijin boirig jaligu jaaleatwi. Oyat jatrmdawi naa Biŕri, oowi Jesucristo iminrr wrijin. Oolawi jaíirr bijuglig wrijin.
46008007	Ooshrt itnnnogot yauju japishicawaaliprn jajaa naa ood-bimog. Bŕn ijei iicapin idoloat, ooshrm jadjuwoug naa idrrirgprn idoloolat ojewi cabicashaalauni bŕn. Cacostumbre cabigshayu jaeb-rg ooshrnida carriyug Dios yerog cawaorglig.
46008008	Bishanjeira Dioat biruuglig biwoug-shrm. Bishanjei jabiwougu, bishanpoi-jei jabishanwoutu.
46008009	Ooshrt jayauluug yashrt brjashirii naa iyaminrcat jalig-shrt caebyu caminrglig nat irriyugolat Dios yerog cawaorglig.
46008010	Naajri irriyugprnjin Dios yerog jawaorglig, jadduugu mateglig mesa-coo idoloot ot-tee mam ebupishiwaja ijeijet, jayeshishanwaitewrnjam idoloat jaijashag-shrm imaminrglig oje mateg-shrm jajan.
46008011	Oyatyajri jashrm naa imaminrg jashirmdrgya Dios-shrt naa majrr irriyugprnjin naa-shrm Cristo rriri.
46008012	Cabigshayu maeb-rgu nat irriyugot Dios yerog cawaorglig, ieb maminrg jan naa Cristoat.
46008013	Jalirgu jaebyu jaminrglig naa ajrrat jashrm naa iwoug, jajeiwi jashanwoutu jalirg-shrtya ajrrat ieb minrglig.
46009001	Cristoat icuiprn shandit-tejam am, idshiuprn shandit-tejam am. Jashanduut-tejam Biŕri Jesús. Yam shandit-tejam id-arrnogot Cristo-lica.
46009002	Brrlat apishishanwaatu Cristoat icuiprna aliglig, yamdawi japishiwajat, ooshrmda yajii jalircat Biŕri-jaa jashrm naa ibeeb yajewalee.
46009003	Ojera amo calat nat jájewet ai-caeb pindig.
46009004	Jashanjei-tejam jabishan-woutu jabiwógu poi naa idirg birat.
46009005	Jabishanquedrt-tejam bi-u birrnogu bijet oje calijani nat brrt Biŕriat icuiprnot, japedwat poi, Pedro poi.
46009006	Oo-tejamwi Bernabé, am poi, ibibeebdig oiirig biwoug shibibeebjee jabijuirgjee naa moyerog juju.
46009007	Boi irujijam itrm sodawa jawoug shibeepe jayuiot poi janogjee moprtooyu-teja. Mojrmca jashanwout-tejam naa ijrmrat. Vaca jimigpog jashanwóot-tejam naa vacaot ijeweat.
46009008	Jayacupoishaat bon bigshayuja jaliglig naa ood-amog, ojeri poi Moiséat inaglig japapera-uu bŕn.
46009009	Jamog, jayee shimacupoijiip naa mojiu mojrmca jabeebat. Dios mogbat oje cayejawajijam nat mojiwit mot-shrt.
46009010	Bishrm shandit-tejam oje jamo Dios, Rcaji bishrmdi jadir jadnagjee naa comparación, jajeijateijee jacabot jaouglig naa ijrmrat, oje poi naa ibeepe.
46009011	Jabicajrmu iyajewalee naa jet-yabigshayu yajeicon, jashanjei-tejam biwouca boi-biougu yashrt jet-bitaale bijeicon.
46009012	Cawouca boi-caougu yashrt nat brrlat idjuiryu miijajabajalig bimii yarrirlig yabijuirg mii. Ooshrt bidu, jamii bishanjeu naa ibijuirg, jajuibipejog-shrt yashrt naa moyerog ijei Cristo-jaa.
46009013	Japishiwashanwaat-téjam nat ibeebet templo-tee, cawoug catairirg templo-tee, otpoi oyem nat mojiu rrirt Dios-jaa.
46009014	Ojera poi durnat Biŕriat jalirg cawouca boi-caouglig cataale yawana nat jajuirt naa moyerog jet-moijeicon, jajet naa idbeebrg jan.
46009015	Ooshrt jamii ashanjeu naa ijuirg, rri-poi janaglig naa papera alapwoo armjee. Ooshrt jajeiwi arriu boi-ashanquedrtu jaminrglig ajii-teat naa iminrg.
46009016	Yau jaquedrliprn ainot shiapindig ijeijet jajuirg-shrm naa moyerog jet-moijeicon, ooshrm anwi jashijuir. Auucugbiid-om jashanjuirtu naa moyerog ijei.
46009017	Jajuirgu naa moyerog ajii-teat, jashiribrgya an jarnii naa abeeb. Ooshrt jajuirgu adcui-shrmtep jijogjet, jashimrnya jaliglig ajaa naa mobeeb Dioat irirg jaminrglig.
46009018	Oyat boirigjam jalirr ajii-jáirig, am jarnii shan-oui yajet naa abeeb. Adjáirg naa iminrcat, jajuirg naa moyerog jet-moijeicon mii-rrijet. Yau jarnü aouliprn naa abeeb am ijuirr.
46009019	Yau moolat jaquedrliprn presoja adrglig cad-ajuirgjee, ooshrt aju-teat jalirg ibeebjee cajewalee, ganando cad-argjee Cristoat bijaligu catogwi.
46009020	Ayaadbat cajet nat judioot, ayaad oje calijani nat irigot Moisés yerog-jaa. Yau Moisés yerocat abigshayu jiipdiprn, ooshrt iminrg oje calijani ganando cad-argjee Cristoat.
46009021	Yau janamdiprn ashrt naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn Moiséat, ooshrt dumat alig Cristo yerog-jaa. Ooshrm ayaadbat cajet nat ishandiot Moisés yerog-jaa, ayaa oje cayaadauni ganando cad-argjee Cristoat.
46009022	Ayaadbat cajet nat irriyugot Dios yerog cawaorglig, ayaad oje irriyugni ganando cad-argjee Cristoat. Jalirg epinolat aluugjee itrmjaniwi cajet cajeijeeya oiiricawiat brjaligu catog nat ganando idargot.
46009023	Jaminrg wrijin naa iminrg jashrm naa moyerog jet-moijeicon, ajii-jai jajet naa ijei idminrg yan.
46009024	Japishiyashanwaat-tejam jadminrgbat camaanyu, caman wrijin jaicabeebjee itrm premio, oyat jatrmwi jaoum naa premio. Ojera poi yarn, yaunog jijogjet moweijin ubata oje jijogjet imaani jayaougjeeya naa ijei Dioat ijeu jadirglig yan.
46009025	Wrijin nat imaanot, cataale cajeicon ijeijet. Yau jadminrliprn naa cataale rriyunn jadougjeeya itrm premio ibeeg-yawan. Ooshrt bidu ebupaabicrt jabiougjee naa premio ishanbeji.
46009026	Ooshrt arnjri ashan-man oje jalijani naa japishishanwaji brrnjaligu janoo. Jashanminrt moprtoyu ojewitep oje jalijani naa ibrrtog jiim-jet.
46009027	Ooshrt jalirg ataaleat ebupaacrdig, jalirg ataaleat irninrglig oje abigshayu jujuat jalirlauni, brjashirii brrt ajuirg quedyem Dioat awawugu jabeeb-shrt.
46010001	Ajrrot jajeu japishiyawaaglig, brn caligli itrm waojribrru nomat wrijin biroomot israelot. Bŕn jaicabaadi rt ipeg wrijin.
46010002	Bautisao caacarg Moisés-jet wrijin waojribŕru-tee naa carmooli drg-uye, rt ipeg-tee poi.
46010003	Jadwougli wrijin naa mowoug Espírituat irirg-prn calat.
46010004	Jadwógli wrijin naa Rt ijug, naa Rt iyrg Jaa-teat, naa Jaa ijug ibog cajet cajrirú-tee. Oola Cristo naa Jaa ijug ibog cajet.
46010005	Ooshrt yau ijáijet Dioat caluuliprn ibagot capet, oyat carri cadcabrg brg-uu.
46010006	Dioat jalirg cainot pishibiwaagjee jayii biruug-shrt naa ieb oje calijani.
46010007	Ooshrmda yaiyacupoirmi idolo-jet oje calijani itrmnogot. Ojeri idnaglig cajaa bŕn, nat epinot categ mesa-coo cayewaijee cawógjee poi, oyat cajuilnig cawagjee.
46010008	Yau jabiquedrliprn ieb biminrglig bitaale-jet oje calijani trmnogot, ooshrmdi carri venti-tres mil itogot, calrg carri itrm wryuteewi.
46010009	Yau jabiquedrliprn jajii bishŕmrglig Biŕri prnpatjet oje calijani ata-on jadircajin ebupaabicrtjee. Ojeri idrgli bŕn, oyat carriri shrp buán-jet cadjashag-shrm.
46010010	Yau jabiquedrliprn biyaadu ieb-jet Dios-jaa calijani nat itrmnogot bŕn, oyat cadjarrirgli naa ángel jarryuuadi morriyu.
46010011	Dioat jalirg ebupaacacrdig capecado cashriminrg-shrt, oyat jadirg cainotjri canagjee papera-uu ibiminrg-shrt oje calijani, bidu irigot dumat janacaduwiat jabeegligwryu.
46010012	Oyat naa jaishamat jaliglig dai-imogjet, janwi jadshiruu jashrt jalrg-shrt shri japecadoteja.
46010013	Yau naa ebuteeshauryuat yabata yadrrliprn jijogjet cashrt nat brrt wryu tepinot. Ooshrt jayaquedtt yabigshayu yalirglig Dios-jaa oiiricat, ooshrm jadshanquedrri yapecadoat yanamdig. Ooshrt yabigyashagbat iebjet Dioya jashirirr japishiyawaagjee yacuudig jashrt jajuprduju jayaminrglig naa ieb, ooshrmya jajricayashicou.
46010014	Ooshrm ajrrot id-ajeuprnot, yaucuut cashrt ijei cabrgbat nat idoloolat.
46010015	Yapinrg yam oje cadipinrlauni mot bicacouot, ooshrmda jayauluug brjaligu amog.
46010016	Naajri tasa jet-bijabendisiarg, oola jet-cadbitadrg bitrmwirig bidu wrijin Cristo-jet, jadirg-shrm jamaa taujee cruza-jaa bishrm. Naajri an ibimopigprn, oola jet-cadbitadrg bitrmwirig Cristo-jet bidu, jadirg-shrmdi jataale iicabamdig cruza-jaa bishrm.
46010017	Bibag bidu, ooshrt jatnnwi naa an ibiwoug jabitadrgjee bitrmwirig bidu wrijin, bidulawi Cristo taale.
46010018	Jayacaluug brjaligu idrg nat israelolat, nat cawoot idcarrirgprnot Dios-jaa, jatrmwi cabigshayu wrijin idcarrireprnot-jaa.
46010019	Brjaliyujam naa ood-amog, ijeinogot-tejam nat idoloot. Janomjri jeiyijam cataa brrt mojiwit-shrt nat idcarrirgprnot idoloat.
46010020	Oo jaliyula naa ood-amog, natjri Dios pishishanwajit,ijei cabrg demonioolat, Dioat shandit cajfu carrirgbat. Ooshrmda jashanjewi yajrrja cadyarglig nat demonioot jáirt.
46010021	Yau jayaquedrliprn yawóglig Biŕri tasa-teat iyawógu demonioot tasa-teat. Yau jayaquedrliprn yayewairig Birri mesa-uu iyayewaiu dernonioot mesa-uu.
46010022	Jabishijewijam Dios binrmrglig. Biwairüijam bidu Dios-shrt bibata jabirgjee.
46010023	Rjeta naa ood-camog, jaiquedrg jaiminrglig wrijin, ooshrt yau wrijin ijei jaminrliprn molat naa iiminreat. Jaiquedrg jairninrglig wrijin, ooshrt yau wrijin naa uminrgprnat jaiirliprn Dios bigshayu mindig mojii-tee.
46010024	Yabig-yacupoishaat yaalei-jaa brrt-shrt, ooshrt jayaujeu caligjee poi ijeijet nat brrt.
46010025	Jayaquedrg jayawouglig wrijin naa jrlug taa idwenderg ebucawenderliprn-tee, yau jaligu camooliprn man idcarrirgprnot idoloat.

46010032	Jayacupoiminrt boirig jaligu jalirr calrglig capecado-teja nat brrt, rri-judioot, rri-poi brrt epinot, rri-poi Dios iglesia atwinot.

46011001	lyauminrg oje irjani ooshrm irninrg oje Cristoat iijani.
46011002	Ajrrot, yainot shiapin ijeijet ooshrm ayeyawaag oiirig, iyaminrgwi oje yajuirlauni.
46011003	Ooshrt jajeu japishiyawaagjee cajuiyaga jaliglig Cristo nat mot catojani. Oyat den juiyaga jalig naa jabón, oyat Cristo juiyaga jalig naa Dios.
46011004	Ieb jashiminrg jajuiyagat naa bon jajuiyag jajaanu Dios japinrgbat, Dios yerog shijapinbat poi.

46011013	Yamdawi bipinrt, jajeyijam Dios capinrgu nat detpalat cajuiyag cashanjaanu.
46011014	Bibigshayuat jalirg japishibiwaagjee, yau jabiquedrliprn jargbibrglig naa bon juu-paatnag.

46011016	Itnnat jabigshay lirgu boyaja birshrt, yau jabirirliprn idminrglig boyaja jashrt naa ibijuirg, rripoi Dios iglesia ijeweat jalirglig idminrglig boyaja jashrt naa ibijuirg.
46011017	Yau yainotshi apindiprn ijeijet jajet naa inag durnat, ooshrm yajuibeeriprnat ijei shanminrri yan, ooshrt ieb jaminrg yan.i

46011022	Bojejam yalii. Jayashanquedrt-tejam yayewaiu ya-ot-tee. Jarg yashanbrtejam Dios iglesia. Jayajewijarn cajii yalrnrglig nat ood-boimulot mowoug. Bojeyajam ashimo yan. Ijei iashipinijam yan jashrm naa iyaminrg. Jai-ashanshripin ijei yajaa.
46011023	Naa ood-amog yan dumat, oolawi Biŕriat oodmogprn yan oolau shairei jajuprdu presoja jadrglig. Biŕriat jawao itrm an jalapuu.
46011024	Oyat jadbendisiarg quedyem naa an, jadmopig jamo, oola ataa naa, jashibeegya yashrm. Jayauwoug, jet-ayeyawaacaya.

46011026	Oiirigya jajet naa an, tasaya poi, cadyautadrgya brjaliguli jarririg Yaŕri ata-on jashri-yucaya.

46011028	Ooshrmda jayaulirg cabicashagjee brjaligu calig Dioat iruuca catojani o cajeiu o caebu jajuprdu an cawouglig jadwog juprdu poi tasa-teat Santa Cena-tee.

46012001	Dumat ajrrot, jajeu japishiyawaagjee brjaligu Espíritu Santoat jalirglig jabiminrgjee bibeeb jan bitojani.
46012002	Yamdawi japishiwajat, bŕn Dios yerog yashanju waordi, jayalirg yateecashaurglig jijogjet yanogjee cajet ijei-yabrgjee nat idoloolat ishanyaalit.
46012003	Ooshrmda jajeu japishiyawaagjee, naajri iebjet imog Jesús-jaa, brlau-shandit jayaad Dios Espíntu-jet. Oyat brr-shandit jaquedrr jaijapindig Biŕriya jaliglig Jesús Espíritu Santoat jashandirtu.
46012004	Cabagla nat regaloot Espírituat irirbrgprnot birat mii-rrijet, ooshrt jatrmwi naa Espíritu.

46012008	Dioat jalirg itrmnogot cayaadig oje bicacouni jajet naa Espíritu. Jadpoirirg itrmnogolat japishiwaagjee jayerog shicapindig ijeijet jajet naa Espíritu.
46012009	Jadirg itrmnogolat cajii calirgjee jajaa jijogjet brrt-shrt jajet naa Espíritu. Oyat jadirg itrmnogolat ishiyu canamdig jajet naa Espíritu.
46012010	Jadirg itrmnogolat jaminrglig brrt ishanrninrri, jadirg itrrnnogolat capinrglig brjaliguya jashirig naa wryu. Jadirg itrmnogolat pishiwaaglig o jayaadu itrm Espíritu-jet o demonio yerog-jet. 46012011	Ojera jadirglig idrg jajet naa itrmwi Espíritu, oolawi jalirr cabigshayu catojani oje jadjeulauni.
46012012	Cristola oje irig motaaleni louot-bagni. Wrijin nat motaale Iouot jatrmwi motaaleja caliglig.
46012013	Oyat wrijin bidu, judioot, griegoot poi, presoot poi, presoja ishandiot poi, bautisao bidcarg bitrmwijeeya bidu Espíritu Santojet, oje itrm motaaleni louot-bagni. Bidulawi Cristo taale, ooshrmda jadirg jabiwógjee wrijin naa Rt ijug, naa itrmwi Espíritu.
46012014	Naajri motaale jashan-trmwi jalou, ooshrt jabag jalouot.
46012015	Moshiim mogu, molap shandit am, ooshrm motaale-pin shandit am, yauya jashijaapdiprn motaale-loua jaliglig oo jamog-shrm.
46012016	Molog mogu, mobig shandita am ooshrm motaale-pin shandit am, yauya jashijaapdiprn motaale-loua jaliglig oo jamog-shrm.
46012017	Mobig jacaligutep wrijin motaale brjewrnjam ncugjuirig-om. Moboo-catrm jacatepdigu wrijin motaale, brjewrnjam ebushücugjiglig-om mojrg-jet.
46012018	Ooshrt Dioat jalirg wrijin motaale-lou ojewi jadjeulauni.

46012020	Jabag motaale louot, ooshrt jatrmwi motaale.
46012021	Naajri mobig, yau jadquedrliprn jamogu molapat, abigrririg mashrt. Rripoi mojuiyag jaquedrliprn jamogu moshiimat yau majeuliprn.
46012022	Ooshrt nat bitaale louot irriyugot, yau jaiquedrliprn mobigrririglig cashrt.
46012023	Ooshrt cadijeu nat motaale Iouot iebnogprnotjin, oyat nat motaale Iouot irijaanot, molatwi cadishijeicon ijeijet moyuiot-jet.

46012027	Dumat yamdawi Cristo taale, ooshrm jataale Iouota yalig yatojani.
46012028	Dioat jalirg-jurg idjacuiprnolat cajnja cadcargjee iglesia-tee, oyat cadjalirg jayerog shipinit, oyat cadjalirg nat jaminrt brrt ishanminrri, ishiyu namat poi. Oyat cadjalirg itrmnogolat cajnja cadcargjee, oyat cadjalirg ebushijewet, oyat cadjalirg iyaalot yawapinot yerog-jet.
46012029	Cristoat icuiprnot-tejam wrijin. Japishicawajijam jaicapindig Dios yerog wrijin. Ebujuirt-tejam wrijin. Jadminrrijam brrt ishanminrri wrijin.
46012030	Jadirrijam wrijin epinolat ishiyuu namdig. Cayaalijam wrijin yawapinot yerog-jet. Wrijin japishicawajijam bijaliyu jaligu cayerog.
46012031	Dumat jayaurm Dios-jet, jadirgjee yan jabigshayu jayaminrgjee naa ijei mii-bajalig. Oyatya yashijuirr jajaa naa drg ijei wrijinshrt.
46013001	Ayaaducug cayerog-jet nat mot wrijin, ángeleot yerog-jet .LO poi, yauya jarnii shiriiriprn brrlat yau-jaligu cayii aluuliprn. Ooshrm jaeb ayerog duuglig cabutogye ojetep tambor itairauni jijogjet, ojetete jashitepdi-jamo.
46013002	Jai-acugpinu ijeijet naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprn an, japishiacugwaagu ipag japishiiwaagli, wrijin poi mobigshayu. Abigshayu acalirgu Dios-jaa jijogjet ata-on wen anama, mii-rriprnjintep amjamo yau-jaligu brrt yii-aluuliprn.
46013003	Jacalirgu uubiidolat wrijin alapwoo, jacalirgu atairig Dios-shrm, boirig shandit ioug Dioat-om brrt yii-ashanduutu.
46013004	Naajri brrt yiiruju, ishan-nrmijeta cadjaliiug prnpatjet ieb caminrgbat jan. Naa brrt yiiruju, ijei jaminrg calat wrijin, yau capin-jet janairiprn, yau jaijashaaliprn ebupishijawaaglig cashrt.
46013005	Naajri brrt yiiruju, rri cadjamrndig moyerog jaapibagprnjinjet. Yau jabigjashaaliprn jaalei-jaa brrt-shrt, rri jannndig mogwaini. Yau jadjeuliprn jabata cadjarglig nat ieb-minrt jan.
46013006	Yau jajii jáiriprn cainot jajuibat brrlat ieb minrglig, ooshrt jajiijái brrlat ijei minrgbat.
46013007	Naajri brrt yiiruju, yau jajii shŕmdiprn ieb yugbat jalica, ooshrt jajii jalirg Dios-jaa, jajeijatei Dioat jaminrgjee jan naa idnn jajet ishan-nrmijet jajricajacou wrijin.
46013008	Jabeeg quedyem naa wryu, brrt yü-cashiruugyaju, ooshrt yauya Dios yerog mashishrijuirliprn, yauya cashiyaadiprn yawa-atwinot yerog-jet, boirica shanditya cíuat wrijin naa pishicawaag dumat.
46013009	Dumat jajaamaiyewi naa pishibiwaag, jajaamaiye poi naa moyerog Dioat irirg jabijuirgjee.
46013010	Ooshrt brlau-jaliguya japishibishiwaa wrijin, jashirmdrgya bishrt naa jamai pishibiwaag.
46013011	Trriwaiya ajuligbadi ayaadi oje trriwaini. Bŕn abigshayu lii oje trriwai bigshayuni, bŕn irninrglig oje trriwaiat iminrlauni. Ooshrt bona alicadu janamnogli ashrt trriwai bigshayuni irig.
46013012	Ojera poi bidu, dumat jabiruug Dios ishŕmjetwi oje moiruulauni vidrio-tee o iiweini aijetep. Ooshrt boi wryulauya jabishiruugya bigtanshrg-jet. Dumat jamairawi naa pishiawaag Dios-jaa, ooshrt boi wryulauya japishiashiwaagya oje apishijawaalauni am.
46013013	Dumat biulig jajaa naa ipoi, bijii bishirirg Dios-jaa, jajeibishitei jabiruugjee ijei jajet, brrt yii-bishiruug. Ooshrt inomjri-jei cashrt nat ipoiot. naala oo jayii bishiruug Dios rjet, brrt poi.
46014001	Jayaujeu brrt yii-yaluugjee yajii-teat, oyat Dios yaurm jadirgjee japishiyawaaglig jayaminrgjee itrm mobeeb Espíritujet. Ooshrt jayaujeu jijogjet jaiyapinjee ijeijet naa moyerog Dioat irirg-prn y an.
46014002	Naajri iyaad yawapinot yerog-jet, jayaad Dioat moolat shandit, ooshrm brr-shandit jayerog pishiwaja, ooshrt Espíritula jalirr jaijapindig naa iishanquedrrí japishiíwaaglig.
46014003	Oyat naa jaipini naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn jan, epinot jajuirg Dios bigshayu minjee cajii-tee, capecado canamnogjee cajii-jáijeeya.
46014004	Naajri iyaad yawapinot yerog-jet, jadirg jabigshayu minjee. Ooshrt naa jaipini naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn jan, jadshirirgya cabigshayu minjee nat iglesia atwinot.
46014005	Jajeu yayaadig yawapinot yerog-jet wrijin, ooshrt janomjri-jeu jayajuirglig naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn yan, jabigshayu minjee cajii-tee nat iglesia atwinot. Janomjri-jeira iiminrgu oje, brrt jaishanpinu brjaliyu jaligu naa oodcamog yawapinot yerog-jet.
46014006	Dumat ajrrot, ayugu yalica ayaadjee yan yawapinot yerog-jet, jaquedrriwrnjam-om yajrrja aligjee Dios yerog-jaa yau-jaligu jayajuiriprn naa moyerog jet-ayaad. Yau jalirliprn japishiyawaaglig brjaliyu jaligu naa moyerog rjet, rripoi itrm moyerog Dioat irirg ajii-tee. Yau jaquedrliprn yajuirglig Dios-jaa ayerog yashanjuiu.
46014007	Dumat comparación biuminrg cajaa nat flauta prt, arpatocaart poi. Jashanjuut naa itocarg ooshrt yau-jaligu jatocarliprn ijeijet, jabiquedrrijam japishibiwaaglig brjaliyu jaligu naa canción itocarg.
46014008	Trompeta eaprgu yrrnijet jet-sodaoot caag, calapin cashijeiwaowijam moprtooyu ubata.
46014009	Ojera poi yam, yau-jaligu yayaadiprn cayerog-jet bojeyaja jadquedrg-shirig japishicawaagjee jajaa naa ood-yamog. Oowi yayaadig iiim-teetep.
46014010	Jabagla cayerog nat wryu tepinot. Japishicawaagwi brjaliyu jaligu cayerog catojani.
46014011	Ooshrt yau jaligu japishiawaaliprn brjaliyu jaligu jayerog, yawapinira jaluuglig naa iyaat. Oyat yawaatwinira at-poi ruuglig naa iyaalat.
46014012	Ooshrm jijogjeta jayaujeu jayaminrglig itrm mobeeb Espírituat irirg japishiyawaaglig. Ooshrmda jayaujeu cajrrja yaligjee jijogjet nat iglesia atwinot jawairügjeeya Dios bigshayu mindig cajii-tee.
46014013	Ooshrm naa iyaad yawa-atwinot yerog-jet, janwi Dios jashirrn japishijawaagjee brjaligu jaligu naa ood-jamog calat cadjajuirgjee.
46014014	Dios apinrgu yawa-pinot yerog-jet, jaiashipinya ajii-teat ooshrt yau abigshayu jajeicondiprn naa moyerog pishiashanwajiat.
46014015	Oyat bojeyajam ishirr. Anwi Dios ashipinr ajii-teat, abigshayujet poi. Anwi canción ashicantarg ajii-teat, abigshayu-jet poi.
46014016	Ijei imapinu Dioat yawa-pinot yerog-jet, bojeyawrnjam jadquedrg shirig Dios capinrglig majet cajii-teat japishicashanwaatu bijaliyu jaligu ood-mamog.
46014017	Ijeira naa oraci-on ood-mamog Dioat, ooshrt yau jamaquedrliprn cabigshayu mawrryrglig Dios-jaa, yau jaligu pishicawaaliprn jajaa naa ood-mamog.
46014018	Ijei ibig Dioat japishiawaag-shrm ayaadig yawa-pinot yerogjet ibajalig-jet yashrt wrijin.
46014019	Ooshrt iglesia-tee cad-ajeu brrt epinot ajuirglig, ooshrm jajeiwi jai-apinu sinco-itog moyerog epinot yerog-jet jashrt naa dies mil moyerog yawa-pinot yeróg-jet pishicashanwaji.
46014020	Ajrrot yabig yacupoishaat oje trriwaini. Iyauminrg oje calijani nat japishishanjuwajit ieb caminrglig, ooshrt yabigyaushag oje bon bicacouprni.
46014021	Bŕn Moiséat inagli papera-uu, ashiyaadya epinolat cacooleat nat mot yaalot yawapinot yerog-jet, cacooleat poi nat yawaatwinot. Ooshrt yauya jadshijuiriprn an, ojeri jamo Birri.
46014022	Ooshrmda Dioat jalirg cayaadig yawa-pinot yerog-jet jet-cadjatadrcat jayerog shanwaorriot, Dios yerog waort-shrm shandit. Ooshrt jadjuirgu naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn calat, ijei jashiminrgya calat nat jayerog waorlat, rri jayerog snanwaorriolat.
46014023	Cajuicabergbat wrijin iglesia atwinolat, cacayaadu yawapinot yerog-jet, oyat caluugbat nat japishishanjuwajit:, natpoi Dios yerog shanwaorriot, yaicashanshaat-tejam iigprnotjina yaliglig yayaadbat yawa-pinot yerog-jet.
46014024	Ooshrt jayajuirgu naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn yan yatojani, jaluugbat naa jayerog shanwaorriprnjin, oopoi japishishanjuwaji, cajii shishrmya capecado jayecawaaglig jadjuibat cayerog wrijin brjaligu camog.
46014025	Oyat jadsniruugya bigtanshrg-jet wrijin nat ieb irig cajii-tee iicajaandi epinot-shrt. Oyatya cashishoo cautjuiyag-jet ijei icapinjeeya Dioat, japishicashiwaagya Dios liglig yajet.
46014026	Ajrrot, yajuiyabergbat ojerawi iyaurr. Jayaulirg itrmat cansión juiwrglig, oyat itrmat Dios yerog juirg, oyat itrmat jaipin itrm moyerog Dioat irirgprn jajii-tee. Oyat itrmat jaipin yawa-pinot yerogjet, oyat briat jaipin brjaliyu jaligu naa oodjamog. «Jayaulirg ijei caminrgjee wrijin culto-tee Dios bigshayu minjee cajii-tee wrijin.

47001010	Bŕn Dioat bishiu rrglig-shrt. Oyat dumat bidjashishiuya poi cashrt nat jajewet bidcarrirglig. Oyat bijü birirg jajaa bidjashiujeeya oiirig.

47001012	Bishijáiya ooshrm japishibiwaagwi bijii-teat ijeira naa ibiminrg naa wryu-tee. Rjetwinda bibigshayu birigbadi yajewalee poi. Ijei biminrg oje Dioat jajeulauni, mot bigshayujet shandit. Ooshrt ijei biminrg Dios bigshayujet, naa idirgprn bijii-tee.
47001013	Jajet naa carta ibinaabrg yan, oowi yabipinrglig jajaa naa iyaquedrg jayajuirig, naa pishiyawaag brjaiiyu jaligu. Oyat jajeu japishiyawaaglig inomjri-jeijet.
47001014	Japishiyawaag itrmnogjet jayerog. Oyat jayugbat Aŕri Jesús ijáijetya bidyashiruug. Ojera poi ijaijetya yabiruug-shirig biinotshi japinbatya ijeijet.
