47001016	Jajeu animnoglig yalica anogbatya Macedonia-teja, oyatya jashrijeu animnoglig yalica auuprtbatya Macedonia-teat. Oyatya jayashiquedrgya yajrrja ayarglig anogjee Judea-teja.
47001017	Amogbadi ajii-tee animnogjee yalica, jacauwijan abigshayu. Abig-ashaijarn oje calijani nat wryu tepinot ood-jaliibrgot icau mojerog.
47001018	Dioat japishiwaagwi yateebishanshaurt, icau moyerog shandit naa ood-bimog yan ooshrt ijetwinda naa ood-bimog yan oje Dios mojani.
47001019	Ooshrm jashancauwi jayerog naa Dios Wá jaa-ibijuirg yajewalee naa Silvano, Timoteo poi, am poi. Ooshrt idshiminrgya oje jarnojani.
47001020	Cristoat jaminrg birat wrijin naa Dioat ood-mogli bŕn. Ooshrmda jabiquedrg bimoglig Amén jatam-jaa naa Jesucristo ijei bibrgbat Dioat.
47001021	Oolawi naa Dios jalirr bishoglig dai-imogjet Cristo-jet, bidu yam poi. Oolawi biája japinita birigjee.
47001022	Jadircat bijii-tee naa Espíritu Santo, japishibiwaagjee jalibrg shirigya naa ood-jamog birat.
47001023	Ooshrmda yapinrg Dioat ijuijet, ashan-nodi Corinto-teja oje jajeulauni bŕn, yajii ashanshrm-rtjee. Rjet jashandidu naa oodamog jajeucug arririg.
47001024	Jashanjeu yacuiri jijogjet jayawaorgjee naa moyerog ibiwaor, ooshrm jayaquedrea yajii yalirlicat jajaa daiimogjet. Ooshrt jabijeu yajrrja yabirglig, yajii jáijeeya jayawaorgshrm jijooligjet.
47002001	Ojeri amo ajii-teat, yauya ashishri nimnooliprn yalica ajiishrmbat yayeiawaaglig.
47002002	Yajii ashŕmrgu yam, boirigya jashiquedrr adjáirglig. Oodawi yam jii ashrmrgprnot.
47002003	Ooshrmda carta anaabrg yan oje inaalauni, ajii yashanshŕmrtjee yarndawi ajáirt. Japishiawaagwi ajáiu am, oyat yashipoijáiya wrijin ajet.
47002004	Bŕn carta anaabrgbat yan, ajii-shrm ipegjet ata-on aquica yashrm. Ooshrt carta ashan-naabrg yan yajii ashrmrgjee, ooshrt janaabrg yan japishiyawaagjee yayii aluuglig ipegjet.
47002005	Ajii jashŕm-rgu naa ieb minrrat, ajii jashanshŕm-rgya am itrmwi, ooshrt yajii jashi-poi shrm-rgya yam poi itrmnogot. Ojera amo yan yainotshiapin-shrt jijogjet wrijin.
47002006	Ooshrt jajeitocat jan naa iyalirg ebupaajacrdi naa ieb-minrat.
47002007	Ooshrt dumat jayaujeicon yajet, jayau-jairg jarri-shrt jajii shŕmyujet.
47002008	Ooshrmda yapinrg ajii-teat, jayaulirg japishijawaagjee-shri jayii yaluuglig.
47002009	Ojera poi inaabrglig yan brn, oyatjri dumat jashiruugya brjaliguya jayawaorg-shirig naa ood-amog yan.
47002010	Dumatjri brr-yashijeiconya yajet, am-poi jashijeiconya ajet, yajrrja yadrgjee Jesucristo tam-jaa.
47002011	Moweijinat biebrg-shrt, ooshrm japishibiwaagwi brjaligu epinot teejashaurglig.
47002012	Bŕn ayugbat moyan-teja jatam Troas ajuirgjee naa moyerog ijei Cristo-jaa, jatairirg ibag abeeb Birriat.
47002013	Ooshrt yau abigrririiriprn on ooshrm jashantairirr bijrr Timoteo on, ooshrm aprntarnshi apin auuprtbat cashrt anogjee Macedonia-teja.
47002014	Dumat ijei ashibrg Dioat, naa jalirr moweijin binamdig bishrt wryu shitojani Jesucristo iwairüyu-jet. Oyat jadirg japishicawaagjee bicooleat naa moyerog Cristo-jaa, oje rt-shicoini irig cabigshayu-shijacoirglig brrn-jaligu canoo.
47002015	Ooshrm bidulawi oje ishicoini irigot Cristoat ibrgot Bií Dioat. Naa Cristo bigshayu ishicoini jalig ibirmog idjajeicon yawaolat, naalat poi ishirmdrgotya jashrt.
47002016	Oje rt shicolat carrir-launi epinot, ojera jalii naa moyerog jalirr japishicawaaglig carri-shirigya Dios-shrt nat jayerog shanjuiyit. Oyat oje rt-shicolat jalirlauni cajuglig epinot, ojera poi naa moyerocat jalirglig japishicawaaglig cashijugyawi oiiricawiat nat cajiirirt jajaa. Oyat brr-jarn naa jaquedrr idrninrglig oje.
47002017	Oje bishandit calijani nat ibagot ijuirt yaujet Dios yerog-shrt calapwoo caougjee. Ooshrt jabijuirr jayerog ijet oje jajeulauni jadduugjee naa Dios. Jaibipin jayerog oje Cristoat jalirlauni jaepinolat idjuirlauni.
47003001	Jayashaijam biinot shibipindig-shri yan ijeijet. Jabíjewíjam bijrrolat biinot naglig carta-tee ijeijet calijani nat itrrnnogot. Jabijewijarn biinot yanaglig ijeijet carta-tee jet-bibitadrca brrlat oje calijani nat itrrnnogot.
47003002	Jabishanjeu yajet carta jet-cadbitadrca ooshrm yamwi jet-cadbitadrgot biinot pishicawaagjee jajet naa moyerog ijei ibinag yajiitee, jadleegjee wrijin epinolat, japishicawaagjee ijeiya jaliglig naa ibijuirg.
47003003	Yamdawi nat cartáot Cristoat inagprnot jet-cadbitadrgot. Jadshan-naat tinta-iet, ooshrt jadnag jayerog yajii-tee Dios Espíritu ijugjet. Jadshan-naat tableta-jaa, ooshrt jadnag cajii-tee nat wryu tepinot.
47003004	Japishibiwaagwi Dioat ijei-minrg shirigya birat ooshrm naa Cristoat irninrg birat.
47003005	Jabishanquedrt ijei biminrglig biirei bigshayu-jet, ooshrt Dioat jalirg birat jawairüyu jet-ijei biminrca ojewi jadjeulauni.
47003006	Oolawi Dios jalirr japishibiwaagjee epinot bijuirglig oje jayerog jujuat jalirlauni. Bishanjei jabiwaorg-shrm naa idnaglig bŕn, ooshrt bijei birig-shrm jajaa naa Espírituat irirg bijii-tee. Naa idnagprn bŕnwin cainot shijapin carri shirigya Dios-shrt, ooshrt naa Espíritu cadjalirg cajuglig oiiricawiat.
47003007	Jijogjedi Dioat iyrr Moisés-jaa idnagbat tableta jaacon-jaa naa moyerog jalirr japishicawaaglig carmdrg-shirigya capecado-shrm. Jadshanquedrt jadduuglig Moisés ú nat epinolat jijogjet idyrgshrm ooshrt naa ibrrt jabeeg cashrt.
47003008	Dumat jijoolig-jetya Dioat ishiyrg bijaa jajet naa moyerog Espíritu Santoat irirg birat.
47003009	Dioat iyrgu ijeijet jajet naa moyerog jalirr carmdrgji capecado-shrm, jashinornjri-jeirigya idyrglig bijaa jajet naa moyerog jalirr japishibiwaaglig bibatjatai-shirigya bidjalirgshrm pecado-rriotni biriglig.
47003010	Naa moyerog bŕnwin idyrgli cajaá bŕn, ooshrt dumat idshanyrt bijaa, ooshrm janomjri-jei bŕnwinjin-shrt naa moyerog juju.
47003011	Ijei jacaliguli naa moyerog iwuug cashrt, janomjri-jeirig jashrt naa moyerog ishanbeji.
47003012	Dumat jajeibishitei naa ijei Dioat oodmoglig birat, ooshrm jijogjet jayerog shibipin, yau biomdiprn.
47003013	Ibishanminrt oje Moiséat irjani, jaú shijaweiri juipu-jet, jadshanduutjee nat israelolat jawuuglig jashrt naa ijei, naa ibrrt itrrmdi.
47003014	Ooshrt cajuiyag shaat nat israelot bŕn dumatpatjei. Bigrriprnjinda cabigshayu jaleegbat Dios yerog bŕnwin. Jajulig-shrm caújaa naa jaiweye cashrt Dios, ooshrm jatrmwi Cristo jaquedrr jadnamdig cashrt.
47003015	Dumatju bigrriprnjin cabigshayu jaleegbat Moiséat inagprn.
47003016	Ooshrt boirigbat jaligu boi-tewuu jajii jalirgjee Biŕri-jaa, oolawi janama jashrt naa jaiweye jabigshayu Dios-shrt.
47003017	Bijriwairüg naa Espíritu. Oyat Biŕri Espíritu ligu cajii-tee cadjashishiuya jashrt naa cabigshayu jiipi.
47003018	Dumatjri wrijin bidu, biú bishanjaan Dios-shrt, ooshrt jabirirg Biŕriat iyrglig bijaa oje yamaíat iyrrlauni uuyem újaa, oje poi ibiyrglig brrt-jaa jadduugjee wrijin Biŕri bigshayu. Oyat bidjashicambiargya ijeijet oje jalijani jabiju-yiijeubat. Ojera idrrbr birat naa Biŕri Espírituat.
47004001	Dioat jalirg bibeedig jan biuubiid jaluug-shrm, ooshrmya bishanjaabi bibeebdig Dioat.
47004002	Bŕn jabinamnog bishrt naa ieb ibiminrg ijaanjet. Biteeshanshishau, bishanjuirt iyaujet Dios yerog-shrt. Jabijuirg naa moyerog rjetwin, japishicawaajee ijei biminrglig Dioat iruucat nat epinot wrijin.
47004003	Oolatwi nat ishirmdrgotya Dios-shrt, japishicashanwaat brjaliyu jaligu naa moyerog ibijuirg jet-bidjajeicon.
47004004	Naa wryu jriwairüg iebprnjin, jadirg bigrriprnjina jaliglig cabigshayu nat Dios yerog shanwaorriot, idshanyrtjee cajii-tee naa moyerog ijei Cristo-jaa. Oolawi naa iyrm ijeijet ojewi Jaíini brtbrt irigjet.
47004005	Yabijuirgbat yau biyaadiprn birei-jaatep, ooshrt jabirirg japishiyawaagjee oo jaligjig Caŕri wrijin naa Jesucristo. Bidu, oowi yajnja yabirglig jayii biruug-shrm Jesús.
47004006	Naa Dios jalirrm ebushiwryuat iyrglig ibrru-teja jayerog-jet;, idyrrcat bijii-tee japishibiwaagjee naa ijei Dios-jaa, naa iyrrm jaújet naa Jesucristo.
47004007	Oyat naa ijei jaligwi bijii-tee oje oro mii-bagni dnrauni shoocon iyaunog-tee, japishicawaagjee nat epinolat Dios Iacatwin naa bibigshayu iwairüg, bipin shandit.
47004008	Jadirg ebupaabicrdi brrn-jaligu biboog, ooshrt jadshanquedrt bibigshayu cawon-rglig. Bijii cashrmrg, ooshrt jabishandirt on birigjee.
47004009	Bibata, bidcarg ooshrt yau Dioat binamnoliprn. Bideapai bilrg niti-uja ooshrt yau birririprn.
47004010	Brrn-jaligu biboo bijaawrg birrijee oje Cristoni, japishicawaagjee jajugwi-rig jabigshayu bijii-tee.
47004011	Oiirigla bidcarrirg-shuglig Jesús-shrm, ooshrm jadquedrg japishicawaaglig jajugwirig jabigshayu bitaale irmdrgyawan-tee.
47004012	Ooshrm ojera idbeebdig bijii-tee naa morriyuat, jadjeu bidjawaorglig bidu. Ooshrt yam, Jesús bigshayu ijug idbeeb yajii-tee, ooshrmya yashijugyawi.
47004013	Ibiminrg oje jalijani naa idnagprn papera-tee bŕn. Ojeri idnaglig, ajii-alircat jajaa, ooshrmda jainotshi-apin. Bidu poi, bijii birircat jajaa ooshrmda jainot shibipoipin.
47004014	Japishibiwaagwi bidjawryrg shirigya wadyeg-teat Jesús-jet naa jawrryrrli Birri Jesús. Oyat bidjashirmogya jalica, yamya poi idjashi-rrnogot jabea bijet.
47004015	Wrijin naa paabicrt yabijuirg-shrm, ijei jaminrg yan. Dioat cabendisiargu nat ibagot, oyat cashipoibagya nat ijei brrt jan, cajáijeeya jadduuglig wrijin.
47004016	Ooshrm brlau-shandit bibigshayu biwon-r. Bitaale wairüyu jashibeeg bishrt iyrmijetwi on birriya, ooshrt Dioat bibigshayu icambiarg jajujujet wryu shitojani.
47004017	Mogwainiya jashiwuu bishrt naa paabicrt naa wryu-tee, ooshrt Dioya jashirirr birat ibag ijei ishanbeji, naa inomjrijei wrijin wryu ijáiryu-shrt, ooshrm naa paabicrt yaijet jashrm.
47004018	Yau bibigshayu birirliprn jajaa naa ibiruug nam wryu-tee, ooshrt jayeibiwaag nat ibishanjulujit. Ooshrm cashibeegya nat ibiruugot, ooshrt ishanbejit nat ibishanjulujit.
47005001	Japishibiwaagwi cabeegbatya bitaaleot naa teebirig naa wryutee, Dioya jashirirr bitaale ishanbeji teebishirigya paraisoteja, naa biot juju idshanminrriprn molap-jet.
47005002	Birigbatju bitaale-tee wooja birig jashrm birigjee bitaale shrnojawin-tee.
47005003	Jashirigya bijaa bitaale shrnojawin oje naawa ijeini, yauya bishiriiriprn taale-rrijet.
47005004	Dumat bijulig bitaale-tee oje moliirauni mo bŕnwinjin-tee, bijaap bijii-nog namju. Jabishanjeu jabirüulig bishrt bitaale bŕnwinjin taale rrijet-cugjin, ooshrt jabijeu jabiyuirig bitaale-juju, jatrrnogjeeya bishrt naa bitaale bŕnwinjin, jadcambiargbatya naa bitaalejuju ijug.
47005005	Oolawi Dios bijeicono jalibrgjeeya bitaale ishanbeji. Jadircat birat naa Espíritu Santo japishibiwaagjee jalubrg shirigya birat naa jeibitei jajet.
47005006	Ooshrmda bijii birirg jajaa oiiricawiat. Japishibiwaagwi bijuuligbat naa bitaale-tee, iyaujeda birii jashrt naa biriiriprn ishanbeji, Birri-shrt poi.
47005007	Bijuligbat nam wryutee, bijü birirg jajaa naa iibishanjuluji, yau jajaa naa ibiruug.
47005008	Ooshrt japishibiwaagwi biyrgbatya bitaaleshrt, bishirigya Biŕri-jet, ooshrmda biju-jái binogjee bitaale-shrt.
47005009	Ooshrmda jijogjet jabiujeu Biŕri bijáirglig bijuuligbat bitaale-tee, biyrg quedyemya poi bitaale-shrt.
47005010	Biradyawi bishishoog Cristoat iruuca biinot shijapinjee bitojani, jadirgjeeya jamii naa ibiminrg bijuuligbat bitaale-tee, o ijei nminrgu o ieb biminrgu.
47005011	Bishiom Biŕri rcat ooshrmda jijogjet cadbijuirg nat mot cajii calirgjee jajaa. Dioat bibigshayu pisniwaa oyat jajeu japishiyawaagjee bibigshayu poi.
47005012	Biinot shibishanpin ijeijet bidyaluugjee. Oowi ibijeu biyeiyawaaglig jashrm naa ibijuirr, japishiyawaagjee consejo iyapindig calat ijeijet nat iomolat mot-shrt calapwoo-shrm, ooshrt boirica shandit calat bijaligu cabigshayu lig.
47005013	Japishibishancawaadu wryu, Dios shrmda biicashag japishibishanwagli wryu. Japishibicawaagu wryu, yashrmda japishibiwaa.
47005014	Cristoat biyii-ruüg ooshrmda jijogjet jabijeu ibiminrglig oje jarnojani. Japishibiwaagwi jarririg itrm cashrm wrijin, ooshrm japishibiwaagwi carririg wrijin bŕn.
47005015	Jarri Cristo cashrm wrijin cabigcashag-shrt cajuuyu-jaatep. Ooshrt jayeicawaagjee naa irriprn cashrm, naa juimigprn wadyeg-teat, caligjee jayerog-jaa.
47005016	Dumatya capishibishanwaji nat epinot oje wryu tepinotni. Bŕn japishibiwaag naa Cristo oje bon wryu tepini, ooshrt dumat japishibi-shanwaat oje boni.
47005017	Jajuju epinda naa irig Cristo-jet, jawuucat jashrt jajuuyu bŕnwinjin. Dumat jajujuat jajuuyu wrijin.
47005018	Ojera idr birat wrijin naa Dioat, bidjajeiconat jajet ooshrm naa Jesucristoat irninrg birat. Oyat jadirg cadbijuirglig brrt, cadjajeiconjeeya jajet.
47005019	Dios lig jajii-tee naa Cristo, cadjajeiconjee jajet nat wryu tepinot. Jadshandirt capecado liglig cajaa. Oyat jadirg birat naa moyerog epinot bijuirgjee japishicawaagjee Dioat jajeulig cadjajeiconjee jajet.
47005020	Ooshrm Cristoat icuiprnota bidu. Dioat caág nat epinot bicooleat, ooshrmda jijogjet yabipinrg Cristo tam-jaa, jayaulirg Dioat yajeiconjee jajet.
47005021	Bií Dioat jalirg bipecado jajaa naa pecado-rri, jadirshogjee bijaa jajuuyu ijei, birig-shrm dai-imogjet Cristo-jet.
47006001	Ibibeeb Cristo-jet, ooshrmda yabipinrg jijogjet yabigrncupoirit jashrt naa ijei Dioat irninrg birat.
47006002	Ojera jamo Dios, jajuibrg man mayaa minnogbat, majrrja margjee, oo wryulauya irirgprn majeiconjee. Dumat jaminocat mayaa. Dumat jaminocat oo wryu majeiconjee ebupaa-mashancrtjee mapecado-shrm.
47006003	Jaibishanwei cashrt naa drg monooliprn shrnoja, biinotshi capinshrt iebjet jajaa naa ibijuirr.-
47006004	Ijei biminrg ouricawiat japishiyawaagjee ibibeebdig Dioat, ooshrmda ishan-nrmijet ebupaabiucrt prnpatjet biwoo-rribat, iebyubat poi birica.
47006005	Bidcapai, presoja bidcarg, bidcamrn poi, oiirig ibibeebdig, ibag shai bishan-owi, buipaabicrt poi.
47006006	Ojera ibirr japishiyawaagjee Dioat icuiprnotá biriglig. Brlau-shandidi ieb biminr bitaale-jet, japishibiwaagwi jabijuirgli naa moyerog rjetwin. Yau binrmdiprn, bijii-jei jaligwi bijet naa Espíritu Santo, yayii biruug.
47006007	Jajet naa moyerog rjetwin ibijuirg, jayaqüedrt japishiyawaagjee brjaligu birig, Dios bigshayu iwairiig-jet bijii-tee poi. Jajet naa ijei ibiminrg bibata jabirg moweijin, ojera poi jaibiweiri bishrt Dios yerog-jet. Uubiidprnotjinda bidu ooshrt jabibrg calat naa mii-ishanbri
47006008	Itrmnogolat birgbrg, itrmnogolat yau birg cabrrliprn. Itrmnogolat biinot shipin ijeijet, itrmnogolat biinot shipin iebjet. Itrmnogolat biishag teeshauota biriglig, itrmnogolat biipin ibijuirglig rjet.
47006009	Itrmnogolat biruug oje pishishanwajitni, oyat itrmnogolat biruug oje pishicawagotni ijeijet. Itrmnogolat jadjeu bidcarrirglig, ooshrt bijujugwi. Jadirg ebupaabicrdi ooshrt yauju birririprn.
47006010	Bijii cashnmg, ooshrt bijii-jái oiiricawiat. Uubiirota bidu, ooshrt jashiribrgya calat mii-bag nat ibagolat jashrm naa ibijuirg. Boirig-shandit iribrg birat nam wryutee, ooshrt jalibrgwi birat wrijin naa iishanduji.
47006011	Yam bijrrot corintioot, biyaadbrcat yan ishalalig-jet. Jabirircat japishiyawaagjee bibigshayu wrijin yayii biruug-shrm.
47006012	Boirig shandit iibijaan yashrt, ooshrt yam jaiyajaan yabigshayu bishrt biyii yashanduut-shrm ijeijet oje yayii biruulauni birat.
47006013	Ooshrmda yapinrg yam oje itrm bonat japinrlauni jatrri, ayaupinrg ishalalig-jet brjaliigu yabigshayu-lig oje yapinrlauni abigshayujet.
47006014	Casa yacupoirit cajet nat Dios yerog shan-waorrirt. Itrmjanitejam jalii naa ijei iebprnjin-jet. Itrmjani-tejam jalii naa ebushi wryu ibrru-jet.
47006015	Itrmjani-tejam jalii naa Cristo moweijin-jet. Itrmjani-tejam cabigshayu lii nat Dios yerog waort cajet nat jayerog shanwaorrirt.
47006016	Jaiquedrrijam cadirirgu idoloot Dios ot-tee. Bidulawi jaoolot naa Dios ijug. Ojera jamo Dios, ashirigya cajii-tee, ashiboolrgya cajewalee. Amyawi cajri-Dios, oodyapoi aepinot.
47006017	Ooshrm jashrimog, yauyucat cashrt, yayauwawug cashrt, ojera jamo Biŕri. Jayacupoiminrt naa jaapibag wryu tepin, oyatya yabatashitai, jarnog Dios.
47006018	Oyatya Yaíija ashirii atrriotya yam, alouotya yam. Ojera jamo Biŕri, naa iwairülig wrijin-shrt.
47007001	Yam idjajeuprnot, Dioat jaipin birat ijei, ooshrt biradwi jabishinamnog bishrt biebyu wrijin, birigjee jaapi-rrijet, jabishanebrtjee bitaale, rripoi bibigshayu. Biradwi jabishirir bitaale Dioat, bibigshayu poi, japinita birigjeeya rjet biom-shrm jarea.
47007002	Biyii yaluugwi rjet yajii-teat. Ieb bishanminrt itrmat, jabishanpoi ebrt boi bigshayu, boi teebishanshaurt poi.
47007003	Jashanjeu yaiapindig iebjet, ooshrm yayii aluug ajii-teat oje arnojaniriyan bŕn, itrmjani jaligjee bibigshayu yajet bijujugbat, birri quedyemya poi.
47007004	Japishiawaagwi jajeirig yabigshayu ooshrm ijáijet yayeawaag. Ibagjet ebupaabicrt oiirigwi ooshrt abigrririgwi ijei jajet naa paaacrt, ajii-jái ipegjet.
47007005	Birninogbat yaprna Macedonia-teja, jadshandirt jiija biriglig. Bibaata bidcarg brrn-jaligu biboog, ebupaabicrd bitaale-jet, oyat biom bijii-tee .
47007006	Ooshrt naa Dios cajáirr jii-shŕmot, jadirg bijii-jáijee jayug-shrm birica naa Tito.
47007007	Bijii-jái jabiruug-shrm naa Tito, oyat poi ijáijet yainot bijui jajet. Jaijapin yajii-shŕmdig jayeyawaaglig yapecado ipegjeta ayajeu ayaluuglig, jayajeu yajrrja ayarglig, ooshrmda ajii-jái.
47007008	Bŕn yajii-shŕm jashrm naa papera inaabrgprn yan, oyat ajii-shrm poi. Ooshrt dumat ajii-shanshŕm japishiawaag-shrm ayerocat yajii shŕmrglig, ooshrt prnpatjet shandit.
47007009	Dumat ajii-jái yajii shŕm-shrm shandit, ooshrt ajii-jái yajii yacambiarcat-shrm ijeijet, yajii shŕm-shrm yapecado iyeyawaaglig. Naa mojii-shŕmyu, ijei jaminrgyan oje Dioat jajeulauni. Ooshrmda japishibi-waag yabigshayu bishan-ebrdi jajet naa papera ibinagprn yan.
47007010	Bijii shŕmu oje Dioat jajeulauni, jadshicambiargya bibigshayu bipecado-shrt Dios-jaa. Oyat bidjashijeiconya ebupaabicrt-shrt bipecado-shrm. Ooshrm jaeb bishanduji naa mojii shŕmyu Dioat irirgprn. Oyatjri cadjarrirg epinot naa mojii-shŕmyu wryu pinat.
47007011	Jayacaluug brjaligu yabigshayu jeiricat yajii shŕm-shrm oje Dioat jajeulauni. Dumat yabigrri shandit yapecado-jet ooshrt jayajeuwi yayajeicondig ibiruugjet. Dumat jaeb yaluugwi yapecado, yaomwi Dios rca, jayajeuwi ayaluuglig, jayajeuwi jayalirglig ebupaajacrtjee naa ieb-minrat, ooshrt japishibiwaagwi boiruudbrg yan yaebyu.
47007012	Jashan-naabrt yan naa papera jashrm naa iebminrr, rripoi jashrm naa ebupaacrtr, ooshrt jajeu japishiyawaagjee yajnja bidyargjee Dios beeb-shrm.i
47007013	Ooshrmda bijii-jái yashrm, oyat Titoshrm poi biju-jái. Ijáijeta yayeijawaag yajrrja jayarg-shim jabirririgjee ijeijet.
47007014	Bŕn yainot shiapin Titoat ijeijet, ooshrt auushanyit yashrm, ooshrm rjetwina jalig naa ood-amog yajaa.i

47007016	Ajii-jái japishiawaagshrm ijet jaliglig yabigshayu. Ooshrmda jaquedrg ajii alirglig yajaa.
47008001	Dumat ajrrot, jabijeu japishiyawaaglig jajaa naa ijei Dioat irirg cajii-tee nat iglesia atwinot Macedonia-tee.
47008002	Ibagjedi ebupaacacrt ooshrt cajii-jái. Uubiidota calig ooshrt ofrenda caliirg oje dapwoo ligotni.

47008005	Jadshan-minrt oje jaibishaalaurn, ooshrt cacalirg-jurg caaleiolat Biŕriat, oyat jadirbrg birat ofrenda oje Dioat jajeulauni.
47008006	Ooshrmda bimog Titoat jadougjee yajewaleot-shrt naa ofrenda ijei juijaberg-jurg bŕn.
47008007	Dumat japishiyawaacat ijei yaminrglig wrijin. Yajii yalircat Dios-jaa ijeijet, japishiyawaagwi jayerog yajuirglig ijeijet. Japishiyawaagwi brjáliyu jaligu jayerog, ijáijet iyabeeb jan, biyii yaluug poi. Ooshrm ijeijeta jayaupin naa ofrenda, naa ibishirgya uubiidolat.
47008008	Iyashancui cajrrja cadyargjee ofrenda-jet jayashanjeuu. Oowi jajeu jayalirglig japishibiwaaglig cayii yaluuglig yajii-teat.
47008009	Japishiyawaagwi naa ijei Biŕri Jesucristoat iminrg birat. Wooligla naa Biŕri, ooshrt bishrmdi jayuu jabogjee bijewalee oje uubiidni jadbrgjeeya yan naa miibag ishanbeji.
47008010	Jayapin yan itrm moyerog, jajeiwi jayauminrg wrijin naa iyaminrg jurglig boi wiig-tee ijaijedi jayaminrg-jurr.

47008012	Ijaijet jaligu jayabrr Dios-jaa naa ofrenda, ijáijetya jadshiruu. Jadjeu yajet itrmnog japei naa iribrg yan. Jashan-rm yajet naa boiruud-brg yan.
47008013	Jashanjeu jalibrglig calat ibagjet yashrt. Jalibrgshrm yan ishrmwi cashrt, bijashirii ebupaayacrt jashrm naa iyabrea.

47008015	Oje idnaalauniri brn, naa iribrg jan ibagjet, oowi naa iriibrg jan naa idjeulii. Oyat ooat jalibrg ishrmwi boirig shandit shri idjeu.
47008016	Ijei abrg Dioat ooshrm jadirg Titoat yaijeulig ijeijet jajii-teat oje auijani.
47008017	Ooshrm Titoat jajeu jadminrglig naa ibirirg jadminrglig. Ipegjeta yayejawaa, ooshrmya jashinimnog yalica jajii-teat.

47008023	Jajeu japishiyawaaglig jajaa naa Tito, oolawi ajetwin naa Tito ibibeeb itrmjaniwi ajet yajrrja yabirgjee. Jayajeuu capishiyawaaglig brrt bijrrot-jaa, oodawi iglesia atwinolat icuiprnot, nat iyugot Cristo-jet.
47008024	Ooshrmda yauminrg calat oje bimojani japishicawaagjeeya naa iglesia atwinolat cayii yaluuglig yajii-teat. Jayaulirg japishicawaagjee rjet jaliglig naa ijei oodbimog yajaa.
47009001	Dumat ishanshri-naabrt yan jajaa naa ofrenda ibibrgprn calat nat Dios jetwinolat.

47009003	Ooshrt cad-acui yalica nat bijrrot brjashirii jashanjulidu naa ofrenda brjashirii rjet jashanditu naa ijei oodbimog yajaa.

47009008	Dioat jaquedrg yaijabendisia-rglig ijeijet jaliibrgjee yan wrijin boirig-jaligu yajeu oiiricawiat. Oyat jashiribrgya yan yapin jayabrgjeeya nat uubiidolat, calat poi nat ibeebet Dioat.

47009011	Cajrrja cadyargu brrt ipegjet Dioya yashibendisiarg jaliibrgjeeya yan ibagjet. Oyatya ijei cashibrr Dioat yajaa nat bijrrolat jabirrnogbrg-shrm calat naa ofrenda iyabrg calat.
47009012	Jajet naa iyabrg calat jashiriibrgya calat wrijin naa idjeu. Oyatya poi jaicashipin ijei Dioat nat ibagolat.

47009014	ijáijetya yayecashiwaa, jadshirmya Dios yajaa. Yayii cashiruugya jashrm naa ijei yaminrg calat.
47009015	Ijei bishibrg Dioat jadirg-shrm birat itrm Regalo inomjrijeirig wrijin ebu-shrt. Jabishan-jeiquedrt jaibipindig ijeijet naa ijei iddirg birat Cristo-jaa.
47010001	Am Pablo, yapinrg jijogjet moyerog ishan-nrmijet oje jalijani naa Cristo. Camog ajaa, uubiidprnjini jalig jaligbat bijet ooshrt bidjapinrg jijogjet japapera-tee jayaubat bishrt.
47010002	Ooshrmda yapinrg jijogjet cabigshayu yauieicon itrmnogot ayaad-shrtya jijogjet animnogbatya yalica. Oosnrm iijogjet jajeu ayaadbrglig calat nat itrmnogot yajetwinot jaicashag-shrm bijii birirglig jajaa naa wryu, biireiot bigshayu-jaa poi.
47010003	Bijuuligbat wryu-tee, mopiu bishan-minrt oje calijani nat wryu tepinot.

47010005	On cabirgjee bibaalot Dios bigshayu-jet, nat jajuiprt Dios jrirüg caaiei bigshayu-jet. Jabishirirg Cristoat presoja bibigshayu-rglig wrijin, jayerog biwaorgjee ijeijet.
47010006	Pronto birica jabirirgjee ebupaayacrdig yapecado-shrm boirigbat jaliguya japishiyashiwaa ijeijet naa moyerog iyawaorg.

47010008	Ainot shiapinu iinodigota biriglig, jajeiwi, ooshrm Biŕriat jalirg yaibijeujee. Jadirg yabijuirgjee jabigshayu-minjee yajii-tee, yashanrmdrtjeeya jashrt.
47010009	Jayacupoi-shaat jajeulig yawrgrglig apapera-jet.
47010010	Ooshrm ojeri camo ajaa, jijogjeta idnaabr birat japapera-tee oje bicacouni, ooshrt jataale rriyug, jashanjei jayaadyu íjuirig.
47010011	Jayaulirg japishicawaagjee nat epinolat, biyugbat yalica ibishiminrgya oje bimojani bipapera-tee.

47010013	Bidu, jabishanquedrt japishibiwaaglig bijaa, yau poi brrt-jaa. Jatrmwi Dios japishiwaja bijaa wrijin. Oolawi jalirr binoglig yalica yam Corintio tepinot.
47010014	Bicashanditu yajet yabijuirgjee bŕn, jabishancug quedrt yabicuinoglig. Ooshrt bidulawi inimnog jurgot yalica yabijuirgjee jajet naa moyerog Cristo-jaa jet-moijeicon.
47010015	Jabishanjeu cadbipinrglig jijogjet brrt ijuirgprnot oje cadbipinrlauni nat idbijuirgprnot. Ooshrt yajeibitei jayawaorgjee jijooligjet cadbijuirgjee ibagjaligjet epinot jayewalee.
47010016	Jabijeu jabijuirglig naa moyerog jet-moijeicon wrijin moyanteja yawaligjet yashrt, on brrt cashanju juirta, ijei ibipin-shrt biirei-jaatep boi beeb-shrm.
47010017	Naa jajewi ijei ijapindig jaalei-jaatep, jayaulirg ijei ijapinjee Birri-jaa.i

47011003	Aom brjashirii moweijinat yabigshayu rrnogu boyeja Cristo-shrt oje Eva teejashaulaunin bŕn. Aom brjashirii jayu yashanduudu Cristo rjet yajii-teat.
47011004	Cayugbat itrmnogot yadjuirgjee boyeja jashrt naa Jesús jaaibijuirg, boirigshrmjam jayajuibrg calat. Oyat jayashirirgya demonio luuglig yajii-teja jashrt naa Espíritu yajuirrli brn. Oyat jayawaorg itrm moyerog jashrt naa moyerog jet-moijeicon iyajuiri bŕn.
47011005	Jai-ashag mii-rriprnjina ashandiglig cashrt nat jaishaat cajeirig Cristoat icuiprnot-shrt, nat jajewet jadjuirig.
47011006	Ashanyaad moyerog ijeijet mot bigshayu-jet. Jashaada aloog, ooshrt jashanshaat ajuiyag. Jabirirg japishiyawaagjee bibigshayu jajet naa ibiminrg oiirig.
47011007	Ieb aminrrijam yajuirg-shrm mii-rrijet naa moyerog jet-moijeicon. Ieb aminrrijam ebupaa-acrdshrm uubiidjet jawrryrgjee yabigshayu shrnoja.
47011008	Jalirg brrt iglesia atwinot jabrglig an jet-awoug mii-abrca alapwoo poi yajrrja yargjee.
47011009	Aligbat yajet jashan-rm awoüg yajet, alapwoo poi, ooshrm jadirbrg an boirig jaligu ijeu nat bijrrolat Macedonia atwinot. Jashandirdi ebupaayacrdjee ashrm, dumatya poi boirig shanditya ishirm yashrt.
47011010	Cristo yerog ijetwin ligwi ajii-tee, ooshrmda amog rjet, jashishan-dirtya alapwoo cabrglig nat Acaya tepinot, brjashirii jadnamu ashrt naa ijei ood-amog ajaa.
47011011	Boirigshrmjam ayaad oje. Yau-teja yayii aluuliprn. Dioat japishiwaagwi yayii aluuglig.
47011012	Boirig shandit ijeu yashrt bŕn, dumat poi boirig shandit ijeu, bojashirii biinot shicapinu ibiminrglig oje calijani nat ganando calapwoort jajet naa idjuirg.
47011013	Cristoat icuiprnot shandit rjet nat jajewet capin caouglig ideajuirgprnot-shrt. Ibeebet teeshauot nat calapwoo yiirujut, jadjeu Cristoat icuiprnot yarnoglig cajaa.
47011014	Idrninrg oje jalijani naa moweijin, naa jajalirr oje ángele ibrgni.

47011016	Yashipinrg shri, jayacupoirirt brrt ayewaaglig iigprnjina aliglig. Ooshrt jaicashagu oje ainot shiashipinya calijani nat iigprnotjinjamo.

47011020	Yam jalirt moolat presoja yarglig yabeebjee calat. Jadirg yateecashaurgjee jadwaorgjee yabeeb mii. Yiijeta cadyaluu nat caishaat cajeirig yashrt, otpoi nat ya-ú paiyat.
47011021	Dumat auuyig arnoglig oje, ooshrt birriyug bidu ooshrm yabi shanpaiyi oje calijani. Jadcajeuu ijei iicapindüg caalei-jaa, ainot shiashipoipinya ijeijet ibiminrgjee oje iigprnotjini.
47011022	Hebreoot tejamot, amda poi hebreoot poi. Israelot tejarnot, amda poi. Abraam jrdwat-tejamot, amda poi jajriwai.
47011023	Idbeebijam Cristoat, am poi ibeepe jan jijoolig-jet cashrt. Ainot shiapin iigprnjini, ooshrt ibeeb jijogjet cashrt. Bibalolat presoja arg ubajalig-jet cashrt, iibajalig-jet poi cashrt adpai, iibajalig-jet cashrt jayriyaijin arriyi.
47011024	Daptrm jaitogli adpai trenta-nueve iitoonog-jet rejo-jet nat judioolat.
47011025	Jai-poiri adpai pun-jet, jaitrmdig adrrirg jaa-jet, jaipoiri bijrimon já-tee. Jaitrm shairei wrgle poi atan rt-teye pun-jaa.
47011026	Jaminrg ibagjet viaje, anog rt-teye eburgligye. Oyat ishegolat jadjeu adrrirglig, oyat ayan-couolat arrirg-shug poi, yawapinot poi. Jadjeu adrrirglig moyan shuwai-tee, brg-uu poi, rt ipeg-teja poi, oyat iglesia tepinot ebuteeshaurt poi jadjeu adrrirglig.
47011027	Jijogjeda ibeeb on ataale rriyuca, jabag shai yau aouliprn. Jaibagli buipaa-acrt, ajii-jro poi, jaibagli boiruud awoug, alica jügli poi jayai-shrmwi alapwoo.
47011028	Ojerawi ieb yuglig alica oiirigwi. Oyat abigshayu mŕm wryu shitojani ayiglrg cashrm nat ibagot iglesiaot jajeuot.
47011029	Jarriyugu itrm iglesia atwin, japoi rriyugam abigshayu-tee. Boi teecashaurgu ieb jaminrgjee, jaeb aluug.

47011031	Naa Biŕri Jesucristo ii Dios, naa oodbimog jan ijei oiiricawiat, japishijawaagwi yatee-ashanshaurt.

47012001	Boirica shandit ainot shiapin yan, ooshrt yapinrg brjaligu Biŕriat jalirglig jaluuglig, jadirg japishiawaagjee jayerog poi.
47012002	Japishiawaagwi itrm bon jajii-rirr Cristo-jaa. Bŕn catorce jatocat wiig jadwrryrgli paraíso-teja shrnoja-shirig crlot-shrt. Japishiashanwaat jadwrryrguli jataale-jet o jadwnyrg jataale-shrt. Dioat japishiwaag.
47012003	Japishiawaagwi jadwrryrglig naa bon shrnoja. Yau japishiawaliprn jadwrryrgu jataale-jet o jadwrryrgli jataale-shrt. Dioat japishiwaagwi jajaa.
47012004	Jadwrryrgbadi paraíso-teja, onda jadjui moyerog ijei, naa moolat ishanquedrri jaicapindig.
47012005	Dumat ijei iashipin jajaa naa bon ood-amog. Ainot shiashanpin ijeijet jajaa naa iminrg dumat, oowi naa iiyapin jajaa naa iminrg arriyugbat.
47012006	Iacajeuu ainot shiapindig ijeijet, ashanyaad oje iigprnjini, ooshrt rjetwina jalig naa ood-amog. Ooshrt ainot shiashanpin aalei-jaa jaiyashag-shrt ajeiriglig jashrt naa epina aliiyu dumat, naa iyaluug iyajui poi.
47012007	Ijeira naa Dioat irirg jaluuglig, ijui poi shrnoja, ooshrmda jadirg moweijinat apairig ishiyu-jet jaiashag-shrt ajeirig brrt-shrt jashrm naa iruug shrnoja.
47012008	Oje uulat motaam-rrlauni motaalee, ojera naa ishiyu liglig ajaa, oyat jarm ipoijet Biŕri jadnamjee ashrt.
47012009	Ooshrt Dios mog an, jajeitogwi man japishimawaagjee mayii aluuglig, ooshrm jijoolig-jet abigshayu min cajii-tee nat taale rri-yugot. Ooshrm ajii-jái jarriyug-shrm ataale jaliibrgjeeya an Cristo bigshayu iwairüg ajii-tee.
47012010	Ooshrmda ajii-jái jarriyugbat ataale, cabata adrgbat poi, bui paa-acrtbat poi. Iebyugbat alica Cristo-shrm ajii-jaf, ooshrm japishiawaagwi jawairiilig jabigshayu ajii-tee ataale myugbat.
47012011	Ainot shiacugpinat yan ijeijet oje iigprnjinat jainot shipindauni, ooshrm yamdawi ainot shishanpinit ijeijet. Mii-rriprnjin shandita am cashrt nat Cristoat icuiprnot iinodigot, ooshrt mii-rriprnjinda am.
47012012	Ibeebat yajewalee, yau ajaapdiprn ijei aminrglig iyaluuca. Jaminrg brrt ishanminrri, ibagjet yashanjulujit poi, japishiyawaagjee Cristoat icuiprna aliglig.
47012013	Jashanminrt brrt iglesia atwinolat inomjri jeirig jashrt naa iminrg yan. Oowi ashandirt ebupaayacrdig ashrm oje calijani, ayauperdonarg yajet jashandirt-shrm ebupaayacrdig.
47012014	Dumat jaipoiri animnogli yalica, Boirig shandit ijeu yajet, aebu ashanjeu yajet, oowi yajeulig yam. Yau trrijulolat jaouliprn calapwoo cawouca poi calat nat caiijit caiinit poi, ooshrt caiijirat jabrg calat.
47012015	Ojera poi am, ijáijet anaam yashrm wrijin naa iribrg an, wrijin ataale iwairiiyu poi, jajeirügyawi yajii yarri quedyem. Jashŕmiwi ayii yaluugli, yayii aluug-shrm ipegjet.

48004006	Oyat Dioat jacui jaWá Espíritu jaligjee yajii-tee japishiyawaagjee Dios trriota yaliglig, ooshrmda naa Espíritu yajii-tee jamog Dioat, mam Aii.

48004008	Bŕndiju jajuprduju japishiyawaaglig Dios-jaa, presoja yabigshayu cargli nat Dioja ishandiolat.
48004009	Ooshrt dumat japishiyawaagwi naa Dios, o jaipin ishalaligjet naajri Dios yapishijawaagwi yam. Ooshrmda ayaupinrg, boirigshrmjam jayashridirg yabigshayu bŕnwinjinat yajiipdig shri iyaminrgjee-shri oje iyarjaniri presoja yajuligbadi moyerog bŕnwinjin-jet.
48004010	Yashri-om itnn wryu-rca itrm-shrt jajeiyajutei itrmnog wryu, jrrbot poi, wiig poi, rtyrg poi.
48004011	Ajii-shrm ipegjet jaiashag-shrm oyateprnoglig jayawaorglig naa moyerog jet-yajuirgli. Jaiashag jarriyaibrjin jamii-rriyii naa ibeebdi Dioat yajewalee.
48004012	Ajrrot yapinig aquiig-shicom, yayauluug ajet ooshrm ashanshri-rii jajaa naa moyerog bŕnwinjin. Yauli ieb yaminrliprn an aligbatdi yajewalee, ooshrmda ieb yacupoiminrri an dumat.
48004013	Yamdawi japishiwajat, yajuirg-jurgbatdi naa moyerog jujujet Cristo-jaa alig-shrmdi yajet ishiyuat awaorg-shrm.
48004014	Dioat jalirbrg an naa ishiyu o jajrica-ataíncouu-om naa paa-acrdi. Oyat yam yauli aeb yaluuliprn ishiyu-shrm, ooshrt ijeijetdi abaatyatai oje jabatitairauni itrm ángele Dios licatwin, oje-poi jabatitairauni naa Jesucristo .
48004015	Oyat dumat, boirigshrmjam yajii-shanjái oje brrni. Bŕn jayacaquedrgulí yabig yabrglig an, jayacugbrgliwrn an-om.
48004016	Oyat dumat, jayashaijam yabata aliglig yapinrg-shrm rjet jajaa naa iebiyaminrg.
48004017	Nat teeshauot jadjeu yabigshayu jaicabeebdig, ooshrt ijeiyawana shandit. Oowi jadjeulig yadwawuglig bishrt, yajii yalirgjee cajaa.
48004018	Jajeiwi mobigishagu brrt-jaa cabigshayu ijeiconjee moyerog rjetwin-jet. Ojerawi iyaurr oiiricawiat, rrira yaminrglig qje aligbattep yajet.
48004019	Yam atrriot, ebupaa-ashricrt yashrm oje ebupaajacrdauni naa denat jayaa-minogbat jatrri jawaojee. Oyat ebupaa-ashiertyaju ata-on Cristo bigshayu licaya yajii-tee.
48004020	Jacugjeu animnoglig yalica ayaadjee yajet dumat jajaa naa inag papera-tee japishiashanwaat-shrm brjaligu yaliglig dumat.
48004021	Ayaupinrg, yam jashrijewet yaliglig jajaa naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprndi Moiseat. Jayashanjuitejamju brjaligu jamog naa moyerog bŕnwinjin.
48004022	Ojera jamo, Abraam cacauli jatrriot, jatrm iyrg den presoja irig-shrt, jatrm jatrri iyrg ja-u presoja-ishandi-shrt.
48004023	Naa presoja-irig trri, jatrt bon bigshayu-jet. Ooshrt naa presoja-ishandi trri, jatrt Dios bigshayu-jet jayaa minogcaduli naa oodjamogprndi Abraamat.
48004024	Naa oodamog oola comparación, nat icauot detpatnira ojera calii nat icauot moyerogot. Naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprndi Moiséat wen Sinai-jaa oje jalijani naa den preso jatam Agar. Oyat nat cajiirirt jajaa naa moyerog bŕnwinjin ebupaacacrt idbeebdig oje presoolat ibeebdauni caacajeiconjee Dios-jet.
48004025	Naa Agar ojera jalii naa wen Sinaí Arabia-tee, oolawi oje Jerusaléni dumat ooshrm presoja cajuulig nat Jerusalén tepinot moyerog bŕnwinjin-jet.
48004026	Ooshrt boirig-shandit caquedrr presoja cadjarglig nat Jerusalén-shrnojawin epinot. Oyat bidu, Jerusalén shrnojawin tepinot.
48004027	Ojera jamo naa idnagprndi papera-tee, majii cujái mam trri-rri mam jashanquedrri matrriri. Majii maujáirg mam japaashancrli matrri mawaolig. Ooshrm naa den trri-rri bon bigshayu-jet, cashinornjri bajaligya jatrriot jashri naa bon-dig.
48004028	Ájrrot yapinrg, bidulawi oje jalijani naa presoja-ishandi trri Isaac. Dioat jalirg jatrriota birigjee jabigshayu-jet oje jadirlauni Abraamat jatrri Isaac.
48004029	Bŕn naa itrtdi bon bigshayu-jet, jabata jadrg naa itrtdi Espíritujet. Ojera poi dumat, nat irigot mot bigshayu-jaa cabata-cadcarg nat iyrgot jajuju Espíritu-jet.
48004030	Oyat ojera jamo naa idnagprndi papera-tee, jamauyrrg naa presoja irig jatrri-jet, ooshrm naa preso-trri yauya jadshiquedrliprn jaouglig japin jajet naa presoja ishandi trri.
48004031	Ooshrm ajrrot yapinrg, presoja irigprnjin trriot shandita bidu, ooshrt oje jalijani birig naa presoja-ishandi trri.
48005001	Cristoat bishiuata bidu, bibigshayu bŕnwinjinat bishrijiipshrt, ooshrm ajrrot yaulig dai-imogjet ojewi yadirlauni naa yashiuwiat. Jayacupoishririrt briat yabigshayu jiipdig jajet naa moyerog imrm jaa-yaligli bŕn.
48005002	Jayaujui ayerog yam ajrrolat, am Pablo yapinrg, jayajeuu yayajeicondig Dios-jet jajet naa costumbre bŕnwinjin, boirica shandit yan naa Cristo.
48005003	Yashripinrrlig naa jajewe jajajeicon siconsismo-jet jandawi jadshiminr wrijin oje Moisés yerog mojaliiri.
48005004	Yam jaishaalat ijeijet Dioat yaluuglig iyaminrg-shrm oje jarnojani naa moyerog bŕnwinjin, jayacug-quedrcat jayanamnoglig-orn naa Dioat iminrg yan Cristo-jaa yayii jaluug-shrm.
48005005	Ooshrt bidujri, jabijeu ijeinogotni Dioat biruuglig jashrm naa Espíritu irig bijii-tee bijii birirg-shrm Cristo-jaa.
48005006	Oyat birigu dai-imogjet Cristo-jet, boirica-shandit birat naa sirconsisión o boiruudu birat. Jajeitogwi birat bijii-birirryu Cristojaa, oyat biyii bishiruuyeg jashrm naa moyerog-juju ibiwaorg. Jayacupoirirt yacostumbre yajiip shririg
48005007	Bŕndi ijeijet jayawaorr naa moyerog rjetwin Cristo-jaa. Brr-jam yabigshayu ebrr jayerog yashan-waortjee dumat.
48005008	Jaiyacupoisnaat Dioja jaliglig naa yabigshayu wawuu jayerog juju-shrt, ooshrt oolawi naa yajuishumdi yam jayerog yawaorgjee.
48005009	Yam ajrrot, japishiyawaagwi iyai moyerog boyeja Dios yerogshrt jadebrg wrijin naa moyerog iyawaorg oje levaduraat jajuituunrlauni wrijin naa masa.
48005010	Ooshrt jaiashag Biŕriat yabigshayu shijeicondigya, yabigyashag-shrt boyeja jayerog-shrt. Dioya cashirirrm ebupaacacrtjee nat yabigshayu ebrlat, boirica shandit iinodigot jaligu, o bicashancowit jaligu poi.
48005011	Oyat ajrrot, jayaujui naa oodamog aalei-jaa, cadapatjri cuiu caacajeiconjee Dios-jet jajet naa costumbre bŕnwinjin, boirigshrmjam cabata-adrg nat cacostumbre juirlat. Boirigshrm-shancuglit aeb caluu-om jacapatjri-juirgu biroomot costumbre Cristo crusashrt.
48005012	Oyat nat yabigshayu ebr-boot cacostumbre-jet naa idminrg wiuyu-jet jajeiwi caaleiot jaliguwi caacocoot wrijin wooja bicargshrt bidu.
48005013	Dumat yam ajrrot, Dioat yaoucat yadshiujee, ooshrt yau jadjeuliprn iyarninrglig oje yataaleat jajeulauni yashandit-shrm jajaa naa moyerog idirgprndi bŕn. Ooshrt janomjrijeirig japishiyawaagjee yaalei-jaa yajrrja-yayarryegjee yayii yaluuyecat-shrm.
48005014	Wrijin naa moyerog Dioat irirgprndi-brn, jaiquedrg jaiipindi itrmwi moyerog-jet,jayii mauluugma majrr ojewi maaleiat mayiiruulauni.
48005015	Oyat yaeb yaluuyegujri, jayajeuu yaprrtoglig oje yoololat caashaalauni, jayauluug yashrt brjashirii yayarmdrrgu yaaleatwi wrijin.
48005016	Oola naa ijeu yapinrglig jajet, yaulig oje Espírituat jalirlauni. Yaligu oje Espírituat jalirlaunijri, yauya iyashiminrliprn oje yabigshayu bŕnwinjinat jalirlauni.
48005017	Yabigshayu bŕnwinjinda jabata jarm naa Espíritu, oyat naa Espíritu jabata jadrg yabigshayu bŕnwinjin. Cabata-caacarg ooshrmda jayashanquedrri iyaminrglig oje jayajeulauni.
48005018	Ooshrt jayalirgu Espírituat yacuirig, yauya yabigshayu bŕnwinjinat yashicuiriprn.
48005019	Jaiquedrg japishiwaaglig brjaligu idrg nat irigolat cabigshayu bŕnwinjin-jaa. Caacawoojeurg, ieb caminrg cataale-jet, cabootogrri jaapibagprnjin-jet.
48005020	Caicarm idoloot-shrt, jadrninrg mojiigyu poi, caeb-caluug brrt, caacamrnyeg, caacaquejaryeg iwairücat, canrm mogwaini, cayecawaag caalei-jaatep brrt-shrt, cacacrdnog brrt.
48005021	Canai boi woojet epin carrirg, cawón, cayowan eb boyecajetep, cabotogrri cataale-jet, jadrninrg ibajet boirig jaligu ieb ooirig. Dumat ajrrot yapinrg oje yapinrlauniri bŕn, nat iminrt oje cashishan-duutya paraíso-teja on Dioat caijeuwa jaepinot.
48005022	Dumat jabiuluug brjaligu id-rg mojii-tee naa Espírituat. Jadirg biyii-biruuyegjee, bidjajáirg, jadirg bibigrririgjee wrijin ieb-shrt, jadirg jajrica-bicoulig prnpatjet naa paabicrt, jadirg ijei biminrgjee brrlat, ijeijet cadbipoiruu, jadirg biriglig dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg.
48005023	Naa Espíritu jadshandirt bijaibishaglig bijeirig brrt-shrt, jadirg jaiwinbishoglig bibigshayu bitaale poi ieb-shrt. Yapinrg, boiruuda itrrn moyerog jaubata naa oodamog yan.
48005024	Oyat nat Jesucristo epinot, jaddircat jaibamjee cruza-jaa cabigshayu bŕnwinjin naa ieb idjeuli jadminrglig.
48005025	Ooshrm bijuugu Espíritu-jet, biratwi jabishirir bijrijawaotegjee naa Espírituat, ibiminrgjee oje jamojani.
48005026	Yau jaibiquedrliprn jaibishaglig ijeinogota biriglig brrt-shrt brjashirii bibinrmrgu, rri-poi binairig brrt dapwoojet, rri-poi caeb biruuglig cabicacouot bishrt.
48006001	Ajrrot, japishi-yawaagu boi bijrrat ieb-minrglig, yandawi jayashipinrr moyerog ijeijet jajuimigjee jaebyu-shrt, yam irigolat dai-imogjet Espíritu-jet. Jajrrja yaulig jauubiid yaluug-shrm. Oyat jayauluug yashrt brjashirii jayugu-poi yalica naa iebprnjin yateejashaurgjee.
48006002	Yajrrja-yayaurg, iajricayaucou naa paayacrt. Iyaminrgu ojejri, iyashrmrnrgya oje Cristoat jajeulaurú.
48006003	Jateejashaurg jaaleatwi naa bicacoula am, imogat, bicashancouwiprnjina jalig-shicom.
48006004	Wrijin bidu bitojam, biratwi jabishiruu boirig jaligu bibigshayu lig. Biradwi jabishiruu boirig jaligu naa ibiminrg nam wryu-tee. Oyat naa jaisham rjet ijeiya jaliglig, jajaquedrg jajajáirglig jajii-tee, ooshrt yau jainot shijapindiprn ijeiya jaliglig brrlat.
48006005	Ooshrna biratwi jajricabishicou bitojani naa imrm bijaa.
48006006	Naa jajuirr boi-jet Dios yerog-jaa, jandawi jajrrja jadshirr naa jajuirr, jadbrg jan naa boiruud-brg jan.
48006007	Yateeyacupoishaurt yaaleattep, brr-shandita jadquedrr Dios tamshijayoirig. Naa iebprnjin jamü shirirgya jan naa ieb idminrg oje itrm ijrmrat cajuishuulauni idjajrmprnot boirigot-jaliguwi.
48006008	Ojera-poi naa ijrmr jet-jadjáirca jabigshayu bŕnwinjin, oyat naa epina-jaliyu bŕnwinjin jashiyoobrgya jan naa jalirr jarririg Diosshrt. Ooshrt jadjrmu naa jet-jaijairg naa Espíritu, jashiyoobrgya jan naa wryu ishanbeji jajet naa Espíritu.
48006009	Ooshrm ajrrot, bicupoijaap ijei biminrglig. Bishanjaapu jabijrmdig ijei, jabishiougya jamu naa ijei ibiminrg jarninogbatya biyaa.
48006010	Ooshrmda ijei biurninrg calat wrijin on jabiquedrca, ooshrt jijooligjet jabiujeu ijei biminrglig bijrrolat cajiirirlat Cristo-jaa.
48006011	Jayacaluu brjaligu janaglig naa papera letra ipeenog-jet alapjettep.
48006012	Nat jajewet sirconsisao yadrglig, oowi idjeu judioolat ijeijet caluuglig, bijashirii cabata cadcargu Cristo cruza-shrm.
48006013	Nat poi sirconsisao cart yau jadminrliprn wrijin oje jamojani naa moyerog bŕnwinjin, ooshrt jadjeu ijei iicapindig caalei-jaatep jayalirg-shrm yataale capandig oje camojani.
48006014	Ooshrt amjir, boirig-jaa shandit ijei amo, oowi ijei jaa-amog naa Biŕri Jesucristo cnisa. Ooshrm naa idminrgli cruza-jaa, jarriat ashrt naa wryu, oyat-poi arn arriat jashrt naa wryu.
48006015	Birigu dai-imogjet Jesucristo-jet, boirica shandit birat naa costumbre bŕnwinjin. Oowi müribrg birat biyrgu jajuju-jet.
48006016	Ooshrm ajrrot jajeu yabigmriglig wrijin ieb-shrt. jajeu yauubiid-yaluuyeglig yam irigolat jajaa naa moyerog juju, wrijin nat Dios epin ot rjet.
48006017	Dumat jashanjeu briat abigshayu eb-rglig mü rriprnjin-jet. Natajaaprnot adpaiprn bŕn ataale-jaa, ooda jalirt japishiyawaagjee Biŕri Jesucristo jetwina aliglig.
48006018	Ajrrot, jajeu Biŕri Jesucristo yajáirglig wrijin, Amén.
49001001	Am Pablo, Jesucristoat icuiprnda am oje Jaíi-Dioat jajeulauni. Dumat janag naa papera calat nat Dios epinolat irigolat Efesio-tee, nat cajiirirlat Jesucristo-jaa.
49001002	Jajeu ijei yaouglig Dios-shrt, jajeu yabigrririglig wrijin ieb-shrt Bií Dios-jet, Biŕri Jesucristo-jet poi.
49001003	Ijei bibrg jan naa Biŕri Jesucristo íi-Dios. Bidjajáirg wrijin ijeijet shrnoatwin-jet birig-shrm daiimogjet Cristo-jet.
49001004	Bŕndi Dioat bidjaou Cristo-jaa jajuprduju jadminrglig naa wryu birigjeeya ijeijet ijjuuca, pecado mnogotni poi.
49001005	Bŕndiju Dioat biyü-duuat, ooshrm bidjaoug jadirgjee jatrriota biriglig jashrm naa Jesucristoat iminrg birat crusa-jaa.
49001006	Ooshrmda ibicantarg Dioat oiiricawiat.
49001007	Cristoat bimübrg jamaa-jet biujaprtrgjee Dioat, janamjee bishrt naa ieb ibiminrgli jarri-shrm bishrm cmsa-jaa biyü jaluug-shrm.
49001008	Naa Dios jadirg japishibiwaagjee biyii-jaluuglig ipegjet jadirgshrrn birat jabigshayu japishibiwaagjee brjaliguya jayrrbrg shirig birat naa ibijeu jabiminrglig.
49001009	Jadpoirirg japishibiwaaglig jajaa naa idjeuli jadminrgli bŕnju jabigshayu ijeijet, naa ijajaandi cashrt bŕn.
49001010	Ooshrm Dioya jashiminrr wrijin oje jabigjashaalauni bŕnju jayaa minogbatya. Ojeri jadjeuli idrg, jadjeu cajuijaberglig wrijin wryu tepinot shrnoja winot poi jatnnjeeyawi caliglig Cristo-jet wrijin, Cajriwairiica jaligjeeya wrijin.
49001011	Naa Dios bidjaoucadi bŕnju jabiougjee jashrt naa ijei idjeu jadbrglig birat itrmota biricat-shrm Cristo-jet;. Wrijin naa oodamog yan dumat jayrg birat oje jadjeulauni naa Dios bicacou.
49001012	Ojera idr birigjee ijeijet epinolat iruuca ijei cabrgjeeya jan bijaa naa Dios iwairücat, bidu bijiirirg jurdi Cristo-jaa.
49001013	Oyat yam poi, Dioat yalirg yatrmjeewi Cristo-jet yajii yalirgshrm jajaa jayajuibadi naa moyerog rjetwin jet-yadjeicon ebupaayashancrtjeeya yaebyu-shrm. Oyat yayaa jaminrgjee Espíritu-jet japishiyawaagjee japfaiita yaliglig.
49001014	Naa Espíritu Santo, oola naa Dioat ibrg birat japishibiwaagjee jalibrg-shirig birat wrijin naa idshibrgya birat cadjashiuat quedyemya wrijin jaepinot ieb-shrt, ijei iicapinjeeya jan naa Dioat, iwairüca jalig-shrm wrijin -shrt.
49001015	Ajrrot yainot ajuiat yajii-yalirglicat Birri Jesús-jaa ijeijet, jajuipoi cayii-yaluuglig wrijin nat Dios epinot.
49001016	Ooshrm yau ajaapdiprn ijei abrglig yajaa Dioat aiarmbat jajet.
49001017	Aiarm Birri Jesucristo jriDios-jaa, naa Bií ijei yabicajacourgjee jabigshayu-jet japishiyawaagjee brjaligu jaligu jayerog, japishiyawaagjee poi boirig-jaligu jabigshayu.
49001018	Japoinn jajet yabigshayu ijayrgjee japishiyawaagjeeya jajaa naa jeibitee jabiruuglig jajet bidjaág-shrmat, japishiyawaagjee poi jamii-bagla birat naa ijei idshibrgya calat nat idmawawugprnolat jan, oo-naa iishanquedrri jamii-ibrglig.
49001019	Aiarm ajriDios-shrt jadirgjee japishiyawaaglig iwairüca jaliglig naa jabigshayu ibeepe bijii-tee, bidu jayerog waort. Naa jawairiiyu jet-bidjawairürg, oola naa jet-cadjatadrgli,
49001020	jadwrryrgbadi Jesucristo moniyu-shrt, oyat jadirg jateglig jawireat paraíso-teja.
49001021	Bií-Dioat jalirg Cajriwairüca jaligjee naa Cristo wrijin nat iinodigot, iwáirügot poi, icuiyut poi. Cajriwairüg poi nat idbiruugot dumat, boi-wryuteeya poi.
49001022	Bií Dioat jalirg Jesucristo shiim-noma wrijin boirig-jaligui, oyad jadirg Cristo pina naa iglesia cajuiyaca jaligjee wrijin nat iglesia tepinot.
49001023	Naa iglesia oola Cristo tarde, ooshrmda jajuijatuunrg jajuuyu-jet, jajuijatuunrg wrijin jabigshayu-jet boirig jaligui.
49002001	Bŕn Dioat yajeunorg Cristo-jet yajuligbatdi jashrt oje irriprnotjini jajet naa ieb iyaminrgli.
49002002	Bŕn yaliglig yapecado-jaa, yayaluugli cajet nat wryu tepinot, ooshrmdi iyaminrg oje jadjeulauni naa mojii iebprnjinat jiim-tee irig, naa cawairürm nat Dios yerog shanwaorriot.
49002003	Wrijin bidu poi, brn birig cajewalee nat bicashancowitprnotjin, ibiminrg oje calijani. Jabiminrgli wrijin boirig jaligui ibijeu jabiminrglig bitaale-jet, ibiminrgli oje bibigshayu bŕnwinjinat jálirlauni. Ooshrmda biebyu-prta jaibicug-beeb naa Dios castigo-om ebupaabicugcrtjee cajet nat brrt iebyuligot.
49002004	Ooshrt biuubiid jaluu Dioat, biyii jaluug ipegjet.
49002005	Ooshrmda bidjajeunoorg Cristo-jet bijuligbat jashrt oje irriprnjini bipecadoshrm, yadjeicon poi ieb-shrt yanogjee paraíso-teja yayii jaluugshrm.
49002006	Dioat biwrryucat morriyu-shrt Cristo-jet, oyat dumat jadirg biriglig jajet ishrnrligjet jashrt naa ieb idminrg nam wryu-tee.
49002007	Ojerawi Dioat ir cadjatadrgjee nat biprnotwinot brjaligu biyiijaluuglig ipegjet, japishicawaagjee poi jadminrglig birat naa ijei Jesucristo-shrm.
49002008	Dioat yayii-ruug ooshrmda yadjeicon yajii yalirg-shrm jajaa. Yau jayaquedrliprn yayajeicondig yaalei bigshayu-jet, ooshrt oolawi Dios yajeicono mii-rrijet ieb-shrt binogjee Paraíso-teja.
49002009	Yau bidjajeicondiprn ieb-shrt jashrm naa ibibeebrg jan bijashirii ijei bibrgu biirei-jaatep.
49002010	Oolawi Dios biminrr jajujujet bijii birirg-shrm Cristo-jaa, ijei biminrgjeeya oje jadjeulauni.
49002011	Dumat ajrrot, jayeyawaag brjaliguli iyaliglig bŕn. Judioot-shandita yam ooshrmda camog yajaa siconsisao ishandiot nat judioot cataa-panat wiuyu-jet, oyat camog caalei-jaa sirconsisao irigprnota bidu.
49002012	Oo-wryubadi yayauli Cristo-shrt, yayauli poi cashrt nat israelot. Bŕn japishiyashanjuwaadi naa moyerog Dioat oodmogprndi calat jet-jajeicateiya ijei jajet. Brr-shanditi jajeiteiyr, ooshrm Dios rriprnotjindi yam bŕn.
49002013	Dumat yam, irigodi yawaja Dios-shrt, yanacatwiat jashrt dumat Jesucristoat jalirg-shrm jamaa yashrm yam irigolat daiimogjet jajet dumat.

49006018	Oyat Dios yaupinrg oiirigwi jayaminrgbat naa moprtooyu moweijin ubata. Dios yaupinrg yajii-teat Espíritu Santo-jet. Yandawi yajashiwrr jayaminrgjee naa moprtooyu oodamog, yaujug, yacupoirriyut, jayaunn Dios cajaa nal jaepinot wrijin.

50001001	Am Pablo, Timoteo poi, ibeebeta bidu Jesucristoat. Jabinag naa papera nat bijrrolat wrijin irigolat Filipo-tee, nat ansianolat poi, deaconolat poi, wrijin nat Dios epinolat irigotat dai-imogjet Jesucristo-jet.
