53002016	Dumat jabijeu yadwairürglig naa Birri Jesucristoat, oopoi Bií Dioat, naa biyiirujuat, naa bijáirr oiirica naa jalirr ijei jeibiteirig jajet.
53002017	Jabijeu jadirglig yashoglig dai-imogjet jaiyapinjee moyerog ijei, jayaminrgjee poi wrijin ijei.
53003001	Oolapegwi yabipinrglig yam bijrrot, Dios yaurm bijaa jabíjuirgjee Birri yerog ijeijet jaminogjeeya calica mogwaini-jet wrijin moyanot tojani, jabatcataijee jayerog cajii-tee oje jabatyatairauniri yamat Tesalónica tepinot.
53003002	Dios yaupoirm bidjashiujee cashrt nat mot iebnogprnotjin jabata jart Dios, ooshrm cabag nat epinot cajii shandirriot Dios-jaa.
53003003	Ooshrt dai-irigla naa Birri, ooshrmda jadshiquedrg yadwairuiglig yashogjee dai-imogjet. Oyat yaijashijeuya jashrt naa iebprnjin.
53003004	Oyat japishibiwaagwi Birriat jashirirr yarninrglig oje yadcuirauni.
53003005	Oyat jabijeu Birriat jaiirglig japishiyawaagjee yajii-tee bijaligu Dioat yayiiruuglig, jabijeu jadirgjee jajricayacoulig prnpatjet jajriat naa paayacrt oje Cristoat jajricacoulauniri jajet naa paajacrdi bŕn.
53003006	Dumat bijrrot, yabicui Birri Jesucristo tam-jaa, yayauwawug jashrt naa bijrr jashanjewi idbeebdig, naajri itepdüpag jequewitep, naa ishandü jajaa naa moyerog ibijuirg.
53003007	Yamdawi pishiwajat brjaiiguya yalig-shirig yaminrgjee oje ibirjani, ooshrm jaishanwi-trmdi birigli yajewalee jequewitep.
53003008	Rri-poi biyewairig yajet mii-rritep. Ooshrt ibibeebdi wrglei shairei poi brjashirii ebupaayacrdu bibaatyatairi.
53003009	Biwoug bidcarmuli yashrtjri, jacupoijei-om. Ooshrt yauli yabirmdiprn biwoug-jaa jabijeu-shrmdi yayaluuglig bijet iyaminrgjee oje birijani.
53003010	Bijuligbatdi yajet yabipinrgli, jayacupoirurt yajet naa jashanjewi idbeebdig.
53003011	Cainot bijui yapeit catepdigma, boirig shanditma idbeeb. Catep-boolrgbrma catepyaadbog brrt-jaa.
53003012	Oyat nat oitepdigot, dumat cadbicui Birri Jesucristo-jaa idbeebjee on-irigjet jalibrgjeeya calat cawoug, calapwoo poi.
53003013	Yam bijrrot, yacupoijaap ijei yaminrglig.
53003014	Brrt jashanjeuu jadwaorglig naa moyerog ibinagprn papera-uu, yayauwawug jashrt, yayeicupoiwai jajet jauuyigjee jaebyu-shrm.
53003015	Jayacupoimud oje mobatni, ooshrt jaebyu iyaupin jan moyerog yrrnijetwi oje yajrr yapinrlauni.
53003016	Dumat jabijeu Birriat jalirglig yabigrririgjee jajet wrijin ieb-shrt, naa Bijeicono Bií Dios jet. Jabijeu jaliglig yajet wrijin.
53003017	Am Pablo, janag yan naa memoria aalei lap-jet, ojerawi jabigtan ashrrglig wrijin nat paperaat idanagprnot.
53003018	Dumat jabijeu Birri Jesucristoat ijei jalirgjee yajii-tee yajáijeeya yaliglig wrijin.
54001001	Am Pablo Jesucristoat icuiprnda am oje jadirlauni naa Dios bijeiconoat, oopoi Biŕri Jesucristo jalirr ijei jeibiteirig.
54001002	Janag naa papera mam Timoteoat, awaala mam rjet jajaa naa jaa-bijii birirg. Jajeu Dioat ijei brglig man, jajeu mauubiid jaluuglig, jajeu jadirglig mabigrririglig jajet wrijin ieb-shrt naa Bií Dios, oopoi Birri Jesucristo.
54001003	Dumat yashipinrg oje amojaniri anogbadi Macedoniaja, cadmaucui nat itrmnogot idshanjuirtjee boyeja jashrt naa moyerog ibijuirg.
54001004	Cadmaupinrg nat Judioot jadshanjuirtjee caloomolat oodmogli cabigshayu-jetep. Boirica shandit japishi-iwaa wrijin moloomotjin tam, oowi catepyaadpairig ojewitep jajaa naa Dioat ishanjewi. Oola naa Dioat ijeu cajet, cajii calirgjee jajaa.
54001005	Ooshrmda jajeu cadmapinrglig cayii caluuyegjee cabigshayu jaapirrijet, cajú calirg-shrm Dios-jaa ijet
54001006	Itrmnogolat jashanminrtcug oje bimojaniri, oyat cabigshayu biguwi cacamrnyeg-shrm jajaa naa mii-rriprnjin.
54001007	Jadjeu ijuirta caliglig Dios yerog-jaa, ooshrt japishicashanwaat brjaligu naa oodcamog. Yau poi japishicawaaliprn brjaliyu jaligu naa idjuirg ijáijet.
54001008	Japishibiwaagwi ijeia jaliglig naa moyerog Dioat irirgprndi bŕn idcajuirgu rjet-om.
54001009	Ooshrt biradwi japishibishiwaa Dioat jalirgli naa moyerog Moiséat ijeinogot-shrm shandit, ooshrt cashrm nat jabata-Diort, nat jayerog shanjuiyit, nat bigshayu jaapibagot poi, nat Dios jaiyegrriot, nat caíi-rriot, caíin poi, brrt epinot poi.
54001010	Dioat jalirgli naa moyerog jet-cadjacuiya cashrm nat botogrriot boyequejetep, otpoi nat mot ieb-minrt caaleot-jetep, otpoi nat epinot snegquet, teeshauot poi, otpoi wrijin nat jabata jart naa moyerog rjetwin Dioat ibrgprn cálat.
54001011	Oyat ojera japoi-moo naa moyerog Dioat ijuirg cui an, jetepinot ijeicon ieb-shrt cadjarrnogjee brtbrt-irigteja.
54001012	Ijei abrg Birri Jesucristoat, naa jalirr an mowairiyu, ooshrm ijeijet aduu alig-shrm dai-imogjet jajaa naa mobeeb shrm-ad-ougli jaminrgjee.
54001013	Bŕndi jaeb aluugli naa Biŕri Jesús, abata jargli moyerog iebprnjin-jet. Ooshrt auubiid jaluu ooshrm bicashancowiprnjindi arn, yauli japishiawaaliprn iebprnjina jaliglig naa iminrg.
54001014	Ijeira naa Biŕriat irninrg an mii-rrijet ayu jaluugshrm, jajrija-adrg ajii alirgjee jajaa. Jadirg jayii-aluuglig, brrt poi, oje cayii-caluuyeglauni nat irigolat itrmjanibr Jesucristo-jet.
54001015	Rjetwinda naa moyerog oodjamog, caladwi jadshiwaor wrijin nat epinolat. Oolawi Jesucristo yug naa wryu-teja cadjajeiconjee nat iebnogprnotjin ebupaacashancrtjee caebyu prta, cadarrnogjee shrnqja. Oje poi idr an iebprnjinda am wrijin-shrt.
54001016	Ooshrt uubiidjet adduug Dioat cadjatadrgjee bijaligu Jesucristoat jajricacoulig am inomjri ebprnjin wrijin-shrt, japishicawaagjeeya cauubiid jajuug-piirig wrijin nat cajii shirirtya jajaa, nat oodjashiribrgolatya wryu ishanbeji.
54001017	Dumat ijei biubrg jan oiiricawiat, biuom jarea naa Bijriwairüg ishanbeji, naa Ishishanrriyiya, naa ibishanjuluji bibig-jet, naa Dios itrmwi bicacou.
54001018	Mam awá Timoteo, jaiashipin man itrm moyerog. Jamanminrg moprtoyu iwairügjet moweijin-ubata oje camojaniri majaa bŕn Espíritu-jet. Maushog dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog imawaorg mabigshayu ijeijet.
54001019	Nat itrmnogot jayerog cashanjui naa cajuuyu juju, capinrr cajiitee, ooshrm cabigshayu cashancambiarri.
54001020	Ojeri jalii poi naa Himeneo Alejandro poi, ooshrmda cadanamnog moweijinat jadirgjee ebupaacacrdig cajaapjeeya jajayrg-carrirglig Dios.
54002001	Oyat mapinrg, cadrnaucui jurg Dios carmjee cajaa nat epinot wrijin, ijei cabrg Dioat oiirigwi caicannbat jashrt.
54002002	Jamaulirg Dios carmdig cajaa nat gobiernoot wrijin nat cajriwairügot-jaa, birigjee ijeijet moprtooyu-shrt, bibigshayu birirgjee Dios-jaa, bidcaluugjee ijeijet wrijin.
54002003	Ojerawi ibishir jabijairgjee naa Dios bijeicono ieb-shrt,
54002004	ooshrm jadjeu cadjajeicondig wrijin ebupaacashancrtjeeya capecado-shrm cadjarrnogjee shrnoja. Jadjeu japishicawaagjee wrijin naa moyerog ijetwin.
54002005	Oowi jatrmwi naa Dios, oowi jatrmwi naa epinot-Jeicono Diosjet, oolawi naa Jesucristo, naa iminyrgli wryu jaluugjee oje boni.
54002006	Naa Jesucristo jajalirg jadrrirglig bishrm wrijin bimii jabrgjee iebprnjin-shrt biujaprtrgjee Dioat. Oyat jayaa minogbat jadirg jaibipindig jajaa naa idminrgli bishrm.
54002007	Ooshrmda adoug jayerog ajuirgjee, jadirg idcuiprna aliglig cadajuirgjee nat judioota ishandiot jadwaorgjee naa moyerog ijetwin. Arnjri ajii-alircat Cristo-jaa ooshrmda rjet naa oodamog, yau ateeshauliprn.
54002008	Ooshrmda jajeu Dios carmdig nat epinolat wrijin brm-jaligui, calap cawrryrgjee Dioat cabigshayu jaapi-rrijet, ishan nrmijet, cabigshayu shancaujeeya.
54002009	Nat detpat, caladwi canawa cashiyui cajaa cataale cajaanjee ijeijet oje bicacouotni. Jashanjeira cajún catiquirgu rripoi cabigshayu calirglig cajaa nat oroconot, butpinot poi, dapyuiot poi, yuiot miibag-jaa poi,
54002010	Natjrí detpat, calatwi jadshiruugr cajaa cabigshayu ijei jalirr ijei caminrglig calat wrijin. Ojerawi idshir nat detpalat, nat caawawubrlat Dioat jashrt naa mii-rríprnjin wryu-tee.
54002011	Nat detpat caladwi jadshijui on-irigjet naa moyerog idjuirg culto-tee, jadwaorgjee ijeijet cajii-tee.
54002012	Yau jalirliprn detpalat cajuirglig nat mot yau detpalat icuiriprn iglesia-tee, ooshrt onda jateg-cuiri culto caminrgbat.
54002013	Dioat jarninrg jurgli Adán, oyat Eva jaminrg.
54002014	Yauli moweijinat teishaurliprn Adán, ooshrt jateijashaurg naa den, oyat japecado lig jajaa.
54002015	Ooshrt cajeijeiyawi nat detpat catrriot ijewet ijeijet, cajii calirgu Dios-jaa, jayii-caluugu ijet, ijei jaligu cabigshayu, bicacounogot jaligu poi, omya cashijeiya oje.
54003001	Rjeta naa oodamog, naajrí jajewe caijajeulig iglesia tepinot, jadjeuwi itrm mobeeb ijei.
54003002	Ooshrm naa iglesia ijewe jandawi ijei jasniminr, briat jainot shipin-shrt iebjet, jatrmwi ja-u. Janwi jashicou ishanyoiyi, bicacou poi japishicawaagjee wrijin bon ijeia jaliglig. Jan-wi epinot batjashitai ijaijet, japishijashiwaag poi Dios yerog jajuirglig.
54003003	Naa iglesia ijewe yau pai yu-jaluuliprn, rri-poi cadjamrndig, rri-poi molapwoo yii-jaluuglig brjashiri jadougu moteishauyu-jet, rri-poi boi japwoo ijanairig.
54003004	Janwi japishijashiwaa caijajeulig jaot-tepinot, jayerog cajuijee nat jatrríolat, caomjee jarca.
54003005	Naajrí japishishanwaji caijajeulig jaot tepinot, yauya-poi japishijashiwaaliprn Dios ot tepinot ijajeulig.
54003006	Jaishanquedrt jairirglig iglesia ijajeulig naa jujet iglesia-atwin, jaijashag-shrt janornjri jeirig wrijin brrt-shrt oje jalijani naa Dioat mamprndi moweijin.
54003007	Oyat nat Dios yerog shanjuwaorriot, caladawi jadshiruu ijeijet naa iglesia ijewe bijashini jaebyu cahiugu jajaa, bijashiruu moweijinat jateishaurgu oje yrriot teecashaurlauni caluugjee wabag-teja.
54003008	Ojera poi nat deaconoot, caladwi ijei cashiminr idduugjet wrijin, capishicawaagjee ijeinogota caliglig. Calatwi idshirninrr oje camojani cayerog cau-shrt, yau pai yii-caluuliprn, rri-poi calapwoo ibag brjashirii jadougu moteishauyu-jet.
54003009	Nat deaconoot calatwi japishicashiwaa ijeijet brjaliyu jaligu naa moyerog rjetwin Dioat irirgprn japishibiwaagli. Calatwi jashijeu jaapi-rririg cabigshayu.
54003010	Cadyacaluug brjaligu-caliglig Dios yerogjaa, rri-jaligu ieb yatairirglig cajaa cadyaulirg deaconoja caligjee.
54003011	Ojerapoi nat ca-ujut, calatwi ijei cashiminrg idduugjet wrijin, capishicawaagjee ijeinogota caliglig. Nat deaconoot ujut cayeshanbat brrt-jaa, yowan shanebit, cashirig dai-imogjet Dios yerog-jaa idminrgjee oje jamojani.
54003012	Oyat naa deacono jatrmwi ja-u, caijashijeu jatrriot ijeijet jaot tepinot poi.
54003013	Nat deaconoot ibeebet ijeijet Dioat ijeijetya cadcashiruu nat capinot, oyat cashirigya dai-imogjet calijani, oyat jijooligjetya jaicashipin naa moyerog idwaorg Jesucristo-jaa.
54003014	Mogwainia jajeu animnoglig yalica, ooshrt janagju yan naa papera,
54003015	japishimawaagjeeya bijáligu imashirg Dios ot tepinolat japrnpatuyaju ayuglig, ooshrm Dios pindawi naa iglesia. Oodawi jaiglesia tepinot jalirt dai-imogjet jayerog nam wryu-tee, ooshrm jajayrg carrirg cayerog nat jajewerat jadnamdig naa moyerog rjetwin.
54003016	Japishibiwaagwi ijeiya jaliglig naa moyerog ibiwaorg japaagshicomcug japishiiwaaglig, Oowi naa jajacambiarmdi bona jaligjee naa Dioat, oyat Espírituat jalirg japishicawaagjee ijeia jaliglig, oyat cadcaluug nat ángeleot, oyat jainot shicapin wrijin nat epinolat, oyat cajii calirg jajaa nat wryu tepinolat, oyat jajuimii quedyem morriyu-shrt jabatcatai Paraíso-teja.
54004001	Dumat naa Espíritu jamog ishalaligjet, janacatuya wryu beeyu jadshinarnnogya naa moyerog idwaorg nat ibagolat, jadjuijeeya nat mojiiot teeshauot, cayerog cawaorgjeeya nat demonioot.
54004002	Cayerog cashijuiya nat oiteprnogot teeshauot, nat jashanquedrriot jadjuirig naa Espíritu iyaad cajii-tee, ooshrmya cajuiyag shishaalat jayerog-shrt.
54004003	Caiwin cashishogya cauuliglig, oyat jaiwin capoishog cashrt itrmnog mowoug Dioat irirgprn mowouca, ijei cabrg quedyem jajaa nat jayerog waorlat, nat japishiwajalat naa moyerog rjet.
54004004	Ijeira wrijin naa Dioat iminrg biwouca, ooshrm yau jabiquedrliprn jabinamnog itrmnog, ooshrt jabiquedrg jabiwougu wrijin ijei bibrgquedyem Dioat jajaa.
54004005	Ooshrm ijei jashiminrgya birat Dios birmu jajaa, ooshrm ojerawi jamo birat naa bijri-Dios.
54004006	Cadmajuirgu bijrrot jajet naa moyeog ijei, ornda ibeepe ijeira mam Jesucristoat. Ooshrmda mamashiwairürg jajet naa moyerog iyawaorg malig-shrm jajaa naa ibijuirg.
54004007	Oyat jamacupoijui cayerog nat itepyaadprnotjin ojewitep, otpoi nat yowantep ebot boyequejetep. Ooshrt marnaujuirg mabishayu mawrryrgjee Dios-jaa.
54004008	Jajeirawi jaijeuu motaale wairügjee, ooshrt janomjri-jeirig jaijeuu Dios bigshayu wairüg-lig mojii-tee. Ooshrm Dios bigshayujet jabiquedrg biriglig ijeijet nam wryu-tee. Oyat jabigshayu bijiitee jadshirirgya birigjee jateeja naa wryu ibishiruugya shrnoja.
54004009	Rjetwinda naa moyerog, calatwi jadshiwaor wrijin.
54004010	Ooshrmda ibibeeb ebupaabicrt jabijuirglig. Bieb-catepduug jaieibitei-shrm jabiruuglig naa Dios ijug caijewe nat wryu tepinot cadjajeicon iebshrt nat cajii-rirt jajaa, cadjarrnogjee paraíso-teja.
54004011	Cadmaujuirg jadwaorgjee naa moyerog, cadmaucui idminrgjee oje jamojani.
54004012	Jamacupoirirt majaiyrg carrirglig bon-trta majuuligshrm, ooshrt ijei mauminrg caicaluugjee majet nat iglesia tepinolaí. Mauyaad ijeijet cayii-mauluug wrijin, majii maulirg ijeijet, jamaujeu jaapi-rriya jaliglig mabigshayu.
54004013	Dumat jajeimateibat arninoglig malica, Dios yerog mauleeg nat bijrrolat, cadmauwairürg jayerog-jet, cadmaujuirg ijeijet.
54004014	Mabigrricupoirig jashrt naa mabigshayu Espírituat ibrgprn man calap calirgbat majaa nat ansianoolat.
54004015	Jijogjeta jamaujeu jamaminrglig wrijin naa Dioat irirg jamaminrglig, jadduugjee wrijin brjaligu Dios bigshayu mindig majii-tee.
54004016	Jamacaluug brjaligu mabigshayu lig. Jamacaluug poi brjaligu cadmajuirglig jajeijee jayrglig wrijin. Maushog dai-imogjet wrijin Dios yerogjet. Jamaminrgu ojejri, ornda mamashijeicon ieb-shrt, oodyapoi nat jajuiyut man.
54005001	Jaimacupoipin jijogjet japecado naa quepaat ooshrt jamaupinrg yrmijetwi oje maíi pinrlauni. Oyat nat mot-trrlotju mauyaad calat oje mayaadauni mapedwalat.
54005002	Oyat nat detpat quepalaat cadmaupinrg oje jaipinrlauni maíin. Oyat mauyaad nat det-trdaalat oje mayaadauni majaadwalat.
54005003	Oyat cajrjja cadmaurg bonjin rriprnot uubiidot jajet naa idjeu.
54005004	Ooshrt naajri bonjin-rriprn trriotdig jajrdwat poi,calatwi japishicashiwaa ijei caminrg-jurglig caot tepinolat. Calatwi cajrrja cashirii caíijit caíinit poi jamii cabrgjee calat naa ijei caminrgprn calat cajushrmnogbat, ooshrm ijaijet Dioat caluug nat iminrt oje.
54005005	Oyat naa bonjin-rriprn ijet itrmtenogwi, jabigshayu jalirg Diosjaa, jaijarm jashrt wrgiei shairei poi.
54005006	Ooshrt naa bonjin-rripin itepboolrg jequewitep, jajajáirg jaaleatep, oowi ojera jatepdü irriprnjini jajujug-shicom.
54005007	Cadmaucui idminrgjeejqje amojani nat iglesia atwinot brrlat caipin-shrt iebjet.
54005008	Yau jaiigu brrt jajrrja carrliprn jajrrot queepaat iebot poi, oowiat jauprdig jashrt naa moyerog idwaorgli bŕn, oyat janornjri eberig cashrt nat Dios yerog shanwaorrirt.
54005009	Oowi catarn jrimaunaglig iglesia papera-tee cajrrja-cadirgjee nat bonjin-rriprnotjin sesenta-shrt aíŕo-bajaligot bon-shanshririiot.
54005010	Nat pishicawaagprnot ijei eaminrglig, nat catrriot bigshugr-ot cabat taiat iminyugot calica, cajrrja cart iglesia tepinot, caijewet itaabot o boirig-jaligui ijei.
54005011	Ooshrt rrira iglesia atwinolat ofrenda brglig calat nat bonjinrriprnot trrijudaatju, ooshrm cabigshayu cau jadjeu-shrmshri cabondiglíg.
54005012	Oyat capeeado lig cajaa cashanshoot-shrm dai-imogjet Cristo-jet oje camojani catestimonio-tee.
54005013	Oowi catepduug boglig moot-tojani, cajamaiat idbeebdig, oyat cayecatepwaabog brrt-jaa, oyat cayaad brrt ebyu-jaa, nat ishanjeyi moyaadu jajaa.
54005014	Ooshrmda jajeu casaja-cashririglig nat bonjin rriprnot det-trrijudaatju, catrriot bicashugrgjee, caicajeu ijeijet caot tepinot, bibalolat caipin-shrt iebjet nat iglesia tepinot.
54005015	Itrmnogot bonjin rriprnot cacatewat bishrt canogjee moweijin prna.
54005016	Oyat nat Dios yerog waort cajrrot-digu motjin rriprnot uubiidot, calatwi jadshibrr calat naa boiruudbr calat, iglesiaat jajrrja cadcarg-shrt ofrenda-jet.
54005017	Calatwi cajrrja cadcashirr nat iglesia ijewet ijeinogot, nat ishanjaabit cadcajuirglig caepinot naa moyerog ijeijet.
54005018	Ooshrm ojera jamo naa idnagprndi bŕn, jayei-shimacupoijiip jawoug-shrt naa ibeebrr man. Oyat jashrimog, molatwi jabeeb mii-ishibnr naa bon ibeepe molat.
54005019	Jayerog macupoijui naa iebjet imog ansiano-jaa icauolat jashanduutu ieb jaminrgli, o ipoiot poi.
54005020	Ooshrt nat irigot capecado-jaa jaimaupin calat naa ieb idminrg, jadjuijee wrijin nat iglesia tepinoíat, caomjee idminrglig oje calijani.
54005021	Dumat mashipinrg Dioat ijuijet,Biŕri Jesucristoat ijuijet poi, idjuijet poi nat ángeleot iinodigot. Cadmaucui wrijin idminrgjee qje naa inaalauni, Macupoiom brrt-shrt capecado jaipinjee.
54005022	Jamacupoirirt mogwaini ansianoja jaliglig caijeujee iglesia tepinot, bijashirii jadebrgu naa iglesia, brjashirii jaebyu liguya majaa jamalirg-shrmat jaijajeulig. Jamauluug mashrt wrijin naa imaminrg brjashirii jayrg ebuya.
54005023	Jaibagli manamdi shiig man, ooshrmda jamacupoiwo-qui rt-catrmtep, ooshrt jamauwog ishŕmjet pun-campog ishiig jadwrnjee manarnde.
54005024	Jabigtanshrcat caebyu nat itrmnogot ooshrmda japishiiwaagwi brjaliguya cashirig jajuprduju Dioat cajainot shipindig ebupaacacrtjeeya capecado-shrm. Ooshrt nat itrmnogot jabigtanshishrgya capecado Dioat cajainot shipinbatya.
54005025	Ojera poi dumat jaiquedrg jairuuglig wrijin naa ijei idminrg nat itrmnogolat. Yau jaligu jabiquedrliprn jabiruuglig idminrgprn dumat, boi wryulauya jabishiruugya wrijin, ooshrm jaishanquedrriya jaiijaandig oopegwi naa iiminrgprn.
54006001	Natjri ibeebet calatwi carg-cashibrr caŕriot bijashirii caŕriot yaadu iebjet cajri Dios-jaa.
54006002	Dios epinot jaligu nat caŕriot, yau jadquedrliprn cayerog cajaulig cajrrota calig-shrm jajaa naa moyerog idwaorg. Ooshrt caladawi idshinornjri beebr calat ijeijet ooshrm Dios yerog waorta calig nat ood-ibeebrgolat cajrrot yii-caluugprnota calig. Dumat cadmaupinrg ishalsüigjet jadminrgjee oje amojani.
54006003	Brrt ijuirgu boyeja jashrt naa moyerog ijei Birri Jesucristoat ibrgprn birat, jadshanjuirtu naa moyerog bibigshayu jawrryrgjee Dios-jaa,
54006004	oowi jajuituundig jaalei bigshayu-jet, oowi bicashancowiprnjin. Oowi idjeu janrmyaadig cajet nat iglesia tepinot. Jadirg caeb caluuyeglig, cauucacajeuyeg poi, cauubiid-cacauon.
54006005	Yau cajaapdiprn cacamrndig nat mot bigshayu tepjrmrlat. Yau japishicawaaíiprn jaicapindig moyerog ijetwin. Jaicashag jajeiwirig mopin iougu jajeí naa iiminrg Dios-jaa. Mamauwawug cashrt nat oitepdigot.
54006006	Rjeta ibishiougya ijei mii-rrijet bijii birirg-shrm Dios-jaa naa wryu dapwoo-shrt. Oola naa bibigshayu ijei ibishiougya Dios-shrt náijet bijii birirg-shrm jajaa.
54006007	Boiríg-shandidi ibirryug bipin bitrtbadi wryu biruugjee. Boirig shanpoiritya ibishirmog bipin binogbatya naa wryu-shrt.
54006008	Ooshrt jaligu birat ishrmwi biwoug büapwoo poi nam wryu-tee, jajeitogwi birat birigjee ijáijet.
54006009	Oyat nat jajewet wooligota caliglig, yau jadquedrliprn cashoglig jashrt naa jet-moweijinat cateeshaurg. Cabigshayu jajiip jajet naa boitep jet-canai, naa jalirrm caluuglig capecado-teja nat mot, carmdrgjeeya Dios-shrt.
54006010	Naajri jawoo-jewe ibagjet, jabigshayu iinaiprnjin shiminya jajii-tee oje iebprnjin tatshutni. Jadshirirgya jadminrglig wrijin ieb jadougjeeya naa jet-janai. Oyat nat itrmnogot jadnarnnocat naa moyerog idwaorgli brn jaicanai-shrm calapwoo ibagjet, oyat cajiinog ealapwoo-shrm, cabigshayu camrm-rg jajet naa iribrg calat.
54006011	Dumat mam bon Dios pin, maucuut jashrt wrijin naa cateeshaurr nat epinot. Jijogjeta jamaujeu ijei maminrglig oiirigwi. Mabigshayu mauwrryrg Dios-jaa, majii-maulirg jajaa ijeijet, jayiimauluug maushog dai-imogjet jajet, jaimacupoishaat japishimawaaglig brrt shrt.
54006012	jamauminrg jijogjet naa moprtooyu moweijin ubata jajet naa moyerog ibiwaorg. Jamawaorg man naa wryu ishanbeji, ooshrm Dioat maágcat testimonio ijei imapinbat ibagolat ijuijet brjaligu majii malirgli Cristo-jaa.
54006013	Dumat mashipinrg Dioat ijuijet jalirr cajuglig wrijin, jadjuijee poi naa Cristoat, naa jatestirnonio iipini jaalei-jaa Ponsio Pilatoat.
54006014	Dumat jamaujeicon ijeijet naa moyerog Birriat ibrgprn man. Jajrimacupoiwao mot yerog-jet, yau ishrmjet brjashiriya mainot shijapinuya iebjet jayugbatya Biŕri Jesucristo.
54006015	Jabishiruugya Cristo jayaa-minogbatya jayuglig, ooshrm oojaligwi itrmwi Bijriwairüg ijei iwairiig. Oolawi Cajriwairüg nat iwairügot wrijin. Oolawi Carri nat carriot wrijin.
54006016	Oowi naa ishanquedrri jarririg, naa irig iwrg-tee iishanquedrrí jainarglig. Yauju itrm bonat jaluuliprn, yau poi jaiquedrliprn jairuuglig. Biratwi bishiom jarea, jabijeu Bijriwairiica jaliglig oiiricawiat, Amén.
54006017	Oyat cadmaupinrg nat wooligot naa wryu-tee, jaicashag-shrt cajeirig brrt-shrt. Cadmaupinrg cajii cashandirtjee jajaa naa mowoo ibeg-yawanya, ooshrt jajeicateijee ijei Dios-jet. Naa Ijug jalirr birat ijei ipegjet birigjee ijeijet.
54006018	Cadmaucui ijei caminrgjee janomjri bajaligjeeya ijei-diglig calat. Cadmaucui cajawrgjee jadbrtegjee uubiidolat naa shrm-cauubiid.
54006019	Ijei caminrgu uubiidolatjri, jashiribrgya calat naa ijei ishanbeji, jashiribrgya calat caliiriprn iishanquedrri jainamdig. Oyat jashiribrgya calat wryu ishanbeji.
54006020	Dumat mam Timoteo, jaimaujeu ijeijet naa mobeeb Dioat ibrgprn jamaminrglig Jamacupoijui calat cayaadbat boyequejetep oitepdig poi, caacamrnyegbat poi jajaa naa moyerog jaa-cateishau jaicashag-shrm Dioat jalirglig japishicawaaglig brrt-shrt.
54006021	Itrmnogolat jajuiat naa oodcamog cabigshayu-jetep nat oitepdigot, ooshrmda cabiguiat jashrt naa moyerog ijetwin ibiwaorg. Oyat dumat jabijeu Dioat ijei dirglig majii-tee ijáijet maligjee. Amén.
55001001	Am Pablo, Jesucristo icuiprnda am oje Dioat jalirlauni, ooshrm jaijapin calat wryu ishanbeji nat ishogolat dai-imogjet Jesucristo-jet.
55001002	Janag man naa papera mam awá Timoteo ijeuprn. Jajeu Dioat jalirglig man ijei, jajeu mauubiid jaluuglig, jajeu madirglig mabigrririgjee jajet wrijin ieb-shrt naa Bií Dios, oo-poi Birri Jesucristo.
55001003	Ijei abrg majaa oiirigwi wryu shitojani shairei poi Dios apinrgbat, naa ood-ibeebrcat abigshayu ijeijet calijani nat ajuprtuwinot
55001004	Oiirigla jayeawaaglig bijafiguli maquiglig ashrm, ooshrmda jajeu maluuglig ajii jáijeeya ipegjet.
55001005	Oyat jayeapoiwaag brjaligu majii malirglig rjet jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg. Naajrí maán Loida, oopoi maiin Eunice, cajii calirgjurg Cristo-jaa, oyat mam-poi majii malirg oje calijani.
55001006	Ooshrmda mapinrg, jamaubrtrg naa drr Dioat irirgprn majii-tee maiabenisiargbat alap-jet.
55001007	Ooshrm Dioat jashanbri birat bibigshayu iomprnjin, ooshrt jadbrg birat bibigshayu iwairüg bicacou, naa jalirr brrt yii-biruuglig.
55001008	Ooshrmda maucupoiyii Birri jainot shimapinjee ijeijet, Maucupoiyig presoja aligshrm am Birri-shrm, ooshrt majuiculuulrg ebupaamapoicrtjee jashrm naa moyerog jet-bidjajeicon ieb-shrt oje jabigshayuat jalirlauni.
55001009	Dioat bijeiconat jashrt naa paacashicrtya capecado-shrm. Oolawi biájaat bidjawawugjee japinita birigjee wrijin biebyu-shrt. Dioat bishanáat ijei biminrg-shrm, ooshrt jadjeu-shrm bidjaáglig biyü jaluug-shrm Jesucristo-shrm jajuijawrgli wryu juprduju japishijawaag bidjaág shirigya.
55001010	Dumat jadirg japishibiwaagli biyii-jaluuglig jadcui-shrm naa Bijeicono Jesucristo, naa janama morriyu bishrt. Oyat jajet naa moyerog ijei jadirg japishibiwaaglig bijii ishanbeji-jaa, naa jashanquedrri jarmdrglig idshibrgya birat.
55001011	Dioat aoug jaiapinjee naa moyerog, adcui cadajuirgjee nat judioota ishandiot.
55001012	Oyat jayerog shrmda adirr ebupaa-acrdig oiirigwi, ooshrt yau auuyüriprn ooshrm japishiawaagwi Cristo, naa-jaa ajii-alirg. Oyat japishiawaagwi jadquedrglig adjeicondig wrijin ieb-shrt ata-on jayugcaya oo-naa wryu jeibitei.
55001013	Jesucristo jetwinda mam, ooshrmda mauiig dai-imogjet jajaa naa ijei jet-majuirg, jamauwaorg ijeijet, cayii-mauluug poi bijrrot.
55001014	Jajet naa Espíritu Santo, jaimaujeu moteishauyu-shrt naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn jamajuirglig.
55001015	Japishimawaagwi adnamnocat wrijin nat Asia tepinolat, ooda capeit nat Fijelo, Hermójene poi.
55001016	Oyat jajeu uubiidjet Biŕriat caluuglig nat Onesíforo ot tepinot, ooshrm jaibagli jadrryubrrligli an naa boiruudbrg an. Yau jauuyüriprn jajrrja adrglig am idjiiprn cadenaot-jet Cristo-shrm. '
55001017	Oyat jaminogbat Roma-tee naa Onesíforo, jijogjeta adjeubog ata-on atairürcawi.
55001018	Ooshrm jajeu Biŕriat jauubiid duuglig oo wryulauya ijei yuulau, ooshrm japishimawaagwi brjaliguli jaitog bijrrja bidjarrligli Efeso-tee.
55002001	Mam awá, mamauwairürg Jesucristo bigshayu iwairüg-jet, naa idbrg birat birig-shrm dai-imogjet jajet.
55002002	Oyat naa moyerog imajuiprn ajet cajewalee nat ibagot jajuiyut, cadmaupinrg nat mot ijeinogot, nat japishiwajat brrt cajuirgligya poi.
55002003	Jajricamaucou naa paamacrt oje Cristo isodawa ijeini.
55002004	Yau itrm sodawaat jajiipdiprn jaleiwia-jet sodawaja jaligbat, ooshrt bigshayu rrijeta jalii jajeijatei idminrgjee oje jacomandanteat jacuirauni.
55002005	Ojera poi naa imaan jadougjee naa regalo idirgprn jan naa iminog-jurg. Yau jaligu jamaandiprn oje camojani jan boirig shanditya idshibrg jan.
55002006	Oyat naa jabeepe jatim, ooya japin shiougjurm cajuicashuuliprn-tee.
55002007	Jayeimawaag jajaa naa comparación oodamog man. Biŕriya jashirirr japishimawaaglig brjaliyu jaligu wrijin.
55002008	Jayeimawaag Jesucristo-jaa naa David jriwai juimigprn morriyushrt. Oolawi naa moyerog ijuirg Cristo-jaa jet-Dioat bijeicon ieb-shrt.
55002009	Dumat ebupaa-acrt jashrm naa moyerog ijei, adjiip cadena-jet oje cadcajiipdauni iebnogprnotjin, ooshrt jadshanquedrt Dios yerog cajiipdig.
55002010	Jashrm naa moyerog jajricaacou wrijin naa paa-acrt, japoirnbrgjeeya calat ijei nat Dioat iougprnolat, ebupaacacrt-shrtya capecado-shrm ooshrt cadjashiwrryrgya jayán ishanbejija brtbrtirigteja cajet nat ishogot dai-imogjet Jesucristo-jet.
55002011	. Rjeta naa oodamog, jarriadu bishrt bijuuyu bŕnwinjin Cristojet cruza-jaa, bishijugyawi biriglig jajet.
55002012	Ebupaabicrtu Cristoshrrnjri, bidjashirirgya epinot ibijeujeeya jajet. Ooshrt jainot shibijaanu, bijainot shijashipoi-jaanya bol wryu-lauya Bií Dios-shrt.
55002013	Rjet-shanditu naa bitestimonio oodbimog jan, rjeta naa oodjashirnogya birat, ooshrm Dioat jashanquedrri jainot shijajaandig Rjetwina jaliglig.
55002014	Jamaulirg jayecawaaglig naa oodarnog. Cadrnaupinrg Dios-jaa, caqueetjee caacamrnyeglig jequewitep Dios yerog-jaa. Boirica shandita oürgu, oowi cabigshayu jaebrglíg nat jajuiyulat cacamrndig.
55002015	Jamaujuirg ijeijet. Jijogjeta jarnaujeu ibeepe ijeiya maliglig Dioat iruuca boirig-shrm shanditjee mauuyii, ooshrt japishirnawaagjee jamajuirglig ijeijet naa moyerog rjetwin.
55002016	Jamacupoijui cajet cayaadbat boyequejetep, ooshrm nat iyaalot oje caluucat caebyu-teja cayaadbat ojewitep.
55002017	Oyat naa moteishauyu idjuirg oowi janeirüglig cajewalee nat epinot cabigshayu jaebrgjee oje buán duuglauni momaa-teja motaale jaebrgjee wrijin. Ojeriwi moteeshauyuat carr nat Himeneo, Fileto poi.
55002018	Jadyrrg jadwaorglig naa moyerog rjetwin, cabiguwi jashrt. Camog jawucata mojuimiglig morriyu-shrt. Ojera caboglig, epinot bigshayu cateu jashrt naa moyerog ibiwaorg.
55002019	Ooshrt Dioat jabrg birat jet-bishog dai-imogjet, oola jayerog iishanquedrri jaicambiarglig. Ojera, jamo jet-japishibiwaaca rjet jaliglig jayerog, Biŕriat capishiwaagwi nat japinit. Oyat jashrimog, wrijin nat irigot Cristo tam-jaa caladwi caacashiwawuu jashrt naa ieb idminrgli.
55002020	Omdawi moshuai-tee cabag nat capinit oolot, cairuug oroconot palataconot poi. Ooshrt cai-poi iruug nat punconot shouconot poi. Itrmnogot capet tee-jalig mübag, oyat itrmnogot tee-jalig brt-tep.
55002021	Naa jajewe Biŕriat jajuituunrglig ijeijet oje jajuituunrlauni tasa orocon miibag-jet, jandawi jabigshayu jashijeicon wrijin ieb-shrt. Biŕri jetwin jaapi-rria jaligjee. Oyat jadquedrg jadminrglig wrijin ijei.
55002022	Maucuut jashrt naa ieb idjeu jadminrglig nat mot-trrlolat. Jijogjeta jamaujeu mabigshayu ijei, maulig dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg, cayii mauluug brrt, mabigrriculig wrijin ieb-shrt cajet nat cairmrt Biŕri-jet cabigshayu jaapi-rrijet.
55002023	Cayerog macupoiwaort madrmu boitep moyerog-jaa, nat jajewet cayaadtepdig. Mamdawi japishiwaja naa jalirr moimrnyegee Dios yerog-jaa.
55002024	Naa ibeepe Biŕriat yau jadquedrliprn jamrndig, ooshrt ishan-nnnijeta cadjaluu wrijin. Jandawi japishijashiwaa epinot jajuirglig, janwi cajrícajashicou prnpatjet.
55002025	Naa Birri-jetwin cadjashipinrg ymijetwi nat jabata-jarg, jadjeujee Dioat cabigshayu cambiarglig cajii-shŕmjee capecado iyeicawaaglig japishicawaagjee poi naa moyerog rjetwin,
55002026	cacuutjee moweijin wabag-shrt, on presoja cadcarca jadminrgjee oje jadjeulauni.
55003001	Oyat mandawi japishimashiwaag jashiebya naa wryu janacaduya jabeeglig,
55003002	ooshrm caalei-jaaya cabicashitepshaa nat moolat, palata yü-cashiruugya calapwoo ibagya poi, jadjeu cajeirig brrt-shrt, cayaad iebjet Dios-jaa, cari yerog cashishanjuiya, caíin poi, cauubiid-cashiconya nat ijei-minrí calat, catamshicayoi nat ijei-brt Dioat.
55003003	Yauya epinot yii-cashiruuliprn, yauya cauubiid-cashiruuliprn, yauya cadcashijeicondiprn brrt-jet, cateeshishauya cajaa, idshiminrgya boirig jaligutep oje iigprnotjini, iyiijetya cadcashirirr brrlat ebupaacrtjee, cabata cadcashirgya ijeinogot.
55003004	Ieb caminrg jaanajet cajrrolat, jadshijeuya cajuprtawinota canomjririglig, jayii-caluug caalei bigshayutep, jadshinomjrijeuya cacajáirglig caaleatep Dios-shrt.
55003005	Boiratep naa culto idminrg Dioat. Yau jadirliprn Dioat cabigshayu jacambiargjee jabigshayu iwairiigjet. Durnat mam, mamauwawug cashrt nat oiirigot.
55003006	Ooda capet nat irnugot epinot ot-teja cateecashaurgjee nat detpat bicashancowit juituunot capecado-jet, nat jaminrt wrijin boirig jaligutep oje jadirlauni cabigshayu iebprnjinat.
55003007	Oürig cacajuirglig, boirigjet jaligutep, ooshrt yau jadquedrliprn japishicawaaglig brjaliyu jaligu naa moyerog rjetwin.
55003008	Oje cabata Moisés carjaniri nat ijiigolat Janes Jambres poi, ojera poi durnat cabata jadrglig naa moyerog nat mot bigshayu tiigot. Oocatepdig, yau jaiquedrliprn jaijuirig naa oodcamog jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg.
55003009	Ooshrt yauya cadcashitairürliprn ibagjet epinot cayerog juiyut, ooshrm capishicashiwaagya nat epinolat boiyeja jatepdiglig cayerog. Ojeri poi capishicawaaglig cajaa nat ieauot jabata jardi Moisés.
55003010	Ooshrt mam, jamawaorcat ijeijet naa ijuirg, jamaluucat bijaligu aliglig naa wryu-tee. Japishimawaagwi naa ijeu jaminrglig, japishimawaagwi brjaligu ajii-alirglig, jajricaacou naa paa-acrt poi. Japishirnawaagwi cajii aluuglig brrt, dai-imogjet ashoo poi.
55003011	Japishimawaagwi bijaligu cabata adrglig, brjaligu poi ebupaaacrdig, oyat jajricaacouli adirgbat ebupaa-acrdig poi Antioquíatee, Iconia-tee poi, Listra-tee poi, ooshrt Biŕriat ashiuat cashrt wrijin.
55003012	Rcaji, cabata-cadcashirgya wrijin nat jajewet cacawawuglig capecado-shrt Jesucristo-pinita caligjee.
55003013	Oyat nat iebnogprnotjin, teeshauot, jadshinomjri-minrgya caebyu, brrt teecapatjrishaurg, oyat nat brrlat cateeshaurrshog poi.
55003014	Ooshrt mam, maulig dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog jaa-mamajuirg, naa-jaa majii-malirg, ooshrm japishimawaagwi brr-jaliguli majuirr.
55003015	Bŕn trriwaiya majuligbat dumat-patjee japishimawaagwi naa Dios yerog idnagprn jalirr japishimawaaglig majeijeeya jashrt naa paacashicrtya capecado-shrm majii-rnalirgshrm Jesucristo-jaa.
55003016	Dios licatwinda wrijin naa moyerog idnagprn papera-uu, oola jet-Dioat bijuirca, jet-bidjapinrca poi biebyu-jaa japishibiwaagjee biriglig ijeijet biebyu-shrt,
55003017	cabigshayu jeijeeya nat Dios epinot, japishicawaagjee ijei caminrglig wrijin.
55004001	Dumat mashipinrg ajii-teat Dioat ijuijet, jadshipoijui naa Birri Jesucristoat, naa ishiyugya iwairüg-jet cainot shijapinjee nat ijugot nat-poi irriprnot, Cajriwairüca jalig-shrmya wrijin.
55004002	Jamaujuirg jijogjet naa moyerog oiirigwi. Majuiculuulrg jaimapinjee Dios yerog brm jaligui manoo cajewalee nat cajiirirt jajaa, o cajewalee nat cajii-shandirriot jajaa poi. Jamaulirg japishicawaagjee ijetwina jaliglig naa moyerog, cadmaupinrg caebyu canamnogjee. Cadmaujuirg moyerog yrmijetwi, ishan-nnnijet.
55004003	Cadmaujuirg jijogjet dumat, ooshrm boi wryulauya jadshishanjuiya naa moyerog ijetwin, ooshrt cacashiágya caliea cadcajuirgjee naa-shrm idjeutep jadjuirig.
55004004	Cashitewugya jashrt naa moyerog ijetwin jadwaorgjee wrijin naa moyerog mot bigshayu-teat iyrg.
55004005	Ooshrt mam Timoteo, maulig dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog ijei pishirnawaag, jajricamaucou naa paamacrt, cadmauág epinot Cristo-lica jayerog-jet cadmajeiconjee ieb-shrt cadjárrnogjee shrnoja. Jamauminrg ijeijet wrijin naa Biŕríat minrg-cui man.
55004006	Dumat amjri, ayaa-minocat adrrirgjee, amaa alirgjee Dios-jaa oje ofrendani. Ayaa minocat adshiujee ataale-shrt anogjee shrnoja.
55004007	Jaquedrcat jaminrglig naa moprtoyu ijei moweijin ubata, jaquedrcat anoglig nam wryu-tee, jawaorcat ijeijet naa moyerog Birri-iaa.
55004008	umat jajeiatei jaluuglig naa ijei Biŕriat ishibrgya an alig-shimat dai-imogjet jayerog-jaa. Amat shanwiritya naa ijei, ooshrt calatya-poi wrijin nat jajeiteiolat jayug shririg jayii caluugshrm.
55004009	Dumat mauyug alica mogwaini,
55004010	ooshrm adnamnocat naa bijrr Demasat jayii jaluugshrm naa wryu, bŕn janog Tesalonica-teja. Oyat naa Cresente, bŕn janog niti Galacia-teja, oyat Tito nog Dalmasia-teja.
55004011	Oowi naa Lucas ijuulig ajet, ooshrmda jamaujeu Marcos, jamaurryug alica mayugbat nani, jadquedrg ajrrja-adrglig jajaa naa ibibeeb Dios-jaa.
55004012	Oyat naa Tíquico, bŕn jacuinogli Efeso-teja.
55004013	t mayuulauya alica jamaurryug an aruana inamyugprn Troasa-tee jaot-tee naa Carpo. Jamaurryubrg poi an alibroot, oyat poi nat apaperaat cadmaurryubrg an, ooshrm cadanomjri-jeu jashrt naa iribrg an.
55004014	Oyat naa Alejandro cobre beepe, ieb jaminrg an ipegjet. Biŕriya jamii-shibrm naa idminrg an.
55004015	poi jamauluug mashrt naa bon ooshrm jijogjet jabata jadrg naa moyérog ibijuirg.
55004016	Bŕn ainot shiapin-jurgbat nat iwairügolat, brr-shandit ajrrjaarm, adnamnog wrijin, ooshrt jashanjeu Dioat cainot shipindig jashrm naa idminrg an.
55004017	Oolawi Biŕri ajnja ann. Awairiiyu jabrg jayerog shiapinjee nat judioota-ishandiolat wrijin, jadjuijee naa moyerog jet-Dioat bijeicon ieb-shrt. Ojerawi Biŕriat ir adshiujee cacooleat nat yoodanot inrmnogot.
55004018	Oyat Biŕriat ajushiuya wrijin ieb-shrt, oyat adshijeiconya aligjeeya jaepinot ijajeuliprn-tee shrnoja. Ijei bibrg jan oiiricawiat, Amén.
55004019	Dumat memoria bibrrnog naa Priscaat, Aquüaat poi, oolat poi nat Onesíforo ot-tepinolat.
55004020	Oyat naa Erasto jajuulig Corinto-tee, oyat naa Trófimo jaliircat Mileto-tee jataap-shrmdi.
55004021	Oyat mam, mauyug álica mogwaini rtyrg juprtuju. Naa Eubulo memoria jabrryu man, oje poi Prudente, Lino poi, Claudia poi, wrijin poi nat bijrrot.
55004022	Dumat jajeu Biŕri Jesucristo shoglig majet. Jajeu ijei jalirglig majii-tee naa bijri Dioat yajáijeeyá yaliglig wrijin yam, Amén.
56001001	Am Pablo, ibeepe Dioat, Jesucristoat icuiprnda arn cadarrnogjee jalica nat Dioat iágprnot, cajú calirgjee jajaa, japishicawaagjee naa moyerog rjetwin cabigshayu cambiarm Dios-jaa.
56001002	Japishicawaagjee poi jajeicateirig naa wryu ishanbeji oodjamog birat naa Dios teeshanshauwi. Wryu-jaminrg juprduju jaijapin jajaa naa idshirirbrgya birat.
56001003	Oyat dumat Dioat jalirg japishicawaaglig jajaa jajet naa moyerog juju idirg jajuirglig naa Dios bijeicono.
56001004	Dumat papera anag man Tito, mam atrri rjet jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg. Jajeu Dioat majáirglig, jajeu mauubiid jaluuglig, jajeu jadirglig mabigrririgjee jajet wrijin íeb-shrt naa Bií Dios, oopoi naa Birri Jesucristo Bijeicono.
56001005	Bŕn malirgli maliglig ashrt ipom-jaa jatam Creta iamaminrgjee naa ibishanju-minrriri. Mapoi-cuiri ansianoot mahrgjee wrijin iglesia-tee moyan-tojani oje amojaniri brn.
56001006	Nat ansianoot calatwi ijei cashiminr, brr-shanditjee japishiwaja cajaa ieb. Cadmaulirg ansianoota nat ujutwi-tnnnogot, nat catrriot juirt Dios yerog cawaorgjee, brjashirii boi mogu iigprnotjinda catrriot nat iglesia ijewet. Ooshrt ishan-nrmijeta caíi yerog cawaorr.
56001007	Naa iglesia iinodig caijajeu Dios epinot ooshrmda janwi ijei jaminr idduugjet wrijin. Yau jadquedrliprn idrninrglig oje jabigjashaalauni brrt jajrrot-shrt. Ooshrt jadpoijui calat bijaligu cabishayu lig brjashirii cadjanrmrgu. Naa iglesia ijewet yau jawondiprn, rri-poi japrrtoglig boi-jet, rri-poi janairig molapwoo ibagjet brjashirii moteeshauyu-jet jadougu. jaluug wrijin naa ijei idminrg otpoi nat ijeinogot. Yau jadquedrliprn jayowan ebdig cajet boyequejetep, ooshrt jadshijeu jabigshayu ijei Dios pina jaligjee rjet. Janwi japishijashiwaa jaiwin jashoglig jabigshayu wrijin iebprnjin-shrt.
56001009	Janwi jashishoo dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog rjetwin ibijuirg. Oyat nat jabata jart, janwi japishijashiwaa on cadjarglig japishicawaagjee ijeta jaliglig naa moyerog oodjamog.
56001010	Cabagla nat Dios yerog shanwaorriot, ijet ibagot capet nat judioot cayaad moyerog mii rriprnjin-jet cateecashaurgjee nat epinot.
56001011	Biradwi on cadbishirr cadcateu-shrt bishrt ibogot epinot caot tepinot poi. Epinot cajuirg palata caougjee cashrt moteeshayu-jet.
56001012	Itrm capei profeta ipom Creta-atwin, ojera jamo jayan couotjaa, cateishau oiirig nat Cretaot, ojera calii jrrlugot inrmotni. Jadjeu cayewairig ibagjet ooshrt cajarnai idbeebdig.
56001013	Rjeta naa oodjamog cajaa, ooshrmda cadmaupinrg jijogjet caligjee dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg,
56001014	cayerog cajuishrt nat judioot cabigshayutep juirt, nat-poi mot catewet jashrt naa moyerog rjetwin.
56001015	Natjri bigshayu jaapishanbajit, jaapishanbajinira iduuglig wrijin. Ooshrt nat bigshayu jaapibagot, jaapibagnira iduuglig wrijin ooshrm jaapibagprnjinda cabigshayu nat Dios yerog snanjuiyit. Oyat jaapibagprnjinda poi naa mojiijin iyaad cajii-tee.
56001016	Japishiawaaglawi Dios camog, ooshrt jajet naa idrninig jadirg japishibiwaaglig yau japishicawaaliprn rjet ooshrm caeb caluug brrt. Yau jadjeuliprn idminrglig oje Dios mojani, yau jadquedriiprn ijei caminrglig, yau ishrmjet.
56002001	Wrijin naa imajuirg, mandawi jamashijuir ijeijet oje jamojani naa moyerog rjetwin.
56002002	Cadmaupinrg nat mot quepaat cashanwonjee, rri-poi cayowan-ebdig boyequejetep, ooshrt cabigcashagjee ishalalig-jet oje bicacouotni cadcaluugjee ijeijet wrijin. Canwi cashishoo dai-imogjet jajaa naa moyerog ibiwaorg, caladwi brrt yücashiruu, ishan-nrmijeta cajricaacashicon wrijin.
56002003	Ojera-poi nat detpat quepalaat, calatwi cashiyaad ijeijet caornshrm Dios rca, cashanyaadjee boyequejetep, cashanwonjee poi, ijei caminrgjee caicaluugjee nat brrlat cajet.
56002004	Nat detpat quepalalat cadcajuirgjee detpat trrijulotju cayii caluugjee camot catrriot poi,
56002005	cabigcashagjee ishalalig-jet, cashanütjee, jaiwin cashogjee cabigshayu cataale poi wrijin boitep-shrt, caot iicajeujee ijeijet, ijei caminrg calat wrijin, camot yerog cajuijee bijashirii boitep camogu jajaa naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprn birat nat jayerog shanwaorrirt.
56002006	Ojera poi cadmawairürcalii nat mot trrijulotju cabicashagjee ishalaligjet oje bicacouotni.
56002007	Oyat mam, ijei mauminrg caicaluugjee majet. Macupoiyoi cadmajuirgbat, ooshrt mauyaad ishalaligjet majii-teat.
56002008	Cadmaujuirg moyerog ijeijet, boi shanyaatjee iebjet bijaa, cauuyigjee nat cabata mart.
56002009	Oyat nat ibeebet cadmaupinrg camot yerog cajuijee ijeijet, jadminrgjee oje jamojani jajaijee cadjaluuglig cayerog cawaoryegshrt cajet.
56002010	Cadmaupinrg caŕri teecashaurg-shrt cabeebjet ooshrt jadirg caŕriot japishiwaaglig rjet jaliglig cabigshayu cayerog poi, japishicawaagjee ijeiya jaliglig naa ibijuirg jajaa naa Dios Bijeicono. Jajaibitai jawondig shrnoat naa Bijeicono
56002011	Dioat jalircat jabiruuglig naa idminrgprn calat nat wryu tepinolat cayii jaluugshrm. Naa jet-bidjajeicon Cristo-jet, cadjaougjee ieb-shrt cadjarmogjee paraíso-teja nat wryu tepinot.
56002012	Naa ijei idminrg birat bidjajuirg jabinamnogjee biebyu, bibigshayu bŕnwinjin poi jalirr bitaale bijairglig. Bidjajuirg birigjee ijeijet naa wiyu-tee, japishibiwaagjee jaibijeulig bibigshayu bitaale poi wrijin ieb-shrt.
56002013	Oyat bidjajuirg jajeibiteijee jabiruuglig naa ijei oodjamogh birat, naa ishiyqgya shrnoat oje drrbrtni, naa bijri-Dios iwairüg, naa Jesucristo Bijeicono.
56002014	Jajeibitei jabiruuglig naa jaalirrli jadrrirgli bishrm bimiiiabrg biujaprtrgjee Dioat wrijin ieb-shrt, jadirgjee jaapi rririg bibigshayu japinita birigjee, ijei biminrgjee bijii-teat.
56002015	Dumat cadmaupinrg wrijin epinot jajet naa oodamog. Cadmawairürg cashogjee dai-imogjet Dios yerog-jaa. Macupoiom cadmapinrglig jadnamnogjee naa ieb idminrg. Jamacupoirirt boirig jaligu jalirr majaiyeg carrirgjee.
56003001	Jamaulirg jadjuirig gobierno yerog, nat poi jaiwin-shoot ieb biminrglig, cajawrgjee jadminrglig wrijin ijei.
56003002	Cadmaupinrg ieb íicapin-shrt brrt-jaa, cashan-nrmjee cacaluuyeglig, cajricacacoujee nat epinot wrijin, cayaadjee wrijin yrmijetwi brjashirii brrt bigshayu caeb-rgu.
56003003	Bŕndi bidu poi bicashancowidi. Dios yerog bishanwaordi, bibiguwiri biboglig, bibigshayu bŕnwinat presoja-birgli jabiminrgjeeri wrijin boirig jaligutep ibijeuli. Bibotogniri boyequejetep oje ugprnotjini, birigli wrijin iebprnjin-jaa, jaibinairi brrt pin, binrmch, bieb bimuyegli.
56003004	Oyatjri naa Dios bijeicono jadirg jabiruuglig naa ijei idminrg cayii jaluug-shrm nat wryu tepinot.
56003005	Yau bidjajeicondiprn ijei biminrg-shrm, ooshrt bidjajeicon ieb-shrt japinita birigjee biuubiidjaluugshrm. Bibigshayu jacambiarg jajujujet Espíritu Santo-jet.
56003006	Dioat jabrcat birat naa Espíritu Santo ipegjet bidjajeicon-shrm biebyu-shrt naa Jesucristoat.
56003007	Oyat Cristo-shrm Bií-Dioat biruug oje ijeinogotni biyü jaluugshrm japinita birigjee, jajeibiteijee jabiruuglig naa wryu ishanbeji.
56003008	Rjeta naa moyerog oodamog, ooshrmda jajeu cadmapinrglig jijogjet idminrgjee oje amojani, jadjeujee ijei carninrglig cajii-teat nat cajiirírlat Dios-jaa. Ijeira naa moyerog oodamog, ooshrm jajeiwi jadwaorgu wrijin caligjee ijeijet.
56003009	Ooshrt jamacupoijui nat caamrnrlat caloomjinot-shrm cacostumbre bŕn-winjin shrm poi. Boirica shandita jaiminr ojewitepda cayaad.
56003010	Om-jaligu boirii itrrn moyerog waorr boyeja Dios yerog-shrt, naa jajewe brrt bigshayu jawawuglig jaalei yerog-jaatep, jamaupinrg jaquetjee itrrnjet o icaujet poi. Oyat jadshanjuibrtu manjri jamauyrrg yajuibeenprn-shrt.
56003011	Japishirnawaagwi jabigshayu tüglig naa bon casheupaya cashrt nat iglesia-tepinot, boitepda oo, jajatep-narn jaaleat jajet naa ieb idrninrg.
56003012	Dumat cadacui malica nat bijrrot Artemas Tíquico poi. Oyat mauyucat alica mogwaini Nicopoli-teja, ooshrm jajeu aliglig jajan idyrgnom.
56003013	Jajrrja jarnaurg ijeijet naa abogado Zenas, oo-poi Apolo, canogjee ijeijet caviaje-tee. Jamaubrg calat jet-canog yawan, boiruudjeeya juirürbrg calat.
56003014	Oyat nat bijrrot iglesia tepinot jamauürg ijei caminrgjee nat uubidolat caicashag-shrt caaleat-tep brrtshrt.
56003015	Wrijin nat ajetwinot memoria cacui man. Oyat jaimaupin calat amemoria nat bijrrot biyii-rujulat jajaa naa jaa-bijü birirg. Jajeu Dioat ijei dirglig yajii-tee yajáijeeya yaliglig wrijin, Amén.
57001001	Am Pablo, presoja idrgprnda am Jesucristo-shrm. Bijrr Timoteo-jet janag man naa papera, mam ibijeuprn Filemón, mam bijrr jajaa naa ibibeeb.
57001002	Memoria bipoi cui nat iglesia tepinolat cajuiberlat maot-tee, memoria poi jere bijrrlaat Apia, Aquipoat poi, naa bijrrja-birm moprtooyu biminrgjee moweijin ubata.
57001003	Jajeu Dioat jalirbrglig yan ijei, jajeu yadirglig yabigrririgjee wrijin ieb-shrt naa Bii-Dios, oopol Birri Jesucristo.
57001004	Oiiriglawi ijei abrglig Dioat mayeiawaagbat aiarmbat jajet,
57001005	ooshrm mainot ajui jayii maluug Birri Jesús ijeijet, jayerog mawaorg poi, cayii-maluug poi wrijin nat Dioat iwawugprnot japinita caligjee.
57001006	Dios arm cajaa nat cajiirirt jajaa matestimonio cajuibatdi, japishicawaabat naa ijei iribrg birat Jesucristo-jaa.
57001007	Ajii-jái ipegjet ajrr, biyii-maluugshrm ijeijet. Oyat ijáijeta poi mayecawaag nat Dios pinirat.
57001008	Ooshrmda jajeu jamaminrbrglig an naa irm mashrt. Cristoat icuiprnda am ooshrmda jaquedrg macuirig jamaminrgjee.
57001009	Ooshrt jajeu marmdig mashrt jamaminrbrgjee an ayii-maluugshrm Jesucristoshrm .
57001010	Jarm mashrt jajaa naa awá Onésimo, atrriatpeg Dios-jaa nam preso moliiriprn-tee.
57001011	Bŕndi majetwina jaligli mu-rriprnjinditep, ooshrt dumatya majrrja madshipegrr ijeijet, am poi oyem.
57001012	Dumat jashicui jauprtjee-shri malica. Jabatmautai ijeijet oje abatmatairauni-cugjin am.
57001013	Jacugjeu jaliglig ajet ajrrja adrgjee presoja ajuligbat jashrm naa moyerog ijei.
57001014	Ooshrt jashanjeu jawaorglig ajet jamashanjeu-shicom bijashiriiya jamashanminrtu majii-teat naa ijei imashiminrgya.

57001016	oje shandit majetwini, ooshrt jamauluugya oje majrr imajeuprni. Amjri jayii aluug ipegjet, ooshrt man, mandawi jayii mashinomjriduuli ijeijet, ooshrm dumat majetwin-catrmshanwirít ooshrt mapeiwaia jalig Birri-jaa.
57001017	Ooshrm amaluugu oje majrmi, jabatmautaiya naa Onésimo oje abatmatairauni am.
57001018	Ieb jacaminrgu manjri, o madewiargu, jajeu jamalirglig ajaa naa jalewia.
57001019	Am Pablo, janag naa papera aalei-dapjet, amdawi jamii-shibrmya naa madeiwiaryu. Ooshrt jacajeuu jacugquedrg arnoglig man-om, amalewia-rg malei juuyujet majuirg-shrmdi, jajet naa moyerog jalirr wryu ishanbeji.
57001020	Rcaji ajrr, naa irm mashrt jamaubrg an Biŕri-jaa. Jajeu ajiirnajáirglig majrija-marcatsham Cristo-jaa.
57001021	Ojerawi inaabrgli man japishiawaag-shrm ayerog mawaorg shirigya. Japishiawaagwi jamaminrg shirigya an inomjri jeirig jashrt naa irm mashrt.
57001022	Oyat japoijeu jamajeicondig aouliprn maot-tee ooshrm Dios jeiatei adshiujee cadenaat-shrt animnogjee malica oje Dios yarmdauni ajaa.

57001024	ot-poi nat ibeebet ajet Biŕriat. Oyat naa Marcos, Aristarco poi, Demás poi, Lucas poi, memoria cacui man wrijin.
57001025	Dumat jajeu Biŕri Jesucristoat ijei rirglig majii-tee majáijeeya maliglig, Amén.
58001001	Ibagjetdi Dios yaadi bŕn nat judioot doomolat cacooleatdi nat profetaot.
58001002	Ooshrt oo-naa wryu Dios yaad birat jaWá Cooleat, naa idirgprndi jadminrgjee naa wryu, wrijin poi nat ibiruugot wryu-uja shrnoja. Jadirg poi Carriya jaligjee naa jaWá wrijin.
58001003	Naa Dios Wá idyrg ijeijet ojewi Jaíiat iyrrlauni. Jadirg japishibiwaagjee brjaliyu jaligu naa Jaíi Dios, ooshrni itnnjaniwi jajuuyu lig Jan-jet. Oyat jawairiiyu-jet jadwao naa wryu, wrijin poi ibogot wryu-uja shrnoja, canogjee cajririi-teye nat crlot, yamat poi, jrbot poi. Oyat bidjajeicon quedyem bipecado-shrt cruza-jaa jateg jawireat naa Jaíi iwairüg shrnoja.
58001004	Naajri Dios Wá inomjrijeirig cashrt nat ángeleot, ooshrm Dioat jalirg jawairürliglig cashrt nat ángeleot.
58001005	Brlau-shandit aWáala mam Dios mo itrm ángeleat. Yau jamooliprn calat mashirirgya mayrglig wryu maluugjee. Oyat Dios shri mogli jaWá-jaa, amya-ship jan, aWáaya-ship oo.
58001006	Oyatjri jadcuibadi jaWá itrmwi nan wryu-teja jamog shri, jayaulirg ijei cabrgjee jan wrijin nat Dios ángeleot.
58001007	Ovat Dios mog cajaa nat ángeleot cadjaminrg oje jümni nat ángeleot. Jaddirg idyrgjee oje drrni nat ibeebet jan.
58001008	Ooshrtjri Dios mog jaWá-jaa, mam Dios, ishanbejira naa maliiriprn. Oyatjri jashri mog caimajeu ijeijet nat juimabergprnot maepinota.
58001009	Ijeijeta jamaluu wrijin naa ijei idminrg, ooshrtjri iebjeta jamaluu wrijin naa ieb idminrg. Ooshrmjri naa Dios-, naa majri-Dios, jadirg majii jáijee cashrt nat majetwinot.
58001010	Oyat jamog shri, mam Biŕri, bŕn jajuimawrgii naa wryu, jamalirgli niti rigjee cajaa nat jaaot. Oyatjri jamarninrg wrijin naa ibiruug wryu-uja shrnoja.
58001011	Cashibeegya wrijin nat ibiruugot, ooshrt mamjri mashirigya oiiricawiat. Bmwina jalicat naa wryu oje nawa bŕnwinjini.
58001012	Cadmashimauloyugya cabeegjee wrijin naa imarninrgprn oje nawa imauloyulauni. Oyatjri cadmashicambiargya wrijin. Ooshrt mamjri mashirigya oiiricawiat, yauya mawüg shibeeriprn.
58001013	Brlau-shandit Dios mog itrm ángeleat, mauteg awireat cadalirgjeeya mashiim nomat mabalolat.
58001014	Mojii ijeinogota wrijin nat ángeleot, ooda ibeebet Dioat. Cadjacui cajrrja cadcargjee nat idjajeiconprnot nat ood-jashiribrgotya wryu ishanbeji.
58002001	Ooshrmda biratwi jayerog bishiwaorg ijeijet naa moyerog ibijuiprn, jabirirg-shrt jaliprdig bijuiyag-teat, bibiguwi-shrt Dios jrirü-shrt.
58002002	Rjetwinda naa moyerog Dioat iipindi cacooleat nat ángeleat, ooshrmda jajeiwi cadjalirglig ebupaacacrtjee nat iebminrlat, natpoi oyem jashanwaomot naa moyerog idirgprn birat.
58002003	Bojewrnjam jabiquedrg-shirig bicuutjee jashrt naa paacashicrdya capecado-shrm, bibigrrirgu jashrt naa Biŕriat iminrgli birat cruza-jaa. Oolawi Biŕriat oodmog jurgprndi cadjashijeiconya epinot ieb-shrt. Oyat nat jajuiyurt jajet, japishicawaagwi ijet jaliglig naa Biŕriat oodmog, ooshrmda jadbrg birat naa moyerog idjuiprndi jajet.
58002004	Oyatjri Dioat jashririrg japishibiwaagjee ijet jaliglig naa moyerog jajet naa idminrgprn ibishanjuluji, brrt ishanminrríot poi. Oyatjri jadirg japishibiwaagjee rjet jaliglig naa moyerog Espíritu Santojet, naa idirg birat mii-rrijet oje jadjeulauni.
58002005	Yau Dioat calirliprn bijriwairüca caliglig nat ángeleot jatee naa wryu ibishiruugya, naa-jaa bimog.
58002006	Ooshrtjri boi-mog idnagprndi papera-tee, boirigotjam nat mot mabigmashagjee cajaa. Boirigotjam nat mot trriot manimnogjee calica.
58002007	Jayairiwi wiig jamalirgli jarriyuglig ángeleot-shrt. Jarnalirglig ijeiya jaliglig. Jarnalirglig caomjee jarea, jarnalirglig caijajeujee wrijin idmaminrgprnot naa wryu-tee.
58002008	Jarnalircat janoma caligjee wrijin. Ojerawi Dioat jalirglig caŕriya jaligjee wrijin. Yaula Dioat jalirliprn naa idshanquedrri jadcuirig, ooshrt yauju jayerog cawaorliprn wrijin.
58002009	Ooshrtjri jabiruugwi naa Jesús, naa Dioat irirgprn iyaiwryui irriyuulig ángeleot-shrt. Dioat biyii-ruug ooshrmda jadirg jarrijee Jesús bishrm wrijin. Dumat Cajriwairüca jalig ijeijet, ijeí cabrg jan wrijin ebupaajacrt-shrm jarrijee cashrm.
58002010	Dioat ebuminrg jaaleatwi wrijin. Jabigshayu-jeta cadjalirg caligjulig wrijin. Oyatjri wrijin nat jatrriot jadjeu caligjee ijeijet oje jalijani iwrg-tejaya. Dioat jalirg cadjajeiconjee naa Jesucristo ebupaajacrt-shrm cashrm, ebupaacacrt-shrt capecado-jaa.
58002011	Jatrmdawi Caíi nat idjajeiconprnot jajet naa Cajeicono, ooshrm uushanyii-jet cadjaluug jajrrota calig-shrm naa Dios Wáat.
58002012	Ojeri jamo naa idnagprndi papera-uu, maiashipinya ajrrolat, ishicantarbrgya man ijeijet cajewaleya nat cajuibertya.
58002013	Oyat jashri-mog, ajii ashirirgya Dios-jaa. Oyat jashri-mog, oolawi am irig cajet nat trrijulot Dioat irirgprnot an.
58002014	Nat itrrn bon trriot cataa-lig camaa-lig poi ojewi caíijitni, ooshrm caíi ricatwinda naa jataa, Ojeri poi naa Jesucristo, jadjeuli jataale jamaa poi oje calijani nat mot jarrijee jadnamjee cashrt naa morriyu-ŕri moweijin.
58002015	Ojerawi idr cadjashiujee wrijin nat irigot cabigshayu imrmprnjin-jaa oje presoot diirauni caom-shrm morriyu-shrt.
58002016	Yau janooliprn cajrrja cadjargjee nat ángeleot, ooshrt janogjri cajrrja cadjargjee nat Abraám jrdwat.
58002017	Ooshrmda jajacambiarg Dona jaligjee naa Dios Wá, itrmjanibr jaligjee jajrrot-jet, caSacerdoteja jaligjee naa iwairüg cadjajeicon Dios-jet, uubiidjet cadjaluugjee, jadnamjee cashrt caebyu nat epinot jamaa jalirg-shrm cashrm.

58003001	Yam ajrrot, Dioat iougprnot janwi, capeta yam nat Dioat iágprnot japinita yaligjee. Jayeyawaag ijeijet naa Jesucristo, naa Dioat icuiprn, naa biSacerdote iwairürlig wrijin shrt bijeiconjee Dios-jet.

58004001	Ooshrmda biratwi bibigshijeiru brjashirii itnn bipeiu boi shanduutu jijaliiriprn-teja Dios shrnoja dumatju jadirgbat biruuglig.

58005001	Wrijin nat saserdoteot nnodigot, cajuicashug capet nat mot jadrmjee Dios jaepinot-shim, jadbrgjee jan ofrenda capecadoshrm, natpoi cajiwit idcarrirgprnot.

58006001	Ooshrmda jajeiwi bibijuirgjee ibajalig-jet Cristo-jaa jashrt naa jet-bibijuirgwrgprndi, bicacouota birigjee jayerog-jaa, yabiishri juirg-shrt yam yabigshayu yacambiargjee jashrt naa jalirr yanirig Dios-shrt, rri-jaligjee shri yabicuirig yajii yahrgjee Dios-jaa.

58006020	Onda Jesús luucat naa templo-teja shrnoja-irig jajuijayig drg birat binogjee jajan. Saserdote iwairiica jalicatpeg oiiricawiat oje jalijani naa Melquisedec.
58007001	Salem jriwairügla naa Melquisedec, saserdoteja jalig jan naa Dios inomjri wairüg wrijin-shrt. Bŕn janog jabatjataijei naa Abraám jaliprtbatdi jamrgshut-shrt cadcanarnat quedyem nat cajriwairügotjin. Oyatjri naa Melquisedec jabendisiarg jalap-jet naa Abraam.

58007003	Boiruud jaíi naa Melquisedec, boiruud jaíin poi, boiruud poi jaloomot. Boiruud jajuiwrrprn, yau poi jashibeeriprn, ooshrm saserdoteja jalig oiiricawiat oje jalijani naa Dios Wa.

58007010	Ooshrm Levi Abraam taalewi jajrdwat poi, nat ishanminyrriotju cabatcataiadyeg naa Abraam Mequisedec-jet.
58007011	Nat saserdoteot Levi jrdwat, jalirt Moisés yerog calat nat israelot. Jadcaquedrguli cacajeicondi jajet naa saeerdoteolat iminrg Moisés yerog-shrm, yau-cug boi-cajeuliprn itrm Saserdote-om oje jalijani naa Melquisedec, yau calijani nat brrt sacerdoteot.
58007012	Cadcacambiargu nat saserdoteot, jadcugpoi cambiarg-om naa moyerog.

58007014	Japishibiwaagwi Biŕri minyrglig Juda jrdwat-shrt, nat epinot saserdoteotya yam ood-jashanmoiodi-Moiséat.

58007016	Saserdote shandit naa Biŕri capet nat epinot Moiséat irirgprnot saserdoteota caligjee. Ooshrtjri ishanbejira naa biSacerdote juju, naa Bijeicono Dios-jet.

58007020	Qjerawi Dios mog birat moyerog jijogjet.
58007021	Natjrí brrt yau Dioat calirliprn saserdoteja caligjee moyerog jijogjet, ooshrt jadirg Jesús Saserdoteja jaligjee moyerog jijogjet. Oje jamogli, Biŕri mog jan moyerog jijogjet, Saserdotejaya-ship mam oiiricawiat oje jalijani naa Melquisedec.
58007022	Ooshrm Jesúlawi naa jalirr birat dai-imogjet naa moyerog juju, naa inomjri-jeirig bŕnwinjin-shrt.

58007026	Ooshrmda naa Jesús, ooiawi naa Sacerdote iwairiig ibijeu, ooshrm ijeiya jalig, boirigshandit ieb idminrg, jaapirrira jabigshayu. Naa Dioat jawawug cashrt nat iebnogprnotjin, jadwrryrg yawaja nomjri cashrt nat ibiruugot wryu-uja shrnoja.
58007027	Jesús shandit oje calijani nat sacerdoteot iinodigot,nat mojiiyu rriotdi Dios tam-jaa wryu shitojani caaleiot pecado-shrm, caepinot pecado-shrm poi. Ooshrt naa Jesús jaalei-maawi idir itrmjetwi cáshrrn nat wrijin, capecado janarnjeeya oopegwi jajalirgbadi jadrrirgjee.
58007028	Naa Moisés yerog cadjalirg saserdoteot iinodigota caliglig nat mot ood-pecado ligot. Ooshrtjri naa moyerog Dioat oodmogpin jijogjet Moisés prnot, jadirg Sacerdote iwairüca jaligjee naa Dios Wá, naa idirg biSacerdote ijeiya jaligjee oiiricawiat.
58008001	Oyatjri ojera bimog yan japishiyawaagjee ishanbejira naa biSacerdote iinodig, naa iteg jawireat naa Bijriwairüg iwairiig shrnoja.
58008002	Jadnn Dios bijaa jatee naa templo ijetwin shrnoja irig, naa Biŕrat iminrgprn, moolat iminrgprn shandit.
58008003	Cadjaoug wrijin nat sacerdoteot iinodigot jadirgjee caepinot ofrenda Dioat, cajiwit capoi-rrirgjee Dioat. Ooshrm naa biSacerdote Jesucristo jadpoi-rirgli ofrenda Dioat.
58008004	Jaligbatju naa wryu-tee yauli saserdoteja jaliiriprn naa Jesús, ooshrm omdi ealig nat sacerdoteot jalirbrdi Dioat naa Moiséat dirg-cuiri Dioat.
58008005	Naa saserdoteolat iminrgli templo-tee, ooiawi jet-cacajuirg bijaligu Dioat iminrg-shirii birat. Japishibiwaagwi cadcaminrgfig cayaaot nat idiruugot shrnoja, ooshrm ojeri Dios mog Moiséat jadminrgbadi Dios ot, jamauminrg jayaa naa-jet matadrgli wen-jaa.
58008006	Ooshrt naa sacerdoteot jri-Sacerdote jadminrg inomjri-jeirig jashrt naa idminrgli bŕn nat brrt sacerdoteolat. Jalibrg birat naa moyerog inomjri-jei bŕnwinjin-shrt jarnaa jalirg-shrm bishrm.
58008007	Jacajeiuli naa moyerog Dioat irirg-jurgli, boirig-shrm shancuglitom jadir itrm moyerog japrnot.
58008008	Ooshrt nat epinot yau ijei caminrliprn Dioat imuca. Ojeri japoimog naa idnagprndi bŕn. Biŕri mog, boi wryulauya jaiashipinya boi moyerog juju nat israelolat judioolatya poi.
58008009	Ojeri Dios shri-mo, naa jajuju oodamog yan, yau oje jalijani naa oodamogli yaloomolat bŕn, calap awaorgbadi cadarmogjee Ejiptoteat. Yau caliiriprn dai-imogjet jajaa naa waorg-acuiri calat, ooshrmda cadanamnog.
58008010	Ojeri jamog shri Biŕri, boi wryulauya ojeya ishirrya israelolat. Jashirirgya cajuiyag-tee naa minrg-acui calat, janaacat ayerog cajii-tee, ooshrmya cajri-Dioja ashiriiya, oyatya aepinota cashirii.
58008011	Oyatjri yauya cacashijuirliprn cajrrot catojani. Brr-shanditya jashipini japewaiat, mandawi japishirnashiwaa Biŕri-jaa, ooshrmya apishicashiwaag am wrijin, natjri ishŕmnogotju, nat-poi oyem quepaat.
58008012	Jamii ashibrgya cacuenta Dioat jadnamjeeya cashrt naa ieb idminrgprn, oyatjri yauya jayeashishriwaaliprn caebyu.
58008013	Jayaadbat Dios jajaa naa moyerog juju, jadirg japishibiwaagjee bŕnwina jalicat naa moyerog ijapin-jurgli. Oyatjri naa moyerog bŕnwinjin jawuucat bishrt.
58009001	Naa moyerog Dioat iipin jurgli calat, oowi jet-cadjajuirg caculto caminrgjee templo-tee, ooshrt wryu-pinda naa templo idminrg.
58009002	Ojeriwi jadrninrgli naa templo, jadrninrgli itrm sala ipeg jatam Sala Santa. Onda jadir ebushiwryu liiriprn, itrm mesa poi pan calirrliprn jet-jayecawaag Biŕri.
58009003	Oyat boi shririg sala, jatam Dios-pin Santisima. Naa sala inomjri-jei jaiwei itrm curtina irün-jet epinot-shrt.
58009004	Onda Dios Sala Santisima-tee naa drr liiriprn orocon ishicoi catairiprn Dioat. Omda japoirü itrm caja iicamagprn oro-jet, naa-tee jalig naa maná liiriprn orocon, jateepin poi. Oo caja-teera japoirii Aarón pun bigshiyrg, nat poi tablani irigot jaaconot jaa-Dioat inagli naa moyerog waorg-jacuiri.
58009005	Oyat caja juiwop-jaa cadcalirg cashogjee oje ángeleotni ijeinogot jet-cadcatadrgjee Dios ligwiri. Nat ángeleot oroconot jaicaweishog cajou-jet naa caja juiwop, omda jadbadi cajiu maa capecadoshrm Dioat iruuca. Oyat dumatjri jabishanquedrt jainot shibipindig shri jajaa naa idminrglig templo-tee bŕn.
58009006	Oyatjri jadminrg quedyem wrijin, nat sacerdoteot caluug Sala Santa-teja wryu shitojani jadminrgjee culto Dioat.
58009007	Ooshitjri itrm sacerdoteot jriwairüg jaluug Dios Sala Santísimateja itrmjetwi wiig shitojani jadrmogjee mojiu maa jadirgjee Dioat japecado-shrm, jaepinot pecado-shrm poi.
58009008	Jajet naa idminrg templo-tee Espíritu Santo jadirg japishibiwaagjee jadminrgbadiju caculto Dioat juishanjuyidi bijrirü biruugjee Dios Sala-teja shrnoja.
58009009	Wrijin naa idminrgli Dioat, oowi jet-bibijuirca Cristo maa-jaa. Naa ofrenda idbrgli Dioat yauli jadquedrliprn cabigshayu jajeicondig, yau poi idcanirgprnot maa-jet.
58009010	Oowitep camogli mowoug-jaa, mowóg-jaa poi, wrijin moijeicon shrg rt-jet. Naa wryu pintep naa minrg cacuiri bŕn, ooshrtjri jawuucat bishrt naa moyerog bŕnwinjin Dioat jalirgbat birat jayerog juju Cristo-jaa.
58009011	Ooshrtjri jaminyucat birica naa Cristo, ooshrm dumat Cristolawi biSacerdote iwairüg jajaa naa ijei Dioat irirg birat. Janomjrijei naa templo shrnoja-irig jrn jaluuca Cristo Dios jarmjee bijaa, naa templo idshanminrnprn mot dap-jet, naa wryu-pin shandit.
58009012	Cristo luug itrmjetwi Dios Sala inomjrijei-teja shrnoja. Yau jadrrnooliprn jajet mojiu maa jadirgjee Dioat, ooshrt jaalei-maawi idirg Dioat bishrm wrijin bidjajeiconjee oiiricawiat ebupaabicrtshrtya bipecado-shrm.
58009013	Cacajeiconu Dioat nat iebnogprnotjin jadshinpai-shrm cajaa mojiu maa jadpompai-shrm poi cajaa cajiu taujim.
58009014	Jashinomjri jeiya Cristo maa jadquedrg jadshrrglig bishrt bibigshayu jaapibagprnjin, jabiminrg-shrt naa jalirr birririg Dios-shrt. Ooshrtjri ibibeeb jan ijeijet naa Dios ijucat, Cristoat jajalirg-shrm jaaleatwi Dioat oje cordero pecado-rrini.
58009015	Oolawi Jesucristo jadquedr jadirgli dai-imogjet naa moyerog juju naalat idja-ágprnolat jarri-shrmdi jadnamjee cashrt naa idmrnrgprndi yauja Dios yerog bŕnwinjin-shrt, jalibrgjeeya calat naa ijei shanbeji Dioat oodmogprndi calat brn.
58009016	Jajujugbat itrm bon jaijapin jawoo jarrat, boirica shandit jajrrat yau-jaligu jarririprnju naa ijapinbrgprn jan.
58009017	Jádshanquedrt jadwaorglig jajrrat ood-mogprndi jan jajujuguju. Ooshrtjri jarri quedyem jajrrjin jashiribrgyapeg jan naa ijapinprndi jan.
58009018	Bŕn cajiwit maa canam jadirgjee dai-imogjet naa moyerog bŕnwinjin.
58009019	Bŕn Moiséat jaipin nat epinot wrijin naa moyerog Dioat waorg-cui calat. Oyat oveja jaashut icrt, mojrmca lou poi jadtuurg oveja maa-tee jriwaoprn rt-jet jadshinpai jajaa naa moyerog jricanagprn, oyat poi papera-tee. Oyat epinot-jaa poi wrijin.
58009020	Oyat Moisés mog calat, naajri oveja maa oolawi jalirr dai-imogjet naa moyerog Dioat waorg-cui birat.
58009021	Oyat Moiseat jashinpai naa oveja maa Dios ot-jaa wrijin poi jet-culto caminrgot.
58009022	Jayriyaibrjin cacajeiconjee oveja maa-jet oje Moiséat inagprnat jaliirlauni. Yau jaligu jamaa canamdiprn, yau cugpoi-om Dioat janamdiprn naa ieb idminrgprn.
58009023	Bŕn jadnam mojiu maa cadcajeiconjee nat shrnoatwinot yaaot. Ooshrt nat shrnoatwinot jadjeu boi maa inomjri-jei mojiu maashrt.
58009024	Oyat naa Cristo yau jaluugliprn jateeja naa Dios sala naa idminrgprn calap-jet. Ooshrtjri jaluug Dios sala-teja shrnoja-irig. Onda jaliiwi dumat Dioat iruucat bijai-jarmjee.
58009025	Yau Cristo luugliprn Dios sala-teja ibajet jadirgjee jamaa oje calijani nat sacerdoteot iinodigot jarrnodi mojiu maa. Rtyrg shitojani caluug Dios isala templo-tee momaa-jet, naa caalei-maa shandit.
58009026	Cristoat jacalirguli jamaa rtyrg shitojani, omda jacupoirri-om rtyrg shitojani bŕnju wryu minjurgbat dumat-patjei. Ooshrt jabigye minogbat jayug itrmjetwi cashrm wrijin, jajalirg calat jadrrirgjee jadnamjee bipecado oiiricawiat.
58009027	Dioat calirg carrijee itrmjetwi nat wryu tepinot catojaniwi, oyatya cainot shijashiprn ebupaacacrtjee capecado-shrm o ebupaacashancrtjee.
58009028	Ojeripoi Cristoat jajalirg jadrrirgjee itrmjetwi jadnamjee capecado nat ibagot. Oyatjri jashiyugya-shri bipecado-shrm shandit, ooshrt jashiyugya cataale jacambiargjeeya ijeijet nat jajeiteyetprnot jayuglig cadjarmogjeeya shrnoja.
58010001	Naajri Moisés yerog ojera jatepdi ebuyaani naa ijei jeicateiri jayuglig. Yauli jadjeicondiprn oopegwi naa idminrgli templotee. Yau Moisés yerocat jaquedrliprn cadjajeicondig Dioat iruuca nat janaart mojiu maajet idcarrirgprnot rtyrg tojani.
58010002	Moisés yerocat jacaquedrgu cadjajeicondig, cacugcai-om, cadcalirgli idcarrirgprnot Dioat, ooshrm m-cugpoi-om capecado mrmdig cajaa-om.
58010003	Ooshrtjri nat idcarrirgprnot Dios-jaa rtyrg shitojani, jadirg japishicawaagjee jajaaju naa ieb idminrg.
58010004	Ooshrmjri mojiu maa jadshanquedrt capecado janamjee.
58010005	Oyatjri jayugbadi Cristo naa wryu-teja jamog Dioat, dumat jamashanjeu mojiu carrirglig man, rripoi ofrenda majeulig cajet. Ooshrt jamaminrcat ataale ofrendaja.
58010006	Yau madjáirrliprn ofrenda-jet, yau poi mojiu-jet idcataiprnot capecado canamjee.
58010007	Ooshrm ojeri jamog, naalawi am, ayugjri jaminryugjee oje jamajeulauni mam Dios, jaminrgjee oje canaalauniri ajaa capapera-tee bŕn.
58010008	Jadpinrg jurgbadi Dioat, yau jamajeuliprn madjáirglig ofrendajet, yau-poi mojiu-jet idcataiprnot capecado canamjee naa idminrg jadwaorgjee naa moyerog bŕnwinjin.
58010009	Oyat jashri-mog, oolawiat am, ayug jaminryugjee oje jamojani, mam Dios, ojeri jamog jadwurgjee cashrt naa idminrglig mojiu maa-jet, jadirgjee jaalei-maawi capecado-shrm mojiu maa-shrt.
58010010	Dios jetwinota bidu jashrm naa Jesucristoat idminrgprn bishrm Jaíi yerog jawayrgbadi. Jadirg jataale calat mojiu-shrt jadrrirgjee itrmjetwi cashrm wrijin, cadjajeiconjee oiiricawiat.
58010011	Wrijin nat saserdoteot jadminrg oje jayerog bŕnwinjinat jalirlauni idminrgjee wryu shitojani. Oiirigwi cadcalirglig Dioat nat idcarrirgprnot capecado-shrm, nat jashanquedrriot capecado Canamdig.
58010012	Ooshrtjri Jesucristoat jalirg jataale itrmjetwi jadrrirgjee jadnarnjee capecado oopegwi oiiricawiat,oyatjri jateg Dios wireat.
58010013	Jalig shrnoja Jaíi-jet, jajeijatei Jaíiat canamjee jabalat jashiim nomat.
58010014	Ooshrt naa jamaa icíirgprndi itrmjetwi cadjajeiconjee capecado-shrt oiiricawiat wrijin nat idjalirgprnot japinita caligjee.
58010015	Oyat naa Espíritu Santo jadirg japishibiwaagjee japinita birigjee oje jamojaniri bŕn.
58010016	Boi wryulauya ojeyawi ishirrya calat, jamogli Biŕri, jashirirgya ayerog cajii-tee. Jajri-ashinagya ayerog cajuiyag-tee.
58010017	Oyatjri yauya capecado iyei-ashishri waaliprn, naa idminrgprndi boyeja ayerog-shrt.
58010018	Ojeri jamog, ooshrmya boi bishanjewi itrmu jashrt jet-bipecado binamacugjin jadquedrg quedyem jadnamdig bishrt.
58010019	Ooshrmjri ajrrot, dumat jabiquedrg biruugjee uushanyii-jet Dios sala-teja shrnoja jamaa-jet naa Jesucristo.
58010020	Binogjee jateeye naa Drg juju Dioat juiyigbrcat birat jajounogbadi naa Curtina jaiweyeiri jaSala Santisima templo-tee. Ojaliyula naa Curtina, Cristo taaleja jalig irmdrgli bishrm jajuijayigjee bijrirü binogjee Dios-lica.
58010021	Jesújri oolawi biSacerdote iwairüg Dios ot-tee shrnoja irig.
58010022	Ooshrmda jabinarg Dios bibigshayu íjetwin-jet bidu bijiirirt dai-imogjet Dios-jaa, jadjeicon-shrmdi bibigshayu jamrm-shrtya, bipecado jadnam-shrm bishrt. Oyatjri bidjashrcat Rt ijug-jet jashrt naa jaapibagprnjin biminrgli.
58010023	Birigjee dai-imogjet jajaa naa ijei jeibitei jabiruugjee, rri-jaligjee bibigshayu caulig ooshrm Dioat ishiminrgya birat oje jamojaniri.
58010024	Oyat biratwi bijrrja bibishirryeg ijeijet bijrrot-jet, biyii biruuyegjee ijeijet ijei biminryegjee.
58010025	Rri-jaligjeeya bicairig bijuibiberglig Dios yerog-shrm oje calijani nat itrmnogot. Ooshrt biratwi bibishiwairür Dios yerog-jet jabiruugbat jabigye naaglicat cainot shijapinjeeya wrijin.
58010026	Jabijeuu biriglig bipecado-jaa japishibiwaag quedyem ijeijet naa moyerog rjetwin, boirigshanditya jaquedrr jadnarndig bishrt naa ieb ibirninrgprn.
58010027	Jabijeuu biriglig bipecado-jaa ooyawi jeibishitei-jamo Dioat biinot shipinjee ebupaabicrtjee bipecado-shrm naa drr-tee jijogeberigjet, naa drr cashibeerrya nat jabata-jart Dios.
58010028	Bŕn yau jauubiid caluuliprn naa Moisés yerog shanwaom iainot shicapinu nat icauot o ipoiot poi jalujutprnot ieb jaminrglig.
58010029	Oje jacaligu jalii, jayeyawajijam ebupaacacrt shishandiya jijooligjet bŕnwinotjin-shrt nat jatagyequet cashim nornat naa Dios wá, nat iyaalot iebjet jajaa naa Dios Espíritu biyü-ruju, nat jaebrt Cristo maa, naa jalirrm dai-imogjet jayerog juju,Dios pinita birigjee.
58010030	Japishibiwaagwi Birriat oodmogli bŕn, amyawi ishiminrr calat oje idminrlauni an. Amyawi camiishibrm jamiija naa ieb idrninrg. Oyat jashri-rnog, Carriya cainot shishipini nat jaepinot.
58010031	Jarglig bidjalirgu ebupaabicrtjee bipecado-prta naa Dios ijucat.
58010032	Dumat jayeiyawaag brjaliguli yaliglig jayalirg-jurgbatdi naa Ebushiwryu, idyrglig yajuiyag-tee. Oyat yautabali prnpatjet jajet naa yalirr ebupaayacrtdig cabata yadrgbat.
58010033	Bŕn cadcamrn itrmnogot yapet wad-uu cadcaluugjee wrijin, ieb carninig yan, oyatjri yarn poi ebupaayacrt cajet nat uubiidcaconprnot.
58010034	Cauubiid yaluugli nat presoja idcargprnodi. Oyat jadebrgbadíl yalapwoo yajii-cujai japishiyawaag-shrm jalibrgwi yan yawoo inomjri-jei shrnoja jashrt naa wiyu pin, ooshrm yauya jashirmdrliprn yashrt naa ishibrgya yan shrnoja.
58010035	Oyat jayacupoinam yashrt naa-jaa yajii yalirg, ooshrm jashiriibrgya yan ijei ipegjet yajii yalirg-shrm jajaa.
58010036	Yanwi jajricayashicou prnpatjet naa paayashicrt jayarninrgjee oie Dioat jajeulauni. Oyatya jashiriibrg yan naa ijei oodjamog yan.
58010037	Ooshrm ojeri canagli papera-tee, mogwainia jashiyuu naa ishiyugya. Yauya japrnshipatdiprn bishrt.
58010038	Oyat nat idajeiconprnot cashijugyawi oiiricawiat cabigshayu calirg-shrm ajaa. Ooshrtjri caúprtu ashrt yauya ijáijet cadashiruuliprn.
58010039	Ooshrt bidujri, capet shandit nat uuprtprnotjin Dios-shrt carmdrgjeeya. Ooshrt capet bidu nat cajiirirt Dios-jaa ijet carmdrgshrtya jashrt.
58011001	-Bijii birirgu Dios-jaa rjet japishibiwaagwi ijuugwi naa Dios, japishibiwaagwi jashiribrgya birat naa jeibitei jajet. Capishibiwaagwi caliglig nat idbishanjulujit bibig-jet.
58011002	Bŕn ijeijet Dioat caluug nat judioot doomotjin cajii calirg-shrm jajaa rjet;.
58011003	Japishibiwaagwi Dioat jaminrglig naa wryu jayerog-jet japishijawaag-shrm jadquedrg jadrninrglig jayerog-jet. Jadminrgli naa wryu ibiruug jajet naa moyerog ibishanduji.
58011004	Abelat jajiirirg Dios-jaa ooshrmdi janomjri-jei naa Abelat ibrg Dioat jashrt naa Cainat ibrgprn. Ooshrmdi ijeijet Dioat jaluu naa Abel, ooshrm-poi jajei naa oveja idbrg Dioat. Bŕn jairi Abel, ooshrt jainot bijui, ooshrmda jabijeu bijii birírglig Dioat oje jalijani.
58011005	Naajri Enóc jajii japoirirgli Dios-jaa, ooshrmdi jashanrriii jataale. Dioat jataale cambiarg jadrmogjee shrnoja, ooshrmda yauli jataalejin caluuliprn. Ojeri camog jajaa, Diola idjáirgli ooshrmda jadrmog jajet.
58011006	Yau jaiquedrliprn jaijáirglig Dios mojii ishandirtu jajaa. Jaijeuu Dios inarglig moíatwi japishiishiwaa jajugwirig naa Dios. Molatwi japishiishiwaajadshinrgyaijei calat jajewerat caju-teat.
58011007	Noé jajiirirg Dios-jaa, ooshrmdi japishiiawaag rjet jaliglig naa Dioat oodmog jajaa naa ieb iishaniuluii. Dios yerog jawaorg rjet, oyat jadminrgli lancha ipeg cadjayrrgjee jaot tepinot ieb-shrt. Jajet naa lancha Noéat iminrg jadirg japishicawaagjee cashirmdrgya capecado-shrm nat wryu tepinot. Oyat ijeijet Dioat jaluug, jadtadrg-shrm jajii jalircat jajaa jajet naa idminrg.
58011008	Naa Abraam jajii jalirg Dios-jaa ooshrmdi jayerog jawaorg jadágbadi janogjee boi niti-teja, naa niti Dioat ijeuli jadirbrglig jan. Abraam nog janiti-shrt japishijashanjuwaat brm-jaligu jashinoo.
58011009	Abraamat jajiirirg Dios-jaa, omda jalir jatee naa niti Dioat oodmogprndi jan,, oje molürauni brrt epinot niti-jaa. Abraam dig juicog-tee iyuiot-con, oopoi naa Isaac, Jacob poi. Naat-poi jajeiteiyet naa ijei Dioat oodmogprndi calat.
58011010	Abraamat jeitei jadduugjee naa moyan irig dai-imogjet oiiricawiat, naa moyan Dioat iminrgprn shrnoja.
58011011	Oyat naa Sara, jajii japoirirg Dios-jaa, ooshrt jawairüyu jabrg jatrririgjee quepalaja jalicatu, japishijawaag-shrm Dioat jaminrgshirig jan oje jamojani.
58011012	Oyat naa quepat Abraam, janacatuwi janogjee naa wryu-shrt oobat jatrririg. Oyatjri nat jajrdwat cabag oje crrlotni, oje maini rt-coo, cadishanquedrt cadicagu.
58011013	Bŕn carri wrijin nat Cristo jeiteiyetprnot jajuprduju jadduuglig naa Dioat oodmog calat, ooshrt jadduugliwi cabigshayu-teat. Oyatjri cajii calirgli jajaa, oyatdi jii-jáijet jayeicawaag. Camogli, ibogotatep bidu nam wryu-tee, iwuugotep bidu, biniti shanditshrm naa wryu.
58011014	Nat iwuugotep bidu imogot jadirg japishibiwaagjee jadjeu boi ni ti shrnoja, capina caligjee jajan.
58011015	Jayeicacawaagu naa niti shrt-cayugprn, jadeugquedrg-om caúprt-shirig jajan.
58011016	Ooshrtjri boi cajeu canitija inomjrijei, naa shrnojawin idjeu. Ooshrm jauushanyii Dios japishicawaagjee cajri-Dioja jaliglig, ooshrm jadjeiconbrcat calat itrm cayan.
58011017	Dios mog Abraamat cashibagya majrdwat ooshrt yau jaiwinjashooliprn Dios-shrt itrmwi ja-wá Dios-shrt jatam Isaac japishijawaag-shrm Dioat jajeulig oje.
58011018	Ojeri Dios mog jan, Isaac licatwinotya nat majrdwat.
58011019	Abraarnat japishiwaa iwairüca jaliglig Dios cadjawrryrgjee irriprnotjin. Japishijawaagli Dios iavíprtrg shirigya jan ja-wa, naa jadduucadi oje iraprnjini.
58011020	Oyat naa Isaac jajii jalirg Dios-jaa, ooshrmda jabenisiarg Jacob, Esau poi, Cadjapinrg jajaa naa íjei ishiyugya calica.
58011021	Jacobat jajii-rirg Dios-jaa, ooshrm jarríbadi cadjabenisiarg nat José trriot, cadjapinrg jajaa naa ijei ishiyugya. Oyatjri ijei jabrg Dioat jijajaíiishog-shicom japauyu-jaa.
58011022	Oyat naa José janibadi jamog calat nat Israelot, boi wiyulauya yashiyrgya Ejipto-teat. Oyatjri cadjacui jauutjin carrnogjee cajet jaa-teja naa niti Dioat ood-mogprndi calat.
58011023	Oyat naa Moisés ii jaíin poi, cajii calirg Dios-jaa, ooshrmda ipoi jrbotjet jadjaan catrri jaminyrg quedyem jadduug-shrm ijeia jaliglig naa trriwai. Yau poi caomdiprn jarea naa iwairüg cacuiyu cadcarrirgjee catrriot.
58011024	Moiséat jajiirirg Dios-jaa, oyatjri bona jalicatu jadshanjeu ja-waja jaliglig naa Faraón dou,
58011025	jadshanjeu-shrm jataale jajáuglig cajet nat ieb-minrt, ooshrtjri jadjeu ebupaajacrdig Dios epinotjet.
58011026	Moiséat jayeiwaag janomjri-jei ebupaaiertu Cristo-shrm jashrt naa mowoo Ejipto-teewin jadduug-shrm jabigshayu-jet naa ijei Dioat oodmogprndi jan.
58011027	Moiséat jajiirirt Dios-jaa, ooshrmda jadnamnog Ejipto. Yau jaomdiprn cajriwairüg rca, ooshrtjri jalig dai-imogjet jajaa naa Dioat minrg-cui jan ooshrm jadduugliwi jabigshayu-jet naa iishanduji mobig-jet.
58011028	Jajii jalirg Dios-jaa, ooshrmda jadminrg naa pascua, jashinpai jacui oveja maa mooj'a-jaa carrirg-shrtya nat israelot jrdwat ipagpraot jayugbatya naa ángel morriyu rryuu.
58011029	Oyat nat israelot cajii calirg Dios-jaa ooshrmdi rt-Icrt iicabat cawugli oje mowuulauni niti ishaat-jaye. Oyatjri nat Ejiptoot carmdrglirt-teja cayugbadi caprna.

59002009	Cayii yaluugu itrrnnogot yajrrot brrt-shrt, ieb yashiminrgyajamo. Oyatjrí Dioya yainot shishipini iebnogprnotjina yaliglig jayerog yashanwaorg-shrm, naa waorg-jacui yan.
