59002011	Naa Dios iyaadprn, macupoiruud boi den-jet ma-u shrt, jamog poi epin macupoi-mrt. Ooshrmjri mashanduudu boi den-jet ma-u shrt, oyat epin marrirg, jamashanminrt naa Dioat minrg-cui.
59002012	Ooshrmda yauyaad ijeijet, ijei yauminrg poi, ooshrm Dioya yainot shipini jajet naa moyerog juju, jet-yadshiu yan iebprnjin shrt.
59002013	Oyatjrí nat brrt uubiidshandujit, yauya Dioat cauubiid shiruuliprn boi wryulauya cainot shijapinbatya epinot wrijin. Oyatjrí nat brrt uubiidujut Dioat jashinamya cashrt caebyu irig cajaa, cauubiid jaluug-shrm.
59002014	Ajrrot, boirigjam jamiirijam Dioat naa ajii alirg Dios-jaa imog, oyatjrí yau ijei jaminrliprn-oicom. Dioat jashijeiconiyajam jashrt naa paacashicrtya capecado-shrm jayerog jashanwaortu rjet.
59002015	Caligu yajrrot uubiidot yuiot-mot, mowougu-rriot poi.
59002016	Oyat yamogu calat, yaunocat ijeijet, yayuiot yauyui, yayeicowaiya teetog-jet. Oyat boirigyajam jashimii calat naa oodyamog jayau jaligu jayabrrliprn naa idjeu cataale yawana.
59002017	Ojera poi nat ajii alirg imogot. Yau-jaligu ijei caminriiprn, rjet-shandit cajii calir Dio-jaa, ooshrt yoanda-cateprno.
59002018	Oyat boi irnogu, mam majii malireat Dio-jaa, oyat amjri ijei aminrg Dioat iruuca. Bojeyajam jamatadrg shirig majii maliryu Dios-jaa, yau jaligu ijei maminrliprn. Ooshrt amjri, matadig jamaluugjee ajii alirglig Dios-jaa jajet naa ijeiiminrg.
59002019	Mamjri japishiwaja jatrmwirig Dios. Jajeirawi naa pishimawaag, ooshrt nat dernonioot japishicawaag poi jaliglig Dios, ooshrnda capiip caom-shim jarea.
59002020	Mam bon ebupishishanwaji, yau-tejarn japishimawaag shuuliprn, yau jaligu itnnat ijei minrliprn, ijet shandit jajii jalírr Dio-jaa, yowanda ajii alirg jateprno.
59002021	Ijeijeta Dioat jaluu naa biroom Abraam jashrm naa idrninrg jadirgbatdi Dioat naa jawá Isaac.
59002022	Ooshrm jajet naa Abraamat iminrgli Dioat, japishiyawaagwi jajii jalirlicat Dios-jaa. Oyatjri jijooligjet jajii jalir Dio-jaa jashrm naa paajacrt Dios-shrm.
59002023	Abraamat iminrg oje naa idnagprn mojaniri jajaa. Ojeri jamog, Abraamat jajiirirg Dio-jaa, ooshrmdi ijeijet Dioat jaluug. Oyat camog jajaa, Dios jrrla naa Abraam.
59002024	Ooshrmda japishiyawaagwi ijeinogotnira Dioat caluuglig nat epinot ijei caminrg-shrm, yau camoyo-shrm ajii alirg Dios-jaa.
59002025	Ojeri poi naa iwoojeuprnjindi Raab. Ijeijetdi Dioat jaluu ijei jaminrg-shrmdi, cabatjatairi nat idjacuiprnot cadjalirg caúprtjee boi drg-uye cabalot-shrt.
59002026	Yau-jaligu bijuuyu liiriprn bitaale-tee, oowi jarririg bitaale. Ojera poi, ijei bishanminrtu jashanjut bijii birirglig Dios-jaa, ooshrtjri yowandatep bijii birirg jajaa bimog.
59003001	Ajrrot, cadyacupoirirt ibagjet yajuirta nat yapeet, ooshrm japishiyawaagwi ieb biminrgu Dioat jashirirgya ebupaabicrtjee inomjrijoaet brrt-shrt bidu ijuirt.
59003002	Wrijin bidu, ibagjeta ijei bishanminrri. Jaligu itnn bon brlaushandít jayaad iebjet, ijeira naa bon. Oyat japishijawaag poiwi jadjiipdig wrijin jataale jaebyu-shrt.
59003003	Jabijiipu cabalyo freno-jet jadmrnrgjee oje jabijeulauni. Frenojeta jabiquedr janoglig jataale bŕn-jaligu jabijeu janoglig.
59003004	Cadyacaluug nat lanchaat ipeinogot poi, jiim jijocat carmog ooshrtjri naa jajriwaotee jadrmog jatimon ishrmjetwi brm-jaligu jadieu janoglig.
59003005	Ojera poi jashrm-cug naa bilog, ooshrtjri jadjeu jayaadig jijogjet. Jayacaluug naa drr ishrmwi jadquedrg jataiu etshuwai.
59003006	Ojera drrni jalig naa bilog. Qje itrm iebprnjin iwairiig dürauni nam wryu-tee cadjaebrgjee wrijin, ojera poi naa büog jalig bitaaletee bijaebrgjee wrijin. Naajri bilog, infíernola jabrtrr, qje drr lirauni ye-uu jatai wrijin naa irig jalrg-uu, ojera poi bilog jadebrg cabigshayu wrijin brm jaligu jarninoi.
59003007	Nat mot jadquedrg jadjiipu wrijin jrriug wiibot poi, pünotpoi, wrijin rt tepinot poi. Cadcaquedrg cadcajáirgu ibagot.
59003008	Ooshrt boiruuda jaquedrr jadjnpdi jaalei-logwi. Yaula jaiquedrüprn yrijairgjee, jajuituun iwan-jet naa molog, jalirrm morrndrglig Diosshrt.
59003009	Büogdeta ijei bishibrr Bií Dioat, oyat bilog-jet iebjet biyaad moolat Dioat irninrgprnot oje jalijani.
59003010	Jatrmwi bicooleat jabiyrrg moyerog ijei, moyerog iebprnjin poi. Ajrrot jashanjei ibiminrgu qje.
59003011	Jadquedrrijam itrm rt-maiat jalirgu rt ijei oyat rt iwanprnjin poi.
59003012	Ajrrot, jadquedrrijam woo-cam digu mri-jaa. Jadquedrrijam mri-cam digu jau-jaa. Ojera poi rt-maiat jadshanquedrt jadyrrglig rt-ishrrt, rt ijei poi.
59003013	Jaligu boi bicacou yajewalee, jayaulirg bidjatadrgjee jabicacouyu-jet jabig jashanahaat jajeirig brrt-shrt. Ooshrm naa mobigshayu ijeiat jashandirt mojaiishaglig mojeirig brrt-shrt.
59003014	Ooshrtjri jawan yabigshayu yanai-shrm boi woo-jet, boi bigshayu-jet poi. Jayacupoipin ijei yaalei-jaatep yabicacou-shrm, ooshrt brttep-cug yarn-orn.
59003015	Shrnoatwin shandita jabigshayu naa jajewe bicacoua jaliglig brrt-shrt, ooshrt wryu bigshajtula iribrg jan, epinot bigshayutep, moweijin-licatwinda naa jabigshayu.
59003016	Nat inaiot brrt bigshayu-jet, nat jajewet ebupishicawaaglig brrt-shrt, cadcaebrg cajrrot bigshayu wnjin. Oyatjri cacamrnyeg cajrrot-jet, jadminrg poi wrijin ieb.
59003017	Ooshrtjri nat bigshayu ligot shrnoatwin, jaapi rrira cabigshayu, cashan-nrm, cajnja cadcarg itrmnogot, jadjui brrt yerog, cauubiid cadcaluuglig brrt, ijei caminrg, yau cayerog cauliprn, teeshauprnotjin shandit.
59003018	Oyat nat jajewet brrt cajeicondig cajet, jadjrm moyerog ishan-nrmijet, jajuicashishugya caaleatwi ijei.
59004001	Boirigjam jalirr cacarrirgjee. Boirigjam jalirr cacamrnyegjee. Cabigshayu iebprnjinda jalirr jadminrglig oje, naa ieb irig yajii-tee oolawi jabata jarm wrijin ijei.
59004002	Yanai jashrm naa boiruudbrg yan, oyatjri epin yarrirg jayashan- quedrt-shrm jayaouglig yabeeb-jet. Caeb yaluug nat oodjalibrgot naa jet-yanai, oyatjri cabata cadyarg. Moprtoyu yaminrg jayashanquedrt-shrm jayaouglig. Boiruud-brg yan naa iyajeu jayashan-rm shrm Dios.
59004003	Oyatjri jayacarmu Dios, yau jadirliprn yan jayarm-shrm jajet iebtep. Oowi iyajeu yayajáirglig yaaleat-tep jajet naa iyarrn.
59004004	Yam epinot bigshayu cauot, yau-tejam japishiyawaaliprn cabata jadrg Dios nat jayiirujut naa wryu. Brjaligu jajewe cajrrja cadjarglig nat wryu tepinot ieb-minrt, cabata jadrg Dios.
59004005	Jayashaijam oocateprnoglig naa idnagprndi bŕn capapera-tee. Naa Espíritu Dioat irirg jaligjee bijii-tee bijaiwinjashog ieb-shrt.
59004006	Ooshrtjri Dioat jajrrja birg biyii jaluug-shrm, ooshrm ojeri jamog naa idnagprndi bŕn, Dios juimig caubata nat jajewet cajeirig brrt-shrt. Ooshrt cajrrja cadjarg nat bigshayu uubiidprnotjin cayii jaluug-shrm
59004007	Yayaubrg Dioat, yabata jayaurg moweijin, oyatya jashicuut yashrt.
59004008	Jayaunarg Dios, oyatya yadshipoi-narg. Ijei yaurninrg yalapjet yam iebnogprnotjin. Yabigshayu jaapi-yacupoibaart yam bigshayu cauot, yam jajewet yaboglig Dios-jet yapecado-jet poi.
59004009	Yajii cueb, yajii cushŕmrg, yauquig yaebyu-jaa. Yacupoiyoi, ooshrtjri jayaulirg yabigpog nogjee. Yayacupoijáirt, ooshrtjri yajii yaushŕmrg.
59004010	Y auuyaubiidrg Dioat iruuca, oyatya yabigshayu yawrryrg wrijin iduuca.
59004011	Ajrrot, yacupoiyaad iebjet yajrrot-jaa. Naajri iyaad iebjet jajrr- jaa, ieb jaminrg jajaa naa moyerog biwaorg. Oyatjri jaeb yaluugu naa moyerog Dioat jawaorg-cui birat yauya jayerog yashiwaoriiprn.
59004012	Jatrmdawi naa jalirr birat naa moyerog waorg jadcui birat, oyatjri oolawi naa cainot shipini wrijin. Oolawi jaquedrrm bidjajeicondig ebupaabicrt-shrt bipecado-jaa, oo-poi jadquedrrm ibdjarmdrrgu jashrt. Ooshrtjri mam, brr-jam jalirr boi unot shimaprnjee.
59004013	Dumatjri jayaujui naa ayerog yam jaipinit, durnat o brlem poi binogjee boi moyan-teja. Bishirigya jajan itrm wiig jabiwendergjeeya biwooja boi biougjeeya.
59004014	Oyat yam, ojera yamo ooshrtjri yau japishiyawaaliprn brjaliguya yashirig brrlem. Bojejam naa birig-shirig nam wryu-tee. Ojera jalii waojribrruni jairuug mogwaini oyatjri jarmdrg bishrt.
59004015	Ooshrmda biratwi bishimog, Biŕriat jajeuu bijuglig, jabishi- minrgya naa ibijeu jabiminrglig.
59004016	Ooshrtjri yam, yayaad oje calijani nat jajewet japishicawaaglig brrt-shrt. Oyat jaebda wrijin naa oje-imog.
59004017	Naajri japishiwajat ijei jaminrg, oyat yau-jaligu ijei jarninniprn, oowi ieb jamimgü.
59005001	Ayerog yaujui yam wooligolat, yauquig, yauwrr-ág jashrm naa paayashicrtya.
59005002	Jalaamat naa iribrg yan, oyatjri nat toolot jadwoucat yayuiot miibagjin.
59005003	Cawinbacat nat yaorootjin, yapalataotjin poi. Yawooya yainot shishipini, naa-jaa yajii yalirg Dios shrt. Yataale jashitaiya oje drmi. Oowi yawoqja boiyaoug ibagpeg jarmdrgjee yashrt oopegwi wryu-tee.
59005004	Naa mii-shicabeebprndi iiwinyashogprndi cashrt nat ibeebrdi yan, yainot shijashipin. Oyat naa ibagot Rri jadjuiat calat nat ibeeberat yan yainot shipinirat.
59005005	Nam wryu-tee yalig ijeijet yawoo jriat. Dumat yayajáirg jajet naa ieb yaminrg nam wryu-tee, yajaayatrdrcat oje cajiu jaacatrdriauni jadrrirgjee. Ojera poi yabigye minoglicat yarmdrgjee.
59005006	Cainot shiyapinat iebjet nat ieb shanminrriot, oyatjri cadyanirg nat yabata yashanrriot.
59005007	Ooshrm yam ajrrot, yapin-cayaucourg ata-on jayuca Biŕri. Jayacaluug naa tiim rri, jajeijatei prnpatjet jajnnca cam ata-on oopegwi wau lrgjee.
59005008	Ojera poi yam jajricayaucou, jayacupoirirt yabigshayu mrmdig, ooshrm janacatwi Biŕri bigye jayuglig.
59005009	Ajrrot, yacupoiyaadyeg yajaa brjashirii yainot shicapinuya poi, ooshrm naajri Dios bijainot shipini jashog inagjetwiat jayugjee.
59005010	Ajrrot, jayacaluug brjaliguli jajricacacouli naa paacacrdi nat Dios yerog shipiniradi, oyatjri jajnca yaucou oje calijaniri.
59005011	Jiijáiota pishibiwaaglig nat jajricacouotdi naa paacacrtdi. Jayajuiat brjaligli jajricacouli prnpatjet nat Jobat. Oyatjri japishiyawaagwi brjaliguli Biŕriat ijei minrgli jobat ebupaajaert quedyem, ooshrm ijeira jabigshayu naa Biŕri, biuubiid jaluug.
59005012	Oyatjri ajrrot, jayacupoipin moyerog jijogjet, ijet amoglig shrnoatwinolat iruugjet, wryu tepinolat íruugjet poi. Jajeiwi yamogu, oyatjri yauminrg oje yamojani. Ojera poi rri yamogu, yanwi rjet yashimog brjashirii Dioat yainot shipinu ebupaayacrtjee.
59005013	Ebupaajacrtu itrm yajrrat, jayaulirg Dios jarmjee. Jajii-jáiu itrm yapei, jayaulirg idcantargjee ijeijet Dioat.
59005014	Ishiyuat jawaorgu itrm yajrr, jayaulirg cadjaágjee nat iglesia ijewet Dios carrnjee jajaa. Jadirg aceite jajuiyag-jaa Biŕri tam-jaa.
59005015	Dios cannbat jajaa ijet cajii-teat, jashijugyawi naa ishiyuat iwaorg. Oyatya Biŕriat jajuishimir jacan-shrt. Jaebyu jaminrguh, Dioat jashinamya jashrt.
59005016	Ooshrmda jayaupinyeg yapecado, Dios yaurm yaaleot-jaa yadjeiconjeeya ishiyu-shŕt. Dioya jayerog shijuiyu naa bon ijei jadnnbat jajii-teat.
59005017	Naa profeta Elias, bondi oje naa birijani. Oyat Dios jama jijogjet wau-lrg shrt, oyatjri japoi rtyrg, wig poi, seis jatog jrbot poi, yau wau-drrliprn nam nita-jaa.
59005018	Oyat Dios jashrirm-shri, oyatjri wau-lrg shrnoat, oyatjri naa niti jadminyrrg-shri naa cajrmca.
59005019	Ajrrot, itrm yajrr úprtu jashrt naa moyerog rjetwin, oyatjri boi bijrrat jaúprtrgu birica shri.
59005020	Japishiyawaagjeeya, naa jaúprtrrm itrm ieb-minrr jajririi iebprnjin-teat, jadjeicon naa iebprnjin jarri-shrtya Dios shrt. Oyatya Dioat jashinam jashrt jaebyu ibagpeg jajrrat jaúprtrg-shrm.
60001001	Am Pedro, Jesucristoat icuiprn, janag naa papera nat idcaniipaiprnolat boyeja bishrt Ponto-teja, Galacia-teja poi, Asía-teja poi, Bitinia-teja poi.
60001002	Bií Dioat yaoucat yam oje jadjeulauniri idrgli bŕnju. Yadwawucat japinita yaligjee Espíritu-jet jayerog yawaorgjee, jaapi-rrijeeya yabigshayu yaiyashrg-shrm Jesucristo maa-jet. Jabijeu yadirglig yabigrririgjee wrijin ieb-shrt.
60001003	Ijei bibrg Dioat, naa Birri Jesucristo ii. Uubiidjeta bidjaluu ipegjet ooshrmda bijii jacambiarg jajujujet jajeibiteijeeya jabiruuglig ijei jajet jajuimig-shrm morriyu-shrt naa Jesucristo.
60001004	Jalibrgjeeya birat nat Dioat oodmog birat, naa brrt ishanquediri jadrmdrrglig, yau-poi jaapibaaliprn, yauya poi jashibeeiiprn bishrt naa ijei Dioat tjeiconbrg birat Paraíso-teja.
60001005	Dioat yajáijeu jabigshayu iwairüg-jet yajii yalirgshrm jajaa, jayatairirgjeeya naa jet-yadjeicon, naa jet-yadshitadrgya oopegwi wryulauya.
60001006	Ooshrmda yayaujáirg ipegjet. Boirica-shandit yan ebupaayacrtu mogwaini jashrm naa yajii-shŕrnrr nam wryu-tee.
60001007	Jadirg oro drr-tee jadduugjee bijaligu jalig. Ojera poi Dioat jalirglig ebupaayacrdig yaduugjee brjaligu yajii yalirglig jajaa. Jamii baligía wrijin oro-shrt jabigshaayu naa jajii-rirrm Dios-jaa daiimogjet ebupaajacrdbat. Oyat Dioya jainot-shipini ijeijet ijei cabigjee jan, jarnií jashibrgya jan jayugbatya Jesucristo.
60001008	Jayashanjuluut naa Jesucristo ooshrt jayii-yaluug. Jayashanjuluut ooshrt yajii yalircat jajaa, oyat yayaujáirg ipegjet. Yau jayaauedrliprn moyerog-jet yamoglig brjaiigu yajii-jáirig,
60001009	yadjeiconshrm ieb-shrt naa Jesucristoat yadrniogjee shrnoja.
60001010	Bmdi nat Dios yerog shipinit jaicapin jajaa naa ijei Dioat ishirirgya calat. Oyat jijogjeta jadjeu japishicawaagjee bigtanshrgjet jajaa naa jet-Dioat bijeicon ieb-shrt, ooshrmda caacarmyeg cajet brjaliyu jaligu naa Espíritu mo calat.
60001011	Bŕnju Cristo Espírituat jalirg japishicawaaglig ebupaajacrtshirigya naa jeicateiprn jayuglig. Oyat jadirg japishicawaaglig jajuishimigya morriyu-shrt jajugjet brtbrt-irigjet. Ooshrmda jadjeu japishicawaaglig brr-jaligu, jadjeu japishicawaaglig jayaa jayuglig.
60001012	Ooshrt Dioat jalirg japishicawaaglig ood-shrm catrm-shanwirit jadir idnaglig bŕn, ooshrt bishrm poi-oyem Espírituat jalirg japishicawaaglig jajaa naa moyerog idjuirg dumat jajet naa Espíritu Dioat icuiprn birat shrnoat. Bŕndi nat ángeleot jadpoijeu japishicawaagli jajaa naa moyerog jet-epinot ijeicon.
60001013	Ooshrmda yabigyaushag ijeijet jajaa naa Dioat ijeu jayaminrglig. Yabigyaushag ishalaligjet yabigshayu jujujet, wrijin yajii-teat jajeiyautei jayaluugjee naa ijei Dioat ishibrgya yan jayugbatya Jesucristo.
60001014	Iyauminrg oje trrijulot caíi yerog juiyutm, iyacupoirt oje epina yaliyu bŕwinjinat jalirlauni iyarglig japishiyawaag juprduli Dios-jaa.
60001015	Ijeira naa Dios yaája jalica, oolawi pecado shanminrri, ooshrmda yaulig ijeijet wrijin iebprnjin-shrt oje jalijani.
60001016	Ojera jamo naa idnagprndi bŕn papera-uu, alig wrijin ieb-shrt, ooshrmda yam-poi yaulig wrijin ieb-shrt apinita yafigjeeya.
60001017	Japishiyawaagu Yafija jaiiglig Dios, naa bijainot shipini jajaa naa ibiminrg, omya jayaulig íebyu-shrt • Yaíi-jaligu naa capecado eb-duju wrijin brr-jaligui, omya yashiom jarea oiirigwi yaligbat naa wryu-tee.
60001018	Japishiyawaagwi Cristoat yamii-brg yadshiujee jashrt naa boitep ídirgli yaminrglig bŕn nat yaloomolat. Yau yamii-jabrrliprn jajet naa irmdrg oje oroni, palatani poi.
60001019	Ooshrt yamii-jabrg jamaa mübag-jet naa Cristoat, naa idrrirgprn bishrm oje cordero ijeijet jaapi-mni.
60001020	Jajuprduju Dioat wryu minrglig, japishijawaagwi jadirg shirigya Cristo rririg yashim yam epinot. Oyat oowi boirauwi jabigtanjashrr naa idminrg yaya jaluugshrm.
60001021	Oyat Cristo-shrmda yajii-yalircat Dios-jaa, naa jawryrgprn morriyu-shrt. Jadirg ijei cabrgjee jan, oyat yam poi jayaquedrg yabigshayu yaiirglig Dios-jaa, jayaquedrg jajeiyateirig jayaluuglig.
60001022	Oyat yam, jayaquedrcat yabigshayu yajeicondig jayawaorgshrm naa moyerog ijetwin oje Espíritu Santoat jalirlauni. Ooshrmda cayii yauluug yajrrot qet yajii-teat. Yayii yauluuyeg ijeijet yabigshayu ijeijet jaapi-rrijet.
60001023	Jajujuolata yam jajet naa mojrmca-big ishanrmdrrí, yau jajet oo-naa ibeeg. Jajujuolata yam Dios yerog-jet, naa mojrmca-big ijug ishanbeji.
60001024	Qjera jamo naa idnagprndi papera-uu, ojera yeeni cataale lii nat epinot wrijin. Ojera yee-shuotni wrijin calapwoo miibag. Oyat jashiig naa yee, oyat calrg nat jashuuot,
60001025	ooshrtjii ishanbejira naa Bim yerog. Oola naa moyerog jet-epinot jajeiccwi ieb-shrt, naa jetyajuirg.
60002001	Ooshrmda jayaulirg yashrt wrijin ieb, wrijin moteishauyu, wrijin naa boitep. Caimacupoinai boi pinit, mayowan-cupoieb boyequejetep, yau ishrmjet.
60002002	Isniigjetawi jayaujeu naa moyerog ijetwi oie trriwai jujuat jaíin jiimigpog jeulauni, jarninjee yajii-tee naa yabigshayu-juju, yajeijeiya jashrt naa paacashicrtya capecado-shrm.
60002003	Japishiyawaagu ijeiya jaliglig naa Birri, yandawi jayashirir jabigshayu mindig yajiitee.

66001001	Oola naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprn Jesucristoat jadirgjee jajetwinolat japishiwaagjee jajaa naa ishiyugya mogwaini. Ooshrmda ángel jacui jajetwin Juan-dica jadtadrgjee bijaliguya jashirig naa wryu.

66001003	Jashijáiya naa jaieeje, naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn, oyat cashipoijáiya nat jajuiyut naa ileeg, nat jabat-taiat cajii-tee naa moyerog ooshrm janacatwiat jayaa naa oodjarnog papera-tee.
66001004	Am Juan, janag naa papera calat nat siete itogolat iglesia Asiatee. 66001005	Oyat jadpoi cui yan moyerog naa Jesucristoat, naa jaipini moyerog íjetwin, naa juimig jurgprndi morriyu-shrt. Oolawi Cajriwairüg nat iwairügot wrijin wryu-tee. Oolawi Cristo biyiiruju, naajashrcr bishrt biebyu jamaa-jet, biebyuat bishrijiip-shrt.
66001006	Oyat bijuijaberg jaepinota birigjee, jadirg iwairiigota biriglig, jadirg sacerdoteot biriglig ibibeebrgjee Jaíi Dioat. Ijei bibrg jan oiiriwiat naa Bijriwairüg iwairüg ishanbeji, Amén.
66001007	Jayashiruugia jayuglig naa Cristo waujribmi-teat. Jadshiruugya cabig-jet wrijin, oodyapoi nat jaibamatprnotdi payo-jet crusajaa. Oyatya wrijin nat wryu tepinot cashiqutgya jashrm naa ieb ídminrg jaduugbatya jawondig Cristo. Rcaji ojeya idshirr.
66001008	Arndawi naa juiwrm wrijin, amdapoi naa jashiberr wrijin, oje letra A, Z poi, ojera jamo Biŕri jaquedrr wrijin. Oolawi naa irig dumat, oolawi irigli brn, oolawi ishiyugya shri iwairürlig wrijinshrt.
66001009	Am Juan, yajrr ebupaacrtr yajet. Arndawi boi capei nat Dioat juibergprnot jaepinota caligjee oje yalijani. Oyat Jesucristo bigshayu-jet jajrica-acou naa paa-acrt oje yalijani. Bŕn presoja-adrg naa ipom-jaa jatarn Patmos jajuirg-shrm naa Dios yerog, jaiapinshrm poi Jesucristo-jaa.
66001010	Oyat boi wryu jayeibiwaaliprn-tee jajuimigliglig Biŕri, oyat naa Espíritu bigshayu yug ajaa jijogjet. Oyat boi ajui itrm moyerog atornat janoot shrg oje trompeta nootni.
66001011	Jamog, arnwi Alfa Omega poi, amwi naa Ebujuiwrmprn wrijin, Jashiberya wrijin poi. Jamaunag papera-uu naa imaluug, oyat jamaucui calat nat siete-itogot iglesiaolat Asia-tee, naa iglesia Efeso, Esmema poi, Pergamo poi, Tiatira, Sardis, Filadelfia, Laodisea poi.
66001012	Oyat ajewug jaluugjee brr-jaligu naa iyaad an, oyat cadaluug siete-itogot lamparaat liiriprnot oroconot.
66001013	Oyat cajewalee nat ebushiwr-yuot lüriprnot, boi aluug itrm oje jalijam naa Iyrgli wryu-jaluugjee. Jalig jajaa jayuiot ipat, oyat japag-uye boirig sintoron orocon.
66001014	Oyat jabrgla jajuu oje lana ibrgni, oje rt-prmi, oyat jabig brtbrt-jafig oje drmi.

66001017	Oyat jaluugbat Aŕri alrg jashiim cooye oje irriprnjini. Oyat jalap jawireatwín jalirg ajaa, jamog an, macupoiom, amdawi naa juiwrmprn wrijjin, amdapoi naa jaberr wrijin.
66001018	Amdawi naa Ijug, bŕn arriri, ooshrt dumat ajugwi oiiricawiat. Jaligwi an jet-jajuuyig moyrgjee morriyu-shrt, irriprnotjin diiriprn-shrt poi.
66001019	Dumat jamaunag papera-uu naa imaluucat, jajaa poi naa uruug nam wryu-tee dumat, oyat poi maunag bijáliguya jashirii naa wryu.
66001020	Oyat nat jaa-japishimashanwaji, nat siete crrlot idmahiugot alap wireatwin-uu, otpoi nat siete ebushiwryuot liiriprnot oroconot. Oojaliyula nat siete crrlot otdawi nat siete iglesia ijewet, oyat nat siete ebushiwryu liiriprnot oola naa siete iglesia.
66002001	Jamaunag papera naa iglesia iijeweat Efeso-tee, ojera jamo naa siete crrlot waowa jalap-uu jawireat, naa iboolrg cajewalee nat siete ebushirwryuot liiriprnot oroconot.
66002002	Japishiawaagwi naa iyaminrg, japishiawaagwi iyabeebdig Dioat ipegjet, ishan-nrmijeta jajricayacou naa paayacrt. 66002003	Japishiawaagwi ishan-nrmijeta jajricayacou naa paayacrt, ibagjeta íyabeebr an ayii yaluugshrm, yau yajaapdiprn yabeebdig an.
66002004	Ooshrt jatrrnda ieb iruug yajaa, yau ayii yaluuliprn ipegjet oje ayii yaluulauniri yajii yalirg jurgbatdi.

66002006	Ooshrt ijeijet yaluug ooshrm jaeb yaluug-shrm naa idminrg nat nicolaitaolat, ampoi oyem jaeb aluug-poi naa idminrg.
66002007	Durnat naajri ood-jabutoglig, jandawi jadshijui brjaligu Espíritu mog nat iglesia tepinolat. Nat moweijin namat cashrt, jashirirgya jadwouglig naa puncam jalirr mojuuyu, naa pun ishog Dios yan Paraíso-tee.
66002008	Oyat irnaunag jan naa iglesia ijeweat Esmirna-tee, ojera jamo naa ebujuiwrm wrijin, oopoi naa jaberr wrijin, oolawi naa írriprndi, oyat jashrijugwi.
66002009	Japishiawaagwi wrijin naa iyaminrg. Japishiawaagwi brjaligu ebupaayacrdig. Japishiawaag poi uubiidota yaliglig, ooshrt jálibrgwi yan naa mii nomjri-bajalig wrijin molapwoo-shrt. 66002010	Yacupoiom jarea naa paayashicrtya. Moweijinat cashinamya itnnnogot yapet presoja moliiriprn-teja jayanamnogjee-cugjin naa moyerog iyawaorg. Oyatya ebupaayashicrt dies wryu, ooshrt yaulig dai-imogjet ata-on yarriya, oyat yashirírgya yajuglig oiiricawiat.
66002011	Naajri ood-jabutoglig, jandawi jadshijui brjaligu Espíritu mog calat nat iglesia tepinolat. Nat moweijin namat cashrt, yauya ebupaacashierdiprn jatee naa morririprn iicau-jet.
66002012	Oyat irnaunag jan naa iglesia ijeweat Pergamo-tee, ojera jar o naa ood-jalig jawiuyu deeshrg icaulejani.
66002013	Japishiawaagwi wrijin iyaminrg. Japishiawaagwi yaliglig cajewatee nat moweijinat icuiprnot, ooshrt jajeiwi yaliglig atamjaa. 66002014	Ooshrt yainot shiashipin ooshrm omda brrdii Pergamo-tee nat jashanjewit jadnamnoglig naa Balaamat ijuirgli bŕn. Naa Balacat icuiprn jadirgjee cadca-wouglig naa idcarrirgprnot idoloolat nat israelolat. Oyat jadpoirirg ieb caminrgjee cataale-jet.
66002015	Oyat itrmnogot yajewalee yau jadjeuliprn jadnamnoglig naa nicolaitaolat ijuirgprn, naajri eb aluug.i
66002016	Ooshrmda yabigshayu yaucambiarg. Yau jaligu yaju shŕmdiprn jajaa naa ieb idminrg, ashiyugya yalica mogwaini-jet moprtooyu aminrgjee caubata jajet naa moyerog iyrg acooleat oje wiuyu deeshigni.
66002017	Naajri ood-jabutoglig, jandawi jadshijui bijaligu Espíritu mog calat nat iglesia tepinolat. Naa moweijin-narna jashrt jashirirgya jadwouglig naa An ijajaanprndi brrt-shrt. 66002018	Oyat irnaunag poi jan naa iglesia ijeweat Tiatíra-tee. Ojera jamo naa Dios Wá, naa biglig oje drrrn, oyat jashiirn dig oje bronse ibrrtni drr-tee.
66002019	Japishiawaagwi wrijin iyaminrg. Japishiawaagwi ayii yaluuglig, yajrrot poi. 66002020	Ooshrt jatrmda iruug yajaa ieb, jayalirg-shrmju jaliglig yajewalee naa den Jezabel naa amawai Dios bigshayu-jet imog. Ooshrt cateejashaurg apinit jajet naa idjuirg ieb caminrgjee cataale-jet, oyat cadcapoi-woug nat idcarrirgprnot idoloolat.
66002021	Jajeiateiat prnpatjet jabígshayu jacambiargjee jashrt naa ieb idminrg, ooshrt yau jadjeuliprn jadnamnoglig naa boyequejetep idrryu jataale-jet.
66002022	Ooshrmda durnat jashirirg ishiyuat jawaorglig ebupaajacrtjee jijogjet jayegshogot-tee. Ot-poi nat ieb-minrt jajet cadashipoirirg ebupaacacrtjee jijogjet yau-jaligu caquediprn jashrt naa ieb idirg jadminrglig.
66002023	Jashirirgya carririg jatrriot naa mawaira moweijin bigshayujet japishicawaagjeeya wrijin nat iglesia tepinolat, am-jaligwi naa cabigshayu pishiwaja wrijin. Japishiapoiwaagwi boirigshrm jaligu jadrninr wrijin naa idminrg, oyat jamu jashibrgya calat catojani naa idminrg.

66002026	Oyat nat moweijin nanat cashrt, nat irninrt oje ajeulauni ata-on carriya, boi wryulauya jashirir caicajeulig nat epinot wryu tepinot.

66003001	Oyat imaunag poi jan naa iglesia ijeweat Sardis-tee, ojera jamo naa oodcalig siete mojiiot ijeinogot, siete errlot poi. Japishiawaagwi wrijin naa iyaminrg, ijugota bidu Espíritu-jet yarnog yajaa, ooshrt yapishiawaagwi irriprnotjinda yam.
66003002	Yayaujeunorg, jayawairürg naa ishŕmwi iribrg yan Dios bigshayu, naa irri-shucatwi yashrt. Jaluugwi naa iyaminrg, jashanjeira Dioat jaluuglig.
66003003	Ooshrmaa jayeyawaag naa moyerog jet-yajuirgh, naa iyawaorg, iyajuiri poi. Dumat jabatyautai yajii-tee, yabigsnayu jacambiargjee, jayeyawaag jii-shrmjet yaebyu. Yashanjeunotu yapecadoshrtjri, ashiyugya yalica oje isheg yuulauni. Yauya japishiyawaaliprn boirig orabat jaligu ashiyuu.

66003008	Japishiawaagwi wrijin naa iyaminrg. Omda nam jayiibrrat yan itrm moyei brrt ishanquedrri juipaaglig yashrt. Japishiawaagwi yau jawairürliprn abigshayu yajii-tee, ooshrt ayerog yawaorcat. Yau ainot shiyajaandiprn Yarriya sdiglig.

66003010	Japishiawaagwi ishan-nrmijeta yajricayacouyeg yajet oje amojani, ooshrmya yashijeicon jashrt naa ieb ishiyugya calica wrijin nat wryu-tepinot. Jajet naa paacashicrtya japishibishiwaagya brjaligu cabigshayu lig wrijin, o Dios yerog waort-jaligu, o mjaligu.
66003011	Mogwainiya ashiyuu ooshrmda jayaujeiwao yajii-tee naa ijei iribrg yan, brr-shanditjeeya jaoum yashrt naa ishibrgya yan.

66003016	Oowi yateprrcairi yaijet. Yau yabata ayarrliprn, yau poi ayii yaluuliprn, oowi yabigmtepdiglig ashrt, ooshrmya yashipag acooleat.
66003017	Yam wooligota bidu imogot, jabacata bilapwoo, boirigshandit boiruud birica imogot.
66003018	Ooshrmda yapinrg, jayau-rm ashrt yabigshayu oje oroni irig idjeiconprn drr-tee jaíibrgjeeya yan naa ijei rjetwin mii-ishanbri. 66004001	Oyat irnug shrnoja, jaluug itnn moyee juiyiinoglig shrnoja. Oyat naa iyaad an, naa noot ajui oje trompeta noot ijuirauni, jamog an, maujon alica mashitadrg jajet naa íshiyugya calica nat wryu tepinot. •
66004002	Oyat oobat-brwiat jayuu jijogjet alica naa Espíritu bigshayu. Oyat jaluug itrm iwairüg tegot ijei shrnoja, jaluug boi teglig jajaa naa iwairüg tegot ishrn.
66004003	Oyat naa iteg jategot ishrn-jaa brtbrtjajalig oje dapyui-big jaspeconi irig cornalinani poi. Oyat jaluug jategot jushrye itnn yaameat iyrg iacjet oje dapyui-big esrneraldom.
66004004	Oyat Dios tegot mauu cadaluug vente-cuatro tegolat, oyat cadaluug vente-cuatro ansianoot itegot cajaa, jabrrnogla cayuiot, cajuiyag-jaa corona orocon catojani.
66004005	Oyat iwaalrg Dios tegot-teat, colocolo ipoi mog jategot-teat jaba? moyerog noot poi. Oyat Dios tegot júprta cadaluug siete ebusniwryuot ibrrlot, oodwi Dios espírituot siete itogot.
66004006	Oyat Dios tegot júprta poi jatrm rt teijeuluug oje uyemteeni. Oyat jategot itrmbalat itrmbalat poi, cadaluug icaunogot ijugot cataale juituun cabigjet iduugjee cajúprta caprna poi.
66004007	Jatrm iruug ijug oje leoni, oyat jatrm ijug oje bueyni, oyat itrm ijug oje bon úni, oyat itrm ijug oje aguilani jajounbat.
66004008	Oyat nat icaunogot ijugot, seis catog cajóuot catojani, oyat cataale juituun cabig-jet wrijin cajouot-jaa poi, cajouot nomat poi. 66004009	Oyat nat ijugot uei cabrg jan naa itecat jategot ishrn-jaa, naa Ijug ouricawiat.
66004010	Oyat categ cautjuiyag jan nat venti-cuatro ansianoot, ijei cabrg jan naa Ijucat ouricawiat. Oyat cacoronaat caliirg jategot júprta.
66004011	Camog jan, mam Birri, mam bijri Dios ijeira mam, ooshrmda ijei bibrg man. Biom menea ooshrm mamwi naa Bicuiyu, mamdawi naa Iminrr wrijin boirig jaligu imajeu jarnaminrglig, oyat caligju ijeijet mabígshayu-jet wrijin.
66005001	Oyat jaluug itrm papera jalapu jawireat naa iteg jategot ishrnjaa. Ojera rolloni jalii naa papera idnagprn itrmbalat japoi-nag itrmbalat, jaicajiiprn siete sello-jet;.
66005002	Oyat jaluug itrm ángele iwairüg, oyat jijogjet jadrm, brr-jam naa ijei jaquedrr jajuijayigfig naa papera. Brr-jam jaquedrr jadshiulig birat jashrt naa-jet jaicajiiprn.
66005003	Oyat brr-shandit jaquedrr jadshiulig naa papera, brr-shandit jaquedrr shrnojawin, brr-shanpoiriit nam wryu-teewin Brr-shandit poi jaquedrr jadduuglig naa idnagprn papera-uu.
66005004	Oyat aquig jpegjet boi cashantairirt-shrm itrmu jashiwija birat naa papera, brr-shanpoirit jaquedrr jadduuglig idnagprn.
66005005	Oyat itrm capei nat ansianoot jamog an, macupoiquüt, omda jalii León iwairüg judioot pei, naa David jriwai, jadquedrcat moweijin janamdig jadshiujee birat naa papera siete jaijiipyu-shrt.
66005006	Oyat Dios tegot mauu, cajewalee nat cuatro ijugot ansianoot poi, jaluug itrm Cordero ishog, jajaa-prndig oje irrirgprniri Dioat, siete catog jajusheuot, siete poi jabigot, oodawi nat siete Dios espírituot idjacuiprnot wrijin wryu-teja.
66005007	Oyat naa Cordero janog jadougjee naa papera jalap jawireatwin-shrt naa Iteg jategot ishrnjaa.
66005008	Oyat naa Cordero jadduugbat naa papera, cashog jan cautjuiyag-jet nat cuatro ijugot, otpoi nat venti-cuatro ansianoot. Oyat nat ansianot arpaat cawao catojani jet-itocargota, cadcapoiwao tasaat oroconot juituunogot insenso-jet. Naa rt-shicoi idtai Dioat, oola carnación nat Dios epinot.
66005009	Oyat jadcantarg itrm canción juju, camog, ijeira mam Birri, ooshrmda jamaquedrg jamawaurglig naa papera jajuimayigjee jajuijiipyu-shrt, ooshrm bŕn madrrirgli bimii mabrgjee mamaa-jet wrijin epinot peet wryu-teja biumaprtrgjee Dioat.
66005010	Oyat jamalirg bijuijaberg jaepinota birigjee naa Bijriwairücat Dios. Jamalircat jasacerdoteota bidu cadbijeiconjee jajet nat epinot. Oyat bidmashirirgya cajriwairügota birigjee caibjjeujee nat wryu tepinot.
66005011	Oyat jashriniug, oyat cayerog ajui nat ángeleot ibagot ishogot Dios tegot ishrn-mauu, nat ijugot poi, ansianoot poi, ibag millones catog.
66005012	Camog jijogjet, ijeira naa Cordero idrrirgprn, ooshrmda Cajriwairüca jalig wrijin, japinita calig wrijin. Bicacoua jalig iwairüg wrijin-shrt ooshrmda biom jarea, ijei bibrg jan jabijeu jabijáirglig.
66005013	Oyat cayerog ajui wrijin nat Dioat iminrgprnot shrnoja, naa wryu-tee poi, naa poi niti noma, rt-tee poi. Jaicapin jijogjet wrijin jayaulirg ijei cabrgjee jan wrijin, jayaulirg caomjee jarea, jayaulirg Cajriwairüca jaliglig oiiricawiat naa Iteg jategot ishrn-jaa, oopoi naa Cordero.

66006001	Oyat jaluug naa Cordero jadshiulig primero sello papera ijiipyu. Oyat jayerog ajui capei nat cuatro ijugot oje jaijuirauni colocólo imoyu, jamog an, jamauluuyucat.

66006011	Oyat Dioat jalir calat catojani cayuiot ibrg. Oyat cadjapinrg jijacaligjeeju yaijetwi ata-on cadcarrirca poi cajrrot ibeebet Cristoat bijaligu catog idjajeuot.
66006012	Oyat naa Cordero jadshiubat naa Sexto sello, jaluug jayai jijogjet naa niti. Oyat naa yamat oje yuiot ipigni, oyat jacrt naa jrrbot jabigpücat oje momaani.

66006015	Oyat wrijin nat iwairügot wryu-tee caacajaan wentejrg-teja, jaa-jewalee poi. Nat poi wrijin iinodigot, wooligot poi, comandanteat poi, wrijin presoot poi, presoja ishandiot poi.

66007001	Oyat cadaluug icaunogot ángeleot cashog icaunog wryu juituunot-jaa, jadwao icaunog jiim idshanprtjee wryu-teja, rri-poi rt-jaa, rri-poi puulot-jaa.
66007002	Oyat jashriruug itrm ángele jajoun yamat yrcat, jadrrnog jasello naa Dios ijug. Oyat jaágjijogjet nat cuatro ángeleot ood-jalibrgolat moyerog jad-ebrgjee wrijin naa niti, rt poi.

66007013	Oyat itrm capei nat ansianoot, jadrm ashrt, jarnog, boirigotjam nat yuiot-brrnogot, bolatwinotjam.

66007015	Cristoat ishrgprnota calig ooshrmda jadquedrg cashoglig Dios tegot mauu, jajrrja jadrg wrglei shairei poi jatemplo-tee naa iteg jategot ishrn-jaa. Oyat cadjashijeiconya jaot-tee.
66007016	Yauya cabuishishiiriprn, yauya poi cajii shijrroliprn, yauya yamalat cataa shitairiprn, yauya poi ebupaacashicrdiprn icai-jet.
66007017	Naa Cordero iteg jategot rtuye ishrn-jaa, caijashijeuya, cadjashirmogya jatairirgjeeya naa Rt ijug. Oyat Dioya cabigpog shimryr cabig-shrt wrijin.
66008001	Oyat naa Cordero jadshiubat naa séptimo sello, on-cairig wrijin Dios yan-tee ora jamaye.

66008006	Oyat nat siete ángeleot cawaoat nat siete trompetaot, caacajeiwao cadcaprgjee.

66008011	Naajri crt jatam Ajenjo, ooshrm tercer parte rt ipeenogot rtmaiot poi cadjacambiart cawanjee. Oyat carri ibagjet epinot jadwógbat naa rt jaeb-shrm oje dootni.

66008013	Oyat jaluug iten ángel jatrg shrnoja wryu-úja. Oyat jajui jawrr-aglig jijogjet, jamog, jashiebya jashiebya ishiyuya calica nat irigot wryu-tee catrompetaot capngbatya nat ipoiot ángeleot biprnotwinot.
66009001	Oyat naa quinto ángele trompeta japrrg. Oyat jaluug itrrn crt drglig shrnoat niti-uja. Oyat jadirbrg jan jet-jajuijayig naa imonyee.
66009002	Oyat jajuijayig naa irnon-yee, oyat ai yrg irnon-teat oje et-ai yrrlauni jijogjet. Oyat naa infierno ai jaijawei yamat, jadpoirirg jabrrulig wrijin naa wryu.
66009003	Oyat cayrg ai-teat nat cruot catrg wrijin wryu-teja, carglig oje shrcat moshrrlauni.

66009006	Oyat jadshijeuya-cug carririg nat wryu tepinot ebupaacacrd-shrm jijogjet, ooshrt yauya jadshiquedrliprn carririg, naa morriyu jashicuutya cashrt.
66009007	Nat cruot cashrrjrt, ojera jalii cataale oje caballo taaleni idcajeiconotni moprtooyu yawana iicaweiprnot jrrconot-jet cabalot-shrt. Oyat cajuiyag-jaa jalig cajuiwoop oroconi irig, oyat caú-lig oje bon úni.
66009008	Oyat cajuu-lig oje den juuni, oyat caleeot-dig oje yoodan deeotni.

66009011	Oyat nat cashrrjrt jriwairüg oola naa mojii iebprnjin monoatwin jatarn Abadón hebreo yerog-jet. Oyat jatamdig Apolión griego yerog-jet Ojaliyula jatam Carmdrrm epinot.
66009012	Oyat jawug naa ieb iyug-jurg, oyat cajuprtuju icauot shri iebot.
66009013	Oyat naa sexto ángele jatrompeta japrrg. Oyat itrrn moyerog ajui iyugprn cajewaleat nat icatmog juseuot altar yawanot naa altar orocon ishog Dios tegot uubatye.
66009014	---Jamog jan naa sexto ángeleat jawaowa trompeta, cadmaushiu nat cuatro ángeleot ideajiiprnot jamauwa naa rt-ipeg jatam Eufrates.

66009016	Oyat jajui brjaligu catog nat Iprtoogot caballoot jaapinot, dosciento millones catog.
66009017	Oyat cadaluug oje moyrrcani nat caballoot, ot-poi caballootjapinot. Cacrt oje drr-brtni nat jrrconot jet-jaicaweiot cataale, íbrrtni oje jacinto iagni, azulfre ijuutni poi. Oyat nat caballoot juiyag jalig oje yoodan juiyagni. Oyat drr yrg cacooleat, drr-ai poi, azulfre poi.

66009020	Oyat nat epinot ishanrriyit naa ieb ishiyug-jet, yau cajú shŕmdiprn caebyu iyecawaaglig, yau cabigshayu cacambiariiprn Dios-jaa jashrt naa ieb idminrg. 66009021	Oyat yau cabishayu cacambiariiprn, yau cajii shŕmdiprn epinot carrirg-shrm, yau poi mojigyu canamnohprn, yau poi cajii shrmdiprn jashrm naa ieb idminrg cataale-jet, wrijin jashrm poi naa ídshegprn brrt-shrt,
66010001	Oyat jaluug itnn ángele iwairüg jawon shrnoat, waojribmiat jaipug. Oyat itrm yamiat iyrg jajuiyag jushrye, oyat jaúat iyrg oje yamalat iyrrlauni, oyat japeep brrt oje drrni.
66010002	Oyat jadwao itnn libro-trri idyigprn jalap jawiieatwin-jet. Oyat jashum jawiieatwin-jet jatag rt-ipeg úye, oyat jashaatwinjet nití jatag.
66010003	Oyat naa ángele jawrr-ág, jaag jijogjet oje yoodan aalauni. Jawrr-ágbat naa ángele, cayaad nat siete colocolo-iraoyu jabijuijee cayerog catojani.
66010004	Oyat cayáad-quedyem nat siete colocolo-irnoyu, jajeu jajrianaglig papera-uu, ooshrt itrm mog an shrnoat, jaimaujaan brrt-shrt naa oodcamog nat siete colocolo-imoyuot, jajrímacupoinat paperauu.
66010005	Oyat naa ángele iruug ishog rt ipeg-jaa niti-jaa poi, jalap jawireatwin jawrryrg shrnoja.
66010006	Jaijapin moyerog jijog jatam-jaa naa Ijug oiirícawiat, naa Iminrr wrijin shrnoja, wryu-teja poi, rt-teja poi. Jamog, dumatjri cayaa wucat caacajeiconjee Dios-jet.
66010007	Jayaa-minogbatya naa séptimo ángel, jadshiprgya trompeta, oyat Dioat jashiminrgya oo-naa ijajaanprndi cashrt, naa oodjamogli jajetwinolat, nat jayerog naaladi papera-uu jajaa naa jeicateiri jayuglig.
66010008	Oyat naa moyerog ijui shrnoatwin, jashriyaadbrg an, shog maunog, jamaowao naa hbro-trri idyüwaoprn jalap-uu naa ángele ishog rt ipeg-jaa niti-jaa poi.
66010009	Oyat anog jalica naa ángele, japinrg jadbrgjee an naa libro-trri. Oyat jamog an, jamauwaorg jamauwoug. Jashüshigya macoolee oje ampogotni, ooshrt jashiwanya manamdee.
66010010	Oyat jawaorg naa libro-trri jalap-uat naa ángele, oyat jawoug, oyat jashiig acoolee oje am-pogotni, ooshrt jawoug quedyem jawan anamdee.
66010011	Oyat jamog an, dumat maucuprt jaimaupin calat Dios yerog nat epinot ibagolat ibag niti jaapinot poi, nat poi iyaalot brrt yerog-jet, nat poi cajriwairügolat.
66011001	Oyat boi cabrg an shuiroog jet-jayaca oje pun-shutni irig, oyat jarnog an, majuicumig jamayaajet Dios templo, naa poi aliar. Oyat cadrnaucag brjaligu catog nat ijeibrt Dioat jatemplotee.
66011002	Ooshrt jamacupoiyat Dios ot jewalee ooshrm Dioat jalirbig nat brrt epinolat cashirigya jatagjee naa moyan ijei cuarenta-dos jrbot.
66011003	Cadashiwairürgya nat icauot jaipinit rjet ajaa. Jaicashipinya naa irirg jaicapindig mil dosciento-setenta wryu cayuiot saco ipig jriat.
66011004	Nat icauot jaipinit rjet Dios-jaa, ooda nat icauot puulot Olivos, ooda nat icauot ebushiwryu liiriprnot ishogot jamauu naa wryu Rrí.
66011005	Oyat itrmat iebminrgbat calat nat Dios yerog shipinirat, oowi drr yrglig cacooleat cadcataijee nat cabalot. Ojera carririi nat jajewerat ieb caminrglig calat.
66011006	Oyat cabigshayu-jet cajuicapaag waujribrru, wau shandrtjee niti uja ataron jaicapina Dios-jaa wrijin idjeu jaicapindig. Dios bigshayu-jet jadearnbiarg rt momaa-jet, jadebrg naa wryu tepinot, jadirg ebupaacacrdig brjaligu jatog jrbot jadjeuüg.
66011007	Oyat jadquedrg quedyem naa mobeeb Dioat irirg calat, jashiyrgya monoat naa iebprnjin pini irig. Moprtooyu jashiminrgya caubata nat Dios yerog shipinit, oyat cadjashinarnya, oyat cadjashirrirgy a.
66011008	Oyat cabalolat jashirirgya cataalejin yegshoglig cayan-waduu, oolawi naa moyan shuwai Sodomani irig, Egiptoni irig poi, oola naa moyan jadwrndeiprnuli Biŕri cruza-jaa.
66011009	Oyat ipoi wryu jamayei poi, cataaleotjin caluug cayegshoglig cayan waduu. Cadcashiruugya wrijin nat wryu tepinolat iyaalolat wrijin moyerog-jet, wrijin tribuot, nitiot poi. Oyat caiwin cashishogya cadcabrglig cataalejin wadyeg-teja.
66011010	Oyat nat wiyu tepinot cajii-shijáiya cadcaluugbat carririg. Oyat cacashijáirg wrijin wooja cadcashanshrirt-shrm, regalo cabrryeg cajrrolat carri-shrm nat icauot Dios yerog shipinit cadcalirg-shrmtü ebupaacacrdig.
66011011	Oyat ipoi wryu jajamaye boi prnat, Dioat cajuurg shri nat icauot jaipinitprnot. Oyat nat calujut caom ipegjet.
66011012	Oyat nat icauot jadjui itrm moyerog noot-shrg shrnoat, jarnog calat, yauyucat nani shrnoja. Oyat cajoun shrnoja waujribrru-tee, cabalolat iruugjet wrijin.
66011013	Oyat oobat brwiat jashiyai jijogjet naa niti wrijin, oyat jalrg decima parte naa moyan. Oyat carri siete mil epinot jayai-shrm niti. Oyat nat brrt epinot caom ipegjet, oyat ijei cabrg Dioat, naa shrnoja iricat.
66011014	Oyat jawucat naa jaicauyu ebupaacacrdig, oyat jayug mogwainí-jet naa jaipoiyu ebupaacacrdig.
66011015	Oyat naa Séptima ángele jatrompeta japrg. Oyat jajui itrm moyerog jijog shrnoatwin, jamog, durnatya wrijin nat iwairügot epinot nam wryu-tee, jaeprnota caligcat naa bijri Dios, oopoi Cristo. Oyat Cajriwairüca jashirigya oiiricawiat.
66011016	Oyat nat venti-cuatro ansianoot itegot categot-jaa Dios tegot coo, categ cautjuiyag-jet jan, ca-ú shicawei, ijei cabrgjee Dioat.

66021015	Oyat naa ángele iyaad ajet jadwao itnn jet-idyag orocon jadyagjee naa moyan, moluughprnot pói, jawai jaacon pói.
66021016	Oyat itnnjanibr jashoonog japoibat-jet wrijin. Oyat ángeleat jayag naa moyan, oola japaadyu dos-mil dosciento kilómetro jalig jaushipeiyu poi. Itnnjanibr japaadyu japoibat poi, jashrnyu pói.
66021017	Oyat naa ángele jadpoi-yag naa wai jaacon, sesenta-cuatro metros jashrnyu, ojerawi jayagli naa ángeleat jajet naa moolat iyag.
66021018	Jaacon jaspe icrtcon naa wai, oyat orocon-catrmda naa moyan, teeijeuluugla naa oro moyan-yawan.
66021019	Oyat nat moyan liiriprnot caacajeicon wrijin jaaot ibrrtnogot oje dapyui bigni. Naa pnmero moliiriprn jaacon icrt jatam jaspe, oyat naa segunda moluriprn jaacon iag jatam zafiro. Oyat tercera jaa jatamdig ágata, oyat naa cuarto esmeraldacon.
66021020	Oyat naa quinto moliiriprn jaa ijuutcon jatam onice, oyat naa sexto comalinacon, naa séptimo crisólitocon, naa octavo berilocon, naa novena topasiocon, naa décimo crisoprasacon, naa undécimo jacintocon, naa duodécimo amatistacon.
66021021	Oyat doce perlaot brtbrt-irigot, nat jebcajuicapagot moluugliprn doce itogot. Oowi itrm perla ipeg jet-cajuijapagot wai-yee tojani. Oyat naa calle ipeg iwug moyan tejamaye, orocon teijeuluug naa calle.
66021022	Boi ashanduut itrm templo jatee naa moyan, ooshrm oolawi catemplo on naa Biŕri Dios iwairüg wrijin-shrt, oolawi naa Cordero.
66021023	Oyat naa moyan, jadshanjeu yamalat iyrglig jajaa, rrípoi jrrbot, ooshrm idshiyrgya ijeijet jajan naa Dios brtbrt-irig, oopoi naa Cordero.
66021024	Oyat nat epinot Dioat ijeiconprnot cashibogya jaiwryutee naa moyan. Oyat nat iwairügot wryu-tepinot jadshirryugya jan ijei jet-jadtadrca oojaligwi Cajriwairüg naa Jerusalén juju Rri.
66021025	Yauya cajuishipaaliprn nat wai-yeot wrglei, boiruud shai on.
66021026	Nat wryu tepinot jadshirmogya regaloot ijeinogot on, ijei cabrgjee jan naa moyan Rriat.
66021027	Brr-shanditya ishiruug jajan jajuju Jerusalén-teja jabigshayu jaapibagprnjin jriat,yauya poi teeshauprnotjin. Ooshrt cashiruugya jajan nat tam-digot Cordero libro-tee cajet nat ood-jaliibrgot wryu ishanbeji.
66022001	Oyat naa ángele atadrg itrm rt ipegjet ijei jalirr mowairüyu ishanbeji. Brtbrt-jalig naa rt, teeijeuluug oje vidrioni. Jaminyrg Dios tegot nomat jategot namat poi naa Cordero.
66022002	Oyat naa moyan jamayee cadiruug nat puulot itrmbalat itrmbalat poi naa rt-ipeg calirt mowairüyu ishanbeji, cacamdig jrbot shitojani, doce-jaitog cacamdig año shitojani. Oyat nat pun yonot epinot Cajeicon ishiyu-shrt.
66022003	Boiraud iiruug on Dioat eb-duug, ooshrt jashirigya on jaliiriprn naa Dios, naa Cordero poi, oyat ijei cabrg jan nat jajetwinolat.
66022004	Ja-ú cashimugya naa cajri Dios, oyat jatarn shijogya caú pomye.
66022005	Yauya ishicupdiprn on, ooshrmda jadshanjewi ebushiwryu on, yauya poi naa moyanat jashijeuliprn yamat, ooshrmya Birri Dioat ishiwrrgya cajas nat jajetwinot oyat caicajeujee jaepinot oiiricawiat.
66022006	Oyat naa ángele jamog an, rjeta naa moyerog oodamog man, jaiquedrg mobigshayu irirgu jajaa. Oo naa Birri oolawi naa Dios jalirr calat naa moyerog oodcamogjatam-jaa. Oolawi Dios jaángele cuiyu cadjatadrgjee jajetwinot jajet naa ishiyugya mogwaini.
66022007	Jamog, ishaibatya ashiyuu. Cashijáiya nat jawaort cajii-teat tjet naa moyerog Dioat ibrgprn Juanat jadnagjee papera-uu.
66022008	Am Juan, oola am jajuiyuprn jalujuprn poi wrijin naa jaa-inag papera-uu. Oyat ángele yerog ajui quedyem, jaluug-quedyem poi naa jet-jatadrg, ateg autjuiyag-jet jashiim cooye naa ángele, ijei abrgjee jan.
66022009	Ooshrt jamog an, oje macupoirt ooshrm arnda poi Dios jetwin oje malijani, calijani poi nat majrrot jaipinit moyerog Dioat ibrgprn calat. Arnda poi calijani irig nat jawaort naa idnagprn jatee naa papera. Oowi ijei maubrg Dioat.
66022010	Oyat jashrimog an naa ángele, jaimacupoijaan epinot-shrt naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn man, naa imanagprn papera-uu ooshrm janacatwiat jayaa.
66022011	Oyat nat iebnogprnotjin cashirigya caebyu-jaa oiiricawiat. Oyat nat bigshayu jaapi-bagot cashirigya jaapibag-jaa oiiricawiat. Oyat nat ijeinogot cashirigya ijeijet oiiricawiat, oyat nat bigshayu jaapi-rríot cashirigya jaapi-rrijet oiiricawiat.
66022012	Rcaji, mogwainiya ashiyug, oyat jashirryugya ajet jamii naa idminrg catojani.
66022013	Amdawi naa Ebujuiwnnprn, amdawi poi naa Ebujuiberr.
66022014	Cashijáiya nat cabigshayu shrgcrt, jadougjeeya jacam naa Pun jalirr wryu ishanbeji, nat iruugot Dios yan moluugliprn-teye.
66022015	Oyat nat Dios shanjewit, nat yootni itepdigot, cashirigya boyeja yaujet Dios yan-shrt, otpoi nat mojigyu-minrt, iwoojeuot poi, epin-rrirt poi, cairmrt idoloot-shrt poi, moteeshauyu juiyut wrijin teeshauot poi.
66022016	Am Jesús, aángele acuiat jaijapinjee naa moyerog nat iglesia atwinolat. Amdawi naa jalirrprndi cajriwairüca naa David, arnda poi jajriwai. Amdawi naa Crt shuwai iyrg ibrrubatju.
66022017	Oyat naa Espíritu Santo jamog, yauyucat jalica. Oyat nat iglesia tepinot camog, yauyucat jalica. Oyat nat jayerog juiyut calatwi cashirnog, yauyucat jalica, Oyat cadyaulirg cayuglig wrijin nat bigshayu jroot, w.rijin poi jajewet cayuglig. Jayaulirg cayuglig jadwogjee mii-rrijet naa Rt Ijug.
66022018	Oyat wrijin nat jajuiyut naa moyerog Dioat irirgprn jadnaglig jatee naa papera, cadapinrg, briat ishri-nagu jajaa naa idnacadi Biblia-tee, Dioya jashirirr jajaa naa ieb jaa-inag jatee naa papera.
66022019	Oyat briat canamu itrmnogot versiculoot jateat naa Biblia jadshanwaortjee naa Dioat irirgprn birat, Dioya jatam jrishimryr jalibro-teat cashrt nat ood-jalibrgot wryu ishanbeji, jaiwin-jashipoishogya cashrt jayán ijei shrnoja, jaa-jamog naa papera-tee.
66022020	Ojera jamo naa Jaipini naa moyerog . . . Rcaji mogwainiya ashiyuu . . . Amén, mauyucat mogwaini, mam Birri Jesús.
66022021	Jabijeu Birri Jesucristoat yajii jáirglig wrijin, Amén.
